(18, '', 'Is Temu Safe? Concerns Over Spying on Western Customers&#039; Text Messages', 'Is Temu Safe? Temu App Accused of Spying on Western Customers&#039; Text Messages', 'IT and Software', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The popular shopping app Temu has been accused of spying on Western customers\' text messages by a US state, with Arkansas prosecutors suing the company for allegedly functioning as \"malware and spyware\" that can access contacts and text messages. The company, owned by Chinese firm PDD Holdings, has denied the allegations, claiming that they are based on misinformation circulated online.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">According to the lawsuit, Temu\'s app is designed to gain unrestricted access to users\' phone operating systems and override data privacy settings. This allows the company to collect and monetize users\' personal data without their consent. Is Temu safe? The answer is unclear, as the company\'s practices have raised serious concerns about user privacy.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The suit also claims that Temu is led by former Chinese Communist Party officials, which raises concerns about national security risks. Is Temu safe? With allegations of malware and spyware, it\'s clear that users should exercise caution when using the app.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Temu\'s popularity has been fueled by its offer of free delivery and cut-price goods shipped directly from China. However, the company has faced scrutiny over whether forced labor is used in its supply chains. The US Congress has already raised concerns about Temu and its rival Shein, which is planning a London Stock Exchange listing.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The lawsuit filed by Arkansas\'s Attorney General Tim Griffin alleges that Temu is not an online marketplace like Amazon or Walmart, but rather a data-theft business that uses its ecommerce platform as a means to an end. Griffin stated that Temu is \"functionally malware and spyware\" and that it is purposefully designed to access users\' phones without their knowledge or consent.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Despite the allegations, Temu has maintained its innocence, stating that the claims are \"totally unfounded\" and will vigorously defend itself against the lawsuit. The company believes that scrutiny will ultimately benefit its development and is committed to the long-term.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'Visionaries Network TeamVision', '2024-10-27', '00:58:12', 'is-temu-safe-to-use', 'article/visonariesnetwork-temuapp-img.webp', 'Temu App', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visonariesnetwork-temuapp-img.webp', 10, 2024, 'Mobile App Security, User Privacy, App Safety, Cybersecurity Issues, Temu, Temu App, Is Temu Safe', 'Is the Temu app safe for users? Explore recent accusations of spying on Western customers&#039; text messages and what it means for your privacy and security.', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(19, '', 'Trident IoT Boosts Development with New Zigbee Chip and SDK', 'Trident IoT Advances IoT Development with Latest Zigbee Chip and SDK', 'iot-and-robotics', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Trident IoT has taken a significant step forward in its strategy to provide comprehensive IoT solutions that simplify IoT development with the latest offering, a Zigbee chip and accompanying SDK designed by product engineers who have collectively developed and shipped millions of IoT products.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The chip itself incorporates the latest silicon technology, but it\'s the developer-focused SDK that sets it apart. The SDK is purpose-built to make IoT development faster, easier, and more efficient, allowing customers to expect more predictable development cycles, faster time to revenue, and better products.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Since its incorporation less than a year ago, Trident IoT has more than doubled its engineering resources and assembled some of the industry\'s foremost experts on wireless connectivity across various protocols. The company\'s engineers have designed the latest offering from the ground up, backed by over a century of collective end-to-end product development experience to ensure it meets the real-world needs of today\'s developers.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Expertise and Support</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Trident IoT\'s three pillars include advanced silicon offerings, best-in-class design and development services, and US-based accredited certification services. The company is also in the process of becoming an authorized test lab to provide enhanced support and services to manufacturers within the industry.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Demonstration at Connectivity Standards Alliance Meeting</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Trident IoT engineers will be demonstrating their latest technology offerings live at the Connectivity Standards Alliance (Alliance) Member Meeting currently being held in Washington, DC. The company is also set to become an authorized test lab, further strengthening the Alliance\'s commitment to supporting its members in bringing compliant and certified devices to market efficiently and effectively.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><em>\"We are excited to have Trident IoT at this year\'s Alliance Member Meeting where they will showcase and demo their newest technology offerings,\"</em> said Chris LaPr&eacute;, Head of Technology, Connectivity Standards Alliance. \"The pending confirmation of Trident IoT as an authorized test lab is significant as it further strengthens the Alliance\'s commitment to supporting our members in bringing compliant and certified devices to market both efficiently and effectively.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Teamvisiona', '2024-10-13', '00:40:25', 'trident-iot-solutions', 'article/visionariesnetwork-iot-img.webp', 'Trident IoT Advances IoT Development', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionariesnetwork-iot-img.webp', 10, 2024, 'Device Connectivity, IoT Innovations, Chip Technology, IoT Development, Zigbee Chip, Internet of Things, IoT Solutions', 'Explore Trident IoT&#039;s latest advancements in IoT technology with the release of its new Zigbee chip and SDK, designed to enhance device connectivity and application performance.', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(20, '', 'Border Smugglers Use Social Media to Enhance Illegal Operations', 'Border Smugglers Leverage Social Media to Facilitate Illegal Operations', 'legal and regulatory compliance', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Social media platforms have become a crucial tool for border smugglers to transport migrants across the southern border, and these cash-hungry traffickers are not afraid to flaunt their illegal activities online. They use these platforms to recruit truck drivers, advertise their services, and boast about evading authorities.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Recent cases in Arizona have highlighted the issue. In August, 22 people were indicted for recruiting truck drivers using Snapchat posts that showcased cash and glamorized illegal migrant smuggling by border smugglers. Many of these posts claimed that drivers could earn substantial sums of money without the risk of being arrested. The posts often featured images and videos of large amounts of cash, implying that the illegal activity was lucrative and relatively safe.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In another case, an Arizona man was sentenced to 71 months in prison for transporting hundreds of illegal immigrants. Investigators found Snapchat posts in which he gloated about cramming people into overcrowded vehicles in unsafe conditions, and how he used minors to facilitate certain smuggling operations by border smugglers. This further exacerbates the gravity of the situation.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">These social media posts not only facilitate illegal activities but also perpetuate a culture of recklessness and disregard for human life. Border smugglers are becoming increasingly brazen in their online activities, and law enforcement agencies must be vigilant in monitoring social media platforms to prevent them from continuing to exploit vulnerable individuals and evade detection.</p>', 'Visionaries Network TeamVision', '2024-10-16', '00:57:01', 'border-smugglers-illegal-activities-online', 'article/viosnariesnetwork-bordersmugglers-img.webp', 'Border Smugglers Use Social Media to Enhance Illegal Operations', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/viosnariesnetwork-bordersmugglers-img.webp', 10, 2024, 'Cybercrime, Digital Platforms, Illegal Trade, Human Trafficking, Drug Trafficking, Criminal Networks', 'Examine the role of social media in modern smuggling operations, highlighting the challenges it poses for law enforcement and border security.', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(21, '', 'Music Industry Giants Sue AI Music Generation Services Suno and Udio for Copyright Infringement', 'Music Industry Giants Sue AI Music Generation Services Suno and Udio for Copyright Infringement', 'ai vr and automation', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Recording Industry Association of America (RIAA) has filed two copyright infringement lawsuits against music generation services Suno and Udio, accusing them of using artificial intelligence (AI) to mass produce copyrighted sound recordings without permission. The lawsuits were filed on behalf of major record companies, including Sony Music Entertainment, UMG Recordings, Inc., and Warner Records, Inc., which hold the rights to the recordings.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The cases cover a wide range of music genres, styles, and eras, with the RIAA stating that the unlicensed use of AI technology is on a \"massive scale.\" The organization\'s Chairman and CEO, Mitch Glazier, emphasized the importance of responsible AI development and collaboration with the music industry.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\"We can only succeed if developers are willing to work together with us,\" Glazier said. \"Unlicensed services like Suno and Udio that claim it\'s \'fair\' to copy an artist\'s life\'s work and exploit it for their own profit without consent or pay set back the promise of genuinely innovative AI for us all.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The lawsuits aim to stop Suno and Udio from continuing their unlicensed use of copyrighted sound recordings and to establish the importance of ethical and lawful development of generative AI systems. The RIAA\'s Chief Legal Officer, Ken Doroshow, emphasized the need for these lawsuits, stating that they are necessary to \"reinforce the most basic rules of the road\" for responsible AI development.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">One notable example of an AI-generated song is \"BBL Drizzy,\" an R&amp;B parody released in May that went viral last month. It was created using Udio, a generative AI model that allows users to generate music from text prompts. Suno, on the other hand, consists of a team of musicians and AI experts who use DeepAI\'s ChatGPT to generate lyrics.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The lawsuit highlights the ongoing debate over the role of AI in the music industry, with some arguing that AI-generated music can be creative and innovative, while others believe it infringes on the rights of artists and songwriters.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Teamvisiona', '2024-06-29', '00:51:57', 'suno-and-udio-sued', 'article/visionariesnetwork-music-industry-giants-sue-music.jpg', 'suno and udio sued', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionariesnetwork-music-industry-giants-sue-music.jpg', 6, 2024, 'suno, udio sued, Music Industry, AI Music Generation, Copyright Infringement', 'Music Industry Giants Sue AI Music Generation Services Suno and Udio for Copyright Infringement', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(22, '', 'AXIS Capital Holdings Limited Partners Elpha Secure', 'AXIS Capital Holdings Limited Strengthens Partnership with Elpha Secure to Enhance Cyber Security Solutions for US Customers', 'brand management digital marketing and business', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">AXIS Capital Holdings Limited, a leading global specialty insurer, has expanded its partnership with Elpha Secure, a premier cyber security solutions provider, to further enhance its cyber security offerings for customers in the US. The expanded partnership builds upon the initial collaboration in 2021, when AXIS became an investor and capacity provider for Elpha Secure.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">According to Lori Bailey, Head of Global Cyber &amp; Technology at AXIS Capital Holdings Limited, the extended partnership will enable customers to access high-quality cyber coverage with embedded security solutions that can improve their risk profiles and mitigate exposure to cyber threats. \"By delivering cyber coverage through Elpha\'s secure digital distribution platform, we can benefit both our customers and AXIS,\" Bailey explained.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As of July 1, 2024, new standalone cyber business submissions for prospective policyholders with revenue up to $100 million will be directed via wholesale broker partners to Elpha Secure. This transition aims to enhance the efficiency and profitability of AXIS\'s small cyber portfolio while opening up access to Elpha\'s range of cyber security services for customers.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Gordon Malin, Co-Founder and CEO at Elpha Secure, expressed his excitement about the expanded partnership, stating, \"We\'re privileged to expand our partnership with AXIS, a collaboration that underscores our shared commitment to innovation and excellence in cyber insurance.\" Malin added, \"This transition is a testament to the strength of our relationship with AXIS, and we are excited to deliver superior protection and peace of mind to our collective customers.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">AXIS Capital Holdings Limited is committed to providing innovative and effective solutions to its customers through its strategic partnerships. As a leader in the global insurance industry, AXIS is well-positioned to continue delivering value to its customers through its expanded partnership with Elpha Secure.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Teamvisiona', '2024-07-10', '21:38:42', 'axis-capital-holdings-limited-partners-elpha-secure', 'article/visionariesnetwork-secure-enhance-cyber-security.jpg', ': AXIS Capital Holdings Limited Partners Elpha Secure', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionariesnetwork-secure-enhance-cyber-security.jpg', 7, 2024, 'AXIS Capital Holdings Limited, Elpha Secure, best news, top news, cyber security news', 'AXIS Capital Holdings Limited Partners Elpha Secure', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(23, '', 'GM Defense Partners with Universities and Navy', 'GM Defense Partners with Universities and Navy to Develop Advanced Electric Vehicle Technology for Military Use', 'smart city and security infrastructure', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Imagine military vehicles running longer, and faster without fuel powered by state-of-the-art electricity. That is the vision behind the breakthrough collaboration between the defense subsidiary of General Motors, GM Defense, and the Pulsed Power and Energy Laboratory at the University of Texas at Arlington. â€‹It is working with the Naval Surface Warfare Center, Philadelphia Division, to test and mature advanced battery technology for the Department of Defense.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The project, called Evaluation of Electric Vehicle Batteries to Enable Directed Energy or EEVBEDE, is supported with funds from the US Department of Defense Operational Energy Innovation Office. GM Defense is heavily investing in the research; it sees the potential for this tech to change the face of military operations.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Department of Defense can leverage our investments in transformational battery technologies that could provide operational capability at the tactical edge, or on an installation anyplace around the world,\" commented Steve duMont, president, GM Defense. He is very excited about the opportunity to support this project and help transition GM\'s defense and government customers to more efficient and powerful electric vehicles.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">At the heart of this project is GM\'s Ultium Platform: a game-changing propulsion architecture that enables power, range, and scalability beyond anything previously seen in electric vehicles. That modular design makes it possible to adapt to evolving needs and new technological advancement, so it will easily fit military duty.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Dr. David Wetz, a professor of Electrical Engineering at UTA and the director of PPEL, expressed his excitement about the collaboration. \"We\'re excited to work with GM Defense to test the Ultium Platform and determine its potential for use in future warfighting applications,\" he said. \"Our lab has years of experience working for the DoD and Office of Naval Research testing the boundaries of batteries for high-power uses, so we\'re uniquely positioned to be able to test this technology and advise on its future use.\"</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Teamvisiona', '2024-07-16', '22:04:23', 'gm-defense-partners-with-universities-and-navy', 'article/visionariesnetwork-gmdefense-partner-universities.jpg', 'GM Defense Partners with Universities and Navy', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionariesnetwork-gmdefense-partner-universities.jpg', 7, 2024, 'GM Defense Partners, Universities, Navy, best news, defense news', 'GM Defense Partners with Universities and Navy', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(24, '', 'magna marketing disruptor digital marketing', 'Magna Marketing Disrupts Digital Landscape with Innovative Lead Generation Strategies', 'brand management digital marketing and business', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In a rapidly evolving digital marketing landscape, Magna Marketing is revolutionizing the industry with its innovative approaches to lead generation. The company\'s cutting-edge strategies have enabled clients to achieve exceptional results, including a staggering 20% conversion rate, significantly outperforming industry norms.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Magna Marketing\'s unique approach involves creating high-converting video content that targets customers\' biggest pain points and attracts cold prospects. By using advanced technology to track customer behavior and attribute revenue across multiple touchpoints and channels, clients can gain a clearer picture of how their efforts impact pipeline and revenue.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><em>\"Our success isn\'t just theoretical. We use the same funnel to attract clients to our business that we offer to our customers,\"</em> said August Tange, Founder of Magna Marketing. \"We aim to revolutionize the digital marketing landscape through our innovative techniques, ensuring that brands and clients get the maximum ROI and the best customer experience.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With a focus on personalized customer engagement, Magna Marketing\'s AI-driven SMS and email marketing campaigns deliver tailored experiences to each potential lead, fostering trust and engagement. This approach has earned the trust of notable agencies across Europe and prominent companies in the UAE, including Brandfirm and Client Culture.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Magna Marketing\'s success has not only exceeded industry expectations but has also significantly impacted the revenue of their clients. In just three years of operation in the UAE, the company has helped businesses earn seven, eight, and nine figures through its lead generation system.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With a vision to be the foremost lead generation and digital marketing expert in Europe and the Middle East, Magna Marketing is dedicated to scaling ambitious businesses through innovative digital marketing and lead generation strategies.</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Teamvisiona', '2024-07-16', '21:38:33', 'magna-marketing-disruptor-digital-marketing', 'article/visionariesnetwork-magna-marketing-disrupts-digital-landscape.jpg', 'Magna Marketing Disrupts Digital Landscape', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionariesnetwork-magna-marketing-disrupts-digital-landscape.jpg', 7, 2024, 'magna marketing, digital marketing, top news, visionariesnetwork news, best news', 'magna marketing disruptor digital marketing', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(25, '', 'Bhoomi namaskar anthem launched', 'Hungama Digital Media and Bhamla Foundation Launch &#039;Bhoomi Namaskar&#039; Anthem to Raise Awareness of Environmental Conservation', 'agriculture and rural development', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Hungama Digital Media and Bhamla Foundation launched the eagerly anticipated \'Bhoomi Namaskar\' anthem at a press conference on Wednesday, surrounded by a distinguished gathering of esteemed guests. The event was honored by the presence of Asif Bhamla, President of Bhamla Foundation, and Neeraj Roy, Founder of Hungama Digital Media, alongside notable figures such as director R Balki, singer Shaan, music composer Aman Pant, and Sujit Patil, Vice President of Godrej Industries Group.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">The \'Bhoomi Namaskar\' anthem is a powerful initiative aimed at raising awareness about environmental conservation and the importance of sustainable living. This thought-provoking song brings together some of the industry\'s most talented and respected artists, each lending their unique voices and creative energies to champion this noble cause. The song\'s poignant lyrics emphasize the need for humans to coexist harmoniously with nature, stressing the imperative to protect the environment and highlighting the benefits of adopting sustainable lifestyles. The melody, which blends various styles, underscores the universal importance of environmental stewardship. By uniting these renowned individuals, the \'Bhoomi Namaskar\' anthem underscores the significance of caring for the planet and encourages people worldwide to make positive changes in their daily lives.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Teamvisiona', '2024-07-30', '20:11:52', 'bhoomi-namaskar-anthem-launched', 'article/visionariesnetwork-launch-bhoomi-namaskara.jpg', 'Bhoomi namaskar anthem launched', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionariesnetwork-launch-bhoomi-namaskara.jpg', 7, 2024, 'Bhoomi namaskar, anthem, best news, digital media news, top news', 'Bhoomi namaskar anthem launched', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(26, '', 'apple discontinues buy now pay later', 'Apple Axes &#039;Buy Now, Pay Later&#039; Service in US, Unveils New Loan Program', 'Banking and FinTech', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In a significant move, Apple has announced that it will discontinue its \"buy now, pay later\" (BNPL) service, Apple Pay Later, in the United States. The company is instead introducing a new loan program that will allow users to access installment loans through credit, and debit cards, and lenders when checking out with Apple Pay.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The decision to discontinue Apple Pay Later comes as Apple seeks to offer more comprehensive payment solutions to its customers. The new loan program aims to provide users with greater flexibility and convenience when making purchases online and in-store. Starting later this year, customers will be able to take advantage of this new loan program, which promises to bring more opportunities for users to manage their finances effectively.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Apple Pay Later was initially launched in March last year, allowing users to split purchases into four payments over six weeks with no interest or fees. While the service was popular among some users, it appears that Apple has decided to replace it with a more comprehensive loan program that offers more benefits and flexibility.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The new loan program is expected to be a game-changer for Apple Pay users, providing them with more options for managing their finances and making purchases. The program is designed to be user-friendly, allowing customers to easily manage their loans through the Wallet app and making it easy to track their payments.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Apple\'s decision to discontinue Apple Pay Later is seen as a strategic move by the company to focus on more innovative and comprehensive payment solutions. The new loan program is likely to attract more customers and increase the adoption of Apple Pay, further solidifying the company\'s position in the digital payments space.</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Teamvisiona', '2024-07-09', '20:58:36', 'apple-discontinues-buy-now-pay-later', 'article/visionariesnetwork-pay-later-apple.jpg', 'apple discontinues buy now pay later', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionariesnetwork-pay-later-apple.jpg', 7, 2024, 'Apple new, best news, pay later, buy now pay later, discontinues buy now pay later', 'apple discontinues buy now pay later', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0),
(27, '', 'holiday inn revolutionizes travel and hospitality', 'Holiday Inn: The Iconic Brand Continues to Revolutionize Travel and Hospitality', 'Tourism and Hospitality', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As the world becomes increasingly connected, travel and hospitality have become essential components of modern life. At the forefront of this revolution is the iconic Holiday Inn brand, which has been a trusted name in travel and hospitality for generations.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With a legacy of innovation and commitment to excellence, Holiday Inn has consistently pushed the boundaries of what travelers expect from their hotel stay. From its early days as a pioneering hotel chain with a footprint in all 50 U.S. states to its current status as a global leader in travel and hospitality, Holiday Inn has been a driving force in shaping the industry.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As the first hotel chain to introduce a centralized hotel reservation system, Holidex, in collaboration with IBM, Holiday Inn revolutionized the industry by making it easier for travelers to book and plan their trips. This innovation paved the way for future technological advancements across the travel industry, making it easier for travelers to plan and book their trips with ease.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Today, Holiday Inn continues to evolve alongside the changing needs of travelers. The brand has unveiled a refreshed and modernized prototype for its Americas estate, with the first fully renovated hotel set to debut in early 2025. This new design will feature a modern exterior that blends classic elements with modern touches, elevated food and beverage options that cater to travelers\' cravings, around-the-clock convenience with an open market offering essentials for travel, and a refreshed welcome area featuring a re-imagined interior layout that sets the tone for a comfortable stay.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In addition to these updates, the guest rooms will be designed with four distinct zones for seamless functionality: a welcome zone resembling a home entryway for convenient belongings storage; a versatile work/relax zone with a dedicated desk space, lounge area, and easy connectivity; a cozy sleep zone with a comfortable bed that features tech plug-ins on either side of the headboard; and a refresh zone offering a bright and clean bathroom. These innovative features are designed to make every aspect of the travel experience more enjoyable and convenient.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With its commitment to providing exceptional service and amenities, Holiday Inn is dedicated to making every guest feel like they are part of the family. Whether traveling for business or pleasure, Holiday Inn\'s goal is to provide travelers with an unforgettable experience that makes them feel valued and appreciated. As Raul Ortiz, Vice President of Global Marketing &amp; Brand Management for Holiday Inn, notes, \"Trust is invaluable... it\'s something that\'s earned year after year through our dedication to providing exceptional service and amenities.\" With its rich history of innovation and commitment to excellence, Holiday Inn remains at the forefront of the travel and hospitality industry, setting the standard for years to come.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Teamvisiona', '2024-07-29', '21:02:22', 'holiday-inn-revolutionizes-travel-and-hospitality', 'article/visionariesnetwork-holidayinn.jpg', 'holiday inn revolutionizes travel and hospitality', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionariesnetwork-holidayinn.jpg', 7, 2024, 'holiday inn,  travel and hospitality, best news, hospitality', 'holiday inn revolutionizes travel and hospitality', 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0),
(28, '', 'softbank ai voice processing phone technology', 'SoftBank&rsquo;s AI- Voice Processing Phone Technology Combats Customer Harassment', 'ai vr and automation', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">A leading Japanese technology giant, SoftBank Corp., has unveiled new phone technology that applies AI-voice processing to engage and at the same time address the increasingly pressing issue of customer harassment during call center operations. The new system, tagged \"emotion-cancelling,\" utilizes artificial intelligence to make angry callers sound calm and composed, thereby releasing calmer voices out and reducing the stress of call center operators.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">The technology has been developed by SoftBank engineers over the past three years. It identifies the tone of an angry caller and changes it by adopting a two-step process. The technology extracts key acoustic features of the comments made by the caller using AI-voice processing and assimilates the acoustic characteristics of a non-threatening voice to create natural and calm tones.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">With over 10,000 items of voice data sampled, the system generalized the patterns common to the delivery of common phrases: 10 male and female actors per phrase and various emotional tones. The technology does not distort the words of the caller, though the intonation is markedly restrained, enabling a representative to understand the context without aggression in the intonations.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">According to the recent survey done by the Japanese largest industrial union called UA Zensen, 46.8% of service industry workers recounted the experience of being harassed by customers over the last two years, some of them found the events to be so distressing that they had to go for counseling.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">The \"emotion-cancelling\" technology in SoftBank is therefore very handy, as call-center staff faces growing stress in face-to-face interactions amid angry outbursts by unsatisfied customers. With the launch of this innovative solution, SoftBank will take a giant leap in ensuring the safety of its call center operators toward a harmonious customer service experience.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Teamvisiona', '2024-07-26', '00:46:52', 'softbank-ai-voice-processing-phone-technology', 'article/visionariesnetwork-soft-bank-ai-voice-processing-phone-technology-combats.jpg', 'softbank ai voice processing phone technology', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionariesnetwork-soft-bank-ai-voice-processing-phone-technology-combats.jpg', 7, 2024, 'softbank, AI news, Voice Processing technology, AI Technology news, Top News, Latest news', 'softbank ai voice processing phone technology', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(29, '', 'Offenso Hackers Academy cybersecurity curriculum', 'Offenso Hackers Academy is Shaping the Future of Cybersecurity', 'brand management digital marketing and business', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With an exponentially growing demand for more skilled cybersecurity practitioners all over the world, Offenso Hackers Academy has come up with a complete curriculum for students at different levels, ranging from beginners to professionals. The wide curriculum, no doubt, will help students garner the necessary knowledge and experience required to deal with an ever-changing cybersecurity environment.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The program spans the broad cybersecurity spectrum and gives the students a strong foundation in fundamentals, along with options to specialize in one particular area of interest. Courses to introduce beginners to network security, ethical hacking, and the security operations center are made available as a good foundation to build upon later in tougher ones.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">For those who seek to make a more profound impact in addition to the knowledge gained so far, Offenso offers a set of value-added courses catering to specific areas of cybersecurity. These more advanced professional modules deal with discipline-specific material such as incident response, vulnerability assessment, penetration testing, and cloud security to name just a few that allow the prot&eacute;g&eacute; to focus his learning according to the desired career path he chose.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The curriculum is not just comprehensive but also hands-on and participatory at Offenso. They inculcate the basic skills and judgment to overcome the challenges of their chosen cybersecurity career through real-world simulations and exercises in courses. This, apart, such an academy brings active, stalwart cybersecurity professionals who are both your peers to learn from and network with.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Farhan Bin Fazil is the CEO of Offenso Hackers Academy and explains the need for a well-rounded education in cybersecurity. <em>\"Our objective,\"</em> Fazil says,<em> \"is to give students the agility required to face all those that already exist, whilst developing a mindset through which they can predict and meet all future challenges in a constantly changing environment.\" </em>With its strong curriculum, experiential learning, and mentorship, Offenso is perfectly placed as a launchpad for young careers in cybersecurity.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The same has been confirmed by industry awards and the reviews left by students. Backed by a reputation for quality and care, Offenso Hackers Academy is a name to reckon with, both for those starting a career and looking to further advance in the field of cybersecurity. With its place at the forefront of the rapidly growing industry of cybersecurity, Offenso stands to lead things forward for many years.</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Teamvisiona', '2024-07-27', '21:32:36', 'offenso-hackers-academy-cybersecurity-curriculum', 'article/visionariesnetwork-offenso-hackers-academy.jpg', 'Offenso Hackers Academy', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionariesnetwork-offenso-hackers-academy.jpg', 7, 2024, 'Offenso Hackers Academy, cybersecurity news, top news, latest news, hackers academy', 'Offenso Hackers Academy is Shaping the Future of Cybersecurity', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0);
