(85, '', 'Skylight Aims to Disrupt TikTok with New Alternative Platform', 'Skylight Aims to Disrupt TikTok with a TikTok Alternative', 'Startups', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Skylight is a new TikTok Alternative&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../startups\">startup</a></span> that aims to take on TikTok. It is launching its mobile app to the public on Tuesday. The short video site is live on the Apple App Store and in beta on the <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/games?device=windows&amp;pli=1\">Google Play Store</a></span> just 10 weeks after it was created. Skylight is backed by billionaire investor Mark Cuban and others. It is based on the AT Protocol, the same technology that the decentralized social network Bluesky is based on.<br><br><strong>A New Player in the Social Media Arena<br></strong><br>Skylight was started by Tori White (CEO) and Reed Harmeyer (CTO), two businesspeople who are interested in enhancing social media and making it more secure. The app offers users trending short videos, an in-app video editor, and the possibility of commenting, liking, and sharing videos. It also offers customized user accounts and features to follow others.<br><br>Skylight contrasts with TikTok because it\'s decentralized. Skylight runs on the AT Protocol (ATProto), so the videos posted on Skylight become accessible and actionable by users of Bluesky and other applications built on ATProto. This automatically connects Skylight users with more than 33.8 million people, considerably expanding engagement capacity.<br><br><strong>Why Skylight Was Created</strong><br><br>White, a retired travel influencer who became a self-taught Seattle software developer, recognized a chance when news of a possible <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c3e18qylq5do\">TikTok ban in the U.S.</a></span> broke out. Afraid to lose her videos and community, she and Harmeyer looked for alternatives.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">They were attracted to ATProto following the fact that Bluesky was stable, compared to the initial Twitter that regularly showed the notorious <em>\"fail whale\" </em>mistake. The reliability of the protocol led them to create Skylight as a decentralized, <em>\"ban-proof\"</em> TikTok alternative.<br style=\"mso-special-character: line-break;\"><!-- [if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--><br style=\"mso-special-character: line-break;\"><!--[endif]--></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Early Development and Community Involvement</strong><br><br>Before coding even a single line, White utilized her social media expertise to market Skylight. She documented Skylight\'s development on TikTok on her @buildwithtori handle and gained almost 50,000 followers within a brief period. This early progress helped Skylight to expand and obtain early beta testers.<br><br><em>\"We knew people needed that, but we needed to get them to care as well,\" </em>White said at the ATmosphere conference in Seattle. \"So, we began with distribution first.\"<br><br><strong>Features and Future Plans</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Skylight now supports three-minute videos, up from one minute. The founders want the app to be more than a mere clone of TikTok. Future releases will include personalized feeds, new forms of interaction beyond scrolling and swiping, and features such as sounds, duets, stitching, bookmarks, and playlists.<br><br style=\"mso-special-character: line-break;\"><!-- [if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--><br style=\"mso-special-character: line-break;\"><!--[endif]--></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Backed by investors such as Mark Cuban</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Mark Cuban has talked about his desire to invest in a decentralized version of TikTok Alternative. His original investment, coupled with funding from Leslie Feinzaig\'s Graham &amp; Walker Venture Fund, has provided a significant cash infusion to the explosive growth of Skylight.<br><br><strong>Public Access<br></strong><br>After exhaustive testing, Skylight is finally available to all on the Apple App Store, with a testing version also on the Google Play Store. While social media consumers look for freer and self-sufficient platforms, Skylight is a convincing TikTok Alternative and other big social media corporations.<br><br>Skylight has a new strategy, a bigger pool of users, and investor backing. It will shake up the short-form video market. But now the million-dollar question: Can Skylight dethrone TikTok? We\'ll see.</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Teamvisiona', '2025-04-02', '00:12:21', 'skylight-aims-to-disrupt-tiktok-with-a-tiktok-alternative', 'article/visionaries-network-skylight-social.webp', 'Skylight Aims to Disrupt TikTok with a TikTok Alternative', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-skylight-social.webp', 4, 2025, 'Skylight, TikTok alternative, social media, disrupt TikTok, new platform, social network, visionaries network, visionariesnetwork', 'Skylight plans to disrupt TikTok with its innovative alternative, offering fresh features to shake up the social media landscape and attract new users.', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(86, '', 'Glenmark Launches Vancomycin Hydrochloride for Injection USP - Effective Antibiotic Treatment', 'Glenmark Launches Vancomycin Hydrochloride for Injection USP', 'biotechnology and pharmaceuticals', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://glenmarkpharma-us.com/\">Glenmark Pharmaceuticals Inc.</a></span>, USA, has announced the launch of Vancomycin Hydrochloride for Injection USP in the United States market. This is a milestone for the company as it diversifies its hospital product portfolio. The new product is being sold in single-dose vials of 750 mg, 1.25 g, and 1.5 g and is bioequivalent to Mylan Laboratories Limited\'s product.<br><br><strong>Improving Treatment Therapies for Body Infections</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Vancomycin Hydrochloride for Injection USP is administered by IV for the treatment of serious <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../biotechnology-and-pharmaceuticals\">bacterial infections</a></span>. It is primarily for use when other antibiotics would not be effective, particularly for MRSA infection. The product launch will likely enable Glenmark to have a better foothold in the anti-infective market.<br><br><strong>A Large Competitive Market with Strong Demand</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">According to IQVIA sales data available for the period of 12 months ending January 2025, the sale of Vancomycin Hydrochloride for Injection USP, in various strengths of vials, was around $39.3 million. Glenmark\'s launch is most likely to provide a cost-friendly and quality choice to healthcare facilities and professionals.<br><br><strong>Leadership Perspective<br></strong><br>Marc Kikuchi, President and Head of Business, North America, Glenmark Pharmaceuticals, welcomed the launch. \"We are pleased to add Vancomycin Hydrochloride for Injection USP to our institutional portfolio. This new product reflects our commitment to growing our portfolio of quality, affordable medicines to meet the needs of healthcare providers and patients.\"<br><br><strong>Commitment to Quality and Innovation</strong><br><br>Glenmark Pharmaceuticals has been attempting to improve its product portfolio, especially in the injectables and specialty segments. The company focuses on research and development to supply safe, effective, and affordable medicines to the U.S. market.<br><br><strong>Looking Ahead </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With increased activity in the pharma business, Glenmark is constantly expanding its products in selected therapeutic areas of importance. The introduction of Vancomycin Hydrochloride for Injection USP is also a part of the overall strategy of establishing the company\'s institutional product franchise and meeting important healthcare needs.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As more and more individuals require effective antibiotic therapy, Glenmark Pharmaceuticals is dedicated to <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../magazine/innovation-excellence-awards-2023-sent\">innovation</a></span> and treatment delivery. They offer effective treatments at reasonable prices to patients.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br><br style=\"mso-special-character: line-break;\"><!-- [if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--><br style=\"mso-special-character: line-break;\"><!--[endif]--></p>', 'visionariesnetwork Teamvisiona', '2025-04-04', '21:22:20', 'glenmark-launches-vancomycin-hydrochloride-for-injection-usp', 'article/visionaries-network-glenmark-launches-vancomycin-hyrochloride.webp', 'Glenmark Launches Vancomycin Hydrochloride for Injection USP', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-glenmark-launches-vancomycin-hyrochloride.webp', 4, 2025, 'Glenmark, Vancomycin, Injection USP, Antibiotic, Bacterial Infections, Medical Launch, Visionaries network', 'Glenmark launches Vancomycin Hydrochloride for Injection USP, an effective antibiotic for treating bacterial infections.', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(87, '', 'Alembic Pharmaceuticals Wins USFDA Approval for Pantoprazole Injection', 'Alembic Pharmaceuticals Wins USFDA Approval for Pantoprazole Injection', 'biotechnology and pharmaceuticals', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://alembicpharmaceuticals.com/default\">Alembic Pharmaceuticals Limited</a></span> has been granted the final approval of the United States Food and Drug Administration (USFDA) for its Pantoprazole Sodium for Injection, 40 mg/vial (Single-Dose Vial). The injectable drug is equivalent to Protonix I.V. for Injection (40 mg/vial) of Wyeth Pharmaceuticals LLC.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Pantoprazole Sodium Injection: Major Applications and Market Influence</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Pantoprazole Sodium Injection is administered on a regular basis in adults to provide short-term relief (no longer than 10 days) from erosive esophagitis (EE) and gastroesophageal reflux disease (GERD). It can be employed in situations of overproduction of acid within the body, e.g., Zollinger-Ellison (ZE) Syndrome.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Pantoprazole Sodium is a drug that exists under the category of proton pump inhibitors (PPI). It functions by lowering the amount of stomach acid produced, which is why it is very effective in treating acid-related problems. It is often given in clinics to those who cannot swallow medicine. The IV form is quick-acting and is very useful for advanced cases of ZE Syndrome and GERD.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">IQVIA data shows that from the start of 2025 to June 30, the U.S. market size for Pantoprazole Sodium for Injection was around $48 million for the period up to December 2024. This presents a big chance for Alembic Pharmaceuticals to grow in the competitive U.S. pharma market.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Boost to USFDA Approvals of Alembic Pharmaceuticals</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With this new USFDA approval, Alembic Pharmaceuticals has achieved a milestone of 221 ANDA (Abbreviated New Drug Application) approvals. Out of these, 195 are final approvals, and 26 are tentative approvals. This milestone makes Alembic Pharmaceuticals an even stronger player in the U.S. generics market, particularly in the injectables segment.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Alembic Pharmaceuticals has continuously enhanced the manufacture of quality generic medicines. They are concentrating on injectable medicines that cater to the growing demands of the <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../healthcare-and-medical-devices\">healthcare</a></span> sector. The company\'s commitment to innovative concepts and regulatory adherence has enabled it to grow its market share and compete with large pharmaceutical companies.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Alembic\'s Expanding U.S. Pharmaceutical Portfolio</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The FDA approval of Pantoprazole Sodium for Injection is according to Alembic Pharmaceuticals\' growth goals in the U.S. pharma business. Alembic Pharmaceuticals has been persistently introducing more products so that patients in the United States have access to affordable and quality generic medication.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Alembic Pharmaceuticals boasts world-class manufacturing facilities with strict USFDA protocols, rendering products safe, effective, and of higher quality. The company\'s robust research and development capability has played a crucial role in achieving successive approvals, which has enabled it to perform better in the global pharma industry.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With an emphasis on compliance, research, and innovation, Alembic Pharmaceuticals is increasingly well-positioned in the U.S. generic industry. This approval further strengthens Alembic Pharmaceuticals\' dedication to delivering innovative healthcare solutions while enhancing its global presence.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Final Reflections</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Alembic Pharmaceuticals has received yet another USFDA approval, which places the company in a strong position to continue growing in the US injectable market. With a portfolio of products, robust research and development strength, and a history of effective regulatory campaigns, Alembic Pharmaceuticals is a major player in the global pharmaceutical industry.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The increasing need for generic injectable medicines is an enormous opportunity for Alembic Pharmaceuticals to expand its visibility and enhance its market position. With ongoing investments in research, manufacturing, and compliance, the company is well set to grow in the future.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Stay tuned for further updates on Alembic Pharmaceuticals\' market news and drug approvals!</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Teamvisiona', '2025-04-04', '21:22:06', 'alembic-pharmaceuticals-wins-usfda-approval-for-pantoprazole-injection', 'article/visionaries-network-alembic-pharmaceuticals-pantoprazole-injection.webp', 'Alembic Pharmaceuticals Wins USFDA Approval for Pantoprazole Injection', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-alembic-pharmaceuticals-pantoprazole-injection.webp', 4, 2025, 'Alembic Pharmaceuticals, Pantoprazole Injection, USFDA approval, pharmaceutical news, drug approval, Pantoprazole injection USP, visionaries network', 'Alembic Pharmaceuticals receives USFDA approval for Pantoprazole Injection, a treatment for gastrointestinal conditions, enhancing its portfolio of FDA-approved drugs.', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(88, '', 'Toyota Teams Up with o9 to Enhance Supply Chain Efficiency', 'Toyota Teams Up with o9 to Boost Supply Chain Efficiency', 'supply Chain and logistics', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In a major landmark for the automotive sector, o9, a provider of enterprise <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/03/microsoft-at-50-celebrating-a-legacy-and-embracing-an-ai-driven-future\">AI software</a></span> platforms, has signed a Software-as-a-Service (SaaS) deal with Toyota Motor Corporation. The deal is designed to leverage o9\'s cutting-edge AI-based platform to drive Toyota\'s supply chain capabilities. Toyota will use the o9&rsquo;s platform to maximize efficiency and decision-making.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The alliance will transform the way Toyota plans and makes decisions regarding its supply chain. o9\'s technology based on artificial intelligence will maximize Toyota\'s operations, get them to function better, and react to fluctuating market conditions.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Toyota Supply Chain Transformation with o9</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">o9 Co-founder and CEO Chakri Gottemukkala also highlighted the advantages of the partnership. \"This partnership will allow Toyota to streamline its supply chain operations and achieve higher efficiency in accordance with market needs,\" he stated.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Toyota hopes to utilize o9\'s advanced <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../ai-vr-and-automation\">AI technology</a></span> to make better decisions, work more effectively with suppliers, and develop a stronger supply chain. Toyota will be able to react quickly to changes in the market, have good stocks, and improve production planning using the o9 platform.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>AI-Driven Supply Chain Innovation</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">o9\'s platform uses AI to provide real-time information, forecast trends, and plan for multiple scenarios. These functions will enable Toyota to base its decisions on facts and raise the efficiency level of its supply chain.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The SaaS model allows Toyota to connect and scale, which allows them to receive frequent updates and upgrades in AI-based supply chain management. With increasingly complex global supply chains, these AI solutions are becoming increasingly vital for market leaders such as Toyota.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>o9 is expanding in the global market</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">o9 has an international presence, with significant development centers, and is headquartered in the United States. It is a leader in transforming the way of doing supply chain management and has aligned itself with large firms in all sectors.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This new partnership with Toyota further establishes o9 as an AI-driven business solutions leader. As companies around the world harness digital technology, o9 is further growing its reach by creating new solutions to complex supply chain problems.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Toyota\'s Drive for Innovation</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.toyota.com/?msockid=2aad64c6e205683d3ed37785e3f26953\">Toyota</a></span> has been a pioneer in leveraging new technologies in optimizing its operations and manufacturing processes for a long time. Using o9\'s artificial intelligence-based supply chain platform aligns with Toyota\'s vision of a quicker and more data-driven approach to working.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">By adopting o9\'s technology, Toyota wants to improve visibility throughout its network of suppliers, tighten the links of relationships between Toyota and suppliers, and help minimize the threats from uncertainties of markets. Through o9\'s supply chain solution, Toyota can establish a smoother, robust, and responsive network that is up to the tasks of the swiftly evolving market.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Conclusion</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">o9\'s partnership with Toyota is a crucial milestone in enhancing supply chain management. With AI solutions becoming the need of the hour to make operations more efficient, this alliance demonstrates how digital transformations are vital in the automobile sector. As o9 excels in AI and Toyota concentrates on efficiency, this alliance will revolutionize how supply chain management operates in the sector. o9 will become a critical player in the car logistics and planning of the future.</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Teamvisiona', '2025-04-04', '21:51:20', 'toyota-teams-up-with-o9-to-boost-supply-chain-efficiency', 'article/visionaroies-network-toyota-teams-up-with-o9.webp', 'Toyota Teams Up with o9 to Boost Supply Chain Efficiency', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionaroies-network-toyota-teams-up-with-o9.webp', 4, 2025, 'Toyota, o9, supply chain efficiency, supply chain optimization, Toyota partnership, supply chain technology, o9 solutions, logistics improvement', 'Toyota partners with o9 to improve supply chain efficiency, leveraging advanced technology to optimize operations and streamline logistics for enhanced performance', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(89, '', 'CBD Life Sciences Expands into Brain-Boosting Mushrooms', 'CBD Life Sciences Expands into Brain-Boosting Mushrooms', 'CBD and Wellness', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">CBD Life Sciences Inc. is entering the rapidly expanding functional mushroom market to spearhead a revolution in health, focusing on brain health, enhanced memory, and natural support for mental function. As individuals seek more natural solutions to artificial supplements, CBD Life Sciences is taking a shrewd step that may revolutionize the future of wellness.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Brain-Boosting Mushrooms Backed by Science</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Research indicates that certain mushrooms, such as <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.healthline.com/nutrition/lions-mane-mushroom#dementia\">Lion\'s Mane</a></span> (Hericium erinaceus), are beneficial for the brain through nerve regrowth and memory. Researchers at the <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.uq.edu.au/\">University of Queensland</a></span> discovered that some of the compounds in the mushrooms stimulated the growth of nerves and enhanced mental processes&mdash;bridging ancient medicinal knowledge and modern science.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">CBD Life Sciences is implementing these findings into its R&amp;D for the development of new <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/glenmark-launches-vancomycin-hydrochloride-for-injection-usp\">health</a></span> products. They are designed to enhance cognitive ability, halt mental deterioration, and enhance overall mental clarity. They are produced by utilizing non-psychedelic, science-backed mushroom extracts, which offer safe and effective alternatives to conventional medicine.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>A Thriving Industry with Billions at Stake</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The global functional mushroom marketplace is expected to expand to $19.3 billion by the year 2030. Natural solutions for health, focus, and living life more are more and more desired by consumers. CBD Life Sciences is coming to market at the tipping point that enables the business to take advantage of a colossal opportunity much beyond wellness supplements.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Mushrooms are also being studied in different fields, like green packaging, biodegradable materials, and even very sophisticated robots produced using mycelium-based technology. CBDL\'s entry into this field is not merely about selling mushroom capsules&mdash;it\'s about becoming part of a world of unlimited possibilities.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Quality, Safety, and Consumer Confidence</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With more focus being put on mushroom wellness, public safety comes first. CBD Life Sciences prioritizes the highest possible quality and regulatory compliance. While companies are selling unregulated psychedelic products, CBDL only utilizes lab-tested, non-psychoactive ingredients in their products.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This assurance of safety and transparency assists in building consumer confidence and solidifying the company\'s leadership as a wellness company. As much as the FDA is watchful of mushroom products, CBDL\'s progressive strategy ensures that it remains ahead of the curve, providing both investors and consumers with confidence.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>A Wise Move Towards Future Expansion </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">CBD Life Sciences is stepping into the functional mushroom space. This is a huge move as the company moves away from being a CBD firm to one that distributes a line of wellness products. This move answers the increasing demand from consumers as well as positions the company as a leader in brain health and natural medicine. Investors take notice: this is not merely a product launch&mdash;it\'s a science-driven growth strategy grounded in market trends and a stringent emphasis on quality. As natural remedies for health increasingly gain traction, CBD Life Sciences is setting the stage for the mental wellness of the future.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Teamvisiona', '2025-04-05', '23:59:23', 'cbd-life-sciences-expands-into-brain-boosting-mushrooms', 'article/visionaries-network-cbd-life-lciences-expands-into-brain-boosting-mushrooms.webp', 'CBD Life Sciences Expands into Brain-Boosting Mushrooms', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-cbd-life-lciences-expands-into-brain-boosting-mushrooms.webp', 4, 2025, 'CBD Life Sciences, brain-boosting mushrooms, wellness, cognitive health, mushrooms, natural supplements, mental clarity, focus, mushroom extracts, nootropics, wellness products, visionaries network, health benefits', 'CBD Life Sciences expands its offerings with brain-boosting mushrooms, promoting cognitive health, focus, and mental clarity through natural wellness solutions.', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(90, '', 'New Research Enhances CBD Absorption in the Body', 'New Research Breakthrough Significantly Improves CBD Absorption in the Body', 'cbd and wellness', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">There may be a new scientific breakthrough that could revolutionize how the body absorbs cannabidiol (CBD). This can result in safer, more effective, and less expensive treatments.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">CBD is famously known to assist with pain, inflammation, and brain protection. It has been used to assist in treating conditions such as epilepsy, multiple sclerosis, and chronic pain. Yet, one of the greatest issues that keep CBD from being effective is that it is poorly absorbed.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">CBD is not soluble in water, meaning that the body can\'t digest it when consumed orally. What that implies is that a significant amount of the CBD individuals consume doesn\'t find its way into the bloodstream in significant quantities.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Finally, researchers at the <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.unisa.edu.au/\">University of South Australia (UniSA)</a></span> have solved this issue by significantly enhancing the bioavailability of CBD absorption using a phospholipid complex.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The new system employs a fat-based molecule that contains phosphorus to form minute particles known as a CBD-PLC (CBD-phospholipid complex). It facilitates the ease with which CBD dissolves within the body and enhances the amount that is absorbed and delivered where it is required.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The study found that these advanced particles helped CBD to dissolve from 0% to a whopping 67.1% in just three hours.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This is a significant breakthrough for CBD-based therapies,\" said <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/thabata-muta/?originalSubdomain=au\">Thabata Muta, lead author and UniSA PhD student</a></span>. \"Improved CBD absorption allows patients to achieve improved outcomes at lower doses, minimizing side effects and cost of treatment.\".</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The researchers also reported that there was an increase in permeability by 32.7% in tests on cells. This would allow more of the CBD to pass through the intestinal lining and into the bloodstream.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Another advantage is that the formulation is stable for a longer duration. Unlike traditional CBD products that can degrade upon exposure to heat, light, or oxygen, the new phospholipid complex was stable even after 12 months of storage.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This improvement benefits CBD users and could also provide a lead to better utilization of other insoluble medication.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The global CBD market is expected to grow from $7.59 billion in 2023 to over $200 billion by 2032. This discovery comes at the ideal time.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/glenmark-launches-vancomycin-hydrochloride-for-injection-usp\">Pharmaceutical firms</a></span> have attempted to make CBD absorption easy with man-made equivalents, emulsions, or gel capsules &mdash; but they have side effects or act erratically. The UniSA researchers\' approach does not involve artificial additives and uses materials that are naturally compatible with the body membranes, and is therefore more comfortable and a safer option.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The scientists are preparing for clinical trials and searching for means of marketing this breakthrough. If it succeeds, this may lead to more effective and consistent CBD medications &mdash; particularly for individuals with epilepsy, multiple sclerosis, anxiety, and pain.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In short, this new way of CBD absorption can now enable us to utilize all the medicinal value of cannabidiol to the fullest. It can provide patients with more consistent, safer, and less expensive treatments for most serious diseases.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Teamvisiona', '2025-04-06', '00:18:07', 'new-research-breakthrough-significantly-improves-cbd-absorption-in-the-body', 'article/visionaries-network-new-research-breakthrough-cbd-absorption-body.webp', 'New Research Breakthrough Significantly Improves CBD Absorption in the Body', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-new-research-breakthrough-cbd-absorption-body.webp', 4, 2025, 'CBD absorption, research breakthrough, CBD bioavailability, CBD effectiveness, health research, wellness, improved absorption, CBD products, natural supplements, bioactive compounds, enhanced CBD delive', 'New research reveals a breakthrough that significantly improves CBD absorption in the body, enhancing its effectiveness and benefits for overall wellness.', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
