(128, NULL, 'Tapcheck Raises $225M to Grow On-Demand Pay Platform', 'Tapcheck Raises $225M to Expand On-Demand Pay Platform', 'Startups', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.tapcheck.com/\">Israeli fintech firm Tapcheck</a></span>, which provides a cutting-edge on-demand <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../magazine/profile/remedy-payment-solutions-aims-to-offer-transparent-pricing-and-personalized-service\">pay platform</a></span>, revealed on Monday that it raised a combined debt and equity of $225 million. The capital includes a $25 million extension of its Series A from current investor PeakSpan Capital and a $200 million credit facility from Victory Park Capital. This massive funding is expected to drive Tapcheck\'s expansion and further establish the firm in the fast-expanding earned wage access (EWA) market.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Founders to Eradicate Paycheck-to-Paycheck Stress</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Started in 2019 by husband-and-wife entrepreneurs <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/rongaver/\">Ron</a></span> and <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/kaylinggaver/\">Kayling Gaver</a></span>, Tapcheck was created to address the real-life financial struggles that many employees face due to rigid pay cycles. By giving employees earlier access to their earned wages before payday, Tapcheck reduces financial stress, increases retention, and improves workplace productivity.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Free for Employers, Empowering for Employees</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Unlike some other borrowing options, Tapcheck\'s platform is no cost to employers and is easily integrated with nearly 300 payroll and timekeeping systems. Employees can borrow their wages responsibly and securely without fear of high fees or interest rates. The company reports that over 70% of employees who use the service indicate that it alleviates their financial stress, and employers experience over a 50% decrease in turnover.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>$1 Billion in Early Wage Access and Growth</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In just five short years, Tapcheck has enabled more than $1 billion in early wage funding and now serves more than 12,000 employer locations across the country. This pace of growth reflects the way on-demand pay is becoming a must-have benefit for forward-thinking employers.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Expansion Plans in the Works</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The funds will be used to finance product development, customer acquisition, and geographic expansion into new markets. With strong support from PeakSpan and Victory Park Capital, Tapcheck will be a pioneer in financial wellness solutions that empower employees.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Why Tapcheck Is Creating Waves in 2025</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Whether you\'re an employer seeking to boost worker happiness or an employee looking to gain more access to your pay, Tapcheck provides a forward-thinking solution to a long-standing payroll problem. As economic flexibility is more crucial than ever in today\'s economy, Tapcheck\'s timely answer to earned wage access isn\'t just timely &mdash; it\'s essential.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-04-16', '23:28:26', 'tapcheck-raises-225m-to-expand-on-demand-pay-platform', 'article/visionaries-network-tapcheck-raises-doller225m-to-expand.webp', 'Tapcheck Raises $225M to Expand On-Demand Pay Platform', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-tapcheck-raises-doller225m-to-expand.webp', 4, 2025, 'Tapcheck, funding, on-demand pay, payroll, fintech, $225M, platform, raise, visionaries network, wages, HR tech, salary access, investment, finance, business growth', 'Tapcheck secures $225M to scale its on-demand pay platform, making instant wage access easier for employees nationwide.', 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0),
(129, NULL, '23andMe Review: Anne Wojcicki Drives Health Tech Shift', '23andMe Strategic Review: Anne Wojcicki Leads Health Tech Change', 'women in leadership', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Among the sea of technology startups, few biotech stars twinkle as brightly as&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/annewojcicki/\">23andMe co-founder and CEO Anne Wojcicki</a></span>. A bold and pioneering figure in the field, Wojcicki didn\'t just create a consumer health product&mdash;she revolutionized the way 15 million individuals think about their health, heritage, and genetic identity. As one of the most influential women in health tech, her reach has extended far beyond boardrooms and laboratories, into the daily lives of over 15 million users.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>23andMe Strategic Review: What\'s Happening?</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In a significant development, <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.23andme.com/\">23andMe</a></span> has announced that it is undertaking a strategic review to explore the best way forward for the company. The Special Committee of the Board of Directors, which is made up of independent directors, has been tasked with considering a broad range of alternatives, including the potential sale, merger, restructuring, licensing of strategic assets, or other alternatives.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">To aid in this process, the company has engaged Moelis &amp; Company LLC to be its financial advisor and Goodwin Procter LLP to be its legal advisor. While decisions have not yet been made, 23andMe stated that further updates will only be released if a material transaction is affected.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>AI, Genetic Data, and the Healthcare Technology of the Future</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The 23andMe strategic review is well-timed with medicine, AI, and genetic data now increasingly intertwining with one another. With one of the largest private genetic databases in the world, 23andMe is a valuable asset in a data-centric world. Industry experts are of the view that the result of this strategic exercise would have spillover impacts on medical research, personalized treatment, and follow-on AI models.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As AI firms look for top-notch data to train smart systems, firms like 23andMe, with robust data infrastructure, are being approached in increasing numbers, not just by <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/alembic-pharmaceuticals-wins-usfda-approval-for-pantoprazole-injection\">pharmaceutical</a></span> giants, but also by tech leaders who want to lead the way in healthcare innovation.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Anne Wojcicki\'s Legacy: Women in Health Tech Leading the Way</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Whether or not new developments result from the 23andMe strategic review, Anne Wojcicki is an indelible fact of history as a female pioneer in the health tech field. She broke glass ceilings within a biotech industry dominated by men and forged a model of transparency, consumer empowerment, and leadership ethics.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Her legacy is not scientific but cultural. Her vision continues to inspire the next generation of women in life science, digital health, and bioethics entrepreneurs. In rewriting the future of 23andMe, one thing is certain: Anne Wojcicki\'s leadership has irreversibly transformed what\'s possible in healthcare.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-04-16', '23:40:29', '23andme-strategic-review-anne-wojcicki-leads-health-tech-change', 'article/visionaries-network-anne-wojcicki.webp', 'visionaries-network-anne-wojcicki', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-anne-wojcicki.webp', 4, 2025, '23andMe, Anne Wojcicki, strategic review, health tech, genomics, DNA testing, innovation, biotech, leadership, healthcare, personalized medicine, startup, genetics, visionaries network, transformation', 'Anne Wojcicki leads 23andMe through a strategic review, signaling a major shift in health tech and personalized medicine.', 1, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0),
(130, NULL, 'Laser Technologies Unveils New Nesting Software', 'Laser Technologies unveils nesting software for cutting', 'it and software', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.lasertechnologies.co.in/\">Laser Technologies</a></span>, the global leader in laser technology, is pleased to present ReTen X, a game-changing nesting software for cutting, which has been developed in partnership with AlmaCAM. The latest software has the potential to revolutionize the cutting industry by maximizing sheet metal cutting, robotic welding programming, and continuous laser cutting processes.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The launch of ReTen X is a significant development for Laser Technologies as the company continues to raise its commitment to providing cutting-edge solutions for its customers. In another related development, Laser Technologies has also signed an agreement with AlmaCAM, further strengthening their partnership and elevating the level of capability in their products.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Leading Adoption through First Movers</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Two of the first customers have already experienced the benefit of ReTen X, reaping the first-mover advantage by introducing the nesting software for cutting into their processes. Amex Engineering\'s Himanshu Seth and Mr. Sunny Kothari of Crish Metal Works Pvt. Ltd. have seen outstanding returns, earning over 10X their investment in the first year. Their success proves the efficacy of the <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2024/10/is-temu-safe-to-use\">software</a></span> and its impact on operational productivity.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Optimizing Output and Reducing Losses</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">ReTen X is designed to address the new demands of today\'s manufacturing with its high-end features to enable effective cycles of production and waste reduction. With the compatibility of multi-cutting technologies like laser, plasma, water jets, oxy-cutting, punching, and even 3D cutting of tubes, ReTen X provides customers unparalleled flexibility. The plasma cutting and laser cutting quoting tools enable accurate estimation of the cost to allow companies to plan and budget for projects easily.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">One of the principal strengths of ReTen X is in its capability for waste reduction. By ensuring optimum utilization of materials, the system allows businesses to not just be more efficient but also profitable, hence being an essential tool to manufacturers wishing to remain at the forefront in an increasingly dynamic market.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>AlmaCAM\'s Experience with Nesting Solutions</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">AlmaCAM\'s 45 years of nesting and CAD/CAM solution expertise have played a critical role in the creation of ReTen X. Initially developed to cut fabric, AlmaCAM\'s expertise has now found its way into robotics and 3D cutting, with its software utilized worldwide for its optimization. The union is the perfect combination of both worlds&mdash;Laser Technologies\' state-of-the-art laser technology and AlmaCAM\'s market-leading nesting solutions.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Smooth Integration Towards Maximizing Efficiency</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">ReTen X is built to seamlessly integrate with existing systems like ERP, MES, CAD, PLM, and other enterprise systems. This enables data sharing in real-time across departments, better communication, and workflow. Additionally, ReTen X\'s cloud-based solutions enable manufacturers to access the software remotely, and the SaaS solution enables scalability to meet the needs of dynamic production environments.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Unmatched Efficiency and Advanced Capabilities</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">ReTen X is designed to optimize every aspect of the cutting process, with first-class nesting efficiency and a full range of support for cutting technologies:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>Multi-Technology Compatibility:</strong> Compliant with any cutting operation like laser, plasma, waterjet, oxy-cutting, punching, and 3D tube cutting.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>Enhanced Quoting and Cost Estimation:</strong> Integrated functionality offers precise plasma and laser cutting quotes to optimize project costing and cost control.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>Flexible System Integration:</strong> Facilitates integration with ERP, MES, CAD, PLM, and other enterprise applications such that collaboration is enhanced and there is real-time data sharing.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>Value-Added Functions:</strong> Offers total inventory control, user-customizable reports, and CNC profile cutting technology support for Laser, Plasma, Oxyfuel, Waterjet, and Punching.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>A Vision for the Future</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/pankti-agarwal-8326a3a2/\">Pankti Agarwal, Executive Director of Laser Technologies</a></span>, welcomed the launch, saying, \"We are thrilled to introduce ReTen X at our 8th Open House, where we continue to expand the horizon of innovation. We aim to provide our customers with innovative solutions that enable them to enhance their manufacturing efficiency and position themselves in a better position in a competitive market.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/rakesh-agarwal-lasertechnologies-india/\">Rakesh Agarwal, Managing Director and Founder, Laser Technologies</a></span>, said, \"Success in today\'s competitive market is two-pronged: productivity improvements and scrap reduction. ReTen X, designed in partnership with AlmaCAM, tackles both these problems and returns 10X ROI in the first year of implementation.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With the latest technology, ReTen X is the best cutting nesting software to be utilized when cutting in manufacturing today, helping companies to get the most out of their manufacturing and stay ahead of the fast-moving market.</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-04-16', '23:50:50', 'laser-technologies-unveils-nesting-software-for-cutting', 'article/vsionaries-network-laser-technologies-unveils-nesting-software.webp', 'Laser Technologies unveils nesting software for cutting', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/vsionaries-network-laser-technologies-unveils-nesting-software.webp', 4, 2025, 'Laser Technologies, nesting software, cutting, CNC, manufacturing, automation, metal cutting, efficiency, visionaries network, fabrication, CAD, CAM, sheet metal, software launch, tech news', 'Laser Technologies introduces advanced nesting software to boost cutting precision and efficiency in manufacturing. Ideal for CNC and sheet metal operations.', 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0),
(131, NULL, 'Flip Axis Launches Virtual Skate Game for Quest 3', 'XR Indie Flip Axis Studios Unveils Virtual Skate for Quest 3', 'ai vr and automation', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Flip Axis Studios, an XR indie developer that has been at the forefront of virtual reality innovation, has just dropped the announcement for Virtual Skate, a multiplayer virtual reality skateboarding game to be released later this year on Meta Quest 3 and SteamVR.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Created to transfer the excitement of real skating into immersive spaces, the Virtual Skate experience packs all the exhilaration with no sprains or bruises.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Innovative 3D Foot Control with Your Hands</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The crown of Virtual Skate is its 3D control system, allowing players to control their feet with their hands. This new mechanic is intended to accurately mimic the movements of real-world skateboarding in a <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/vr-for-alzheimers-detection-is-a-breakthrough-in-early-diagnosis\">VR</a></span> environment, providing precision and imagination previously unseen.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Physics-Based Illusions without Canned Animations</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Unlike other VR skateboarding games that use scripted moves, Virtual Skate uses a physics system. That is, players have total freedom to style out tricks, flip the board, and manage momentum in a way that is natural and aurally pleasing&mdash;traits of the sort of innovation you\'d anticipate from an XR indie studio.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Multiplayer mode with built-in replay recording</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Skating with buddies is always more fun, and Virtual Skate accomplishes that with a multiplayer feature that delivers co-op skate VR sessions. Even better is in-game camera support, where you can record your friends\' lines and tricks. That alone would make the game a social media favorite among VR content creators.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Developed by Skater XL creator Jon West</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Flip Axis Studios is receiving a huge credibility boost with the addition of <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/itsjonwest/\">Jon West, Easy Day Studios co-founder and lead developer of the popular PC and console game Skater XL</a></span>. His addition to the team means that Virtual Skate can be the next step in the evolution of the skate game genre&mdash;this time in fully immersive VR.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Available Soon on Quest 3 and SteamVR, though no word is yet out on when Virtual Skate officially releases, Flip Axis Studios hints that it will be \"soon,\" arriving on Quest 3 and SteamVR. As XR indie titles continue to innovate on these platforms, Virtual Skate is one of the most highly anticipated titles in development.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Join the Virtual Skate Community. Fans can stay updated on the progress by checking the <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.virtualskategame.com/\">official Virtual Skate website</a></span> and by joining the game\'s Discord server. The channels are likely to post the first announcements on beta testing, early access, and store page drops.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-04-17', '23:55:29', 'xr-indie-flip-axis-studios-unveils-virtual-skate-for-quest-3', 'article/visionaries-network-xr-indie-flip-axis-studios.webp', 'XR Indie Flip Axis Studios Unveils Virtual Skate for Quest 3', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-xr-indie-flip-axis-studios.webp', 4, 2025, 'Flip Axis Studios, XR, Virtual Skate, Quest 3, VR game, indie studio, skateboarding, visionaries network, immersive, virtual reality, action game, gaming, Oculus, VR sports, innovation', 'Flip Axis Studios unveils Virtual Skate, an immersive XR skateboarding game for Quest 3, bringing indie-style tricks and thrills to virtual reality.', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0);
