(137, NULL, 'LG CNS Launches Smart City Project in Hogansville', 'LG CNS Smart City Hogansville Georgia Project Kicks Off', 'smart city and security infrastructure', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">South Korea\'s top AI and digital transformation firm,&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.lgcns.com/en/\">LG CNS</a></span>, has officially entered the U.S. market with its inaugural smart city project, selecting Hogansville, Georgia, as its initial location. The cutting-edge project aims to improve city living through smart infrastructure, and Hogansville has been selected as the pilot site for the company\'s North American entry.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The LG CNS <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/westown-smart-city-south-africa-set-to-transform-kwazulu-natal\">Smart City</a></span> Hogansville Georgia initiative will transform the small but forward-thinking city with smart poles and an integrated control system that will enable public safety, enhanced connectivity, and efficient urban management. The initiative will initially be applied in Hogansville\'s downtown and surrounding parks.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Smart Poles: Combining Lighting with Technology</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The highlight of the project is a smart network of poles built with <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/mtn-powers-the-future-of-smart-city-south-africa-with-iot-tech\">Internet of Things (IoT)</a></span> cutting-edge technology. The poles will introduce the following features to a normal street lamp:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Smart lighting management that adjusts light levels in accordance with surrounding data and pedestrian flows</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Public Wi-Fi hotspots are to increase digital access across the city</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Environmental sensors to monitor air quality, humidity, and temperature</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->CCTV surveillance to improve traffic flow management and surveillance</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">These aspects will be controlled by LG CNS\'s Cityhub Building platform that will provide a single system for real-time monitoring and service. This will enable Hogansville officials to optimize city services with precision and efficiency.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>More Than Just Lighting</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In addition to their intelligent lighting and connectivity, the smart poles will offer:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Electric vehicle charging stations, encouraging environmentally friendly travel</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Digital signage for displaying public service messages, emergency alerts, and regional messages</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Emergency call buttons are directly connected to local emergency services to facilitate faster response during emergencies</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">These improvements are designed to increase safety and convenience for Hogansville residents, leading the way to a city that is more attuned to the needs of its people.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">An LG CNS executive explained, \"Our vision of the smart city isn\'t about high-tech &mdash; it\'s about quality of life. The LG CNS Smart City Hogansville Georgia initiative is a wonderful example of how innovation starts small and grows big from there.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Local Roots, Global Horizons </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">LG CNS also has a deep wealth of international smart city development experience. In South Korea alone, it has led pioneering projects such as:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo3;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>Sejong Smart City &ndash;</strong> National pilot smart city with autonomous mobility, AI, and sustainability vision</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo3;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>Busan Eco Delta Smart City &ndash;</strong> An ecologically focused urban development project</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo3;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>Global projects in Indonesia</strong> <strong>and Southeast Asia -</strong> LG CNS will install smart infrastructure and city-wide data systems</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The firm\'s experience in mass urban projects in Korea makes it well-suited to apply these technologies to smaller U.S. cities. By choosing Hogansville as its initial American partner, LG CNS shows a commitment to developing scalable, community-focused smart city models.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>A Portal to Local Growth</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As the Hogansville opening starts, LG CNS is already projecting into the future. The company intends to spread the smart city idea to other Georgia cities in the region, such as LaGrange and West Point, potentially creating a regional smart city corridor.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The LG CNS Smart City Hogansville Georgia initiative could serve as a model for peer cities seeking to go high-tech without busting budgets. Should the initiative prove successful, it could encourage further public-private partnerships to bring next-generation infrastructure to the rural and mid-sized American towns.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Conclusion </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">LG CNS\'s entry into the US smart city market is not only a business opportunity &mdash; it\'s a promise that innovation is not the monopoly of cities. With its blend of global knowledge and local passion, the LG CNS Smart City Hogansville Georgia project is opening the door to smarter, safer, and more connected communities throughout America.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br><br><br style=\"mso-special-character: line-break;\"><!-- [if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--><br style=\"mso-special-character: line-break;\"><!--[endif]--></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br style=\"mso-special-character: line-break;\"><!-- [if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--><br style=\"mso-special-character: line-break;\"><!--[endif]--></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\">&nbsp;</span></p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-04-18', '23:15:08', 'lg-cns-smart-city-hogansville-georgia-project-kicks-off', 'article/visionaries-network-lg-cns-smart-city-hogansville-georgia.webp', 'LG CNS Smart City Hogansville Georgia Project Kicks Off', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-lg-cns-smart-city-hogansville-georgia.webp', 4, 2025, 'LG CNS, smart city, Hogansville, Georgia, technology, infrastructure, innovation, urban planning, IoT, AI, visionaries network, digital transformation, city development, sustainability, project launch', 'LG CNS kicks off its Smart City project in Hogansville, Georgia, aiming to drive innovation, connectivity, and sustainable urban development through advanced technologies.', 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0),
(138, '', 'Aveva Pioneers Knowledge-as-a-Service Platform Model', 'Aveva Leads Shift to Knowledge-as-a-Service Platform Model', 'it and software', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As operational technology (OT) and information technology (IT) increasingly converge, a new industrial revolution is underway&mdash;led not just by software, but by domain knowledge and real-time insight. Leading the charge is&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.aveva.com/\">Aveva Group</a></span>, UK industrial software giant now wholly owned by Schneider Electric. The firm is driving its partners forward with an irresistible agenda: converting specialist knowledge into scalable services through a Knowledge-as-a-Service platform.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Aveva\'s Ambitious Gamble on a Platform Future</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Aveva\'s vision is to see beyond tool selling&mdash;it\'s about empowering partners with the ability to provide smart, reusable, AI-driven solutions based on vast industry expertise. Tim Sowell, lead digital portfolio strategy, and <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/alexeylebedev/\">Alexey Lebedev, vice president of Pacific</a></span>, described how Aveva is enabling its ecosystem to shift from conventional system integrators to domain-specific solution providers.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&ldquo;We consider ourselves to be offering an informatics Connect Platform,\" Sowell said. \"We\'re adding blocks on top of that&mdash;what we refer to as the purple Aveva blocks&mdash;that embody our 50 years of experience in agents and components.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>From Service Providers to Knowledge Experts</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">These \"purple blocks\" of modular capability allow partners to deliver customized solutions like pump optimisation, not just once, but as a reproducible service across industries. Take Harmony Gold, a leading South African mining conglomerate. Without in-house pump performance expertise, it partnered with a former system integrator who now delivers that customized service via Aveva\'s ecosystem.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">That third party isn\'t a consultant anymore&mdash;they\'re a trusted, regular contributor, embedded directly into Harmony\'s systems through the Knowledge-as-a-Service platform.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><em>&ldquo;This is a change from marketing a product to becoming a part of the customer\'s trusted knowledge network,\"</em> Sowell said.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>No More Licensing: The Subscription and SaaS Revolution</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This change is alongside a change away from perpetual licensing and on-prem deployments. As Sowell describes, cloud-based solutions now allow businesses to scale solutions globally&mdash;something that the old on-prem model could not.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&ldquo;For partners, it\'s a matter of how they consume their IP and present it as reusable knowledge modules,\" Lebedev said. <em>\"We\'re witnessing businesses move away from selling projects and selling insights instead. This is even more potent when delivered via a cloud-based, flexible, and constantly evolving Knowledge-as-a-Service platform.\"</em></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Various Regions, Various Readiness</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The adoption rate varies across the globe. Whereas the engineering firms in Europe are saturated with long-term projects and keen on injecting know-how into scalable solutions, nations such as Australia are experiencing skill deficits, and hence, reusable, <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/ai-powered-stroke-rehabilitation-technology-enhances-patient-safety\">AI-powered solutions</a></span> are more critical.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Lebedev added that partners in these markets need to embrace faster deployment models and leave behind huge, packaged deployments. Instead, they need to use data-driven insights and platform services to keep pace.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Aveva\'s Own Transition Reflects Industry Transformation</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Aveva itself began life as a state-funded CAD center in 1967. After decades of takeover and restructuring, it was acquired by Schneider Electric in 2018 and became fully owned in 2022. Today, Aveva is not just offering design and simulation software&mdash;it\'s offering a platform for partners to build, grow, and monetize their area of expertise.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The company\'s strategy is to empower partners with the capability to bring their skills to the world, using AI, cloud, and real-time data as imperatives. <em>\"The IT world is converging into OT,\"</em> Sowell stated. <em>\"And as IoT grows, the engineering paradigm is shifting, as well.\"</em></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>The Future Lies in Expertise, Not Tools </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Aveva\'s message to partners is straightforward: shake off the mindset of product suppliers, and start thinking as knowledge suppliers. Those who can turn domain expertise into a service will thrive. Those that do not may be left in the dust. By adopting the Knowledge-as-a-Service platform model, Aveva is not merely changing its own business&mdash;but the whole ecosystem that revolves around it too.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\">&nbsp;</span></p>', 'visionariesnetwork Teamvisiona', '2025-04-22', '00:34:26', 'aveva-leads-shift-to-knowledge-as-a-service-platform-model', 'article/visionaries-network-aveva-shift-knowledge-as-a-service-platform.webp', 'Aveva Leads Shift to Knowledge-as-a-Service Platform Model', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-aveva-shift-knowledge-as-a-service-platform.webp', 4, 2025, 'Aveva, Knowledge-as-a-Service, KaaS, digital transformation, cloud platform, industrial software, data insights, smart manufacturing, visionaries network, AI, SaaS, enterprise solutions, digital twin, analytics, connected systems', 'Aveva leads the shift to a Knowledge-as-a-Service model, delivering intelligent, connected platforms for smarter industrial operations and insights.', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(139, '', 'NVIDIA to Build AI Chips in Texas Factory', 'NVIDIA Texas Factory to Build AI Chips Amid Tariff Shift', 'semiconductors', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In a move that mirrors President Donald Trump\'s tariff policy,&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://blogs.nvidia.com/\">NVIDIA</a></span> said it will manufacture its AI supercomputers entirely in the US. The move follows Trump\'s threat to impose tariffs on foreign-made semiconductors imported into the US. The move puts NVIDIA at the forefront of the latest tech giants to support the tariff-fueled move towards domestic manufacturing, putting the company at the forefront of the reshoring of the <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/micron-technology-adds-surcharge-to-offset-trump-tariffs\">semiconductor</a></span> industry.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>NVIDIA Texas Factory at the Center of AI Production</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">NVIDIA Texas factory is a key part of this aggressive strategy. \"Aside from its leading manufacturing partners, the company has acquired more than a million square feet of manufacturing capacity to produce and test NVIDIA Blackwell chips in Arizona and artificial intelligence supercomputers in Texas,\" NVIDIA said in a press release.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>The Role of Foxconn and Wistron in AI Supercomputers</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">NVIDIA Texas factory is one of multiple initiatives to produce NVIDIA\'s newest chips. Blackwell chips, specifically designed for artificial intelligence, have already started production at the Phoenix factory of TSMC, with the other factories in Texas to soon follow. NVIDIA is collaborating with Foxconn in Houston and Wistron in Dallas for the AI supercomputer production facilities. Both of these facilities will go into mass production in the next 12 to 15 months.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Securing the U.S. Supply Chain through Domestic Operations</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">To support the move, NVIDIA is working with Amkor and SPIL for Arizona-based packaging and testing operations. The company also approximates that in a period of four years, it will produce up to half a trillion dollars\' worth of AI infrastructure in America, further solidifying the role of the NVIDIA Texas factory in defining the future of AI.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>The Impact of Tariffs on NVIDIA\'s U.S. Manufacturing Plans </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">NVIDIA\'s aggressive plans to ramp up production in the U.S. come as the U.S. government is keeping a close eye on semiconductor imports and manufacturing. It\'s clear from President Trump\'s signals that semiconductors will be targeted with tariffs in the near term, and it\'s putting a spotlight on NVIDIA\'s plans. Under such circumstances, NVIDIA\'s plant in Texas is a prime location of activity in keeping America ahead of the AI race worldwide.</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Teamvisiona', '2025-04-22', '00:34:54', 'nvidia-texas-factory-to-build-ai-chips-amid-tariff-shift', 'article/visionaries-network-nvidia-texas-factory-build-ai-chips.webp', 'NVIDIA to Build AI Chips in Texas Factory', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-nvidia-texas-factory-build-ai-chips.webp', 4, 2025, 'NVIDIA, AI chips, Texas factory, semiconductor, chip manufacturing, tariffs, US production, technology, artificial intelligence, supply chain, domestic manufacturing, tech news, silicon, visionaries-network, AI hardware', 'NVIDIA announces a new Texas factory to build AI chips, boosting U.S. production in response to shifting tariffs and global supply chain needs.', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(140, NULL, 'Lacy Guo Net Worth 2025 Tops Charts, Beating Taylor Swift', 'Lacy Guo Net Worth 2025 Tops Charts, Beating Taylor Swift', 'women in leadership', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Make way for the new billionaire\'s club queen.&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/lucy-guo-a7804955/\">Lacy Guo</a></span>, a trailblazing <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/alibaba-cloud-spring-launch-2025-unveils-global-ai-tools\">artificial intelligence</a></span> entrepreneur, has officially emerged as the youngest self-made woman billionaire at 30 years old. Her stratospheric ascension dethrones global sensation Taylor Swift, who held the previous record at age 35 with a $1.6 billion net worth. With buzz surrounding Lacy Guo net worth 2025, the tech community is taking notice of this upstart powerhouse.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">But who is Lacy Guo, really? How did she accumulate these ginormous amounts of money before most people even bought their first house? Here\'s everything you need to know about Lacy Guo\'s net worth, her background, and the billion-dollar decisions that made her a household name.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Lacy Guo\'s Net Worth: The Billion-Dollar Breakdown</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Forbes estimates Lacy Guo\'s fortune at $1.25 billion. That is mostly on the strength of her original stake in Scale AI, a machine learning company she and <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/alexandrwang/\">Alexandr Wang</a></span> started in 2016. Even though she left the company in 2018, Guo smartly held onto about 5% of Scale AI\'s equity.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">That 5% holding is now worth hundreds of millions after a behemoth new deal giving the company a $25 billion valuation. According to Fortune, there is an ongoing tender offer that enables early investors and workers to sell some of their holdings. In the event of the deal going through, Lacy Guo net worth 2025 is on the agenda, with her paper wealth soaring&mdash;and that is without even considering her holdings in her second successful venture, Passes.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>How Lacy Guo Made Her Money</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://scale.com/\">Scale AI</a></span> was founded to label and curate data to train AI systems, a foundation in today\'s rapidly growing artificial intelligence ecosystem. The company\'s rise mirrors the AI boom, which has seen valuations across the industry balloon in recent years.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Although Guo departed Scale AI only two years after its co-founding, her initial investment has multiplied many times over. But she did not rest on her laurels.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">After Scale, Guo also co-founded Backend Capital, a venture capital company that invests in early-stage technology startups. She then also started Passes, a platform where content creators can monetize their content better. Passes has already established itself for providing tools best relevant to today\'s digital creators&mdash;i.e., YouTubers, influencers, and solo artists.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Guo&rsquo;s ability to spot high-potential trends early on&mdash;AI, creator economy, and venture capital&mdash;allowed her to build a diversified and scalable empire. Now, anyone who types Google for Lacy Guo will see her listed among the most influential names in the tech space.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Interesting Facts About Lacy Guo</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>College Dropout Tech Tycoon:</strong> Guo left Carnegie Mellon University, where she was studying computer science, to pursue her entrepreneurial dreams.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>Design Meets Code:</strong> At Scale AI, she was not a typical coder&mdash;she oversaw operations and product design, ensuring the company\'s software was not only functional but also user-friendly.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>On the Forbes Radar:</strong> She was included on the Forbes 30 Under 30 list in 2018, before she was 24.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>Keeping It Real:</strong> When asked if she cared that she was a billionaire, she texted Forbes: \"I don\'t think about it much, it\'s a little crazy. Too bad it\'s all paper haha.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>One of Six:</strong> Guo is one of just six women billionaires globally aged under 40&mdash;one of a very exclusive and highly select group.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Lacy Guo vs. Taylor Swift: Billionaire Battle</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">For years, Taylor Swift was the standard for women self-made billionaires under 40. With her music empire, tours, and shrewd business decisions, Swift reached a net worth of $1.6 billion at age 35.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">But Lacy Guo has now shattered the age record, becoming a billionaire five years ahead of schedule. Although Swift remains to have a higher net worth overall, Guo\'s early membership in the exclusive billionaire club has made her a new inspiration to tech-entrepreneurs globally.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The increasing searches for Lacy Guo net worth 2025 indicate how much interest and admiration she\'s gaining globally.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Why Lacy Guo Is a Name to Watch</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Lacy Guo\'s story is not one of high dollars. It\'s one of vision, timing, and tenacity. She saw AI when the world was scrambling to catch up. She left a successful company because of disagreements, not out of fear. And she didn\'t rest on her laurels&mdash;she started new companies and continued to innovate.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As the world becomes increasingly digital-first, Lacy Guo will be among the drivers of the future. As AI software becomes smarter, creator platforms soar, and venture capital invests in emerging tech frontiers, Guo is well-positioned to continue winning.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Lacy Guo, aged 30, is an AI entrepreneur who has just become the youngest self-made woman billionaire, surpassing Taylor Swift. With stakes in Scale AI and her firm Passes, her net worth is placed at $1.25 billion. Great choices, perfect timing, and a bold vision have turned her into a modern-day tech icon</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-04-22', '00:37:14', 'lacy-guo-net-worth-2025-tops-charts-beating-taylor-swift', 'article/visionaries-network-lacy-guo.webp', 'lacy guo youngest self-made woman billionaire at 30', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-lacy-guo.webp', 4, 2025, 'Lacy Guo, net worth 2025, richest celebrities, Taylor Swift, wealth ranking, celebrity earnings, billionaire, Forbes, financial success, entertainment industry, top earners, visionaries network, business, celebrity news, richest women', 'Lacy Guo&rsquo;s net worth in 2025 surpasses Taylor Swift, securing her place as the top-earning celebrity of the year and making financial history.', 1, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0),
(141, '', 'Inside Near-Zero Carbon 3D printed Homes of Texas', 'Inside Near-Zero Carbon 3D printed Homes of Texas', 'Beyond-Silicon-Valley', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Deep in the heart of Texas, something new and ambitious is being built&mdash;layer by sustainable layer. The future of houses is not a distant fantasy but a reality being built by green thinking, innovation, and robots. Welcome to the era of Near-Zero Carbon 3D-Printed Homes Texas, where sustainability and modern style converge.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As the climate changes accelerate and traditional construction methods fall behind sustainability goals, builders like <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.iconbuild.com/\">ICON</a></span> and <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.hive3dbuilders.com/\">Hive 3D Builders</a></span> are looking to new technologies to meet the times. With colossal 3D printers, <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/03/ai-powered-urban-mobility-solutions-transforming-european-cities-for-a-greener-future\">eco-friendly materials</a></span>, and intelligent design, these homes aren\'t just built&mdash;they\'re built for the future.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Why 3D-Printed Houses?</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">3D-printed homes have made global news for speed, cost, and capacity to cover housing shortages. In Texas, where growth is booming and the climate is severe, builders are thinking anew about building houses.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Instead of traditional wood framing, massive robotic arms pump out sheets of cement-like material to form durable, energy-efficient buildings. The robots employ digital blueprints to print walls in a matter of days, reducing labor and material waste dramatically.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">But beyond speed and expense reduction, the real innovation is what the homes are constructed of&mdash;and how businesses like ICON and <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://ecomaterial.com/\">Eco Material Technologies</a></span> are conceptualizing differently the blocks upon which the future will be constructed.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Green Materials Are Changing the Game</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Regular Portland cement is among the largest carbon emitters in the world, responsible for nearly 8% of all COâ‚‚ emissions. Visionaries Network introduces you to PozzoCEM Vite, a game-changing product from Eco Material Technologies that reduces those emissions by up to 92%.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This product is utilized in houses printed by Hive 3D Builders, the first company in Texas to engage in green building. PozzoCEM Vite is produced from industry waste products rather than limestone, reducing carbon emissions in production.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Through the use of energy-efficient design and renewable energy integration, these technologies render Near-Zero Carbon 3D-Printed Homes Texas a sustainable and scalable solution to climate change and housing shortages.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>The Casitas of The Halles: Round Top\'s Eco Oasis</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In Round Top, Texas, something special is being built by a partnership between Hive 3D Builders and Eco Material Technologies. Named The Casitas at The Halles, the project is composed of snug homes from 400 to 900 square feet that are affordable and green.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Made of carbon-reducing PozzoCEM Vite and structured to include smart-home technology and solar energy, these casitas prove that functionality and beauty can go hand-in-hand. With streamlined construction and lower material expenses, Hive 3D Builders is making these casitas available at price levels within the budgets of the ordinary Texan.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In a state where affordability usually clashes with green-friendly development, this community is a rare but welcome, win-win.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>ICON and Lennar: The Future in Georgetown</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">While Hive 3D Builders is leading the charge in Round Top, Austin-based company ICON has teamed up with national homebuilder Lennar and world-renowned architectural firm BIG (Bjarke Ingels Group) to construct the world\'s largest 3D-printed community in Georgetown, Texas.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This high-profile project at Wolf Ranch includes 100 homes printed on ICON\'s Vulcan industrial-grade robot printer and a custom compound called Lavacrete&mdash;engineered to be durable and long-lasting. The homes offer three to four bedrooms, luxury insulation, and solar-ready roofs.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As told by residents interviewed by The Cool Down, not only do the homes look wonderful, but they are also naturally cooler and more insulated than their conventional counterparts. \"The most energy-efficient home I\'ve ever lived in,\" one resident said.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This is not a future model&mdash;it\'s a thriving community, built for families, working professionals, and environmental consumers.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Why Texas Is Leading the Way</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Texas is in a prime position to lead the 3D-printed housing revolution. With plenty of land area, regulatory flexibility, and growing demand for affordable housing, the state offers an ideal proving ground for new construction technologies.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Severe weather events like heat waves and floods also require that homes be not only affordable but also resilient. The combination of strength, speed, and sustainability in these new homes is an appealing solution.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">And as ICON and Hive 3D Builders have demonstrated, Near-Zero Carbon 3D-Printed Homes Texas are not a trend&mdash;they\'re a blueprint for scalable, habitable, and climate-resilient communities.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Looking Ahead: A New Age of Construction</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">These developments in Georgetown and Round Top are just the start. ICON is working with NASA on space applications, in addition to constructing affordable housing for Austin\'s homeless. Hive 3D Builders, meanwhile, is pushing forward with their affordable, eco-friendly means of delivering green homes to even more Texans.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">And with the technology continuing to develop and with growing awareness, 3D-printed homes will be the norm across America. Conclusion: Texas Builds Smarter Texas has always been big-thinkin, and now it\'s smart-building.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Thanks to visionaries such as ICON, Hive 3D Builders, Lennar, and Eco Material Technologies, sustainable housing has a place in the real world in the Lone Star State.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As the intersection of climate challenges, affordability crises, and housing deficits becomes more ubiquitous, the solution may be arising from the ground up, layer by layer. And if the remainder of the country is listening, Near-Zero Carbon 3D-Printed Homes, Texas may soon be more than a local phenomenon&mdash;soon they might be a national standard.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'Visionaries NetworkVisionaries', '2025-04-22', '00:34:43', 'inside-texass-near-zero-carbon-3d-printed-homes', 'article/visionaries-network-inside-texas-near-zero-carbon-3d-printed-home.webp', 'Inside Texas&#039;s Near-Zero Carbon 3D-Printed Homes', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-inside-texas-near-zero-carbon-3d-printed-home.webp', 4, 2025, '3D-printed homes, Texas housing, sustainable homes, near-zero carbon, green building, eco-friendly construction, carbon neutral, renewable energy, smart homes, innovative housing, visionaries network, sustainable living, prefab homes, energy-efficient, future homes', 'Explore Texas&rsquo;s innovative 3D-printed homes built with near-zero carbon impact&mdash;leading the way in sustainable, affordable, and eco-friendly housing.', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0);
