(155, NULL, 'Zimbabwe Trade Fair Redevelopment Plans Revealed', 'Zimbabwe International Trade Fair Redevelopment Plans Unveiled', 'smart city and security infrastructure', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://zitf.co.zw/\">The Zimbabwe International Trade Fair (ZITF)</a></span> Company invited Expressions of Interest (EOIs) from qualified local and foreign companies to collaborate in the redevelopment of its site. Some of the proposed projects include the development of three-star or five-star hotels, a convention centre, an office block, and a theme park. The project is a landmark step towards the Zimbabwe International Trade Fair redevelopment.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>US$12 Million Investment Triggers Redevelopment Activities</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">ZITF has already secured a US$12 million development partner commitment for the construction of a new shopping centre. The investment shows great confidence in the future of the property and is a key milestone for the Zimbabwe International Trade Fair redevelopment. The shopping centre will be supported by other buildings to be developed, such as the convention centre and hotels, and will be part of an integrated business and leisure complex.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Prioritize Existing Firms for High-Profile Projects</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">ZITF is looking for companies with a minimum of 10 years\' experience in handling large-scale infrastructure projects. Companies wishing to execute the project should prove high technical and financial capability. ZITF, as indicated, reserves the right to accept or reject any or all EOIs and only shortlist companies to the next level on internal evaluation criteria. Suitable companies will be able to make a contribution to a project that will determine the fate of Bulawayo.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Progress Highlight at 65th Zimbabwe International Trade Fair</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">During the 65th Zimbabwe International Trade Fair in Bulawayo, <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/busisa-moyo-8b66361/?originalSubdomain=zw\">ZITF Company board chairman Mr. Busisa Moyo</a></span> outlined the work that had been done in spearheading redevelopment to date. He emphasized that the shopping centre, as well as the soon-to-be-opened international convention centre, are the epicentre of the grand vision. These new complexes could help put Zimbabwe on the map as a destination for international business events and exhibitions.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Renamed to Zimbabwe International Conference and Exhibition Smart City (ZICES)</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The vision of the grounds is to see it transform into the Zimbabwe International Conference and Exhibition Smart City (ZICES). The vision is to enhance technological advancement, green infrastructure, and urban development that is integrated. Zimbabwe International Trade Fair redevelopment forms part of the country\'s development to improve <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/03/amcham-korea-signs-landmark-mou-for-seamless-integration-into-us-infrastructure\">infrastructure</a></span> and drive economic development, making the grounds a business and tourist hub for Southern Africa.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Building Bulawayo\'s Business and Tourism Opportunities</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The new infrastructure would also enhance Bulawayo as a business and tourist hub. With a new convention center, upmarket hotels, and other recreational facilities, the city would be well-positioned to compete in international exhibitions, conferences, and tourist activities. The massive infrastructural push will bring in new investments, increase visitor arrivals, and create employment opportunities for local communities.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Theme Park to Acquire Leisure Attractions</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Among the exciting additions to look forward to on the site is a theme park. Not only will this provide entertainment to the visitors and residents alike, but it will also enhance the overall attraction of the <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/lg-cns-smart-city-hogansville-georgia-project-kicks-off\">Smart City</a></span>. By consolidating business districts and recreation, the redevelopment will amount to a vibrant, multi-purpose center for a wide range of audiences.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Contributing to National Goals of Sustainable Development</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Zimbabwe International Trade Fair redevelopment is also aligned with a broader national vision for sustainable development, innovation, and global competitiveness. The re-use of the land of the ZITF as a Smart City is aligned with Zimbabwe\'s Vision 2030 plan to achieve an upper-middle-income economy via new investment and infrastructure.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Vision for the Future </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Finally, the development of the Zimbabwe International Trade Fair is a progressive and strategic initiative to rebrand Bulawayo and Zimbabwe as the business, trade, and tourism center of the African continent.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Already, the key investments are in place, and plans for world-class facilities are in progress, and the outlook is bright. The ZITF Company\'s commitment to modernization will bear long-term fruits for the economy, society, and the nation\'s international image.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-04-28', '23:19:51', 'zimbabwe-trade-fair-redevelopment-plans-revealed', 'article/visionaries-network-zimbabwe-international-trade-fair-redevlopment.webp', 'Zimbabwe International Trade Fair Redevelopment Plans Unveiled', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-zimbabwe-international-trade-fair-redevlopment.webp', 4, 2025, 'Zimbabwe International Trade Fair, ZITF, redevelopment, infrastructure upgrade, trade fair, Zimbabwe economy, investment, exhibition center, economic growth, Bulawayo, visionaries network, business hub, regional trade, trade promotion, ZITF plans', 'Zimbabwe unveils major redevelopment plans for the International Trade Fair, aiming to boost trade, investment, and modernize infrastructure in Bulawayo.', 1, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0),
(156, '', 'Qatar Airways at ATM 2025 Travel Reinvented', 'Qatar Airways Arabian Travel Market 2025: Travel Reinvented', 'tourism and hospitality', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.qatarairways.com/en/homepage.html\">Qatar Airways</a></span> Arabian Travel Market 2025 exhibition set the bar high for the international aviation sector with a breathtaking display of cultural, technological, and luxury travel innovation. The five-star airline stole the show on the first day of <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.wtm.com/atm/en-gb.html\">ATM Dubai 2025</a></span> with a futuristic glimpse of the future of travel in the Arab world and beyond.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Sama: The First Arabic-Speaking AI Cabin Crew</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">One of the highlights of the Qatar Airways Arabian Travel Market 2025 experience was Sama, the globe\'s first AI-powered digital human cabin crew. Sama, now fully conversant in Modern Standard Arabic and also well-versed in a number of Arabic dialects, interacted with passengers in live conversations. She offered flight reservations, destination advice, and in-depth information on Qatar Airways\' award-winning products.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Sama\'s launch is a milestone for personalization and accessibility among Arabic-speaking travelers. Launched on Qatar Airways\' mobile app and the airline\'s interactive virtual reality platform, QVerse, Sama bears witness to Qatar Airways being a leader in digital innovation while being deeply rooted in the culture of the region.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>The ORCHARD in QVerse: Hamad International Airport Comes Alive</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Qatar Airways also welcomed guests to the ORCHARD in QVerse, a virtual reality simulation of the world-famous indoor garden in Hamad International Airport. Guests were able to virtually walk through the foliage, bask in the serene ambiance, and experience one of the airport\'s most recognizable zones without ever getting on a flight.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This immersive experience inside Qatar Airways\' Arabian Travel Market 2025 pavilion showcased the manner in which the airline is combining nature, technology, and hospitality in order to make travel more open and relaxed from the moment a journey commences.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>A New Era of Luxury: Next Gen Qsuite and the Multi-Sensory Pod </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Another major news was the launch of the Qsuite Next Gen, the second-generation version of Qatar Airways\' award-winning business class product. Passengers found enhanced personalisation features, added comfort, and creative privacy features in the reimagined Qsuite.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">To further bring the physical model to life, the airline unveiled a multi-sensory pod &mdash; an immersive experience that stimulated the senses of visitors through sight, smell, movement, and sound. The pod enabled visitors to fully envelop themselves in the Qsuite environment, providing a glimpse of the ultra-premium experience Qatar Airways passengers will enjoy in the near future.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Strategic Partnerships to Encourage Global Tourism</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Commercially, Qatar Airways marked major new Memoranda of Understanding (MoUs) with Visit Maldives and the <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://kemenparekraf.go.id/en\">Ministry of Tourism of Indonesia</a></span>. These agreements will bring more visitors through Doha\'s award-winning Hamad International Airport, tapping new leisure markets and solidifying Qatar as a global hub.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Commenting on the incident, Qatar Airways Group Chief Executive Officer Engr. Badr Mohammed Al-Meer said:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&ldquo;We at Qatar Airways are thrilled to be back at ATM with innovation that leads the industry in celebrating the spirit and diversity of our region. Sama, the globe\'s first AI cabin crew, now talks naturally to millions of Arabic-speaking travelers. Our ORCHARD in VR, our Qsuite Next Gen, and our multi-sensory pod are only a few examples of how Qatar Airways is creating a future that\'s not just digital, but human.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Conclusion </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With its bold vision and commitment to both innovation and human connection, Qatar Airways stole the show at the Qatar Airways Arabian Travel Market 2025. The airline\'s stunning combination of AI, immersive <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/xr-indie-flip-axis-studios-unveils-virtual-skate-for-quest-3\">VR</a></span>, <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2024/07/holiday-inn-revolutionizes-travel-and-hospitality\">luxury travel experiences</a></span>, and strategic collaborations reflects its leadership in the transformation of the aviation future. As the event wrapped up, one thing was certain: Qatar Airways is not only mapping out the future of travel &mdash; it\'s building it.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-04-28', '23:30:45', 'qatar-airways-at-atm-2025-travel-reinvented', 'article/visionaries-network-qatar-airways-arabian-travel-market.webp', 'Qatar Airways Arabian Travel Market 2025', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-qatar-airways-arabian-travel-market.webp', 4, 2025, 'Qatar Airways, ATM 2025, Arabian Travel Market, travel reinvented, aviation, tourism, visionaries network, luxury, Middle East, flights, global travel, Doha, airline, expo, business', 'Discover how Qatar Airways is redefining global travel at Arabian Travel Market 2025 with innovation, luxury, and world-class service.', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(157, NULL, 'Walmart Resumes China Shipments Amid Tariff Pressures', 'Walmart China Shipments Resume Amid Tariff Pressures', 'retail and ecommerce', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In a breakthrough that promises relief to world supply chains, Walmart China shipments resume after weeks of trade tension between the world\'s two largest economies.&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.walmart.com/\">Walmart</a></span>, as reported by SCMP, has requested several Chinese suppliers to resume shipping merchandise to the United States.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This report comes as <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/03/china-manufacturing-sector-faces-challenges-amid-trade-tensions\">tensions between the U.S. and China trade escalate</a></span>. The President Donald Trump administration recently placed steep tariffs, some up to 245%, on a wide range of Chinese imports. The tariffs, which started in early April 2025, led many American companies to suspend Chinese orders temporarily for cost-related reasons.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">One of Ningbo, Zhejiang province\'s largest office supplies exporters, reported being told by Walmart last week to resume normal shipments. The same directive has been issued to Jiangsu suppliers and other primary manufacturing regions in China. The move is seen as a tactical move by US retailers to stock up ahead of the summer sales season.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Tariffs and Changing Trade Practices</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With tariff uncertainty, the majority of exporters have adjusted their business models. Chinese suppliers are more and more transitioning from Delivered Duty Paid (DDP) terms to Free on Board (FOB) pricing. This allows U.S. importers to take responsibility for tariff handling and customs clearance through their own brokers, giving them more control in managing regulatory changes.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">A worldwide supplier of garment hangers and packaging reported that U.S. customers began requesting Chinese manufacturers to resume shipments as early as April 23. Walmart China shipments resume news has been creating a ripple effect, as other big-box stores followed to reduce the risk of stock shortages.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Interestingly, Chinese exporters have indicated that US buyers are paying the cost of the new tariffs themselves to a great extent, easing the pressure on Chinese firms and increasing the chances of them continuing to export despite the increased duties.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Retail Giants Warn of Empty-Shelf Woes</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Walmart and Target have reportedly been outspoken in warning the Trump administration of the negative effects of prolonged tariffs. Both CEOs have asserted that the ongoing trade war can lead to global product shortages and push prices higher for ordinary consumers.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The retailers made behind-closed-doors sessions with U.S. officials in an attempt to bring attention to the economic and logistics burden imposed by the new tariffs, CBS News reports. As a response, the White House is reportedly considering a working group to examine the supply chain disruptions and inflation threats of the dispute.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Trump has since hinted at the possible reduction of tariff levels, informing Time magazine in an interview that he had phoned Chinese President Xi Jinping to talk of reducing the trade war. Beijing did not, however, confirm the fact of the direct phone call, although it expressed willingness to negotiate&mdash;on the basis of negotiations being conducted on equal terms.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Why It Matters to Smaller Importers</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Walmart China shipments resume is back in balance is welcome news for multinationals retailing in the United States&mdash;but potentially also for medium and smaller-sized American importers. As China-U.S. shipping dynamics firm up, smaller businesses might find more stable rates for logistics costs as well as improved container availability.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Besides, the move to FOB pricing provides such smaller companies greater leeway to deal with tariffs and simplify customs clearance, which is ever more precious in a volatile trade environment. With Chinese manufacturers ramping up production and U.S. retailers in need of restocking, the resumption of shipments is viewed as a cautious but welcome step toward the revival of the U.S.-China trade relationship&mdash;at least on the retail and shipping fronts.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-04-29', '00:01:22', 'walmart-china-shipments-resume-amid-tariff-pressures', 'article/visionaries-network-wallmart-china-us-shipment-terrif.webp', 'Walmart China Shipments Resume Amid Tariff Pressures', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-wallmart-china-us-shipment-terrif.webp', 4, 2025, 'Walmart, China shipments, tariff pressures, US-China trade, supply chain, logistics, retail, visionaries network, cost-cutting, diversification, India imports, trade tensions, sourcing, logistics centers, Walmart suppliers', 'Walmart resumes shipments from China despite tariff pressures, aiming to stabilize supply chains and maintain product availability amid trade tensions.', 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0),
(158, '', 'Kiyosaki Predicts 2025 Great Depression | Explained', 'Robert Kiyosaki Great Depression 2025 Prediction Explained', 'blockchain and cryptocurrency', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In an April 18, 2025 X (formerly Twitter) post recently, personal finance writer&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/robert-kiyosaki-46b532145/\">Robert Kiyosaki</a></span> issued a grim warning: America might be headed toward an economic crisis more dire than the Great Depression of the 1930s. No exaggeration. The signs he cites &mdash; from record-high debt to rising joblessness &mdash; are true and disturbing. His \"Great Depression 2025 prediction\" is getting serious attention.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Economic Red Flags Are All Around</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Let\'s take a look at the numbers. Americans now have a record $1.21 trillion in credit card debt, according to the Federal Reserve Bank of New York. At the same time, the U.S. national debt has grown to $36.22 trillion, with worries about long-term fiscal health.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Meanwhile, the labor market is deteriorating. The unemployment rate rose to 4.2% in March 2025, and many workers are facing dwindling 401(k) balances because of market volatility.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Kiyosaki is convinced these trends signify more than a recession &mdash; he is concerned there will be a long, ugly downturn. The Robert Kiyosaki Great Depression 2025 prediction lays out the possibility that this crash is going to be more disastrous than even the infamous 1930s financial collapse.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\"This coming Great Depression will make millions poor&hellip; and a few who act will be very rich and free,\" Kiyosaki cautioned.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Kiyosaki&rsquo;s Solution? Assets That Are Outside the System</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Unlike stodgy financial planners of the past, Kiyosaki is not suggesting weathering the storm in a basket of stocks and bonds. Instead, he appears to favor precious metals like gold and silver &mdash; assets not beholden to national currency or central banks.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Kiyosaki has quoted bullish price targets that represent his long-term bullishness:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo3;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Bitcoin: $1 million a coin by 2035</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo3;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Gold: $30,000 an ounce</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo3;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Silver: $3,000 per coin</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Though these figures may seem extreme, they\'re repeated by other optimistic voices. Twitter co-founder Jack Dorsey and <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/catherinedwood/\">ARK Invest CEO Cathie Wood</a></span> have both forecast that Bitcoin will reach or surpass $1 million in the next decade.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Gold Is Already Rising Rapidly </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Kiyosaki\'s gold philosophy isn\'t conjecture &mdash; it\'s fact. Near the end of 2023, he predicted gold going over $2,100 an ounce. In April 2025, gold sits at around $3,300, well on its way to its further-down-the-road target of $3,700 or more.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Gold has long been a haven, and global turmoil in recent years has caused demand to hit record highs. Hedge fund legend Ray Dalio stated in February, \"When bad times come, gold is a very effective diversifier.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Investors can now buy gold in several forms:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo4;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Physical coins and bars</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo4;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Gold-backed ETFs</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo4;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Equity in mining companies</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo4;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Tax-Favored Gold IRAs</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Bitcoin 2025: Unpredictable but Promising</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/bitcoin-price-after-trump-news-boosts-crypto-market-sentiment\">Bitcoin</a></span> remains a contentious investing topic. It temporarily broke through the $100,000 level in December 2024 before it reversed. Kiyosaki is unfazed, however, proclaiming this only the beginning of its growth.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Robert Kiyosaki prediction of the Great Depression in 2025 has its roots, in part, in Bitcoin being a major store of value when faith in fiat currencies declines. Experts in the field concur, with Dorsey and Wood both forecasting seven-figure prices for Bitcoin in the 2030&ndash;2035 timeframe.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">For beginners to cryptocurrency, it has never been easier to buy Bitcoin with:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Crypto exchanges like Coinbase and Binance</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Bitcoin ETFs in brokerage accounts</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Bitcoin ATMs (with varying fees)</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>How to Prepare for What\'s Ahead</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">While nobody can predict the exact timing of a crash, most agree that the system is under pressure. The smart thing to do? Prepare ahead of time.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This is what financial thought leaders such as Kiyosaki suggest:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Spread your investments outside stocks and bonds</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Hold inflation-proof assets like gold, silver, and Bitcoin</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Pay off debt, especially high-interest credit card debt</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Keep pace with market risk and emerging investment products. The Robert Kiyosaki Great Depression 2025 prediction might be over-the-top to some, but history has shown that financial systems can and do fail. Whether the next recession is mild or doomsday, action now can protect your wealth later.</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-04-30', '00:30:07', 'robert-kiyosaki-great-depression-2025-prediction-explained', 'article/visionaries-network-robert-keyosaki-great-depression-2025.webp', 'Robert Kiyosaki Great Depression 2025 Prediction Explained', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-robert-keyosaki-great-depression-2025.webp', 4, 2025, 'Robert Kiyosaki, 2025 prediction, Great Depression, economy, crash, financial crisis, inflation, recession, visionaries network, markets, rich dad, investing, gold, dollar collapse, economic forecast', 'Robert Kiyosaki warns of a Great Depression in 2025. Discover the reasons behind his prediction and what it could mean for the global economy.', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(159, NULL, 'Crawley MBST for Hand &amp; Foot Pain Relief', 'Relieve Hand &amp; Foot Pain with Crawley MBST for Small Joints', 'healthcare and medical devices', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In a non-invasive joint breakthrough,&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.chiropractic-uk.com/crawley\">Crawley Spinal Health</a></span> has launched a <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://mbstmedical.co.uk/\">Magnetic Resonance Therapy (MBST)</a></span> for the smaller joints of the hands, feet, and ankles. This is the clinic\'s first treatment of this focused therapy &mdash; opening up new hope for those needing relief from pain without surgery or drugs.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>A New Chapter in Non-Surgical Joint Therapy</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Treatment has been available since 25 April 2025 and is for arthritis, fracture, sprained ligaments, and other degenerative and traumatic conditions of smaller joints. The addition is a significant move for the clinic to enhance the availability of <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/03/apple-watch-upgrade-set-to-transform-wearables-by-2027\">cutting-edge technology</a></span> previously only available at their Horley partner clinic, which is focused on the treatment of the spine, hip, and knee.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Crawley Spinal Health MBST for small joints uses targeted magnetic fields to enhance the body\'s own healing responses. By accelerating cell regeneration of cartilage, tendons, ligaments, and bone, MBST promotes natural healing, significantly diminishing pain and inflammation.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Why is MBST special?</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">MBST is a fully non-surgical treatment. In contrast to surgery or steroid injections, MBST treatments are not painful, do not involve recovery time, and are free of the side effects of traditional treatments. The treatment is already widely used among the best European athletes for speeding up the healing of injuries, but is now becoming more popular for general practice.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\"We\'ve had wonderful outcomes for treating back, knee, and hip issues with MBST,\" said <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/philip-mitchell-635a9153/\">Crawley Spinal Health Clinical Director Philip Mitchell</a></span>. \"Patients would occasionally ask if we could treat their hands or feet. Now, with this new machine, we can say yes &mdash; and our own son, who\'s just broken his ankle, will be the first to benefit. That\'s like the ultimate start.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Adjusting to an Evolving Healthcare Environment</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As of January 2025, 7.43 million individuals in the UK remain on the NHS waiting lists. While the figures are better, a great many patients are still waiting for long periods of time. This has created a mounting need for private treatment: in Q3 of 2024 alone, 223,000 admissions were made to private hospitals &mdash; a 1% rise on the same quarter of 2023.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With Crawley Spinal Health MBST for small joints, the clinic is riding this trend. The fact that it can offer surgery-free, drug-free treatment is appealing to a wide cross-section of individuals, from older adults with osteoarthritis to injured young athletes.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Real-Life Outcomes Without Surgery</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The benefits of MBST are already apparent at Crawley Spinal Health. Mitchell had a number of success stories:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><em>&ldquo;We\'ve watched grandparents return to gardening, teenagers return to their school athletic teams, and people delay planned surgery because MBST provided them with the relief they were searching for. It\'s a game changer.&rdquo;</em></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This clinic is now providing free consultations for the purpose of piloting whether MBST is suitable on a case-by-case basis with each patient. This entails the serious examination of joint status, general medical history, and individualized treatment planning.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>The Future of Joint Care Local </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With the addition of Crawley Spinal Health MBST for small joints, patients in Crawley can now take advantage of one of Europe\'s most state-of-the-art treatments. It provides an alternative to the intrusive process of conventional medical procedures and an even quicker and safer way to recovery.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Whether you\'re coping with arthritis in your fingers, recovering from a foot injury, or simply tired of chronic joint pain, this new therapy could be just the relief you\'re seeking &mdash; right in the heart of Crawley.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-04-30', '00:41:10', 'crawley-mbst-for-hand-foot-pain-relief', 'article/visionaries-network-relieve-hand-foot-pain-with-crawley.webp', 'Relieve Hand &amp; Foot Pain with Crawley MBST for Small Joints', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-relieve-hand-foot-pain-with-crawley.webp', 4, 2025, 'MBST therapy, hand pain, foot pain, Crawley, small joints, arthritis, joint pain, non-invasive, therapy, regenerative treatment, pain relief, visionaries network, stiffness, physiotherapy, UK clinics', 'Discover how MBST therapy in Crawley offers effective, non-invasive relief for hand and foot pain in small joints.', 1, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0),
(160, '', 'Pay10 Launches UAE&rsquo;s First Live Open Finance Platform', 'Pay10 Leads UAE with First Live Open Finance Launch', 'banking and fintech', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://pay10.com/\">Pay10</a></span>, a rising fintech leader, has made headlines as the first company to go live on the Central Bank of the UAE&rsquo;s Open Finance Framework. This marks the debut of regulated Open Finance infrastructure in the UAE&mdash;surpassing all other <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/03/smartbiz-becomes-first-fintech-bank-approved-under-trump\">banks and fintechs</a></span>&mdash;giving Pay10 a significant head start in the rapidly evolving alternative payments market.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Based in the UAE, Pay10 is a Business Alternative Payment Method (APM) solutions company that offers innovative payment solutions to businesses. With the latest development, the company is now officially licensed to provide payment initiation services, such as the highly anticipated variable recurring payments.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This milestone is not only a company achievement &mdash; it\'s a breakthrough for the UAE fintech sector. By going live on the Open Finance platform, Pay10 is setting a new standard in digital finance and cementing its place as a regulatory innovation leader.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This is Pay10\'s third regulatory license in the UAE. It already has Retail Payment Services and Card Schemes (RPSCS) and Stored Value Facilities (SVF) licenses. Adding Open Finance to its platform is a powerful reinforcement of strengths that allows Pay10 to deliver an end-to-end digital, interoperable financial experience.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>What It Means for the UAE</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The UAE Central Bank launched the Open Finance Regulation in mid-2024 to boost secure, open access to consumer financial data by authorized third-party providers. It is one of the pillars of the country\'s digital economy initiative, which aims to extend financial inclusion, data openness, and innovation.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">However, although Pay10 is the initial one to be launched, the true potential of Open Finance will be realized when other banking players come on board. As the integrations are completed, businesses and consumers will be able to benefit from faster payments, better financial tools, and better access to tailored services.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/prabhpreet-singh-harry-gill-41852728b/\">Prabhpreet Singh Gill, Pay10 Chairman</a></span>, explained:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\"To be the first fintech to go live in production on the Open Finance framework is an honor and a duty. We believe in the importance of setting a standard&mdash;operationally, technically, and in governance&mdash;for others to build upon.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Gill further stated that the licence presents new opportunities for embedded finance, digital identity authentication, and financial institution interoperability without friction.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Why the Pay10 Milestone Matters</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With this regulatory go-ahead, it now possesses all three core authorisations that are applicable in the UAE\'s digital finance landscape. Its first-mover benefit in Open Finance puts it on a path to become a significant player not only regionally, but across the Middle East and emerging markets too. As the UAE looks to become a digital finance hub, Pay10\'s pioneering step shows what can be achieved when regulation and innovation walk together.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\">&nbsp;</span></p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-04-30', '23:32:22', 'pay10-leads-uae-with-first-live-open-finance-launch', 'article/visionaries-network-pay10-leads-uae-with-first-live-open-finace-app.webp', 'Pay10 Leads UAE with First Live Open Finance Launch', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-pay10-leads-uae-with-first-live-open-finace-app.webp', 4, 2025, 'Pay10, Open Finance, UAE fintech, digital banking, finance launch, API, visionaries network, payments, UAE, fintech, live launch, open banking, financial technology, money transfer, Pay10 UAE', 'Pay10 leads innovation in UAE with the nation&#039;s first live open finance platform, transforming digital payments and banking services.', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(161, NULL, 'Microsoft Backs EU Digital Markets Act Compliance', 'Microsoft Digital Markets Act response supports EU law compliance', 'legal and regulatory compliance', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In a sweeping gesture of transatlantic tech diplomacy,&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/bradsmi/\">Microsoft President Brad Smith</a></span> reaffirmed the company\'s commitment to European regulation. Addressing Brussels, Smith announced Microsoft \"has long respected and complied with European laws&mdash;even when we\'ve lost cases in European courts.\" The visit is taking place against a backdrop of higher levels of regulatory scrutiny and tensions between the United States and the European Union.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The remarks came after the European Commission had charged hefty fines, fining Apple &euro;500 million and Meta &euro;200 million over violations of the Digital Markets Act (DMA). The response by former U.S. President Donald Trump came by way of a threat to use retaliatory tariffs, terming the EU action as \"overseas extortion.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Steering clear of US Tech Lobbying</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-in?msockid=2aad64c6e205683d3ed37785e3f26953\">Microsoft</a></span> took a different approach to the more confrontational approach taken by some American companies and politicians. While the White House has labeled the EU\'s regulatory approach as anti-U.S. technology, Smith reacted tactfully. \"We understand that European regulations govern our business practices in Europe, just as local regulations govern in the United States,\" he wrote in introducing Microsoft\'s five digital commitments to Europe.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">One of the greatest advantages of this proposal is Microsoft\'s alignment with the DMA, which is intended to foster fairness, transparency, and accountability in the digital environment. The company\'s reaction to the Microsoft Digital Markets Act response is being read far and wide as an attempt to lead by example and position itself as a reliable digital partner in Europe.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Massive Infrastructure Investment to Underpin Commitments</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Backing its talk with action, Microsoft announced it would grow its European <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/google-cloud-next-2025-unveils-smarter-ai-tools-and-chips\">cloud</a></span> infrastructure. Over the next two years, it will add 40% datacenter capacity in 16 countries in Europe. It will have over 200 datacenters in the region by 2027&mdash;a total investment of tens of billions of dollars.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This growth is not just a business strategy&mdash;it\'s also Microsoft\'s effort to be part of the European digital fabric. \"We are not only dedicated to building digital infrastructure for Europe, but to respecting the role that European laws play in governing our products and services,\" Smith emphasized.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Maintaining Sovereignty and Securing Information</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">One of the highlights of the Microsoft Digital Markets Act response is a pledge of European digital sovereignty. Smith promised that if Microsoft is ever requested by a foreign government to temporarily suspend services in Europe, it will \"immediately and vigorously challenge such action.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">To further promote confidence, Microsoft has launched a new \"European Digital Resilience Commitment.\" It will be legally binding and included in agreements with national governments and the European Commission, thus offering confidence and legal certainty.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>A Bridge, Not a Battleground </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Smith ended by saying, \"We are at a moment in time when business needs to be a bridge across the Atlantic.\" By doing so, he was framing Microsoft as a stabilizing presence in the face of increasing transatlantic tensions.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Microsoft Digital Markets Act response can ultimately become an example for global technology businesses to operate in regulatory-heavy ecosystems without tension. By positioning itself in alignment with European values and legal systems, Microsoft is not just defending its business interests but also increasing its profile as a responsible technology leader.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-04-30', '23:39:30', 'microsoft-digital-markets-act-response-supports-eu-law-compliance', 'article/visionaries-network-microsoft-digital-markets-law-compliances.webp', 'Microsoft Digital Markets Act response supports EU law compliance', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-microsoft-digital-markets-law-compliances.webp', 4, 2025, 'Microsoft, Digital Markets Act, EU law, compliance, tech regulation, DMA, antitrust, visionaries network, Europe, big tech, competition law, digital regulation, Microsoft EU, DMA response, EU compliance', 'Microsoft affirms its support for the EU&#039;s Digital Markets Act, pledging full compliance with new digital competition and transparency regulations.', 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0);
