(162, NULL, 'Nozomi Networks to Lead Cybersecurity at GISEC 2025', 'Nozomi Networks GISEC 2025 Set to Lead Cybersecurity Conversation', 'iot-and-robotics', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.nozominetworks.com/\">Nozomi Networks</a></span> GISEC 2025 will be one of the main attractions of the GISEC Global event between May 6-8 at the Dubai World Trade Center. As a global OT (Operational Technology) and <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/mtn-powers-the-future-of-smart-city-south-africa-with-iot-tech\">IoT</a></span> (Internet of Things) cybersecurity innovator, Nozomi Networks will showcase its cutting-edge solutions aimed at protecting critical infrastructure in IT, OT, and IoT environments.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>What to Look for from Nozomi Networks at GISEC 2025</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Attendees at GISEC 2025 will see firsthand the power of Nozomi Networks\' converged <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/ms-cyber-attack-halts-online-orders-in-uk-and-ireland\">cybersecurity</a></span> platform. The solutions provide security professionals with single-pane-of-glass visibility, real-time threat detection, and compliance simplified. As digital transformation accelerates in industries like energy, utilities, and manufacturing, security has never been more critical.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Significant innovations to be showcased at Nozomi Networks GISEC 2025 are:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>Nozomi Arc:</strong> Extending visibility to industrial endpoints, this feature helps eliminate security blind spots on expansive OT networks.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>Guardian Air:</strong> An RF-level visibility threat detection system, Guardian Air provides wireless coverage where rogue devices might hide.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>Vantage IQ:</strong> Vantage IQ applies machine learning to speed up detection and automate incident triage, so teams can react faster and smarter.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Partnership to Success: Nozomi Networks and HelpAG</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Nozomi Networks\' GISEC visibility goes beyond product demonstrations. Nozomi will be co-exhibiting with HelpAG, one of the region\'s leading cybersecurity partners. They will be showcasing real-world deployments and integrated solutions uniquely designed for Middle Eastern organizations.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Their co-exhibiting approach is symptomatic of Nozomi\'s \"partner-first\" approach, designed to deliver localized care and better outcomes for customers. \"Middle Eastern critical infrastructure is becoming more exposed through interdependent systems and growing cyber threats,\" added <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/bachirmoussa/\">Bachir Moussa, AVP EMEA at Nozomi Networks</a></span>. \"We\'re demonstrating here at GISEC how our AI-driven platform protects against physical, virtual, and wireless environments &mdash; backed by strong regional partnerships like the one with HelpAG.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Where to Meet Nozomi Networks and HelpAG at GISEC 2025</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Visitors may also meet the team at Booth F62 in Hall 2, where cybersecurity experts and engineers will offer live demos and consultations. The HelpAG team will also be present at Booth B90 in Hall 7 for further details about their combined deployments and services.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Nozomi Network Industry Awards</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Nozomi Networks is still a cybersecurity leader. The organization was recently named a Leader in the Forrester Wave&trade;: OT Security Solutions Q2 2024, and part of the first-ever Gartner&reg; Magic Quadrant&trade; for Cyber-Physical Systems Protection Platforms.</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-05-02', '00:02:09', 'nozomi-networks-gisec-2025-set-to-lead-cybersecurity-conversation', 'article/visionaries-netwrok-nozomi-networks-gisec-2025-leads-cyber-security.webp', 'Nozomi Networks GISEC 2025 Set to Lead Cybersecurity Conversation', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-netwrok-nozomi-networks-gisec-2025-leads-cyber-security.webp', 5, 2025, 'Nozomi Networks, GISEC 2025, cybersecurity, cyber defense, ICS security, OT security, threat detection, network security, industrial cybersecurity, cyber threats, digital safety, GISEC Dubai, visionaries network, cybersecurity leader, cyber solutions', 'Nozomi Networks takes center stage at GISEC 2025, driving key cybersecurity discussions and showcasing advanced threat detection solutions.', 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0),
(163, NULL, 'GR Digital Marketing Launches New Growth Agency', 'GR Digital Marketing Opens New Agency for Online Growth', 'brand management digital marketing and business', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.grdigitalmarketing.com/\">GR Digital Marketing</a></span> is&nbsp;thrilled&nbsp;to announce the launch of&nbsp;its&nbsp;brand&nbsp;new <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2024/11/digital-marketing-agency-collaborates-marketer\">digital marketing</a></span> agency located&nbsp;in the USA. The&nbsp;firm&nbsp;specializes in&nbsp;core&nbsp;services&nbsp;that&nbsp;help businesses grow online, including Pay-Per-Click (PPC) advertising on Google and other&nbsp;search engines, ADA website compliance, and Conversion Rate Optimization (CRO).&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">GR&nbsp;Digital Marketing was established&nbsp;by founder Grayson Robinson&nbsp;and&nbsp;is built on a&nbsp;solid&nbsp;foundation of&nbsp;relationships,&nbsp;strategic&nbsp;planning, and a commitment to delivering real, measurable results.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The agency is led by founder Grayson Robinson, who discovered the strength of digital strategy early on in his career. His first-hand experience via internships and real-world projects allowed him to develop an intimate understanding of the industry&mdash;breaking algorithms to running high-converting ad campaigns. That knowledge now powers the mission of his agency: to offer easy digital marketing solutions that are transparent, effective, and created to drive measurable success.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&ldquo;It is important to us that our client is successful and thrives,\" said <span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/grayson-robinson-5b8a711a7/\">Grayson Robinson, Founder at GR Digital Marketing.</a></span> \"We are results-driven, but above all, people-driven. Each campaign, audit, or optimization we perform is goal-driven by the client.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Personalized Online Marketing for Real Results</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">GR Digital Marketing provides three main services dedicated to addressing the most important points of a business\'s online success:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>1. Pay-Per-Click (PPC) Advertising</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With Google PPC campaigns and other leading platforms, the agency helps clients drive high-quality traffic. By conducting rigorous keyword research and constant performance optimization, GR Digital Marketing gets every ad dollar to work as hard as possible. From ad copywriting to analytics, they do it all to enable business owners to focus on what they do best.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>2. ADA Website Compliance</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Accessibility is now more crucial than ever. The firm offers full ADA compliance services so that client sites become WCAG 2.1 compliant. This not only protects businesses from legal risk but also improves the experience of disabled users, making their brand more powerful and expanding their reach to more people.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>3. Conversion Rate Optimization (CRO)</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Traffic is only the beginning&mdash;turning that traffic into customers is what matters. By using A/B testing, analysis of user behavior, and continuous site optimization, the agency is constantly refining each stage of the customer journey. These strategic optimizations result in more engagement, better user retention, and more revenue.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Why \"Easy Digital Marketing USA\" Matters</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Small and medium-sized businesses find it challenging to break through the din of online competition. GR Digital Marketing offers a smoother, more affordable path to victory. The strategy of the agency is based on transparency, clear communication, and data-driven decisions that make the digital process easy to understand.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Grayson\'s leadership is more about support and clarity and less about gimmicks and buzzwords. Their company slogan, \"Growing your business, one meaningful connection at a time,\" speaks to their customer-centric focus.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Designed for Entrepreneurs Willing to Grow </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Whether you are an independent business owner or a company ready to grow, this new USA-based agency is at your service. With adaptable service models and customer-first thinking, the team provides smart solutions minus the fluff.</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-05-02', '00:08:55', 'gr-digital-marketing-opens-new-agency-for-online-growth', 'article/visionaries-network-gr-digital-marketing-opens-new-agency.webp', 'GR Digital Marketing Launches New Growth Agency', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-gr-digital-marketing-opens-new-agency.webp', 5, 2025, 'GR Digital Marketing, new agency, online growth, digital strategy, SEO, PPC, content marketing, branding, social media, web development, lead generation, marketing agency, visionaries network, digital growth, marketing services', 'GR Digital Marketing unveils a new agency focused on driving online growth through digital strategies, SEO, and targeted marketing services.', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(164, NULL, 'Xcel Brands Gets $9M UTG Boost for Global Expansion', 'Xcel Brands Secures $9M UTG Investment for Global Expansion', 'brand management digital marketing and business', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As a part of a strategic push to drive international growth,&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.xcelbrands.com/\">Xcel Brands</a></span> has closed a $9 million equity investment with United Trademark Group (UTG), a Shanghai-based brand-building and licensing firm. The bold move is the latest push internationally by the New York-based company best known for building celebrities and influencers into scalable social commerce brands.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This transaction unites two social commerce, <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/toyota-teams-up-with-o9-to-boost-supply-chain-efficiency\">supply chain</a></span>, and brand management leaders,\" said <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/robert-d-loren-b5490240/\">Robert W. D\'Loren, Xcel Chairman and CEO</a></span>. \"We\'ve been seeking an international partner, and UTG accomplishes that, particularly with their European, Middle Eastern, and Asian presence.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>A Global Alliance of Strategic Scope</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">UTG, a $2 billion firm with strong distribution channels and a master license to distribute Jeep apparel in China, will provide Xcel with operating size and global logistics to grow. The investment also helps Xcel to refinance debt and build working capital.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">George Liu, UTG co-founder, had also voiced tremendous resonance with the mission of Xcel: \"We believe there is huge synergy here. Social commerce is huge in China, and we think Xcel\'s content model is the wave of the future. We also have great supply chain expertise, which we think will further enhance their operations.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Liu also indicated that UTG sees this as a long-term partnership: \"This isn\'t a one-off deal. We\'re looking to potentially acquire and build brands up together.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Influencer-Led Brand Portfolio Grows</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Xcel Brands is in the business of creating brands around family names. It owns or operates Halston, Judith Ripka, C. Wonder, and Tower Hill by Christie Brinkley. The company also has interests in Isaac Mizrahi and video commerce platform Orme Live. Xcel also owns the Longaberger home brand through Longaberger Licensing LLC.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Recent product launches demonstrate the firm\'s focus on accessing creator economies:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Cesar Millan\'s \"Trust-Respect-Love\" pet line, launching Spring 2026</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->A bakeware brand with chef Gemma Stafford, her debut product line, is also launching in Spring 2026</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Food and cookware line by Latina influencer Jenny Martinez, debuting Fall 2025</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">D\'Loren went on, \"This week we hit 40 million followers across our portfolio of brands. We\'re targeting 100 million by the end of 2026.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Supply Chain, Tariffs, and Future Outlook</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As it\'s a brand manager rather than a maker, Xcel Brands has overseas partners in Pakistan, China, and Turkey to manufacture. Although foreign tariffs might increase cost, D\'Loren stated they\'re well-positioned: \"We have sufficient inventory to weather short-term disruption, most notably in categories like jewellery.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Having visited China, D\'Loren stated that diversified sourcing is practiced by QVC, an important sales partner. \"Our risk is contained. We expect a great deal of global trade agreements to settle out over the next 90 to 120 days.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>Financial Update: Streamlining for Profitability</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Xcel\'s most recent data reveal a patchy picture:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Revenue in the nine months through Sept. 30 fell 54% to $7.1 million, primarily due to the exit from the wholesale segment under its \"Project Fundamentals\" reset</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Net loss was $15.3 million, up from $14.3 million in the prior period</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Adjusted EBITDA loss decreased to $2.7 million from $4.6 million, demonstrating cost discipline improvement</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">These findings point towards a leaner but more strategically concentrated business model.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Vision for the Future </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/alex-chengjin-wang-96135721/\">Alex Wang, chairman and cofounder of UTG</a></span>, captured the enthusiasm for the alliance: \"By merging our international experience with Xcel\'s social commerce capabilities, we\'re creating huge opportunities. We\'re going to create the next generation of great brands together.\" With UTG on board and new influencer-led products in the works, Xcel Brands seems to be on its way to becoming a top player in the international consumer market.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-05-02', '00:15:28', 'xcel-brands-secures-9m-utg-investment-for-global-expansion', 'article/visionaries-network-xcel-brands-secures-9m-utg-investment.webp', 'Xcel Brands Secures $9M UTG Investment for Global Expansion', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-xcel-brands-secures-9m-utg-investment.webp', 5, 2025, 'Xcel Brands, UTG investment, global expansion, fashion, retail growth, brand strategy, funding, apparel, lifestyle, $9M funding, investor support, business growth, visionaries networkt, UTG partnership, international markets', 'Xcel Brands secures a $9 million investment from UTG, fueling its global expansion plans and brand development strategy across fashion and lifestyle markets.', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(165, NULL, 'KFin Technologies Launches KRA, Advancing Digital KYC', 'KFin Technologies KRA Launch Marks Digital KYC Breakthrough', 'blockchain and cryptocurrency', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The stock of&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.kfintech.com/\">KFin Technologies Limited</a></span> was at â‚¹1,149.10, losing â‚¹48.50 or 4.05 per cent on the NSE today at 12:02 PM. The decline followed after the company announced the launch of KFIN KRA, a next-generation KYC Registration Agency, designed by its wholly owned subsidiary, KFin Services Private Limited.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The KFin Technologies KRA launch is a major move by the <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../magazine/profile/singlestone-transforming-financial-services-insurance-government-with-data-innovation-analytics-ai-modern-technology\">financial services</a></span> behemoth to drive India\'s digital onboarding infrastructure with next-generation technology. The new platform takes advantage of the power of blockchain and will make investors\' identity verification processes simpler. Providing a single, secure, and seamless Know Your Customer (KYC) experience, KFIN KRA aims to eliminate redundancies and enhance user experience across the board.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>What sets KFIN KRA apart</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Unlike the slow and disjointed legacy KYC systems, KFIN KRA is constructed on a <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/03/crypto-etfs-approved-wall-streets-biggest-bet-on-blockchain-stocks-yet\">blockchain</a></span> platform to guarantee data integrity and transparency. Additionally, it has AI-based verification capabilities to speed up onboarding and avoid fraud. Among some of the most significant features of the platform are:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Completely digital investor onboarding</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Integration with CKYC (Central KYC)</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Safe authentication via DigiLocker and eAadhaar</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Real-time status and alert information</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Ease-of-use registration, renewal, and document download capabilities</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">They enable financial services companies to save processing time, eliminate document duplication, and enhance compliance &mdash; key requirements in India\'s fast-expanding fintech sector.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Leadership Comments on the Launch</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Sreekanth Nadella, CEO and MD, KFin Technologies, said again that the company\'s vision is to ease regulatory compliance for all. \"Our goal is to enable ease of business as well as digitalisation of financial ecosystem. Through KFin Technologies KRA launch, we are providing an end-to-end digital KYC solution which is ready for the future,\" Nadella said.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/sreekanth-nadella-1966032/\">Krishna Kishore Chukkapalli, MD and CEO at KFin Services</a></span>, also commented on the importance of the new platform: \"India\'s KYC ecosystem has historically been besieged by fragmentation. KFIN KRA overcomes this by using AI and blockchain to build a harmonious, secure experience for both institutions and investors.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Market Response: Short-Term Decline or Long-Term Opportunity?</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Despite the announcement of the new platform, KFin Technologies\' shares declined by over 4% during today\'s trading session. Market analysts attribute the drop to overall volatility and short-term profit booking. Others believe that the market\'s price of the potential of the new platform has not yet been fully factored in.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">But the long-term outlook is not gloomy. KFin Technologies is a significant player in India\'s financial services space, already a:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Largest investor solutions company in Indian mutual funds</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->The biggest issuer solutions provider by number of customers</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->One of the three functional Central Recordkeeping Agencies (CRAs) of the National Pension System (NPS)</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The KFin Technologies KRA launch further consolidates the company\'s already strong position, likely creating new revenue streams through KYC services, fintech start-up partnerships, and broader market coverage.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>What It Means for India\'s Digital Economy</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">India\'s digital finance ecosystem is evolving at a fast pace, and efficient KYC solutions need to onboard tens of millions of new customers into formal financial services. As regulators call for greater transparency and digital compliance, platforms like KFIN KRA are likely to emerge as a vital infrastructure.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">For investors, the temporary decline in share price can be a strategic entry point, especially if the platform experiences mass industry adoption quickly. For the industry, it can be the beginning of a new normal in digital identity management. As the impact of the KFin Technologies KRA launch takes hold over the next several quarters, stakeholders across the fintech and financial services value chain will be watching closely.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\">&nbsp;</span></p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-05-02', '23:02:12', 'kfin-technologies-kra-launch-marks-digital-kyc-breakthrough', 'article/kfintech-sreekanth-nadella-ceo.webp', 'Sreekanth Nadella, CEO and MD, KFin Technologies', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/kfintech-sreekanth-nadella-ceo.webp', 5, 2025, 'KFin Technologies, KRA launch, digital KYC, eKYC, fintech, investor services, KYC compliance, digital onboarding, visionaries network, KRA India, financial services, secure KYC, fintech India, digital identity, investor onboarding', 'KFin Technologies launches its KRA platform, revolutionizing digital KYC processes and enhancing investor onboarding with secure, paperless compliance solutions.', 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0),
(166, NULL, 'Meta AI App Premium Tier Launches New Revenue Stream', 'Meta AI App Premium Tier Unveiled as New Revenue Stream Opportunity', 'ai vr and automation', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Meta Platforms is testing a new revenue stream with the launch of a Meta AI app premium tier,&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/mark-zuckerberg-618bba58/\">CEO Mark Zuckerberg</a></span> announced on the company\'s Q1 2025 earnings call this week. The action would put Meta on par with other tech giants with paid access to premium-tier AI features and prioritizing user growth over short-term profits.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The standalone <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://ai.meta.com/\">Meta AI app</a></span>, launched just a few days back, takes the company\'s <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/genai-research-delayed-over-industry-battle-slows-progress\">generative AI</a></span> assistant away from social media such as Facebook, Instagram, and WhatsApp, and onto its own turf. The app allows you to chat with the AI bot, generate images, and more. Already, it has signed up nearly a billion users worldwide&mdash;a healthy beginning for Meta\'s latest innovation.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Paid Features in the Works</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">While <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/meta-smart-glasses-october-2025-new-features-and-launch-details\">Meta</a></span> so far has continued its AI tool for free, Zuckerberg indicated that there is more and more opportunity to offer further capabilities for a charge. \"There\'s an opportunity to offer a premium service to people who need to unlock more compute or more functionality,\" he said during the earnings call.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This Meta AI app premium tier would be directly in competition with similar products by OpenAI (ChatGPT Plus), Google (Gemini Advanced), and Microsoft (Copilot Pro). Premium tiers typically entail faster speed, early release of new features, and better models&mdash;something which can easily be replicated or even surpassed by Meta, given its massive user base.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>AI Investment Hits $72 Billion</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Zuckerberg further revealed that Meta doubled its spending on AI from the previously cited $65 billion to a staggering $72 billion. \"We now expect to spend up to $72 billion on AI,\" he declared, highlighting the strategic significance of artificial intelligence to the company\'s long-term vision.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Even with a quarterly revenue of $42 billion, Meta does not seem to be in a hurry to monetize the AI app. Rather, Zuckerberg focused on the company\'s user adoption and engagement, saying, \"I expect that we\'re going to be largely focused on scaling and deepening engagement for at least the next year.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Advertisements and Product Recommendations Coming Soon</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In addition to subscriptions, Meta is also set to roll out ads and product recommendations to the AI experience. But Zuckerberg made clear that monetization would roll out later. \"Before we\'re really ready to start building out the business,\" he said, Meta would like to optimize the user experience and develop its AI infrastructure.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This user-centric approach sets Meta apart from others, who have been quick to roll out premium models. By holding off on monetizing right away, Meta is attempting to build a more solid, loyal user base before introducing a premium-level Meta AI app.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Why This Matters</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The introduction of a Meta AI app premium tier has the ability to significantly change the AI assistant industry. Having nearly a billion users already on board, Meta\'s foray into the paid AI space will have an impact on consumer behavior as well as the strategies of competing platforms.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Furthermore, the app\'s integration into Meta\'s broader ecosystem&mdash;spanning social media platforms to virtual and augmented reality&mdash;gives it a unique edge. With generative AI as the focus of digital experiences, having a capable assistant whose origin is in Meta\'s infrastructure might be the difference between a seamless and highly personalized user experience.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Conclusion </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">No official launch date has been released, but it appears that shortly Meta will be launching a paid version of its AI app. With a $72 billion injection and an enormous user base, Meta AI app premium level will likely be the foundation of the firm\'s new AI strategy. In the meantime, Meta is content to play the long game&mdash;focusing on scale, engagement, and customer satisfaction rather than opening the monetization faucet.</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-05-02', '23:24:48', 'meta-ai-app-premium-tier-launches-new-revenue-stream', 'article/visionaries-network-meta-ai-app-premium-tier-unveiled.webp', 'Meta AI App Premium Tier Unveiled as New Revenue Stream Opportunity', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-meta-ai-app-premium-tier-unveiled.webp', 5, 2025, 'Meta AI, premium tier, AI app, new revenue, monetization, Meta platform, AI tools, subscription model, tech innovation, app upgrade, Meta services, artificial intelligence, visionaries network, AI monetization, digital services', 'Meta unveils a premium tier for its AI app, introducing new monetization opportunities through advanced features and subscription-based services.', 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0),
(167, NULL, 'GTA 6 Release Delayed to 2026, Rockstar Confirms', 'GTA 6 release delayed to 2026 as Rockstar confirms new date', 'Entertainment and Recreation', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The world of gaming was left reeling this week when&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.rockstargames.com/\">Rockstar Games</a></span> finally confirmed GTA 6 release delayed to 2026. In a blog post that appeared on their site, the game developers informed that the next installment of the Grand Theft Auto series won\'t be available in 2025 as first intended. Grand Theft Auto VI will instead appear on May 26, 2026.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The title was revealed following months of rising rumors and silence on the part of the developers. \"We are sorry that this is later than you hoped,\" Rockstar wrote. \"The interest and anticipation for a new Grand Theft Auto has been humbling for our entire team. We appreciate your patience and your support as we work to finish the game.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Rockstar continued to explain that the delay is needed to ensure that the game meets the extremely high standards that its predecessors have set. \"With every game that we have released, the goal has always been to try to surpass your expectations, and Grand Theft Auto VI is no exception,\" they added.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>A Disappointment to Fans, But Not Surprising</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The fact GTA 6 release delayed to 2026 will be disappointing to many hardcore fans who have been holding on for more than a decade now that GTA V was released in 2013. The initial teaser of GTA VI was released in December 2023 and went on to become one of the fastest game trailers in <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.rockstargames.com/\">gaming</a></span> history, accumulating more than 250 million views in a matter of weeks. Nevertheless, the absence of follow-up content had already been creating rumors of delays from insiders.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The teaser included a revisit to Vice City, the Rockstar fictionalized Miami. It also included a new playable avatar, Lucia, who is the first female protagonist of the series. Lucia is seen getting involved in all kinds of criminal ventures with her supposed partner, Jason, for an action-filled and dramatic plot.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>New Protagonists, Larger World</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The game will have two playable protagonists, Lucia and Jason, and will have a suspenseful storyline with heists, betrayal, and frenzied gameplay typical of Grand Theft Auto. Other characters like Stefani, a prison counselor, and a Joker-inspired antagonist figure have leaked and appeared on forum posts. The other characters rumored to appear in the game are Wyman, Dre, Kai, Billy, Sam, and Zach.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Rockstar is said to be creating the largest open-world map in the company\'s history with dynamic weather, AI, and even changing neighborhoods over time. Insiders said that the production of the game is ambitious and resource-heavy, and that could be the reason why GTA 6 release delayed to 2026 became inevitable.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Final Thoughts</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">While it\'s never pleasant to wait longer for a game you\'re excited about, Rockstar\'s history is that patience does pay off. Both GTA V and Red Dead Redemption 2 were delayed and became blockbusters.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">If history is any indicator, Grand Theft Auto VI might just revolutionize the open-world formula when it finally releases in 2026. All the fans can do for now is wish that the expanded timeline means an even bigger game. And with the GTA 6 release delayed to 2026 made official, it\'s evident Rockstar is completely dedicated to creating the most groundbreaking Grand Theft Auto game ever.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-05-02', '23:39:21', 'gta-6-release-delayed-to-2026-as-rockstar-confirms-new-date', 'article/visionaries-network-gta-6-release-delayed-to-2026-as-rockstar.webp', 'GTA 6 Release Delayed to 2026, Rockstar Confirms', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-gta-6-release-delayed-to-2026-as-rockstar.webp', 5, 2025, 'GTA 6, Rockstar Games, release delay, 2026 launch, Grand Theft Auto, video game news, gaming update, GTA 6 release date, game delay, visionaries network, PS5, Xbox Series X, gaming industry, Rockstar update, new GTA', 'Rockstar Games officially delays GTA 6 release to 2026, confirming the new launch timeline for the highly anticipated open-world title.', 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0),
(168, NULL, 'TECHMATE by MathWorks: Technical Mentorship for Startups', 'TECHMATE by MathWorks Offers Easy Technical Mentorship for Startups', 'Startups', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In today\'s pace of innovation, coming up with a revolutionary idea is just the beginning. For most startups, the actual challenge is bringing that idea to life as a working, scalable product&mdash;particularly when technical hurdles get in the way.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">While there are many accelerator programs available that provide business advice and access to investors, few fill the gap of hands-on engineering expertise that startups truly require. That\'s where TECHMATE, a revolutionary program by <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://in.mathworks.com/?s_tid=gn_logo\">MathWorks</a></span>, steps in&mdash;providing easy technical mentorship for startups to close the gap between idea and product.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">MathWorks, the maker of MATLAB and Simulink, launched TECHMATE (Technical Mentorship and Support Program for MATLAB Entrepreneurs) to meet the immediate requirement for tailored technical support.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Focused on early- and mid-stage companies that take part in the MathWorks Accelerator Program or Startup Program, TECHMATE seeks to enable startups with the tools and resources necessary to fix engineering issues timely and effectively.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>What sets TECHMATE apart</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">TECHMATE is not generic advice. It\'s a six-month mentorship program with a technical emphasis on each startup\'s technical goals. Attendees get one-on-one, hands-on mentoring with experienced MathWorks application engineers&mdash;people who have first-hand experience of the real-world application of MATLAB and Simulink in real industries such as robotics, <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/crawley-mbst-for-hand-foot-pain-relief\">healthcare</a></span>, energy, and automotive.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">These mentors help startups streamline simulations, optimize algorithms, and accelerate prototyping stages so that they can smoothly transition from development to deployment.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Program Highlights:</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Customized technical guidance: Every startup is unique, and TECHMATE ensures that its guidance is unique as well. Mentorship plans vary based on project complexity, maturity level, and industry-specific challenges.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>Real-time engineering support:</strong> <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/ai-startup-investments-in-india-2025-break-records\">Startups</a></span> enjoy in-house access to MathWorks\' technical expertise, enabling them to make the right decisions and prevent expensive development dead ends.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>Exposure and integration within communities:</strong> In addition to mentorship, startups are able to tap into the massive MathWorks community&mdash;networking with other peers, potential business partners, and even venture capital. They benefit from increased exposure through websites, PR, and social media of MathWorks too. Two startup companies from the first cohort had their stories brought to the international stage already.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>Culture of scalability-first:</strong> TECHMATE doesn\'t fix today\'s problems&mdash;it sets up technical scalability and product longevity in the long run.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Why It Matters: Easy Technical Mentorship for Startups</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">For seed-stage founders, affording a full engineering team or consulting firm is typically out of the question. That is why easy technical mentorship for startups like TECHMATE is so important. It lowers the barriers to entry by providing founders with access to enterprise-grade tools and expert-level advice for startup-friendly pricing.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Whether a robotics firm looking to optimize motion planning or a healthtech firm needing to validate complex simulations, TECHMATE offers clear, actionable advice informed by decades of engineering expertise.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>A New Standard in Startup Support </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As the startup ecosystem becomes more competitive, access to quality technical mentorship can be the difference between success and stagnation. TECHMATE by MathWorks sets the bar higher by offering easy technical mentorship for startups&mdash;allowing innovators to build, refine, and scale faster than ever.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-05-05', '22:54:54', 'techmate-by-mathworks-offers-easy-technical-mentorship-for-startups', 'article/visionaries-network-techmate-by-mathworks-easy-technical-membership.webp', 'TECHMATE by MathWorks Technical Mentorship for Startups', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-techmate-by-mathworks-easy-technical-membership.webp', 5, 2025, 'TECHMATE, MathWorks, startup support, mentorship, engineering, technical help, MATLAB, Simulink, visionaries network, incubator, accelerator, tech startup, software tools, prototyping, R&amp;D', 'TECHMATE by MathWorks offers startups free technical mentorship, tools, and guidance to accelerate innovation using MATLAB and Simulink.', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0);
