(176, NULL, 'RuneHero Beta Offers $10K Prize Pool in Web3 Gaming', 'RuneHero Beta Prize Pool Offers $10K in Web3 Game Rewards', 'Entertainment and Recreation', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://cointelegraph.com/explained/what-are-web3-games-how-do-they-work\">Web3 gaming</a></span> is going full steam in 2025, and two massive games&mdash;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://runehero.io/\">RuneHero</a></span> and Mighty Action Heroes (MaH)&mdash;are leading the charge. With RuneHero\'s closed beta live and featuring a massive $10,000 prize pool, and MaH beginning season 10, blockchain games are attracting the attention of both crypto and mainstream gamers.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The much-awaited RuneHero beta prize event was live on May 4 and will continue until May 24, 2025. Built on the Immutable blockchain platform, RuneHero is an action RPG of Diablo\'s genre that unites the excitement of dungeon raids with NFT rewards and real-world economic incentives.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>RuneHero Closed Beta Is Live</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">RuneHero is a top-down action MMO RPG featuring action-packed combat, rich character customization, and a fully on-chain economy. The closed beta phase is inviting players to jump into a fantasy world of monsters, magic, and loot&mdash;to battle for the lucrative RuneHero beta prize.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Unlike most RPGs, RuneHero lets you go your own way through a loose multi-class system. You can start off as a knight who uses a sword and turn into a battle mage who can cast fireballs. This freedom of playstyle provides massive replay value, especially with the extra motivation of in-game rewards.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The beta is already downloadable on Windows, and initial player reviews speak of its seamless combat system, intelligent skill leveling, and unobtrusive blockchain integration. Players can buy and sell in-game NFTs&mdash;such as weapons, armor, and characters&mdash;via the integrated auction house. It\'s not a game; it\'s a Web3 economy playable as a game.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With $10,000 offered as prize, the RuneHero beta prize has been the biggest anticipated spectacle this year in 2025 crypto <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/05/gta-6-release-delayed-to-2026-as-rockstar-confirms-new-date\">gaming</a></span>.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>MaH Season 10: \"Gold Justice\" Brings New Heroes and Hype</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">While RuneHero dominates the RPG world, Mighty Action Heroes (MaH) still dominates the shooter world. The mobile battle royale game developed by Mighty Bear Games has just rolled out its Season 10 update titled \"Gold Justice.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This new season introduces two new explosive heroes, new powers, and high-risk gameplay that\'s creating ripples among both Web2 and Web3 audiences. MaH offers 20-player arena-style battles where the last one standing is the winner&mdash;and sometimes, crypto prizes.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Since its release in July 2023, MaH has had regular content drops every one to two months, with a dedicated player base and consistent gameplay loop dynamic. What sets it apart in the oversaturated shooter market is its multi-platform release, with releases on mobile, browser, and Telegram&mdash;with varying levels of Web3 functionality.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>GOAT Gaming Telegram Bot Enters 330K User Base</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Behind the success of MaH is GOAT Gaming, a new Web3 gaming platform that is steadily becoming a Telegram behemoth. With over 330,000 monthly players that engage with its Telegram gaming bot, GOAT Gaming is creating a niche for low-friction, mobile-driven crypto games.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Its portfolio features offbeat hits such as Kitty Solitaire, Waifu Clash, and Crypto Crawler, all built with in-game mechanics. This expansion has not gone unnoticed&mdash;GOAT Gaming raised millions in funding earlier this year from TON Ventures and other top players in the blockchain industry.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Their placement on Telegram provides them with an advantage, with users in a position to play right away without having to download heavy apps or navigate complicated wallet setups. This accessibility model is one of the key drivers of their rapid adoption.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Final Thoughts </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As blockchain gaming matures, the RuneHero beta award and MaH\'s milestone tenth season show that Web3 games are no longer niche experiments&mdash;they\'re mainstreaming. No matter if you\'re a fan of hack-and-slash RPGs or over-the-top shooters, both games deliver: real payouts, sticky gameplay, and lively communities.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">While RuneHero rewards you with a real $10,000 payout and MaH is always changing, 2025 could be the year Web3 games finally find their footing.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-05-07', '23:35:28', 'runehero-beta-prize-pool-offers-10k-in-web3-game-rewards', 'article/visionariess-network-web3-game-rewards.webp', 'Web3 Game Rewards', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionariess-network-web3-game-rewards.webp', 5, 2025, 'RuneHero, Web3 game, crypto rewards, blockchain gaming, NFT game, beta launch, prize pool, play-to-earn, visionarires network, crypto gaming, Web3 rewards, gaming contest, NFT prizes, GameFi, beta test', 'Join RuneHero Beta and compete for a $10K prize pool in this exciting Web3 play-to-earn game powered by blockchain and NFT rewards.', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(177, NULL, 'Vasco&rsquo;s AI Earbuds Win 2025 Top Design Award', 'Vasco&rsquo;s AI Translation Earbuds Win Top 2025 Design Awards', 'telecommunication and electronics', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Vasco Electronics, a global market leader in smart communication technology, has achieved outstanding recognition at the 2025 MUSE Design Awards and the 2025 Red Dot Design Awards. Vasco\'s two top-selling items, the&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://vasco-translator.com/\">Vasco Translator V4 and the Vasco Translator E1</a></span>, have been commended for their high-quality design and functionality, further establishing Vasco as the leader in the rapidly growing field of AI translation earbuds and smart multilingual products.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">At the MUSE Design Awards, the Vasco Translator V4 won Gold in the Educational Tools category for overall language learning and classroom communication effectiveness. The actual showstopper, however, was the Translator E1, which won two Gold awards: <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/google-and-samsung-to-launch-xr-glasses-in-2026-with-smart-features\">Wearable Technologies</a></span> and Tech Accessories. And that was only the start. At the Red Dot Design Awards, which is one of the most coveted design awards, the Translator E1 won the highly sought-after Best of the Best award in Communication Technology with a near-perfect 99 out of 100 score from judges.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This recognition by both MUSE and Red Dot confirms the innovation and hard work that drive our team,\" said <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/maciejgoralski1/\">Maciej G&oacute;ralski, CEO of Vasco Electronics</a></span>. \"We\'re thrilled to develop products that combine innovative design with practical functionality to bridge communication gaps.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Revolutionizing Communication with AI Translation Earbuds</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Vasco Translator E1, introduced earlier this year, is heavily promoted as a next-generation real-time language translation device. The AI-powered earbuds can translate more than 50 languages, and the possibility of having real-time, multi-directional conversation becomes feasible. While other translation systems exist, the E1 has the capability of accommodating ten individuals engaged in a seamless, multilingual conversation&mdash;positioning it as a great partner for business meetings, international trips, and multicultural social gatherings.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Its counterpart, the Vasco Translator V4, offers voice, photo, and text translation in a portable handheld format. With a powerful Group Chat feature for up to 100 members and a pre-loaded language-learning software with support for 28 languages, the V4 is especially useful for teachers, business groups, and frequent travelers.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Record-Breaking Sales Reflect Booming Demand</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Vasco Electronics saw astronomical growth in 2024, shipping over 100,000 devices across the globe, a 27% increase compared to last year. The U.S. market led the way with an astonishing 200% increase in sales, a testament to the growing need for intelligent, wearable translation devices like AI translation earbuds.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Growing telework, global collaboration, and remote work have fueled the need for frictionless interaction. Vasco\'s user-friendly solutions are meeting this need, allowing people worldwide to connect, understand, and cooperate more seamlessly than ever before.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Design Meets Functionality</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">What distinguishes Vasco from other tech brands is that it is dedicated to bringing together strong features with award-winning design. The Translator E1\'s ergonomic design and easy-to-use interface make it as beautiful as it is functional. And the Translator V4\'s longer battery life, fast response times, and offline mode for travelers crossing regions with unreliable internet.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">These are the same qualities that compel design professionals and consumers to take notice. Back-to-back wins at two of the world\'s most renowned design competitions prove that Vasco is not just a technology company&mdash;it\'s a design-driven innovator.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>A Future of Fluent Connection </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As global communication becomes more important, Vasco Electronics is leading the way with reliable, elegantly crafted devices that transform how we break down language barriers. With its award-winning AI translation earbuds, the organization is not just creating smarter devices but also a more connected world. For those who desire elegant, travel-friendly translation solutions with a cutting-edge performance, Vasco Electronics is creating the new global standard&mdash;one conversation at a time.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-05-08', '23:02:57', 'vascos-ai-translation-earbuds-win-top-2025-design-awards', 'article/visionaries-network-vascos-ai-translation-earbuds-win-top-2025-design.webp', 'Vasco&rsquo;s AI Translation Earbuds Win Top 2025 Design Awards', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-vascos-ai-translation-earbuds-win-top-2025-design.webp', 5, 2025, 'Vasco, AI earbuds, translation device, 2025 design award, wearable tech, smart earbuds, visionaries network, tech awards, AI translation, gadget of the year, language tech, smart wearables, product design, top tech, global awards', 'Vasco&rsquo;s AI-powered translation earbuds win top 2025 design awards for innovation in smart wearable and language tech solutions.', 1, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0),
(178, NULL, 'Alice.Tech Raises $4.8M for AI Learning Platform', 'Alice.Tech&rsquo;s AI Platform Raises $4.8M to Personalize Learning', 'edtech and learning', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Denmark-based edtech&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.alice.tech/\">Alice.Tech</a></span>, whose technology employs AI to create custom study material, has raised $4.8 million of seed capital to scale up its product. Y Combinator alumnus as of 2024, Alice.Tech wants to disrupt students\' exam prep&mdash;through tailored study materials made possible by the help of <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/05/meta-ai-app-premium-tier-launches-new-revenue-stream\">artificial intelligence</a></span>.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Cherry Ventures and Y Combinator also put money in the round, which saw PSV Tech and US and European angel investors also contribute. The money will be used to fuel product development and increase the footprint of Alice.Tech in schools and universities.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>How Alice.Tech&rsquo;s AI Platform Tailors Learning</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Alice.Tech\'s AI platform reworks general textbooks, lecture slides, and notes into customized learning materials for each student\'s learning style. Organizing key concepts, producing flashcards, or generating multiple-choice quizzes, the platform adapts to what each learner needs to succeed.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\"Where Duolingo did it for language, we do it for high school and college exams,\" said <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/kimrants/\">Alice.Tech\'s co-founder and CEO Kim Rants</a></span>. \"We aim at what the student needs to practice through real-time performance analysis and feedback.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>A Freemium Model with Growing Demand</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The company uses a freemium business model, offering free access to core functionality to students and premium plans on a monthly or annual subscription. The company is also in negotiations with institutions to offer the platform at scale, integrating it into classrooms and curricula.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Alice.Tech also has an AI platform with social learning, where students learn in real time with others. It encourages learning in groups but still offers individualized study support depending on the performance of every student.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Rants described the concept behind the product: \"I saw too many students get left behind because old-school learning tools weren\'t designed for them. With AI, we can now design education for the student, not the other way around.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Built for the Future of EdTech</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As the world rapidly shifts towards digital and hybrid learning, there is a growing need for intelligent adaptive learning platforms. Alice.Tech\'s AI platform is a welcome response in the new edtech landscape, providing students with more effective tools to learn more&mdash;and worry less. The successful pitch deck showed not just the technology but also its real impact: improved test scores, more confident students, and scalable adoption potential in schools worldwide.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\">&nbsp;</span></p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-05-08', '23:25:07', 'alice-techs-ai-platform-raises-4-8m-to-personalize-learning', 'article/visionaries-network-alice-tech-ai-platform.webp', 'Alice.Tech&rsquo;s AI Platform Raises $4.8M to Personalize Learning', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-alice-tech-ai-platform.webp', 5, 2025, 'Alice.Tech, AI learning, personalized education, edtech funding, visionaries network, education tech, adaptive learning, smart platform, AI in education, tech startup, learning AI, investor funding, education innovation, machine learning, future of learning', 'Alice.Tech secures $4.8M to enhance its AI-driven learning platform, aiming to personalize education and transform the edtech landscape.', 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0),
(179, '', 'How Digital Fashion Avatars Change Brand Marketing', 'How Digital Fashion Avatars Are Changing Brand Marketing', 'brand management digital marketing and business', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/hottest-summer-outfit-ideas-2025-to-shop-now\">fashion</a></span> and <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/05/gr-digital-marketing-opens-new-agency-for-online-growth\">marketing</a></span> world is evolving at the speed of lightning&mdash;and leading the charge are digital influencers and digital solutions that marry technology and imagination. At the top of the most impactful trends here is the emergence of digital fashion avatars, computer-generated characters that brands use to promote products, engage with consumers, and make content creation easier.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">These virtual characters assume a variety of forms. Totally computer-generated models like <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.cut-the-saas.com/ai/the-ai-behind-virtual-influencer-lil-miquela\">Lil Miquela</a></span> and <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.virtualhumans.org/human/shudu\">Shudu</a></span> are purely virtual, interacting with fans through manipulated social media posts and brand endorsements. Others, such as Hatsune Miku, combine digital animation with human elements, such as voiceovers or motion capture. Whatever their form, these virtual personas have emerged as powerful marketing tools, particularly among Gen Z consumers who spend more time online than any other generation.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Real People, Virtual Faces</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The international influencer marketing industry is booming, with its market size in 2024 being over US$24 billion and projected to expand to US$32 billion in 2025. A large part of the expansion is due to the adoption of AI-driven marketing solutions, including virtual influencers and digital fashion avatars, especially in Asia where technological development is fast and widespread.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In Europe and the United States, fashion giants are also catching up. Levi Strauss &amp; Co., for instance, has collaborated with AI modeling companies to create digital avatars for their campaigns. Fast-fashion chain H&amp;M has also recently launched digital clones&mdash;AI-created copies of actual models&mdash;to sell their clothing lines. These avatars provide brands with flexibility, cost savings, and a scalable method of creating high-quality images for various channels.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>The Future of Digital Twins</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Another trend gaining speed is the deployment of digital twins&mdash;computer duplicates of actual people who serve as substitutes in fashion magazines and internet commercials. Virtual influencers are unique in that they don\'t appear on social media or have histories. They are strictly for imagery purposes. Mango, for example, employed AI-generated models in a teen girls\' campaign to demonstrate the ability of AI in unifying fashion and technology.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">While these technologies provide evident operational benefits&mdash;e.g., quicker production and customized content&mdash;they also raise perpetual ethical issues. Critics ask if computer models will displace human talent, e.g., photographers, stylists, and live models. Others worry about consent, image rights, and the authenticity of AI content.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Balancing Innovation with Responsibility</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">One of the most significant dangers that brands take when using digital fashion avatars is that they put consumer trust at risk. Should the public learn that a seemingly genuine person within a campaign is, in fact, completely AI-generated, then the brand\'s integrity is compromised&mdash;especially if this was not clearly made evident. Honesty, then, is essential. Audiences are respectful of honesty, and brands must signpost digital personas obviously to ensure they do not compromise their integrity.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">And then, naturally, there\'s the problem of representation. AI technology, as much as it can create diverse images, can quite easily mirror biases if it is not well-designed. An online avatar that is inclusive-looking in design but created without diverse input will nevertheless be short in representing fully. Brands that want to use AI responsibly must prioritize inclusivity, not just in appearance but also in the process of creating their campaigns.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>The Future of AI in Fashion </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As AI becomes more deeply embedded in the fashion industry, the trend of employing only digital avatars will continue to expand. Digital fashion avatars are not a passing technology fad&mdash;but rather a harbinger of a deep change in the way fashion is created, promoted, and consumed. Avatars can potentially allow brands to reach more consumers, try out styles, and react quickly to quickly evolving trends.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">But to flourish with this technology, brands must balance creativity with responsibility. With ethical foundations based on consent, diversity, and transparency, fashion brands can surf the innovation wave without sacrificing trust.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-05-08', '22:18:27', 'how-digital-fashion-avatars-are-changing-brand-marketing', 'article/visionaries-network-digital-fashion-avatars-changing-marketing.webp', 'How Digital Fashion Avatars Are Changing Brand Marketing', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-digital-fashion-avatars-changing-marketing.webp', 5, 2025, 'digital fashion, avatars, brand marketing, virtual influencers, fashion tech, metaverse, branding, visionaries network, 3D avatars, virtual fashion, marketing trends, immersive branding, AI fashion, virtual try-ons, future of fashion', 'Explore how digital fashion avatars are reshaping brand marketing through virtual experiences, personalization, and immersive consumer engagement.', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(180, NULL, 'DoorDash Acquires SevenRooms to Boost CRM Tools', 'DoorDash Acquires SevenRooms to Expand Hospitality CRM Tools', 'tourism and hospitality', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In a display of enormous ambition to broaden its backing for hospitality businesses,&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.doordash.com/?msockid=2aad64c6e205683d3ed37785e3f26953\">DoorDash</a></span> has said it will acquire <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://sevenrooms.com/\">SevenRooms</a></span>, a New York City hospitality technology company with a history of a formidable suite of hospitality CRM tools. The deal, which is slated to close in the second half of 2025, is subject to customary regulatory approvals and closing conditions.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This acquisition is an extension of DoorDash\'s Commerce Platform, the restaurant and local business solution used to drive in-store and delivery-based revenue. With the inclusion of SevenRooms\' software, DoorDash is poised to help merchants create more meaningful customer relationships, increase guest retention, and maximize long-term profitability.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>SevenRooms: A Guest Experience Technology Leader</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Established in 2011 by Joel Montaniel, Allison Page, and Kinesh Patel, SevenRooms is currently a leading choice provider for operators to optimize the guest experience. SevenRooms\' system combines reservation management, marketing automation, and guest profiling in one smooth CRM system.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The technology is particularly prized in the restaurant and <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/thrs-marketing-initiative-sway-aims-to-redefine-hospitality\">hospitality</a></span> industries, where guest loyalty and customer insight are the drivers of success. They\'re the same opportunities DoorDash is attempting to tap into with this acquisition&mdash;arming its merchant partners with hospitality CRM tools that can fuel both marketing and service optimization.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>DoorDash\'s Bigger Plan</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/parisa-sadrzadeh-43878829/\">Parisa Sadrzadeh, DoorDash VP of Strategy</a></span> and Operations, focused on the larger context: \"We\'re building the DoorDash Commerce Platform so that merchants can serve their customers on all channels. With SevenRooms, we\'re thrilled to help local businesses bring new customers into their businesses, build loyalty, and market smarter and data-driven.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This acquisition is the follow-up to other recent moves by DoorDash to transition out of a food delivery app and into a full-service commerce platform. This acquisition is not only an investment in logistics and delivery but also in technology that enhances in-app dining experiences and customer lifetime value.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Highlight Local Business and Sustainable Growth</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/joel-montaniel-1a244316/\">SevenRooms CEO and co-founder Joel Montaniel</a></span> described how the company was founded with an \"operator-first\" mindset. \"We founded SevenRooms to empower hospitality operators to know their guests and drive their business sustainably,\" he said. \"Restaurants and hotels are the pulse of neighborhoods. Our mission has always been to empower them to make each guest feel like home.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Montaniel further added that the partnership with DoorDash will allow SevenRooms to grow faster and reach more individuals. \"Together, we\'re bringing next-generation hospitality CRM tools to even more operators around the world&mdash;empowering them to succeed in both digital and physical channels,\" he further added.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Global Reach and Innovation Forward</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The union of SevenRooms\' deep software expertise with DoorDash\'s scale globally will be driving innovation, according to DoorDash. DoorDash says that merchants will have access to a rich ecosystem that enables improved delivery as well as in-person guest experiences.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The firms also emphasized that they will have an \"open, partner-friendly\" culture&mdash;enabling merchants to integrate tools in ways that they prefer, instead of locking them in a closed system.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With SevenRooms joining the DoorDash family, the focus will be on growing the innovation roadmap, with a focus on personalized marketing, data insights, and automation&mdash;key elements of any competitive hospitality CRM tools.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Deal Details</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">William Blair was the exclusive financial advisor to SevenRooms, and legal advice was provided by Goodwin Procter. Legal advice to DoorDash was provided by A&amp;O Shearman. This transaction is one of a broader trend throughout the technology and hospitality industries, where companies are investing more in personalization, customer information, and multi-channel commerce.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With this transaction, DoorDash is becoming a customer engagement and logistics leader&mdash;empowering local businesses to connect with guests wherever they are.</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-05-10', '01:06:49', 'doordash-acquires-sevenrooms-to-expand-hospitality-crm-tools', 'article/visionaries-network-doordash-acquires-sevenrooms.webp', 'DoorDash Acquires SevenRooms', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-doordash-acquires-sevenrooms.webp', 5, 2025, 'DoorDash, SevenRooms, acquisition, CRM tools, hospitality tech, restaurant software, customer data, tech merger, food delivery, guest experience, restaurant CRM, hospitality software, business growth, visionaries network, strategic acquisition', 'DoorDash acquires SevenRooms to strengthen its hospitality CRM tools, enhancing guest experience and restaurant tech capabilities across its growing platform.', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(181, '', 'Federal Automation Tool to Reshape U.S. Workforce', 'Federal Workforce Automation Tool Set to Reshape U.S. Jobs', 'it and software', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">A controversial new software tool is being implemented stealthily across U.S. government agencies with a single purpose: speed federal firings. Supported by&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.doge.gov/\">Elon Musk\'s Department of Government Efficiency (DOGE)</a></span>, the Workforce Reshaping Tool is a web-based replacement for the Pentagon\'s old AutoRIF program. It\'s designed to speed what was formerly a time-consuming, spreadsheet-based process&mdash;a swift, algorithmic solution.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Behind it all is a broader trend toward federal workforce automation, a notion rapidly shifting from theory to reality. Supporters claim it\'s about modernization and cost savings. Critics worry it\'s about pinching&mdash;and on human beings.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Layoffs Already Underway</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Since President <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/micron-technology-adds-surcharge-to-offset-trump-tariffs\">Donald Trump</a></span> returned to office in January, nearly 260,000 federal workers have departed from their positions due to buyouts, early departure, or outright firing, according to a Reuters tally. The transition, however, has not been smooth. Dozens of employees were erroneously fired and then rehired, which points to loopholes in the present manual procedure.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As the new tool becomes a reality, drastic cuts are expected to rise. Organizations such as the Department of Veterans Affairs will be eliminating tens of thousands of positions, and the Internal Revenue Service has indicated plans to reduce its staff by 40%.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Workforce Reshaping Tool: A Deeper Insight</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Originally named AutoRIF (Reduction in Force), the program was developed by the Pentagon more than 25 years ago to search employee records and identify layoff targets based on seniority, performance, and veteran status. But it was slow to use and prone to errors. The new version, designed by OPM developers for the use of Musk\'s DOGE, is cloud-based and supports real-time collaboration among HR staff. Agencies need not manually enter individual data points but can bulk upload databases for faster analysis. This reduces the time it takes to carry out a mass layoff by orders of magnitude.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Its proponents see the tool as a required step in federal government workforce automation that will make the government more responsive and flexible during periods of agency reorganization or budget stringency.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Problems of Speed and Equity</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">But not everyone is so sure. Public sector unions and lawyers fear that making redundancies automatic will lead to arbitrary, if not downright discriminatory, results. \"If bad assumptions are built into the <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/aveva-leads-shift-to-knowledge-as-a-service-platform-model\">software</a></span>, those assumptions can scale up quickly,\" said <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/donald-moynihan-9b160115/\">Don Moynihan of the Ford School of Public Policy at the University of Michigan</a></span>.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The software also comes as there are legal battles, with a number of lawsuits brought to oppose recent agency reductions. All agencies, such as the U.S. Agency for International Development and the Consumer Financial Protection Bureau, have already experienced substantial staffing cuts.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Despite all these controversies, the rollout of the Workforce Reshaping Tool signals the end of federal workforce automation as a future possibility&mdash;it\'s now a reality. And while Elon Musk steps back from DOGE to focus on his private business, OPM will now spearhead the rollout of the tool to agencies.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\">&nbsp;</span></p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-05-10', '01:15:23', 'federal-workforce-automation-tool-set-to-reshape-u-s--jobs', 'article/visionaries-network-federal-workforce-automation.webp', 'Federal Workforce Automation Tool Set to Reshape U.S. Jobs', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-federal-workforce-automation.webp', 5, 2025, 'automation, federal workforce, AI tools, job automation, government tech, U.S. jobs, digital transformation, visionaries network, labor shift, technology adoption, workforce change, AI in government, federal jobs, automation trends, job future', 'A new federal automation tool aims to transform U.S. jobs by streamlining processes, increasing efficiency, and reshaping the future of the public workforce.', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(182, '', 'Nvidia MediaTek N1 SoC May Transform Gaming Laptops', 'Nvidia MediaTek N1 SoC Could Redefine Gaming Laptops', 'semiconductors', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.computextaipei.com.tw/en/index.html\">Computex 2025</a></span> just around the corner, everyone is on tenterhooks waiting for two industry titans &mdash; <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.nvidia.com/en-us/drivers/\">Nvidia</a></span> and <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.mediatek.com/\">MediaTek</a></span> &mdash; to make an appearance, with rumors rife about a mighty new chip that will revolutionize gaming laptops. As per a ComputerBase report (via PC Gamer), the two firms will release an Arm-based laptop chip at the forthcoming expo, and news of the same is already causing ripples throughout the tech community.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The rumor focuses on the <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/nvidia-texas-factory-to-build-ai-chips-amid-tariff-shift\">Nvidia</a></span> MediaTek N1 SoC, a fresh system-on-chip that will introduce Blackwell GPU performance and Arm CPU efficiency to thin, high-performance laptops. This may be the turning point for the Windows on Arm ecosystem, which has yet to catch up with the brute performance of Apple\'s silicon in the laptop market.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>What We Know So Far About the Nvidia MediaTek N1 SoC</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2024/10/trident-iot-solutions\">chip</a></span> is reportedly a miniaturization of the GB10 Superchip &mdash; which was earlier demonstrated in Nvidia\'s Project DIGITS AI supercomputer (now known as DGX Spark). While the initial GB10 was meant for high-end AI workloads and servers, the new one seeks to balance power and portability.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Early reports show that the Nvidia MediaTek N1 SoC will have 8 to 12 CPU cores, much fewer than the 20-core version the whole GB10 is. It may cut down memory support to 16GB or 32GB from 128GB on its desktop counterpart. But the specs may be more than sufficient for gaming, streaming, and content creation tasks on the go.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Benchmark leaks on Geekbench show promising scores, with the chip reaching 3.9GHz, a single-core score of 2,960, and a multicore score of 10,682. They are on par with performance chips in the latest generation but Apple\'s M4 Max is still a bit more integrated and efficient.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Why It\'s a Big Deal for PC Gaming</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Windows on Arm has gone a long, long way recently, especially thanks to Qualcomm\'s Snapdragon X Elite, but gaming has always lagged behind with GPU issues and app support. That\'s where Nvidia\'s intervention comes into picture.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Nvidia MediaTek N1 SoC is said to include 50-series RTX parts such as 5th-gen Tensor Cores and 4th-gen Ray Tracing Cores. This could finally bring real-time ray tracing, DLSS, and high-definition gaming to Arm-based laptops, a huge leap from previous Windows on Arm implementations.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Gaming laptops powered by this chip may provide improved battery life, thinner and lighter form factors, and still be able to play graphically demanding games like Cyberpunk 2077 or Doom: The Dark Ages. That would put the playing field on par with Apple\'s own efforts using its M-series chips, as games like Resident Evil Village and Death Stranding are already natively supported on macOS.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>A Highlight of Computex 2025?</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Although nothing is actually on the table yet, all indications are pointing towards a major Computex 2025 announcement. With both Nvidia and MediaTek delivering keynotes, unless things change drastically, we should expect to see the N1 chip officially announced &mdash; perhaps with some early demos of prototype laptops or dev kits.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">There is also speculation that this chip will come with Microsoft support in the form of Windows 12 optimizations, further optimizing app performance and native compatibility for gaming and productivity.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Final Thoughts </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With the tech community gearing up for Computex, the leaked release of the Nvidia MediaTek N1 SoC has already set tongues a-wagging among PC enthusiasts, developers, and gamers. If the chip lives up to its promise, it would mean a paradigm shift in the laptop industry &mdash; one where serious gaming no longer depends on legacy x86 platforms.</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-05-13', '22:31:24', 'nvidia-mediatek-n1-soc-could-redefine-gaming-laptops', 'article/visionaries-network-nvidia-mediatek-n1-soc-could-redefine-gaming.webp', 'Nvidia MediaTek N1 SoC Could Redefine Gaming Laptops', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-nvidia-mediatek-n1-soc-could-redefine-gaming.webp', 5, 2025, 'Nvidia, MediaTek, N1 SoC, gaming laptops, visionaries network, ARM, mobile gaming, AI, RTX, SoC, power efficiency, portable gaming, gaming performance, next-gen laptops, thermal design', 'Discover how the Nvidia MediaTek N1 SoC could revolutionize gaming laptops with enhanced performance, AI features, and power efficiency.', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(183, '', 'Kyvos Dialogs Brings Chat-Based Analytics to Data Insights', 'Kyvos Dialogs Revolutionizes Data Insights with Chat-Based Analytics', 'data analytics and visualization', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Making a huge leap in business intelligence,&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.kyvosinsights.com/\">Kyvos Insights</a></span> has launched a very powerful, chat-based analytics solution that brings data insights to all. The solution, in the form of Kyvos Dialogs, allows users to converse with their enterprise data the same way they would chat with friends. With plain English questions, users receive instant answers in charts, summaries, and trends format&mdash;no subject-matter expertise required.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This innovation is timely as companies are bogged down by intricate dashboards and isolated tools. With Kyvos Dialogs, organizations can now bypass the conventional report-building process and proceed directly to decision-making. Simply ask a question such as, \"How did our top three products perform last quarter by region?\" and receive clean, data-driven responses in seconds.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>What Makes Chat-Based Analytics Unique</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Compared to other traditional BI platforms that require training and SQL queries, a chat-based analytics tool is natural language, smart, and intuitive. Kyvos has created this product such that it can understand not just words, but the business intent of words. The tool can identify hierarchies, relationships, and KPIs, so users don\'t have to speak things perfectly to get meaningful responses.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The best of all? It doesn\'t have to end in a single question. You can continue to have a Q&amp;A discussion with your data&mdash;drill down, modify your question, or switch gears without having to begin anew. That makes it perfect for managers, analysts, and executives who require answers to be fast and easy.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Key Features of This Powerful Tool</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Here\'s what customers can look forward to from this next-generation chat-based analytics solution:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>Natural Language Q&amp;A:</strong> Just ask your question as you would in a chat. The system is familiar with business language and provides you with comprehensible responses in real-time.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>Intelligent Follow-Up:</strong> Improve, edit, or repeat previous questions without ambiguity. Kyvos Dialogs retains context.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>On-the-Fly KPI Definition:</strong> End-users can define, change, and adjust business metrics on the fly&mdash;no holdup waiting on IT support.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>Enterprise Data Ready:</strong> It handles very large amounts of data and blends structured and unstructured data, such as email and documents.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>AI Applications Available:</strong> Kyvos also enables AI training with access to tools such as the LangChain SQL Toolkit and Document Loader.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Whether you\'re generating reports for a meeting or monitoring trends between groups, this tool provides you with what you require&mdash;quick, visual, and easy.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>How Kyvos Dialogs Helps Business Leaders</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">For business executives, Kyvos Dialogs cuts through decision-making roadblocks. No more digging through a dozen charts or waiting for analysis teams to create custom reports. The <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/laser-technologies-unveils-nesting-software-for-cutting\">software</a></span> speaks for what counts, monitors performance metrics, and gives you immediate snapshots of what\'s succeeding&mdash;and what\'s not.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The future of analytics is going to be conversational,\" says&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/rajesh-murthy-59875560/\">Rajesh Murthy, COO at Kyvos Insights</a></span>. \"You need to be able to ask, \'What are my underperforming products in my East region for the last six months?\' and receive an honest answer, not a dump of data. That\'s what Kyvos Dialogs is intended to do.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Analytics That Are Effortless</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Kyvos has built a platform that doesn\'t respond&mdash;it understands. With its semantic intelligence engine at its back, Kyvos Dialogs delivers high accuracy with minimal false data and unnecessary noise. This quality of data clarity is especially crucial for organizations that rely on AI models, financial projections, or operational dashboards.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Wherever your data resides, on-premises or in the cloud, this cloud-native, chat-based offering is a smooth fit in every environment, so it\'s a simple addition to any data plan.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Final Thoughts </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">If you\'re looking for a chat-based analytics platform that delivers real value without the learning curve, then Kyvos Dialogs might just be the solution your business needs. It packages the power of AI, the convenience of chat, and the richness of enterprise data into one intelligent platform&mdash;so your people can forego the digging and get on with deciding.</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-05-13', '00:15:48', 'kyvos-dialogs-revolutionizes-data-insights-with-chat-based-analytics', 'article/visionaries-network-kyvos-dialogs-revolutionizes-data-insight.webp', 'Kyvos Dialogs Revolutionizes Data Insights with Chat-Based Analytics', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-kyvos-dialogs-revolutionizes-data-insight.webp', 5, 2025, 'Kyvos, Kyvos Dialogs, chat-based analytics, data insights, BI tools, AI analytics, natural language, business intelligence, data querying, self-service BI, enterprise data, visionaries network, analytics platform, data visualization, user-friendly analytics', 'Kyvos Dialogs enables chat-based analytics, making it easier for users to explore and analyze data through natural language queries.', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0);
