(184, NULL, 'Sateliot Expands 5G Satellite IoT Network in Australia', 'Sateliot Australia 5G Satellite IoT Set for $15M Expansion', 'iot-and-robotics', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Sateliot&rsquo;s 5G satellite IoT services are now up and running, a major milestone in linking rural and remote communities where there is no cellular coverage. As the first to deliver 5G standard-based connectivity via non-terrestrial networks (NTNs) with its own low-earth orbit (LEO) satellite constellation,&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://sateliot.space/\">Sateliot</a></span> has made its mark in the Australian market&mdash;acquiring a string of contracts and poised to connect over 300,000 IoT devices. These installations are set to bring in over $15 million AUD in recurring annual revenues.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">After receiving their final approval from regulators, Sateliot Australia 5G satellite IoT solutions are now ready to be deployed nationwide. This ensures Australian telecommunications law compliance and opens the door to high-volume applications in large industries such as <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/dot-and-nabard-join-hands-for-digital-empowerment-in-rural-india\">agriculture</a></span>, mining, logistics, and <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/03/pure-unveils-purepower-a-game-changer-in-indias-renewable-energy-landscape\">environmental monitoring</a></span>. Commercial operations are planned to be rolled out during the second half of 2025.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Pilot Program to Support Early Adoption</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">To make it easy to enter the market, Sateliot has launched a pilot program through which local IoT providers can pilot its 5G satellite connectivity. It provides businesses with a chance to pilot the service in real-life conditions and gain priority access to commercial plans once it is operational.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This is not a matter of launching satellites into space&mdash;it\'s a matter of applying real-world solutions to real-world connectivity problems,\" said <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/gianlucaredolfi/\">Gianluca Redolfi, Sateliot\'s Chief Commercial Officer</a></span>. \"Sateliot Australia 5G satellite IoT is built to fit into current systems perfectly, without the need for companies to upgrade their devices or SIM cards.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Seamless Integration, No Hardware Modifications</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">What sets Sateliot apart is that it can offer standards-based, 3GPP-compliant connectivity. Sateliot\'s solution does not need new hardware or software updates, unlike traditional satellite solutions. Sateliot\'s solution allows enterprises to deploy with their current IoT devices and SIMs. This plug-and-play solution saves a lot of money and decreases deployment time.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The technology is especially valuable in Australia, where distances are enormous and the terrain is unforgiving, with conventional connectivity being challenging. By combining satellite coverage with land networks, Sateliot offers a hybrid solution that offers continuity over deserts, mountains, and coastlines as well.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Constructing Local Linkages through Sectoral Partnership</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In an effort to become more rooted in the local IoT ecosystem, Sateliot became a member of the IoT Alliance Australia (IoTAA), Australia\'s leading industry association for IoT innovation. Membership in the association allows Sateliot to participate in national debate on connectivity standards, digital infrastructure, and rural inclusion.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The company is also working in association with Australian partners to put its services in place in the following industries:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Wildlife and livestock monitoring</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Fleet tracking and asset management</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Smart farming</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Remote environmental data acquisition</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">These collaborations show how Sateliot Australia 5G satellite IoT can serve real, urgent requirements on the continent. Supported by leading International Investors Globally, Sateliot enjoys robust financial and strategic support.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Backed by the Spanish Government, the European Investment Bank, and <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/03/fcc-probe-investigation-into-chinese-electronics-and-telecom-firms\">telecommunications</a></span> industry leaders such as Deutsche Telekom and Telef&oacute;nica, the company is growing vigorously. Its latest &euro;70 million Series B investment guarantees deployment of additional satellites and expansion overseas on a large scale.</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-05-13', '23:47:10', 'sateliot-australia-5g-satellite-iot-set-for-15m-expansion', 'article/visionaries-network-sateliot-australia-5g-satellite-iot-set.webp', 'Sateliot Australia 5G Satellite IoT Set for $15M Expansion', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-sateliot-australia-5g-satellite-iot-set.webp', 5, 2025, 'Sateliot, 5G, satellite IoT, Australia, expansion, IoT network, space tech, visionaries network, remote monitoring, satellite communication, low Earth orbit, IoT devices, $15M investment, telecom, smart infrastructure', 'Sateliot plans a $15M expansion of its 5G satellite IoT network in Australia, enhancing connectivity for smart devices in remote and rural areas.', 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0),
(185, NULL, 'Zoox Robotaxi to Launch in 2025 with California Facility', 'Zoox Robotaxi Set for 2025 Launch with New California Facility', 'iot-and-robotics', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Amazon\'s self-driving car unit Zoox is going into high gear as it readies to introduce its first U.S. commercial robotaxi services. Next year, the company will open a new factory in California\'s Bay Area, according to the Financial Times. The new capacity will massively boost production levels and enable Zoox\'s larger vision for self-driving city mobility.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Now based in a smaller Fremont building, <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://zoox.com/\">Zoox</a></span> is poised to move beyond pilot projects into actual service. With operating and financial support from <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/03/amazon-retail-chief-stresses-balance-between-cost-cutting-and-innovation\">Amazon</a></span>, the company is well-positioned as one of the leading players in the crowded autonomous space.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Purpose-Built Vehicles Specifically for Autonomy</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Unlike other driverless car manufacturers that modify current models, Zoox manufactures cars from the ground up. It is a square, symmetrical vehicle with no steering wheel and pedals. Face-to-face, passengers ride inside a spacious cabin &mdash; a configuration intended for driverless transit.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This unique car design is all part of Zoox\'s vision to create a new type of ride-hailing experience. Co-founder of Zoox Jesse Levinson told FT in an interview that the company is preparing \"to make hundreds and then thousands\" of cars, ramping up from the two dozen units that are being tested in six U.S. cities.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Zoox Robotaxi to Launch in Las Vegas and San Francisco</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The much-anticipated Zoox robotaxi service will debut in Las Vegas later this autumn, followed by San Francisco. Both cities provide high-density urban settings best for driverless transportation testing and rollout. The growth hub will facilitate these rollouts, also acting as an assembly base, fleet maintenance, and software support facility.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">By launching in two large metropolitan areas, Zoox will establish public trust and accrue valuable performance information. The initial markets will pave the way for national rollout, introducing self-driving mobility to additional U.S. cities in the near term.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>New Regulatory Ecosystem Facilitates AV Development </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Zoox\'s growth comes at a time of greater leeway in the U.S. from federal regulators towards autonomous technology. These are recent government measures such as exemptions from specific safety requirements as well as relaxed regulations on accident reporting. Such relaxing of regulations would facilitate the deployment of robotaxi fleets at a faster pace.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">However, safety is a concern. Zoox, and companies like Waymo and Cruise, have been questioned by federal regulators looking into the reliability and performance of autonomous vehicles. It will be crucial to navigate this complex regulatory environment as the industry continues to evolve.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Amazon\'s Investment Gives Zoox Strategic Edge</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Amazon\'s purchase of Zoox in 2020 gave the start-up a significant fillip &mdash; not just financially, but operationally. Speculation is rife that in addition to ride-hailing, Zoox\'s platform can be used for autonomous delivery of packages, possibly supplementing Amazon\'s vast e-commerce network.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">What sets Zoox apart from AV competitors is its vertically integrated strategy. Instead of selling its cars, the company will keep its own fleet of Zoox robotaxis. This end-to-end control lets Zoox be in charge of each phase of the passenger experience, from maintenance of the cars to in-app ride bookings.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br><strong>No Drivers in a Future World? </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Zoox robotaxi service is a groundbreaking step toward a world in which ride-hailing doesn\'t require a human driver behind the wheel. If its first public rollouts in 2025 go well, Zoox can be a trailblazer in a sector that\'s likely to transform transport in the coming decade.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With deep pockets, creative product design, and regulatory tailwinds, Zoox is creating not just a car &mdash; but an end-to-end autonomous mobility platform. Next year will be a test case, and everybody is waiting to see how the company executes its ambitious plan.</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-05-13', '23:57:37', 'zoox-robotaxi-set-for-2025-launch-with-new-california-facility', 'article/visionaries-network-zoox-robotaxi-set-for-2025-launch.webp', 'Zoox Robotaxi Set for 2025 Launch with New California Facility', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-zoox-robotaxi-set-for-2025-launch.webp', 5, 2025, 'Zoox, robotaxi, autonomous vehicles, 2025 launch, California, self-driving car, Amazon, mobility, visionaries network, electric vehicle, smart transport, Zoox facility, future mobility, ride-hailing, tech innovation', 'Zoox plans to launch its autonomous robotaxi service in 2025, supported by a new state-of-the-art facility in California.', 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0),
(186, NULL, 'Dubai&rsquo;s Grand Millennium Hotel Offers 30% Off for Crypto', 'Grand Millennium Crypto-Friendly Hotel in Dubai Offers 30% Off', 'blockchain and cryptocurrency', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In a historic collaboration of luxury&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/05/doordash-acquires-sevenrooms-to-expand-hospitality-crm-tools\">hospitality</a></span> and digital finance, <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.millenniumhotels.com/\">Grand Millennium Hotel Dubai</a></span>, a crypto-friendly hotel, has now officially partnered with international cryptocurrency exchange Bybit. The Abu Dhabi-based hotel has announced Tuesday, May 12, that it will now provide customers with up to 30% discounts for those who pay with their Bybit Card&mdash;a major incentive for crypto users to access luxury experiences in the UAE.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>A Breakthrough for Crypto Tourism</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Bybit and Grand Millennium Dubai Hotel collaboration was cemented in a signing ceremony that took place on May 9. The two parties\' executives came together to commemorate what they refer to as a milestone move in lifestyle and travel. From serviced apartments and luxury suites to dining and meeting function spaces, all of the hotel\'s amenities, minus one, will be offered at reduced prices to Bybit Card holders.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&ldquo;This collaboration is an indication of the way that the future of lifestyle and travel is going,\" says <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/giacomopuntel/\">Giacomo Puntel, General Manager of Grand Millennium Hotel Dubai</a></span>. \"We\'re thrilled to make luxury accessible to the crypto-aware traveler.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Why This Crypto Hotel Transaction Matters</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The campaign is not just a publicity stunt. It\'s evidence of an even bigger, fast-growing trend in crypto-friendly travel. As digital currencies become increasingly mainstream, hotels, airlines, and retail stores are seeking ways to attract tech-savvy customers who wish to pay with cryptocurrency.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Bybit, with its fast-expanding crypto exchange and cutting-edge card program, already has over 1.7 million registered users globally. Bybit cardholders are able to pay merchants globally using their crypto by converting it to fiat at the point of purchase. With this Dubai hotel promotion, the company is again demonstrating its dedication to making it rewarding and convenient to pay with crypto.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\"Bybit is committed to bringing crypto payments into everyday expenditure and everyday luxury for our users,\" said Helen Liu, Partner and COO of Bybit. \"Dubai is among the world\'s most crypto-embracing cities. This alliance reflects our determination to enable crypto adoption in every sphere of life.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>A Crypto-Friendly Dubai Hotel Emerges to the Fore</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">For anyone in need of a crypto-friendly hotel in Dubai, Grand Millennium now takes the top spot. One of a handful but increasing number of high-end properties welcoming crypto payments as the new norm, the hotel isn\'t just a convenient option for tech-savvy travelers, but it puts Dubai on the world map of global leaders for adopting cryptocurrency.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Dubai was in the headlines this year with its foray into crypto as an accepted currency for public service charges, and Emarat pioneered MENA with the acceptance of digital currency payments for fuel. This expanding ecosystem is making the UAE more appealing than ever to digital nomads, entrepreneurs, and crypto investors.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>What Bybit Cardholders Receive</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Bybit cardholders paying for purchases at Grand Millennium Hotel Dubai can enjoy:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Room booking with up to 30% discount</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->In-house bar and restaurant special offers</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Reduced event and meeting room rates</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Banquet and catering service discounts</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Long-term stay special packages in serviced apartments</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This kind of offering makes Grand Millennium a crypto-friendly hotel in Dubai, a hotel that is responsive to the needs and desires of the contemporary traveler.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Final Thoughts </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Whether it is for a business trip, a vacation, or a long holiday, having a hotel like Grand Millennium in Dubai, which is so crypto-friendly, gives owners of digital currencies an attractive incentive to make Dubai their next destination for holidaying. The more locations are opened up for payment by cryptocurrency, the image of the city as a visionary, blockchain-friendly hub only enhances.</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-05-14', '00:04:17', 'grand-millennium-crypto-friendly-hotel-in-dubai-offers-30-off', 'article/visionaries-network-grand-millenium-crypto-friendly-hotel-in dubai.webp', 'Grand Millennium Crypto-Friendly Hotel in Dubai Offers 30% Off', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-grand-millenium-crypto-friendly-hotel-in dubai.webp', 5, 2025, 'Grand Millennium, Dubai hotel, crypto-friendly, cryptocurrency payments, hotel discount, travel deals, blockchain, Bitcoin, Ethereum, digital currency, crypto tourism, luxury stay, visionaries network, crypto hotel, smart travel', 'Grand Millennium Hotel Dubai offers 30% off for guests paying with cryptocurrency, embracing digital payments in the luxury travel space.', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(187, NULL, 'Valve Deckard Leak Fuels New VR Headset Rumors', 'Valve Deckard Leak Sparks Fresh VR Headset Release Rumors', 'ai vr and automation', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The virtual reality space is on fire in 2025. Apple, Meta, Sony, and HTC have all released new headsets, and interest is growing fast. But&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.valvesoftware.com/en/\">Valve</a></span> VR headset rumors are the topic of interest these days regarding something a bit more mysterious&mdash;and maybe life-altering. It\'s known as the Valve Deckard by its internal codename.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">First hinted at back in 2021 via leaked patents and backdoor code, the fact that Valve has a next-gen headset has been an open secret. Now, fresh rumors indicate we might not need to wait until late 2025 to get it. In a report by <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.techradar.com/\">TechRadar</a></span> and information posted by trusted VR leaker, SadlyItsBradley, Valve has just started importing certain parts&mdash;specifically facial interfaces&mdash;for VR headsets.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This is a major indicator. Facial interfaces are among the last things to be put together inside a VR headset, and as such, production is going full-tilt. Though there is no promise that the headset will be on store shelves tomorrow, it may imply an earlier-than-expected release date. Late 2024 or early 2025 now seems to be a genuine prospect.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>A New Player in the Standalone VR Market?</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">If you\'ve already experienced the Valve Index, you\'ll appreciate the company\'s focus on <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/vr-for-alzheimers-detection-is-a-breakthrough-in-early-diagnosis\">premium VR</a></span>. But the Index required a powerful PC and external base stations&mdash;immersive, but clunky. With the Deckard project, Valve seems to be targeting a different demographic: wireless, standalone freedom.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Recent reports on the Steam backend confirm it. There are references to experimental ARM container tools and a Linux SteamVR Link driver from developers. These suggest that Valve is preparing its software for a headset that doesn\'t need to be plugged into a PC&mdash;putting it firmly in competition with the Meta Quest 3 and Apple Vision Pro.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">If so, Valve Deckard would place PC-grade VR in a single, cordless package. For players, it would provide butter-smooth graphics, HD screens, and the entire SteamVR library at their fingertips without a desktop environment.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>The Power of Silence</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In spite of all the rumors and leaks, Valve has still not officially confirmed the existence of the device. The tongue-in-cheek site IsValveDeckardOut.com still has a huge \"NO\" on the screen. It\'s a reference to Valve\'s notorious habit of remaining quiet until a product is 100% complete&mdash;a habit that fans have nicknamed \"Valve Time.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">All that aside, most signs point to something very real being just around the corner. Code names, controller references (apparently dubbed \"Roy\" in line with Blade Runner motifs), and now hardware imports&mdash;these are getting to be very telling signs that Valve Deckard is more than just a piece of paper.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Should You Wait?</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">If you\'re looking to buy a new VR headset in 2025, this is the million-dollar question. While headsets like the Meta Quest 3 and PSVR2 are already out, Deckard might be the one with the performance jump, especially for those who want the wireless version without compromise. Until Valve comments officially, it\'s all rumor. But whatever is certain: the latest updates on Valve VR headsets are more exciting than ever, and if rumors come true, the next great leap in VR is around the corner sooner than ever before.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br style=\"mso-special-character: line-break;\"><!--[endif]--></p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-05-14', '23:27:09', 'valve-deckard-leak-sparks-fresh-vr-headset-release-rumors', 'article/visionaries-network-valve-deckard-leak-sparks-fresh-vr-head.webp', 'Valve Deckard Leak Sparks Fresh VR Headset Release Rumors', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-valve-deckard-leak-sparks-fresh-vr-head.webp', 5, 2025, 'visionaries network, Deckard, VR headset, VR rumors, gaming, virtual reality, Valve leak, SteamVR, Deckard specs, headset release, VR tech, next-gen VR, gaming news, Valve Deckard 2025, Valve rumors', 'A fresh leak about Valve&#039;s Deckard headset has sparked new rumors about an upcoming next-gen VR device in development. Could a launch be near?', 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0),
(188, NULL, 'CareBand Patents Low-Power AI Wearable Tech', 'CareBand Secures Patent for Low-Power AI Wearable Technology', 'wearable technology', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In a significant breakthrough in next-generation wearables technology, CareBand, a world leader in context-aware health and safety wearables, has been awarded U.S. Patent No. 12,290,339 for its \"Edge Computing System with Low Power Wide Area Network Connectivity and Autonomous or Semi&ndash;Autonomous Machine Learning.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">A patent for an end-to-end system that converts raw sensor inputs into real-time actionable data&mdash;without the need for constant cloud connectivity&mdash;has just been issued.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With the fusion of edge computing, machine learning, and low-power wide area networking (LPWAN), the solution of <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://carebandremembers.com/\">CareBand</a></span> is best suited for long-term, intelligent monitoring in high-risk segments like eldercare, lone-worker protection, and hazardous industrial settings.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Why It Matters Today</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The timing here is crucial. The world is faced with an intersection of challenges that CareBand\'s patented solution is particularly built to reverse:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>Aging Population:</strong> Over 57 million individuals have dementia globally, and it is increasing by 10 million new cases each year. Continuous, private, and safe monitoring is becoming an utmost priority in healthcare.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>Growth of Edge Computing: </strong>Comarch\'s 2025 Trends report states that edge computing is booming&mdash;projected to expand from $60 billion in 2024 to $110 billion in 2029. Edge systems enable quicker, proximate decision-making, minimizing latency and safeguarding user privacy.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>Battery Constraints:</strong> Conventional cellular-powered wearables must be recharged constantly, which restricts their utility. CareBand\'s hybrid LPWAN approach allows months of battery life, which means low-maintenance, uninterrupted monitoring.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>What the Patent Includes</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">CareBand\'s new patent outlines a technologically advanced yet rational solution to actual problems:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Dual-Chip Architecture:</strong> A machine learning-based inference engine and a sub&ndash;GHz LPWAN microcontroller enable fall, wandering, or gas exposure incidents to be handled on-device without battery drain.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Event-Based Transmission:</strong> Instead of forwarding continuous data, the system forwards useful events individually, saving bandwidth and energy.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Multi-Protocol Radio Stack:</strong> Support for prominent LPWAN protocols like LoRaWAN, NB&ndash;IoT, Sigfox, Amazon Sidewalk, and even satellite LPWAN makes it versatile for global deployments.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Smart, Domain-Trained Models:</strong> The solution employs domain-trained models for specific settings like dementia care, factory safety, and remote workforce monitoring, with greater accuracy and fewer false alarms.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>The Future of Smart Monitoring</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/meta-smart-glasses-october-2025-new-features-and-launch-details\">wearable technology</a></span> matures from consumer trends to critical infrastructure, CareBand leads the way with a platform designed for real-world resilience and reliability. Its patented platform demonstrates to the world how edge AI combined with low-power design can dramatically improve safety outcomes with reduced infrastructure needs.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With the aging population and the need for more efficient safety devices by employers, this technology could not have come at a better time. CareBand technology is not just longer battery life&mdash;it\'s longer, safer, and independent living.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br style=\"mso-special-character: line-break;\"><!-- [if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--><br style=\"mso-special-character: line-break;\"><!--[endif]--></p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-05-14', '23:34:34', 'careband-secures-patent-for-low-power-ai-wearable-technology', 'article/visionaries-network-careband-secures-patent-for-low-power-ai-wearable.webp', 'CareBand Secures Patent for Low-Power AI Wearable Technology', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-careband-secures-patent-for-low-power-ai-wearable.webp', 5, 2025, 'CareBand, AI wearable, visionaries netwok, low-power technology, health tech, wearable AI, senior safety, IoT, elder care, smart wearables, innovation, medical device, wearable patent, AI health, tech news', 'CareBand has secured a new patent for low-power AI wearable technology, advancing smart health solutions for elder care and remote patient monitoring.', 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0),
(189, '', 'Willis Unveils Fintech Insurance with FinTech Plus', 'Willis Launches Fintech Insurance Solutions with FinTech Plus', 'banking and fintech', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">International insurance broker Willis, a business of WTW, has launched&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.wtwco.com/en-gb/solutions/products/fintech-plus\">FinTech Plus</a></span>, a new insurance product that has been customized to meet the evolving requirements of financial technology firms across the world.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Developed in collaboration between Great Britain and the United States, Willis FinTech specialists, FinTech Plus addresses the more sophisticated challenges of expansion in an increasingly digitally integrated, financially fueled marketplace. Featuring a single proposal template and concise policy language, the solution streamlines the process of insurance so fintech firms can obtain coverage easily and swiftly.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This launch positions FinTech Plus as a leader among<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/pay10-leads-uae-with-first-live-open-finance-launch\"> fintech</a></span> insurance products available in the market today. It offers protection in the most important areas of cyber and financial risk, supported by a handpicked panel of Lloyd\'s syndicates and London market insurers renowned for their extensive sector knowledge.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\"FinTech Plus is a testament to Willis\' commitment to innovation and our alignment across the global network,\" said <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/trenton-mcnee-5b315b2a/\">Trenton McNee, Great Britain fintech and digital assets industry leader.</a></span> \"Through collaboration with our U.S. colleagues, we created a lively solution that empowers fintech leaders on their journey to scale.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Created for Startup Development and International Growth</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">FinTech Plus is unique because it is highly adaptable, meaning it can handle businesses at all phases from scale-up to start-up. Coverage adjusts to meet the requirements of a firm, so it will suit companies that are facing high growth as well as increasing regulatory stress.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Especially, this insurance offering is designed to speak to C-suite executives, founders, and risk managers directly. By eliminating unnecessary complexity, it delivers what Willis refers to as \"clarity, confidence, and a smarter way to approach risk.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The product is in response to a trend in the industry towards responsive, sector-led solutions. The traditional insurance models struggle to cope with quickly evolving sectors like fintech, and FinTech Plus will fill this gap by offering fintech insurance solutions that are responsive and robust.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Built with Global Vision FinTech Plus is not only about innovative coverage&mdash;it\'s also a testament to cross-border collaboration. Attendees from both sides of the Atlantic provided thoughtful commentary on regulatory environments, digital infrastructure, and operational risk.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\"FinTech Plus is evidence of our innovative approach to fintech risk management,\" stated <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/anthonyrapa/\">Anthony Rapa, Willis\'s North America fintech industry leader</a></span>. \"By combining our expertise with collaboration with innovative, flexible specialist insurers, we have created a product that will allow fintech innovators to innovate without restraint.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>A Smarter Insurance Model for Today\'s Fintech</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">FinTech Plus arrives when fintech insurance products must keep pace with the industry that they are insuring. Whether digital lending and embedded finance startups or cryptocurrency platforms, fintech today must scale and adapt&mdash;the type of protection that does not include stacks of paperwork and vintage policy templates.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">For FinTech companies wanting insurance that works just like they do&mdash;rapidly, nimbly, and responsively&mdash;Willis\'s FinTech Plus is a policy that\'s more than a policy. It\'s a growth partner.</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-05-14', '23:54:14', 'willis-launches-fintech-insurance-solutions-with-fintech-plus', 'article/visionaries-network-willis-launches-fintech-insurance-solutions.webp', 'Willis Launches Fintech Insurance Solutions with FinTech Plus', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-willis-launches-fintech-insurance-solutions.webp', 5, 2025, 'visionaries network, FinTech Plus, fintech insurance, insurtech, digital insurance, financial technology, insurance solutions, fintech, Willis news, smart insurance, tech partnership, FinTech launch, insurance tech, fintech services, fintech innovation', 'Willis partners with FinTech Plus to launch innovative fintech insurance solutions, aiming to modernize coverage through digital platforms and smart technologies.', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(190, NULL, 'Dubai Business Insights from Smart City Summit', 'Top Dubai Business Opportunities Revealed at Smart City Summit', 'smart city and security infrastructure', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In the recently conducted&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://news.smartcitiescouncil.com/news/post/scc-announces-smart-cities-summit-north-america-2025\">Smart Cities Summit North America 2025 in San Francisco</a></span>, more than 450 global government, business, and educational leaders gathered to share ideas on how cities of the future can be safer, smarter, and greener.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">One of the summit\'s highlights is the partnership between IFZA (International Free Zone Authority), Dubai\'s premier free zone community, and the <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://smartcitiescouncil.com/\">Smart Cities Council (SCC).</a></span> Their partnership is a testament to a powerful new direction for Dubai business opportunities and global innovation.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The session focused on \"Public Safety, AI, and the Middle East in Focus,\" and IFZA led the way in demonstrating how Dubai is emerging as a global startup and entrepreneurial ecosystem. As one of Dubai\'s leading free zones, IFZA demonstrated how free economic zones and smart cities can work together and drive economic transformation and global collaboration.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\"Dubai is not just an economic prospect&mdash;it\'s a vision for the future,\" said <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/holger-schlechter-39b5a814/\">Holger Schlechter, IFZA CFO</a></span>. \"We are privileged to partner with Smart Cities Council to empower entrepreneurs with new paths to success by connecting them with Dubai business opportunities that are inclusive, fast-paced, and borderless.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Encouraging Business Setup in Dubai Like Never Before</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">For <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/why-superpowers-affordable-longevity-app-is-booming\">startups</a></span> and entrepreneurs who want to set up a business hassle-free in Dubai, <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://ifza.com/en/ifza-smart-cities-global-growth-scsa-2025/\">IFZA</a></span> is the go-to choice. With streamlined registration processes, tax-free benefits, and international accreditation, IFZA provides the ideal platform for entrepreneurs to scale quickly and expand in the high-growth markets of the Middle East, Africa, and Asia.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The summit also saw the announcement of two important initiatives:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Smart Cities Council Middle East &ndash; an organization established to address increasing demand for Middle Eastern smart city solutions.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Smart Cities Academy&trade; &ndash; a learning platform committed to teaching professionals and leaders about smart city innovation.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Corey Gray, President of the Smart Cities Council, referred to the power of global collaboration: \"By connecting Silicon Valley\'s innovation with Dubai\'s dynamic business community, we\'re giving startups the chance to pilot and scale their solutions globally.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Dubai: A World-Class Smart City Leader</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Dubai is the city innovation leader, placed 4th in the 2025 IMD Smart Cities Index. With its strong digital infrastructure, smart government services, and strategic location, it is the place to be for such smart city investments as Saudi Arabia\'s NEOM and Egypt\'s New Cairo.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Perhaps the most highly awaited launch of the summit was Scale360, IFZA\'s open innovation platform with Plug and Play. The platform connects international startups with corporate partners, investors, and emerging markets&mdash;offering new Dubai business opportunities for innovators worldwide.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Why More American Startups Are Moving to Dubai</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With over 1,500 U.S. businesses already established in the UAE&mdash;Microsoft, Uber, and Cleveland Clinic are just a few of them&mdash;the UAE is already a hotbed of interest for U.S. businesses seeking to expand internationally. And with 75% of the country\'s GDP now driven by non-oil industries, the region is more and more tech- and innovation-driven.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">IFZA\'s attendance at the summit is the launching of its US expansion strategy, with major upcoming events including Deep Tech Week San Francisco (June 2025) and Deep Tech Week Dubai (November 2025). These innovations will create new bridges between Dubai\'s growing investor community and US startups, further fueling the pipeline of Dubai business opportunities for international entrepreneurs.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br style=\"mso-special-character: line-break;\"><!--[endif]--></p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-05-16', '00:12:36', 'top-dubai-business-opportunities-revealed-at-smart-city-summit', 'article/visionaries-network-top-dubai-business-opportunities-reveal.webp', 'Top Dubai Business Opportunities Revealed at Smart City Summit', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-top-dubai-business-opportunities-reveal.webp', 5, 2025, 'Dubai, Smart City Summit, business opportunities, UAE economy, smart tech, innovation, startups, Dubai tech, visionaries network, smart cities, entrepreneurship, MENA business, future cities, digital transformation, Dubai summit', 'Explore top business opportunities in Dubai unveiled at the Smart City Summit, driving innovation, investment, and growth in the region&#039;s digital economy.', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(191, NULL, 'Apyx Medical&rsquo;s Body Contouring System FDA-Cleared', 'Apyx Medical&#039;s Body Contouring System Cleared by FDA for 2025', 'healthcare and medical devices', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://apyxmedical.com/\">Apyx Medical</a></span> is preparing for the commercial availability of its latest innovation&mdash;the Apyx body contouring system, branded as AYON&mdash;following FDA clearance for a broad range of aesthetic treatments. This one-platform technology is designed to help surgeons who perform fat reduction, skin tightening, and other body contouring treatments, combining a number of technologies into one advanced device.<br><br>The heart of AYON is Apyx\'s proprietary Renuvion technology, which uses helium plasma and radiofrequency energy to tighten and contract loose skin. The system also includes ultrasound-assisted liposuction and electrocoagulation, enabling the removal of excess tissue and contouring to be done more effectively. With these features, AYON is poised to meet the growing needs of patients who undergo significant body transformation.<br><br>The Apyx body contouring system will be aimed towards a targeted commercial launch in the second half of 2025, in which the company will be making the system available to targeted aesthetic and plastic surgeons.<br><br>&ldquo;The aesthetics market is anticipating a significant surge in body contouring treatments next year,\" <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/charlie-goodwin-1b294b3b/\">Apyx Medical CEO Charlie Goodwin</a></span> stated. &ldquo;Over 15 million patients already taking GLP-1RA anti-obesity medications are seeing rapid fat loss, and most are now looking for effective treatments for tightening loose, sagging skin. The AYON system addresses those needs in one platform.\"<br><br><strong>Aesthetic Market Trends with GLP-1Ras</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The treatment with GLP-1 receptor agonist drugs like Ozempic and Wegovy has revolutionized patient profiles in the aesthetic industry. Though the patients lose a considerable amount of weight within a few months, they are left with loose skin&mdash;particularly on the tummy, arms, and thighs. This has created a new need for skin tightening and body contouring procedures.<br><br>Apyx Medical\'s AYON system appears to be set to meet this emerging market. The Apyx body contouring system is able to accommodate both minimally invasive and traditional surgical procedures, which can accommodate the full spectrum of treatments, ranging from minor recontouring to more thorough body sculpting.<br><br>Market figures by GlobalData project that the aesthetic body contouring device market will grow from $721 million in 2024 to nearly $978 million by 2034. Non-invasive and minimally invasive devices will be the trend, with nearly 60% of market share coming from non-invasive solutions.<br><br><strong>An Emerging, Competitive Climate</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The North American body contouring devices market is competitive, with market leaders providing sought-after solutions like CoolSculpting by market leaders Allergan Aesthetics (a subsidiary of AbbVie). AYON is distinct as it is multifunctional and comes with the additional advantage of Renuvion.<br><br>In the UK, the British Association of Aesthetic Plastic Surgeons (BAAPS) recently released statistics of a 5% increase in cosmetic surgery in 2024, including liposuction, abdominoplasty, and other body-focused procedures. With patients all over the world wishing to preserve the results of severe weight loss, technology like the AYON is more and more relevant.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Surgeons and Patients Gain from Integration</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">What makes the Apyx body contouring system different from the others in the market is its effectiveness and range. To clinics, it offers a single machine that reduces the utilization of several machines, saves space, and facilitates training.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">To patients, the integration of the technologies may mean shorter treatment time, less cutting, and better post-procedure results. As aesthetics moves towards increasingly result- and patient-focused treatments, AYON may be a flagship device for result-based practices.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/05/neuralink-brain-chip-for-speech-impairment-gets-fda-nod\">FDA clearance</a></span> in hand and strategic roll-out on standby, Apyx Medical is positioned at the forefront of an increasingly fast-moving, opportunity-filled market.<br><br><br style=\"mso-special-character: line-break;\"><!-- [if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--><br style=\"mso-special-character: line-break;\"><!--[endif]--></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br style=\"mso-special-character: line-break;\"><!-- [if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--><br style=\"mso-special-character: line-break;\"><!--[endif]--></p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-05-16', '00:27:34', 'apyx-medicals-body-contouring-system-cleared-by-fda-for-2025', 'article/visionaries-network-apyx-medical-body-contouring-system.webp', 'Apyx Medical&#039;s Body Contouring System Cleared by FDA for 2025', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-apyx-medical-body-contouring-system.webp', 5, 2025, 'Apyx Medical, body contouring, FDA clearance, medical device, Renuvion, cosmetic surgery, visionaries network, non-invasive treatment, skin tightening, aesthetic medicine, FDA approval, beauty tech, plastic surgery, medical innovation, health tech', 'Apyx Medical receives FDA clearance for its advanced body contouring system, paving the way for innovative cosmetic treatments in 2025.', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0);
