(212, NULL, 'Mahindra BE6 XEV 9e Gets Wireless Apple CarPlay Update', 'Mahindra BE6 XEV 9e Wireless Apple CarPlay Update Rolls Out', 'ai vr and automation', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://auto.mahindra.com/\">Mahindra</a></span> has introduced a long-awaited software update to its electric SUV flagship lineup &mdash; the Mahindra BE6 and XEV 9e. The biggie? Wireless<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/03/apple-watch-upgrade-set-to-transform-wearables-by-2027\"> Apple</a></span> CarPlay and Android Auto. The Mahindra BE6 XEV 9e wireless Apple CarPlay update is a big one, fulfilling one of the largest promises the company made when the vehicles were put on sale.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Feature Now Available On All Trims</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The upgrade is now included on all new shipments of both models. No matter whether you opt for the affordable Pack One or the high-end Pack Three, you\'ll enjoy wireless connectivity out of the box. The upgrade puts an end to months of wait from customers eager to enjoy hassle-free <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/uk-startup-developing-blackberry-inspired-qwerty-smartphone\">smartphone</a></span> connectivity without the inconvenience of cables.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Mahindra has now formally confirmed that all factory-shipped BE6 and XEV 9e models come with this software pre-loaded. Yes, no more downloading or visits to the dealership for new buyers &mdash; a massive user experience and convenience win.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Built for High-Tech Cabins</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Both vehicles boast state-of-the-art triple-screen setups with 12.3-inch screens, an augmented reality head-up display, and a Qualcomm Snapdragon-based high-powered infotainment system. Mahindra BE6 XEV 9e wireless Apple CarPlay update integrates smoothly into this upscale hardware, with rapid response and silky user interface.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The connectivity upgrades also push into Mahindra\'s connected car ecosystem. Drivers now have the opportunity to enjoy wireless streaming of music, navigation, and app integration, along with entertainment app access and remote car control via the Mahindra mobile app. This makes the BE6 and XEV 9e competitive in the technology-driven market.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Present owners may need a visit</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">While new deliveries are now updated, current owners will need to visit their local Mahindra dealer to receive the Mahindra BE6 XEV 9e wireless Apple CarPlay update. A confirmed over-the-air (OTA) release has not been made by Mahindra yet, but an announcement should be imminent. Owners should contact their local service centers for specific instructions.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>XEV 9e: Luxurious Comfort Blended with Extended-Range Technology</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Starting at â‚¹21.9 lakh, the Mahindra XEV 9e is for individuals who desire luxury and innovation. It features a 656 km range, Level 2+ ADAS, a 16-speaker sound system, and in-cabin tech that immerses you &mdash; all of which are further enhanced now by the seamless connectivity that the new version offers.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With the Mahindra BE6 XEV 9e wireless Apple CarPlay update, the in-car experience is simplified even further so that drivers and passengers remain connected on the go without the need to use USB cables or third-party applications.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>BE6: Sporting Capability Coupled with Everyday Practicality</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Mahindra BE6, priced at â‚¹18.9 lakh, receives a sportier variant with 683 km range, quick acceleration, and a distinctive rear-wheel-drive layout. The fighter plane-inspired interior design is an immersive, driver-focused experience. The refresh adds a missing piece to the puzzle &mdash; wireless Apple CarPlay &mdash; giving drivers the best of both worlds: exhilarating performance and next-generation convenience.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Huge Demand, Fast Production </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Both models recorded an increase in bookings when they were launched, with over 30,000 bookings in the initial 24 hours. The XEV 9e has marginally taken the lead, with 59% of the total bookings. Mahindra is increasing production to reduce waiting time, with over 11,000 units already shipped.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-05-28', '23:14:24', 'mahindra-be6-xev-9e-wireless-apple-carplay-update-rolls-out', 'article/visionaries-network-mahindra-be6-xev-9e-wireless-apple-carplay-update.webp', 'Mahindra BE6 XEV 9e Wireless Apple CarPlay Update Rolls Out', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-mahindra-be6-xev-9e-wireless-apple-carplay-update.webp', 5, 2025, 'Mahindra, BE6, XEV 9e, Apple CarPlay, wireless update, Mahindra BE6 features, infotainment, SUV, visionary network, software update, car tech, visionaries network, smart car, auto news, Mahindra electric', 'Mahindra rolls out a wireless Apple CarPlay update for the BE6 XEV 9e, enhancing in-car connectivity and infotainment features.', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(213, '', 'Harry Potter HBO 2025: Meet the New Hogwarts Trio', 'Harry Potter HBO Cast 2025: Meet the New Trio at Hogwarts', 'Entertainment and Recreation', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Wizarding World is officially returning&mdash;and with an all-new trio at the center. HBO recently released the Harry Potter HBO cast 2025, introducing new young talents to play Harry, Ron, and Hermione in the new web series retelling of J.K. Rowling\'s beloved books. The news, shared on Instagram, got the internet buzzing even as HBO took a strategic step back to disable comments on the post in an attempt to protect the new cast from early online criticism.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>A New Golden Trio</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dominic_McLaughlin\">Dominic McLaughlin</a></span> played the role of Harry Potter, taking over from Daniel Radcliffe. He is joined by Arabella Stanton as Hermione Granger and Alastair Stout as Ron Weasley. HBO did their casting under a themed announcement post:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\"Dear Mr. Potter, Miss Granger, and Mr. Weasley: We are pleased to inform you that you are accepted at Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Over 30,000 hopefuls auditioned following HBO\'s casting call last year, making the final three\'s choice a huge moment. The young actors will bear the huge burden of the original films\' legacy as they take the story forward for a new generation.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Veteran Stars Join the Ranks</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Harry Potter HBO cast 2025 is not complete without the golden trio. The series has a great supporting cast:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->John Lithgow as Professor Albus Dumbledore</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Janet McTeer as Minerva McGonagall</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Paapa Essiedu as Severus Snape</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Nick Frost as Rubeus Hagrid</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Luke Thallon as Professor Quirrell</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Paul Whitehouse as Argus Filch</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Francesca Gardiner, with a prestige drama background, will serve as showrunner and executive producer. She\'s also busy adapting the scripts so that the show will still be extremely faithful to the seven books by J.K. Rowling.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>A Strategic Move: Comments Disabled</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Interestingly, HBO disabled the comments for the Instagram post about the new Harry Potter HBO cast 2025. While fans were able to comment elsewhere on studio posts, this one was closed down. The action seems to be a defensive measure to protect the young actors from the crudeness of early internet criticism.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Social media responses had already shifted to other sites such as X (formerly Twitter). One of the commenters said, \"Wish the kids luck. They\'re going to be under a microscope the rest of their lives.\" Some people posted throwback pictures of Daniel Radcliffe, Rupert Grint, and Emma Watson, and there were some arguing about the casting&mdash;namely the much-debated Paapa Essiedu in the role of Snape.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>What Lies Ahead</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The HBO reboot of Harry Potter is one of the most eagerly anticipated shows in production right now. It\'ll likely be on for several seasons, one for every one of the seven books. The transition to cast new actors has excited and unsettled viewers, but the global fan base for the series is holding its breath to see how the magic will be recast.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With an experienced cast in the background and an eager ensemble eager to enter their iconic roles, the Harry Potter HBO cast 2025 could be the beginning of a new era for the Wizarding World. Only time will tell if the fans will embrace this new vision or not, but for now, the limelight is once again at Hogwarts.</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-05-28', '00:01:46', 'harry-potter-hbo-cast-2025-meet-the-new-trio-at-hogwarts', 'article/visionaries-network-harry-porter-hbo-cast-2025.webp', 'Harry Potter HBO Cast 2025: Meet the New Trio at Hogwarts', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-harry-porter-hbo-cast-2025.webp', 5, 2025, 'Harry Potter, HBO series, 2025 cast, new trio, Hogwarts, visionary network, Hermione, Ron, Harry, visionaries network, wizarding world, TV show, fantasy series, new actors, Hogwarts students', 'Discover the new Harry, Hermione, and Ron in HBO&rsquo;s 2025 Harry Potter reboot. Meet the fresh faces at Hogwarts!', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(214, NULL, 'Charles Schwab Stock Forecast 2025: Buy SCHW Now?', 'Charles Schwab Stock Forecast 2025: Is SCHW a Smart Buy Now?', 'banking and fintech', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.schwab.com/?msockid=2aad64c6e205683d3ed37785e3f26953\">Charles Schwab Corporation</a></span>, a financial giant, is gaining growing attention from investors seeking stability and growth over the long term. With its market capitalization of $161.04 billion and its 37-year record of uninterrupted dividend <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/ebay-klarna-partnership-2025-brings-flexible-payments-to-the-us\">payments</a></span>, Schwab continues to prove its resilience. For investors seeking the Charles Schwab stock forecast 2025, the company\'s current momentum and potential for the future suggest a bright destiny in an otherwise uncertain <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/05/treasury-confirms-end-of-penny-production-usa-by-2026\">financial</a></span> landscape.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Current Performance Highlights</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With interest rate volatility and increased competition, Schwab has shown phenomenal financial strength. SCHW has shown a perfect Piotroski Score of 9, a wonderful indication of a healthy balance sheet, InvestingPro says. Schwab has shown EPS of $3.30 for the past twelve months, and EPS will increase to $4.26 by the end of FY 2025, according to estimates.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This growth trajectory places Schwab ahead of its peers in the brokerage category as well as overall financial services industry standards. Its impressive PEG ratio of 0.68 shows that the stock has a solid value proposition relative to its future growth.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Strategic Initiatives Fuelling Growth</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Schwab\'s acquisition of TD Ameritrade has been successful, bringing 1.3 million active traders onto its platform, injecting Net New Assets (NNA) and boosting Return on Client Assets (ROCA). Looking to further expand product offerings&mdash;such as cryptocurrency trading, pending regulatory approval&mdash;Schwab is set to keep innovating.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">To the fore, management has identified several key drivers of growth:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Aiming for 5&ndash;7% yearly NNA growth</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Higher securities lending penetration</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Installation of sophisticated risk management software</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Spending $20 billion on projected excess funds on share repurchases and dividend increases by 2027</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">These efforts are the foundation of setting the Charles Schwab stock forecast 2025, which most analysts see with positive expectations.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Competitive Position and Market Outlook</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In spite of the intense competition from both established brokers and<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/05/willis-launches-fintech-insurance-solutions-with-fintech-plus\"> fintech</a></span> companies, the full-service package and brand name of Schwab have allowed it to hold onto market share. Holding institutional clients in addition to gaining young investors is a strategy that ensures long-term survival.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Schwab\'s platform versatility&mdash;providing everything from plain-vanilla brokerage accounts to high-end wealth management&mdash;is a competitive advantage. Analysts observe that such diversification is a major reason for optimistic expectations for the Charles Schwab stock forecast 2025.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Risks and Considerations</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">No security is entirely risk-free, and SCHW is not an exception:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>Interest rate sensitivity:</strong> Interest rates influence profitability at Schwab, where changes impact net interest income</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>Regulatory headwinds:</strong> Upcoming changes in U.S. financial regulations will temper product innovations</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>Fee compression:</strong> Increased competition might prompt Schwab to drop fees or splurge on platform upgrades</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">All the same, Schwab\'s solid equity base and conservative hedging cushion the company against these.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Analyst Targets and Valuation Metrics</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">SCHW is popular among leading analysts. Below are price forecasts for 2025:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo3;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Goldman Sachs: $100</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo3;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Citi Research: $102</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo3;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Deutsche Bank: $98</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo3;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->JMP Securities: $94</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">These estimates represent a consensus that Schwab is underpriced relative to its future earnings and future cash flows.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Conclusion: Is SCHW a Wise Purchase in 2025? </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With solid finances, strategic planning, and aggressive capital management, Schwab is ready to grow. Its consistent performance and flexibility have turned it into a retail and institutional investor darling.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">For investors taking a look at the Charles Schwab stock in 2025, the direction is toward sustained appreciation, backed by judicious implementation and shareholder-centric strategy. For income, growth, or both, SCHW offers a good balance and a great opportunity in the new financial age.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-05-29', '00:10:04', 'charles-schwab-stock-forecast-2025-is-schw-a-smart-buy-now', 'article/visionaries-netwok-charles-schwab-stock-forecast-2025.webp', 'Charles Schwab Stock Forecast 2025: Is SCHW a Smart Buy Now?', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-netwok-charles-schwab-stock-forecast-2025.webp', 5, 2025, 'Charles Schwab, SCHW stock, stock forecast, visionaries network, investment, stock analysis, buy SCHW, stock market, financial services, brokerage, investing, smart buy, portfolio, finance news, SCHW performance', 'Explore the 2025 stock forecast for Charles Schwab (SCHW). Is it a smart investment now? Key insights and analysis ahead.', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(215, NULL, 'Eco-Friendly Games to Shine at Summer Game Fest 2025', 'Eco-Friendly Video Games 2025 to Shine at Summer Game Fest', 'Entertainment and Recreation', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Non-profit business&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://partners.planetplay.com/\">PlanetPlay</a></span> is presenting its Green Games Showcase on June 7, 2025, at <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.summergamefest.com/\">Summer Game Fest</a></span>, a highly awaited international gaming festival every year. The showcase will present a handpicked set of eco-friendly video games 2025, with the aim of raising awareness regarding climate change, sustainability, and the power of play to build a better world.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The tournament will be hosted live in front of an audience by renowned gaming journalist Will Freeman, a regular contributor to GamesIndustry.biz. It will feature innovative games that entertain and inform, created by leading studios like Amazon Games, Lockwood Publishing, Sharkmob, Team17, Netspeak Games, and Wicked Saints Studios.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Climate Action Through Gameplay</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">PlanetPlay\'s vision extends far beyond the promotion of green games. The company is committed to actually making a positive impact on the environment. The objective for this campaign is to raise $300,000 by June 30, 2025, to fund the planting of 50,000 trees in Timor-Leste, a country severely affected by deforestation. This reforestation project will be achieved through collaboration with WithOneSeed, a local non-profit dedicated to long-term land restoration.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Gaming groups, according to <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/rhea-loucas/\">PlanetPlay CEO Rhea Loucas</a></span>, have untapped potential for climate campaigning:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\"This is not an exhibition, it\'s an appeal. The <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/05/runehero-beta-prize-pool-offers-10k-in-web3-game-rewards\">gaming</a></span> community is one of the most enthusiastic and creative forces on the planet.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Industry Leaders Join the Conversation</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In addition to increasing the reach of the showcase, PlanetPlay ambassador and gaming legend Ian Livingstone will also appear live at the event for a Q&amp;A session. He will be joined by Freeman to discuss how games can drive change on climate and encourage gamers to take concrete action in their own lives.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Livingstone is among four new ambassadors PlanetPlay welcomed last month, including actress Briana Evigan and Formula E world champion Pascal Wehrlein, who are equally passionate about sustainability and digital activism.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Players Are Making a Difference Already</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">PlanetPlay has recently released fresh findings from its Play2Act survey, which it conducted in collaboration with the United Nations Development Program (UNDP). It\'s good news: nearly 50% of gamers indicated that they made sustainable changes&mdash;like decreasing electricity consumption or purchasing in-game items online&mdash;after playing climate-themed games.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">These findings verify that climate-friendly video games 2025 are able to influence behavior and help players become part of the solution.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Join the Green Gaming Movement </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The environmentally friendly video games 2025 exhibition is not just an event&mdash;it\'s a movement in the making. Developers are more and more creating games that incorporate environmental storytelling, resource management systems, and real-world impact projects.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As the trend picks up steam, the world of gaming is demonstrating that sustainability and fun do indeed go together.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">So, if you care about the planet and you enjoy gaming, mark June 7, 2025, in your calendar and tune into the Green Games Showcase at Summer Game Fest. Let\'s change gaming together as not just a source of enjoyment, but as a force for change on a global scale</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-05-29', '23:59:58', 'eco-friendly-video-games-2025-to-shine-at-summer-game-fest', 'article/visionaries-network-eco-friendly-video-games-2025.webp', 'Eco-Friendly Video Games 2025 to Shine at Summer Game Fest', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-eco-friendly-video-games-2025.webp', 5, 2025, 'eco-friendly games, green gaming, sustainable games, Summer Game Fest 2025, indie games, visionaries network, sustainable tech, eco-conscious, gaming trends, 2025 games, green events, video games, eco innovation, planet-friendly', 'Discover the top eco-friendly video games making waves at Summer Game Fest 2025 with sustainability-driven stories and green tech.', 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0),
(216, '', 'Finish College with Oklahoma Adult Degree Program', 'Finish College with the Oklahoma Adult Degree Completion Program', 'edtech and learning', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Things don\'t always work out as they should. The majority of Oklahoma adults began college with dreams, only to have life intervene in the way of work, family, or financial issues. But now, there is a second chance. The&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.reachhigher.org/\">Reach Higher initiative</a></span> is enabling adults to return to college and finish the degrees they put on hold.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This Oklahoma adult degree completion program is governed by the Oklahoma State Regents for Higher <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/05/alice-techs-ai-platform-raises-4-8m-to-personalize-learning\">Education</a></span> and was created to help adult students juggling more than one responsibility. With online classes, scholarships, and personalized counseling, it\'s having a real impact for people across the state.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>What is the Reach Higher Program?</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\"Reach Higher is a state degree completion program,\" says program manager Tisha Bradford. \"That\'s the advantage of it. You can be anywhere in the state. It\'s for adults who\'ve been to college but, for whatever reason, had to stop out. Now they\'d like to come back and complete that degree.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The program is geared towards the working adult. Regardless of whether you work full-time, have kids, or both, Reach Higher provides the support you need to go back to school on your schedule.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Designed for Real Life: Adapting Classes and Full Support</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Blending school with adult life is most likely the biggest challenge adults face in going back to school. Reach Higher confronts this challenge head-on by providing flexible class schedules&mdash;online, evening, and weekend classes that fit busy lifestyles.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Each of the 27 Oklahoma schools participating in the program has a navigator. The navigators work with the students one one-on-one every step of the way, from signing up to graduation. \"They assist you from where to park on day one to where to park when you receive your diploma,\" Bradford explains.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">They also help the students to apply for the Finish Line Scholarship, which provides grants to adult students seeking their degree.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Beyond scholarships, navigators help students access other community resources&mdash;like childcare or transportation support&mdash;to help remove the practical barriers to returning to college.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Who is Eligible? </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The program is for adult learners who have previously attended some college credits but never graduated. The program provides both associate\'s and bachelor\'s degree levels.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\"To qualify, you simply need to visit one of the 27 Oklahoma schools that belong to it,\" adds Bradford. \"It\'s all on our website, including the schools, the programs they have, and the individual to contact for that wonderful navigator I described.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This Oklahoma adult degree completion program is not about attending school again&mdash;it\'s about creating a path to a better tomorrow. If you\'re in need of a career change, looking for job stability, or completing a lifelong aspiration, Reach Higher can help.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>How to Get Started</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Interested adults can visit ReachHigherOK.org, the program\'s website. There, you can search schools, find scholarships, and even fill out a free student interest form. The form, once filled out and submitted, will go directly to Bradford and the navigator at your school of choice.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\"I contact them in a matter of seconds and say, \'Congratulations! I saw you. You\'re off to school. Let\'s get this done,&rsquo; \" Bradford says. \"And then I take them through the next steps.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">A Degree Within Reach Oklahoma is making education goals more accessible than ever before, even if the journey started years earlier. With personalized counseling, financial aid, and the convenience of online courses, the Oklahoma adult degree completion program is opening doors for thousands who thought college was out of reach.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">So, if you\'re one of the many Oklahomans with some college credit but no degree&mdash;listen up: it\'s never too late to complete what you began. And now, you don\'t have to do it alone.</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-05-30', '01:28:42', 'finish-college-with-the-oklahoma-adult-degree-completion-program', 'article/visionaries-network-finish-college-oklahoma-adult-degree-completion.webp', 'Finish College with the Oklahoma Adult Degree Completion Program', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-finish-college-oklahoma-adult-degree-completion.webp', 5, 2025, 'adult degree, Oklahoma college, degree completion, adult learners, flexible programs, higher education, career advancement, returning students, adult education, degree options, college access, nontraditional students, visionaries network', 'Complete your college degree with the Oklahoma Adult Degree Completion Program&mdash;flexible, affordable, and designed for adult learners.', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(217, NULL, 'Costco Stock Forecast 2025: Investor Outlook &amp; Trends', 'Costco Stock Forecast 2025: What Investors Should Expect', 'retail and ecommerce', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.costco.com/join-costco.html\">Costco (COST)</a></span> continued to wow Wall Street with its announcement of beating estimated Q3 earnings, showing strength in an uncertain retail environment. The big-box retailer experienced earnings per share up 13% to $4.28, above the predicted $4.24. Revenue was up 8% to $63.2 billion, above the estimated $63.13 billion.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The strong results are despite comparable store sales barely beating expectations. Same-store sales overall rose 5.7%, falling short of analyst estimates by a hair at 6%. Adjusted for gas prices, the number rose a healthy 8%, reflecting Costco\'s ability to drive core retail growth.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>U.S. and Canada Post Mixed Performance</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Domestically, Costco is strong. U.S. stores saw same-store sales rise 6.6%, while Canadian stores saw less impressive 2.9% growth. U.S. same-store sales gains in April were 5.2%, down from 9.2% in January. Excluding the sale of gas, comps rose 7.1% in April, reflecting ongoing strength in core merchandise categories.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">April sales were worth $19.8 billion, up 7% from last year. March sales were bigger still at 8.6%. Everyone is watching the trend closely to see how it will do in the second half of the year, given the macroeconomic pressures on consumer wallets.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Gold Bar Craze and Payment Flexibility</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In one of the more unusual headlines, Costco has imposed a buy restriction on gold bars&mdash;two per buyer every 24 hours. The change, added to the website in mid-May, comes as demand remains high and gold prices swing. Wells Fargo estimates Costco is selling $100 million to $200 million worth of gold bars each month since the initiative began in summer 2023.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Costco is also becoming more convenient to shop at. On May 14, the company announced a deal with Affirm to provide installment payments for big online purchases from $500 to $17,500. This is aimed at both small business owners and cash-strapped families, making bulk shopping more affordable.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Moreover, the company boosted its quarterly dividend to $1.30 a share from $1.16, reiterating its shareholder-friendly strategy for the second quarter running.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Costco Stock Near Buy Zone</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">COST shares remained flat after the earnings announcement, hovering around its buy zone. The <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/05/centerpoint-energy-stock-forecast-2025-upgrades-boost-outlook\">stock</a></span> had already broken out above a cup-with-handle base at $1,018, and the buy zone was as high as $1,068.90.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The stock has been supported at its 21-day exponential moving average and is at its 10-day line. With the broader S&amp;P 500 and Nasdaq in a confirmed power trend, they are waiting for the breakout to continue.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The average true range (ATR) of COST stock is 1.76%, which represents stable price action as compared to volatile stocks. This would be a more stable growth scenario for growth investors.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Analyst Take: Costco Stock Forecast 2025</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Upcoming days will witness analysts keeping their fingers crossed when it comes to the Costco stock forecast 2025. Bernstein has just reaffirmed its \"outperform\" rating of Costco on the basis of the company\'s pricing strength and nimble merchandise purchasing.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Although the company reduced its price target from $1,153 to $1,148, it justified that any drop would be a good entry point because shares are currently \"priced to perfection\" at 53x earnings.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With the firm\'s steady performance, dividend growth, and services like in-store payment flexibility, the Costco stock forecast 2025 shows growth continuation. Investors anticipate earnings growth to be robust as the company rides on customer loyalty and operational effectiveness.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In summary, as much as same-store sales growth has come down, Costco is still a retail behemoth. For long-term growth investors with moderate volatility, the Costco stock forecast 2025 still holds great prospects.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-05-30', '23:00:18', 'costco-stock-forecast-2025-what-investors-should-expect', 'article/visionaries-network-costco-stock-forecast-2025-what-invest.webp', 'Costco Stock Forecast 2025: What Investors Should Expect', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-costco-stock-forecast-2025-what-invest.webp', 5, 2025, 'Costco stock, COST forecast, 2025 stock prediction, stock market, retail stocks, Costco earnings, investment forecast, NASDAQ COST, stock growth, dividends, Costco analysis, visionaries network, Costco shares, investor guide, stock performance', 'Explore Costco stock forecast for 2025, including expert predictions, earnings outlook, and key trends investors should watch before making investment decisions.', 1, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0),
