(254, '', 'Squid Game Season 3 India &ndash; Release Time &amp; What to Expect', 'Squid Game Season 3 in India: Release Time and What to Expect', 'Entertainment and Recreation', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong>Squid Game Season 3 in India: Release Time and What to Expect</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.netflix.com/in/login\">Netflix</a></span> will be dropping the final and most anticipated season of its global hit on June 27, 2025. <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.themoviedb.org/tv/93405\">Squid Game</a></span> Season 3 in India is coming out this Friday, and fans are waiting a couple of hours to witness the explosive finale of Gi-hun. With the killing game returning once again, fans globally can\'t wait to know when and where to catch it.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>When Will Squid Game Season 3 in India Release?</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Netflix follows a global release schedule in Pacific Time, where all its content gets released around 12:00 AM PT (3:00 AM ET). The hour in each region differs based on the time difference.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Squid Game Season 3 in India is set to release at 12:30 PM IST on Friday, June 27, 2025. That lunchtime release is perfect for those viewers who\'d like to enjoy the first episode over lunch or binge the entire season over the weekend.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This season is shorter than the last two, with only six episodes compared to the nine of Season 1 and seven of Season 2. Don\'t, however, mistake brevity for lack of intensity&mdash;last chapter is said to be the most dramatic one ever.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Squid Game Season 3 Release Times Across the World</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Here\'s when the show is available to watch outside the US:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 l