bsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->South Africa &ndash; 10:00 AM</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Turkey &ndash; 11:00 AM</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Thailand &ndash; 3:00 PM</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Philippines &ndash; 4:00 PM</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Japan &ndash; 5:00 PM</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Australia (AEST) &ndash; 5:00 PM</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->New Zealand (NZST) &ndash; 7:00 PM</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>What\'s the Story This Time?</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Squid Game Season 3 in India will have English subtitles and dubbed versions released shortly after it comes out. The plot continues from where it was left off in Season 2: Gi-hun is not a volunteer anymore. Seething, he\'s set to bring down the Squid Game operation from within. But taking out the Front Man and the powers that drive the game will not be easy.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As the series plunges into its last arc, anticipate a lot of emotional flashbacks, new alliances, and fierce psychological wars. The season will certainly bring answers to the age-old questions and give the series the rightful finale that it deserves.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>New Cast and Coming Back </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Squid Game Season 3 in India is a mix of old and new faces. Here is the roster:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Lee Jung-jae as Seong Gi-hun (Player 456)</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Lee Byung-hun as The Front Man</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Wi Ha-jun as Hwang Jun-ho</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Yim Si-wan as Myung-gi (Player 333)</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Kang Ha-neul as Dae-ho (Player 388)</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Park Sung-hoon as Hyun-ju (Player 120)</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Yang Dong-geun as Yong-sik (Player 007)</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Kang Ae-sim as Geum-ja (Player 149)</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Jo Yuri, Jun-hee (Player 222)</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Lee David is Min-su (Player 125)</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Roh Jae-won Nam-gyu (Player 124)</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Park Gyu-young as No-eul</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">It is expected that these characters will raise the stakes of the do-or-die game.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>First Six Minutes Teaser by Netflix</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">To further build suspense, Netflix premiered a six-minute preview of the pilot episode. The preview features Gi-hun being brought back to the game center in one of those mythical gift-wrapped coffins. In the mind of the guards, he is dead; in real life, he is very much alive&mdash;and very much a man on a mission for vengeance. The mood is darker, and the stakes have never been higher.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Why Squid Game Season 3 in<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/05/india-strikes-back-operation-sindoor-full-details-2025\"> India</a></span> is Important Squid Game is a global phenomenon, and its Indian fan base is no exception. With its economic inequality, psychological survival, and unadulterated human emotion, the show strikes a chord here.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">It is no wonder that there is so much buzz around Squid Game Season 3 in India, given the emotional and political surprises that the last season has in store.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Last Words </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Squid Game Season 3 is streaming in India on June 27 at 12:30 PM IST on Netflix. Whether you\'ve been on the ride from the beginning or even joined in the middle of the season amidst all the buzz, this is one finale that you wouldn\'t want to miss. Regardless of whether you\'re tuning in for the story, suspense, or social commentary&mdash;its game time for the final time.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-06-28', '00:29:33', 'squid-game-season-3-in-india-release-time-and-what-to-expect', 'article/visionary-network-squid-game1.webp', 'Squid Game Season 3 in India: Release Time and What to Expect', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionary-network-squid-game1.webp', 6, 2025, 'Squid Game Season 3 India, visionaries network, Squid Game Season 3 Netflix India, Squid Game Season 3 plot, Squid Game Season 3 cast, Squid Game S3 expectations', 'Squid Game Seasonâ€¯3 streams on Netflix in India from Juneâ€¯27,â€¯2025 at ~12:30â€¯PM IST. Discover the countdown, full plot details, returning cast, intense new games, and why it&rsquo;s the final season &mdash; plus what twists await Giâ€‘hun&rsquo;s last stand.', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(255, '', 'Nike Plans Price Hike in US After Weak Q4 Sales | Visionaries Network', 'Nike Price Hike in US Planned After Weak Q4 Sales', 'brand management digital marketing and business', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">US sportswear behemoth Nike is to face strategic restructuring including a&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/05/where-to-buy-kobe-6-protro-dodgers-2025-full-guide\">Nike</a></span> price hike in US, after a disastrous fourth quarter in fiscal year 2025. The firm posted a 14% drop in year-over-year direct sales and an eye-watering 26% fall in internet sales, and management reacted with cost control measures, product restaging, and judicious price increases.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Nike\'s fiscal quarter runs from May 31 to June 1, and the March&ndash;May quarter closed with total revenue 12% lower year on year at $11.1 billion. In North America, Q4 revenue was 11% down, and in EMEA it was 10% down. Greater China, comprising China, Hong Kong, Macao, and Taiwan, saw sales decline 20%, though CEO Elliot Hill explained that it was \"largely in line with our plan.\".</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Despite this fall, Nike managed to surpass analyst expectations, with revenue and earnings per share (EPS) coming in 3.74% and 16.67% above projections, respectively. This led to Nike <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/06/hims-stock-plunges-over-20-after-wegovy-deal-collapses\">stock</a></span> rising 10% in after-hours trading on the New York Stock Exchange as an expression of cautious investor optimism.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>CEO Hill Oversees Strategic Turnaround</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/elliotthillnike/\">CEO of Nike, Elliot Hill,</a></span> who emerged from retirement in October 2024, is spearheading a full-scale revival of the brand after previous mishaps, including pruning wholesale relationships and emphasizing lifestyle products at the expense of performance products.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Today, the company is repositioning in core sporting goods, investing in retail relationships, and adding new product lines. Hill characterized the new strategy as being based on what he calls a \"sport offense\" to establish more engaging relationships with athletes, fuel innovation, and differentiate itself in a competitive marketplace.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&ldquo;We\'re organizing ourselves into a sports offense to have a more intimate relationship with the athletes we service,\" Hill told analysts, &ldquo;To better know them, to drive sports-specific innovation, to tell great stories and differentiate ourselves in the marketplace.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Nike price hike in US Begins Fall 2025</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Most important of all is price hikes on certain footwear lines in the US starting fall 2025. Nike price hike in US is supported by a broader plan to insulate profit margins from the increasing cost of production&mdash;specifically those resulting from new US tariffs on Chinese imports, now imposed by the Trump administration.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Hill described the price increases as \"surgical,\" part of Nike\'s seasonal strategy. While some of the cost will be shared with retail partners and absorbed by suppliers, consumers will see higher price tags on some models in stores this fall.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Supply Chain Adjustments and Tariff Relief</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">China, which accounts for about 16% of Nike\'s US footwear imports, is also part of Nike\'s evolving strategy. Nike aims to reduce reliance on Chinese manufacturing by the end of fiscal 2026 by working to get down to the high single-digit percentage range. The move will guard against higher tariffs without harming Nike\'s global supply chain efficiency.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">However, Hill pointed out that China will be one of the key centers for Nike\'s global business, although US-market production will be relocated to less-tariff-affected nations.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As estimated by CFO Matt Friend, the tariff cost impact would be $1 billion, with a 75-basis point gross margin impact for fiscal 2026&mdash;mostly in the first half.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Other Significant Developments: Inventory, Partnerships, and Delays in Women\'s Line</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In addition to the price and supply realignments, Nike is also working to rid inventories, with a 0.4% reduction seen last quarter. Nike is also rebuilding relationships with major merchants such as Amazon by introducing a stand-alone Nike store on the platform.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">But all is not well in the company. NikeSkims, the much-awaited line by Kim Kardashian, was delayed due to production issues, which slowed down the momentum on Nike\'s women\'s product business.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Future: A Page Turning Moment </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Despite the disappointments of today, Hill is sure that Nike\'s repositioning will pay off in the end. \"Where we sit, we believe our business is going to begin to improve. It\'s time to turn the page,\" he explained to shareholders.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As Nike price hike in US looms to take effect, and in renewed emphasis on sporting performance, retail alliances, and innovation, the company is wagering on a slimmed-down, agile future to ride out economic downturns and stiff competition in the worldwide sportswear industry.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-06-29', '23:11:35', 'nike-price-hike-in-us-planned-after-weak-q4-sales', 'article/visionaries-network-nike-price-hike.webp', 'Nike Price Hike in US Planned After Weak Q4 Sales', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-nike-price-hike.webp', 6, 2025, 'Nike price hike 2025, Nike Q4 earnings report, Nike price increase USA, visionaries network, Nike footwear price hike, Nike apparel pricing strategy', 'Nike is set to raise prices across select U.S. footwear and apparel starting Fall 2025 after reporting weak Q4 sales and facing $1 billion in expected tariff costs. Get details on which products will be affected, when the changes take effect, and why Nike is shifting its pricing strategy.', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(256, NULL, 'Micro Center&rsquo;s $349 Ryzen 7 Deal: Budget-Friendly PC Build Opportunity | Visionaries Network', 'Micro Center&rsquo;s $349 Deal Makes Ryzen 7 PC Builds Budget-Friendly', 'it and software', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">If you\'re looking to build a high-performance PC on a&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/pay10-leads-uae-with-first-live-open-finance-launch\">financially</a></span> reasonable price tag, <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.microcenter.com/\">Micro Center\'s</a></span> new package is your dream come true. You receive a Ryzen 7 processor, a GIGABYTE B650 <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/05/nvidia-mediatek-n1-soc-could-redefine-gaming-laptops\">GAMING</a></span> X AX V2 motherboard, and a 32GB G. SKILL Flare X5 DDR5-6000MHz RAM set for $349.99. That is a whopping $169.98 savings, and this is one of the best-value PC upgrade offers of 2025.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Why Ryzen 7 Bundle Is a Steal</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The pi&egrave;ce de r&eacute;sistance is the AMD Ryzen 7 7700X, an 8-core, 16-thread processor that can go up to 5.4GHz in boost. The processor is ideal for gamers, creators, and multitaskers who require the best performance without having to pay much for it. Having the Ryzen 7 at this price and pairing it with a new board and high-speed RAM is unheard of.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>GIGABYTE B650 GAMING X AX V2: Future-Proof and Feature-Rich</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This Micro Center bundle includes the GIGABYTE B650 GAMING X AX V2, a top-tier AM5 motherboard that is preloaded with the latest features. PCIe Gen 5 for blazing fast SSD performance, Wi-Fi 6E for incredibly low-latency wireless connectivity, and native Ryzen 9000 series support for upgradable future-proofing in your system.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Overclocking support, good-quality VRMs, and a number of M.2 slots for storage expansion make it ideal for enthusiasts. Whether building a gaming PC or a productivity computer, this board gives you everything you\'ll ever need to power your system.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>32GB DDR5 Memory: Bye-Bye Bottlenecks</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Aside from the Ryzen 7 CPU and sturdy motherboard, you\'ll also receive a 32GB kit of G.SKILL Flare X5 DDR5 RAM with a speed of 6000MHz. The fast memory offers silky-smooth multitasking, faster game loading, and better performance in memory-hungry applications such as video editing or 3D rendering. Doubling the default 16GB RAM enables you to have more applications open, switch between tasks with ease, and have your PC prepared for heavy use.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Create a Ryzen 7 Gaming PC Without Breaking the Bank</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">One of the highlights of this package is the way it gets your build ready for gaming at high-end levels. The Ryzen 7 7700X has no issues with fresh AAA titles, and with a mid-range or better graphics card such as the RTX 4060 or RX 7700 XT included, you\'re set to go for 1440p or 4K gaming.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Even if you are not a gamer, the multithreading capability of the Ryzen 7 processor makes it a great option for developers, streamers, and power users.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Why This Is the Best Budget PC Offer of 2025</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">For a mere $349.99, you\'re getting a top-of-the-line processor, a robust motherboard, and next-generation memory&mdash;components that would set you back much more if purchased as individual components. In a market where things are getting more expensive, this is one of the best ways to get into the world of Ryzen 7 without spending a fortune.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This acquisition also leaves your budget open for other necessities like a good SSD, graphics card, or PSU&mdash;all the components you would need to create a well-balanced, high-powered PC.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Final Thoughts</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">If you\'ve been waiting patiently for assembling a new rig or upgrading your current one seriously, this Micro Center Ryzen 7 package presents the best value. With the powerful CPU, top-shelf motherboard, and 32GB of fast DDR5 RAM, this package has everything you need to build a future-proof PC.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">But get it fast&mdash;Ryzen 7 rigs at this price point don\'t sit around on the shelf.</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-06-30', '00:05:35', 'micro-centers-349-deal-makes-ryzen-7-pc-builds-budget-friendly', 'article/visionaries-network-7pc-builds-budget-friendly.webp', 'Micro Center&rsquo;s $349 Deal Makes Ryzen 7 PC Builds Budget-Friendly', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-7pc-builds-budget-friendly.webp', 6, 2025, 'Get the Ryzen 7 5700X CPU, motherboard, and RAM for just $349 at Micro Center. Perfect for budget-conscious gamers and DIY PC builders. Limited-time deal!', 'Visionaries network, Ryzen 7 5700X deal, Micro Center Ryzen bundle, budget gaming PC build, Ryzen 7 PC build 2025, cheap Ryzen CPU motherboard combo, Micro Center CPU deals, DIY PC build Ryzen 7', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(257, NULL, 'Apple to Upgrade Siri with AI from OpenAI &amp; Anthropic | Visionaries Network', 'Apple Plans AI-Powered Siri with Help from OpenAI, Anthropic', 'ai vr and automation', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">Apple is said to be in discussions to bring state-of-the-art AI models from OpenAI and Anthropic into a redesigned version of Siri, a potentially significant pivot in direction for the company into voice assistant technology.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">The redesigned version, internally called \"LLM Siri,\" is said to have wiser, more natural language abilities, fueled not only by Apple\'s internal engineering but the intellectual capital of leading AI vendors in the field.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">The change is a signal that Apple is trying to play catch-up in the rapidly evolving space in generative AI. Siri has been behind Google Assistant and Amazon\'s Alexa for a decade. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">Apple has kept development in-house, prioritizing privacy and on-device processing at the expense of features. But that strategy has stunted Siri. By potentially introducing external models, Apple is saying that Siri may need to leverage technologies developed elsewhere in order to provide a truly AI-driven Siri.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">According to sources familiar with the matter, Apple has requested OpenAI and Anthropic to develop bespoke versions of their models to host on Apple\'s internal cloud. This would allow Apple to maintain its strict privacy controls but reap the rewards of more advanced AI systems. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">As Apple develops its own language models for Siri, this hybrid approach would potentially allow it to accelerate its timeline without jeopardizing user trust.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">Why Apple Needs an AI-Powered Siri</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">Siri once ruled the intelligent assistant category, going live before Google and Amazon. However, in the last decade, competitors have outpaced Apple by leveraging powerful cloud-based language models. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">The core issue for Siri has been processing natural language in a conversational way and offering helpful assistance. Apple\'s concern for privacy translated to having the majority of processing local to the device, limiting Siri\'s functionality.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">By introducing an AI-powered Siri, Apple would be revolutionizing the manner in which users interact with iPhones, iPads, Macs, and even newer ones like the Vision Pro. Composing emails, setting calendars, making summaries, or even translating a conversation in real time would all be optimized and made intelligent. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">More significantly, however, users would finally be able to have multiturn conversations with Siri&mdash;something present assistants cannot do.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">Technical Challenges and Delays</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">Apple\'s path to this future-generation assistant hasn\'t been easy. Releasing a smarter Siri in 2025 was the original goal, but internal issues pushed that to 2026 or beyond. Building language models as good as, if not superior to, ChatGPT or Claude AI has proven challenging, especially in the company\'s highly controlled environment. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">Apple has therefore looked to firms already well ahead of the pack when it comes to generative AI.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">Despite the shift towards external partnerships, Apple is focused on keeping the user private. Any integration with OpenAI or Anthropic would be done in a sandbox environment&mdash;Apple\'s cloud, on Apple\'s terms, encrypted by Apple. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">Apple is not in the business of outsourcing control but of leveraging its own capabilities to deliver the AI-powered Siri users have grown accustomed to.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">How AI-Powered Siri May Function </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">Apple has already dipped its toes into the water. During WWDC 2024, the company announced the possibility of Siri sending complex questions to ChatGPT. This was a temporary measure and a precursor to more extensive integrations down the line. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">If these alliances do materialize, subsequent Siri updates may use Apple\'s in-house AI for simple inquiries, but more sophisticated requests would be sent to OpenAI or Anthropic cloud-based models.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">The vision is a single, unified experience. Users wouldn\'t have to know which model is responding&mdash;just a smarter Siri. The AI-powered Siri would be able to recall preferences, respond with empathy, and serve as a real-time personal assistant across apps, services, and devices.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">Transforming the Competitive Landscape</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">Apple\'s shift to leverage outside AI is a sign of competitive pressure that it\'s under. Google is deploying its Gemini AI to Android and Search, and Microsoft continues to fold in Copilot tools in Windows and Office with OpenAI technology. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">Even Amazon is in a hurry to update Alexa with LLMs. Apple\'s been the lone large player to not yet have a large-scale generative AI platform in widespread deployment.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">But by integrating existing AI systems and also maintaining a tight grip on data security, Apple may well end up offering the safest version of the same tools. Customers are becoming increasingly aware of privacy risks, and an AI-powered Siri that ensures their data stays secure could be a winning differentiator. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">Looking Ahead</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">Information on a company launch schedule is still sparse, though sources report Apple is racing to introduce new AI features in 2026. Powered by OpenAI, Anthropic, or both, the next AI-powered Siri is shaping up to be one of the most ambitious projects the company has ever undertaken. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">If successful, it can redefine Apple\'s place in the era of AI&mdash;and at last bring Siri into the future promised to consumers for years.</span></p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-07-02', '00:17:23', 'apple-plans-ai-powered-siri-with-help-from-openai-anthropic', 'article/visionaries-netwrok-apple-siri-open-ai.webp', 'visionaries network Apple Plans AI-Powered Siri with Help from OpenAI, Anthropic', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-netwrok-apple-siri-open-ai.webp', 7, 2025, 'Apple, Siri, OpenAI, visionaries Network, AI-powered Siri, Apple AI plans, iOS AI update, latest news, Apple and OpenAI partnership, Apple artificial intelligence', 'Apple is set to revolutionize Siri using cutting-edge AI from OpenAI and Anthropic. Discover how this partnership could transform your iPhone experience.', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `article_table` (`sl`, `news_edition`, `title`, `headline`, `category`, `content`, `author`, `date`, `time`, `url`, `image`, `alt`, `thumnail`, `month`, `year`, `keywords`, `description`, `sponsore`, `isActive`, `mostViewed`, `latestnews`, `sponsoredarticles`, `featuredcompanies`) VALUES
(258, NULL, 'Microsoft Introduces New Windows&nbsp;11 &ldquo;Black Screen of Death&rdquo; Update | Visionaries Network', 'Microsoft Unveils New Windows 11 Black Screen of Death Update', 'it and software', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">In a radical overhaul, Microsoft is retiring its classic Blue Screen of Death and will replace it with a new, more minimalist-looking version called the Windows 11 black screen of death.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">The feature will be coming in Windows 11 version 24H2, which will roll out later this summer. The move is Microsoft\'s effort to improve the user experience when the system crashes, with error messages more legible, restarts faster, and recovery for IT personnel easier.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">The Blue Screen of Death Comes to an End</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">For years, the Blue Screen of Death was the ultimate indication that Windows had reached a critical failure. While users feared its appearance, the blue screen went on to become one of Microsoft\'s most recognizable features of its operating system. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">The Windows 11 black screen of death, however, replaces this iconic image with a cleaner, more user-friendly layout that is more in line with Windows 11\'s contemporary appearance and feel. This change is part of Microsoft\'s overall strategy to make system crashes less frightening and more functional.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">Why Microsoft Released Windows 11 Black Screen of Death</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">This new crash screen is not just a face-lift. It is the Windows Resiliency Initiative, unveiled following a 2024 crash event that caused infinite Blue Screen of Death cycles on millions of devices worldwide. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">The black screen is carefully crafted to reduce user anxiety and frustration and make the recovery process easier. Microsoft\'s embracing of the Windows 11 black screen of death is an indication that it is dedicated to delivering a more resilient and user-friendly operating system.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">Features of the Windows 11 Black Screen of Death</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">The Windows 11 black screen of death brings some notable enhancements. The background is no longer such a bright blue but instead goes black, providing a dimmer and sleeker look for the screen. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">The sad face emoji and QR code that were utilized on the blue screen are eliminated, instead being replaced by a brief error message with plain-to-read stop codes and failed driver details. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">Such enhancements are beneficial to users and IT support staff alike, as they can immediately see what went wrong. Restarts are also considerably enhanced, with most devices rebooting in a couple of seconds.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">The second significant feature is Quick Machine Recovery, which automatically recovers non-booting machines in the event of large-scale incidents. Such automation simplifies large-scale incident management for IT administrators and reduces end-user downtime.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">Improved User Experience and Rapid Recovery</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">The Windows 11 black screen of death brings the fear typically associated with system crashes a step down. The new black background and plain messaging soften the screen and make it less jarring and more in line with the aesthetic of Windows 11. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">With restarts only taking seconds and more comprehensible diagnostic data being shown, users will be in for a less shocking recovery experience.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">For IT professionals, the new screen provides critical information on the spot, reducing the need to dig through complex crash dump files. The Quick Machine Recovery feature is most valuable for business, as it expedites troubleshooting and reduces support tickets for system-wide failure.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">When Can Users Look for the New Windows 11 Black Screen of Death?</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">Microsoft started to roll out the Windows 11 black screen of death during its Insider preview releases. The complete rollout will be done in the public release of Windows 11 version 24H2 later this summer. The update will be followed by subsequent systems updates that enhance security, stability, and overall user experience.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">A Shift in Culture Besides the Visual Change</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">While the color of the screen is shifting, the phrase \"BSOD\" will certainly be a part of technological culture and common discourse. The Blue Screen of Death was a symbol of computing for more than 30 years, and its legacy continues even as Microsoft is changing how it handles system crashes. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">The Windows 11 black screen of death is a symbol of a new era of simplicity, serenity, and robustness.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">Looking Ahead: Smarter, Calmer Windows </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">The move from Blue Screen of Death to Windows 11 black screen of death is just a piece of Microsoft\'s journey towards smarter, more personalized computing. As operating systems become more sophisticated, Microsoft is taking advantage of more robust recovery mechanisms, faster restarts, and better communication to reduce downtime for hundreds of millions of people worldwide. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN;\">Windows errors of the future are no longer something to fear but an opportunity to recover quickly and continue working.</span></p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-07-02', '00:31:57', 'microsoft-unveils-new-windows-11-black-screen-of-death-update', 'article/visionaries-network-new-window-11-black-screen.webp', 'visionaries network Microsoft Unveils New Windows 11 Black Screen of Death Update', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-new-window-11-black-screen.webp', 7, 2025, 'Windows&nbsp;11, Black Screen of Death, BSOD, Windows&nbsp;11 24H2, Microsoft Quick Machine Recovery, windows latest news, Windows error screen, visionaries network, Microsoft Windows alert redesign, Windows resiliency initiative', 'Microsoft is replacing its decadesâ€‘old Blue Screen of Death with a sleeker, more informative Black Screen of Death in Windows&nbsp;11 24H2. Learn how this update enhances crash diagnostics, includes Quick Machine Recovery, and streamlines restart times.', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(259, NULL, 'Ferrari Amalfi Debuts &ndash; The Elegant Successor to the Roma | Visionaries Network', 'Ferrari Amalfi Debuts as the Elegant Roma Successor', 'Manufacturing Construction and Industrial Engine', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.ferrari.com/en-IN\">Ferrari</a></span> has done it again &mdash; unveiled a head-turning masterpiece that combines emotion, beauty, and engineering nuance. Say hello to the Ferrari Amalfi, a completely new 2+ roadster coupe that supersedes the popular Roma. Designed with the stunning Amalfi Coast in mind and crafted with revolutionary innovation, the Amalfi not only propels Ferrari\'s heritage forward &mdash; it takes it to new heights.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Timeless Style with a Contemporary Twist</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Designed under the visionary leadership of Flavio Manzoni, the Ferrari Amalfi exterior embodies sculptural grace. The front end introduces a bold change &mdash; the iconic grille is replaced by a smooth, body-colored floating wing that enhances aerodynamic efficiency. Sleek headlamps and a sharper lower splitter give the car a wider, more aggressive look.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">At the back, discreet references to Ferrari\'s past intersect with contemporary minimalism. Concealed tail lamps recall vintage styling, as the broad rear diffuser emphasizes serious aerodynamics. The Verde Costiera livery &mdash; a bright teal color inspired by the Amalfi Coast &mdash; bestows sculpted bodywork with blinding gloss in sunlight.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>A Cabin for the 21st Century Motorist</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Internally, the cabin is an entirely new interpretation of Ferrari\'s grand tourer philosophy. Borrowing a page from the 12Cilindri, the dashboard is configured with a monolithic shape with the digital cluster and air vents merging into a single aerodynamic surface.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The anodised aluminium centre tunnel appears to be suspended, housing the gear selector, wireless charging tray, and key controls. Side sail-style door grips cover the dual-cockpit configuration and form a tight yet performance-oriented cockpit for passenger and driver.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Optional comfort seats come in three sizes and feature massage and ventilation systems. Long road trips are downright luxurious with five programmable massage modes and three intensity levels. And if your navigator is the music, the optional Burmester 14-speaker system with 1,200 watts of power delivers symphony-quality sound at any pace.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Aerodynamics in Motion</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">What sets the Ferrari Amalfi apart as a truly pioneering <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/05/byd-beats-tesla-in-europe-april-2025-as-ev-leader-shifts\">automobile</a></span> is its dynamic aerodynamic design. The rear active mobile wing is dynamic and varies in real time to match driving conditions and has three drive modes: Low Drag, Medium Downforce, and High Downforce.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Whether slicing through coastal switchbacks or tearing it up on the autobahn, the wing optimizes downforce and stability. It\'s a great example of how design and technology come together to bring out the best in the driver.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Built for Performance, Engineered for Versatility</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Beneath the bonnet, the Ferrari Amalfi boasts a twin-turbo V8 engine that has been re-tuned to produce 631 horsepower. With an 8-speed dual-clutch transmission, it goes 0&ndash;100 km/h in 3.3 seconds and 200 km/h in 9 seconds.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Ferrari has also introduced a revised brake-by-wire system called ABS Evo, which provides higher braking accuracy and response. With a class-leading power-to-weight ratio of 2.29 kg/hp, the Amalfi is not only a class leader in luxury, but also in raw driving dynamics.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Practical day-to-day use has not been forgotten either. The car can be equipped with a front lifter system, raising the front up to as much as 40 mm &mdash; perfect for raising driveway ramps or speed bumps at speeds of up to 35 km/h.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Ferrari Amalfi: A New Grand Touring Chapter</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Ferrari Amalfi is more of a statement of intent rather than a new model. By marrying traditional looks, track-bred performance, and luxury with practicality, Ferrari has come up with a car that will engage collectors and enthusiasts.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Being the spiritual successor to the Roma, the Amalfi builds on the success of its predecessor and carves out a distinct identity of its own. Whether by virtue of the dramatic styling, heart-stopping power, or the interior design that\'s fixated on luxury, all have been finely tuned to deliver an experience that\'s uniquely Ferrari.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">If you want a tourer that fuses everyday practicality with heart-stopping excitement, the Ferrari Amalfi awaits &mdash; sophisticated, powerful, and irresistibly Italian.</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-07-02', '23:29:09', 'ferrari-amalfi-debuts-as-the-elegant-roma-successor', 'article/visionaries-network-ferrari-amalfi-debuts-as-the-elegant.webp', 'Ferrari Amalfi Debuts | Visionaries Network', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-ferrari-amalfi-debuts-as-the-elegant.webp', 7, 2025, 'Visionaries Network, Ferrari Amalfi, Ferrari Roma successor, new Ferrari 2025, luxury GT car, Ferrari grand tourer, Italian sports car, Ferrari Amalfi debut', 'Ferrari unveils the Amalfi, a stunning new grand tourer that succeeds the Roma with refined design, advanced tech, and timeless Italian elegance.', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(260, '', 'Nothing Phone 3 Launched in India With Flagship Features|Visionaries Network', 'Nothing Phone 3 Launches in India With Flagship Upgrades', 'telecommunication and electronics', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In a big step ahead of the UK-based technology brand,&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.amazon.in/s?k=nothing+phone+3a&amp;adgrpid=1322714844038873&amp;hvadid=82669905311806&amp;hvbmt=be&amp;hvdev=c&amp;hvlocphy=190&amp;hvnetw=o&amp;hvqmt=e&amp;hvtargid=kwd-82670742591958%3Aloc-190&amp;hydadcr=25227_2783772&amp;mcid=9e20b6d8e8593b89b1aff78b7b33ee2f&amp;msclkid=2b3b376af6a111fca40a5f0fb6e91439&amp;tag=msndeskstdin-21&amp;ref=pd_sl_jjb4fow7d_e\">Nothing Phone 3</a></span> has officially announced its release in India, which is the company\'s most important <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/06/trump-mobile-launches-499-gold-phone-47-45-plan\">smartphone</a></span> launch to date. Following months of rumors and teasers, the latest device has been launched as the company\'s very first true flagship, which contains major upgrades in terms of design, performance, and software.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Nothing Phone 3 launch brings a fresh approach to phone design with extreme design revamps on the back panel and numerous hardware and software enhancements. The phone retails at â‚¹79,999 for the 256GB model and is set to disrupt the conventional premium players such as Samsung and Apple, but adhering to Nothing\'s distinctive design philosophy.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>A Revamped Design: Essential Key, Glyph Matrix, and More</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Nothing Phone 3 maintains the minimalist aesthetic of the company but introduces several new features that are immediately apparent. One of the most obvious is the new Glyph Matrix, which is home to 489 addressable LEDs, more useful than ever before. Users are able to personalize glyphs for various notifications, charging statuses, and even app-specific notifications.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">There is also an important addition in the form of the Essential Key, which is a side hardware button that is programmable. The user can set shortcuts to launch apps, turn on the flashlight, or turn on silent mode &mdash; a personalizing feature that is not usually available on mainstream smartphones.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The new camera island deviates from the conventional positions, and this allows the back panel to have a contemporary and streamlined appearance. Very narrow bezels that are only 1.87mm wide along the screen facilitate an immersive viewing experience.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Display and Performance: Flagship-Class Power</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Nothing Phone 3 features a stunning 6.67-inch bendable AMOLED display with a maximum of 4500 nits of peak brightness and a 120Hz adaptive refresh rate for stunning display in any environment. From gaming, streaming, to web surfing, the screen offers state-of-the-art quality with vibrant colors and deep blacks.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Internally, Nothing Phone 3 is powered by Qualcomm\'s Snapdragon 8s Gen 4 chipset, manufactured on a 4nm process by TSMC. The octa-core chipset is clocked at up to 3.21GHz and powered by an Adreno 825 GPU to deliver stunning graphics performance. The onboard Hexagon NPU handles AI processing aside from image optimization and intelligent power management.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Nothing promises a stunning performance jump over the previous generation, making the Phone 3 perfect for heavy gaming, multitasking, and pro-level photography.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Triple 50MP Camera System: Imaging All-Round</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Cameras have been at the forefront of smartphone innovation, and Nothing Phone 3 does that beautifully in that aspect. It boasts a triple 50MP camera setup at the rear, which includes:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->A 50MP primary camera with Optical Image Stabilization (OIS)</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->A 50MP periscope tele-lens that supports OIS</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->A 50MP ultra-wide sensor</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This flexible setup allows for everything from wide-angle landscape to close focus zooming. Out front is a 50MP front camera with 4K video capture and AI portrait modes.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With the new Glyph interface and red recording indicator light, users also can record content while monitoring notifications subtly &mdash; a tip of the hat to the needs of content creators.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Battery and Software: Smart Interface, Long Life</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Nothing Phone 3 has a 5500mAh silicon-carbon battery, which has greater life than regular lithium-ion cells. It supports 65W wired fast charging, filling the phone to full capacity in under one hour.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">On the <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/04/laser-technologies-unveils-nesting-software-for-cutting\">software</a></span> side, the phone uses Nothing OS 3.5 based on Android 15 and provides a bloat-free and minimalistic experience. The company also revealed Nothing OS 4.0 based on Android 16 will be out in Q3 2025. Some of the new software features are:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Essential Space: a distraction-free working area</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Essential Search: a search box available everywhere across settings and apps</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Deep Glyph integration for app notifications, battery levels, etc</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Price and Availability in India</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Nothing Phone 3 will be available in two colors &mdash; White and Black. Pre-order starts on July 4, 2025, and first sale on July 15, 2025, on top e-commerce portals and select offline stores.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Priced at â‚¹79,999 for the 256GB variant, the phone is in the premium category but is value-for-money in the context of innovation and class-leading features.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Final Thoughts </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With the Nothing Phone 3, the company makes a huge leap into the flagship segment with top-tier specs combined with its clear design and Glyph interface. For the design-conscious as well as the tech-savvy buyer, the phone can very easily be a showstopper in a market that\'s over-saturated.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Whether or not the Nothing Phone 3 can carve out a larger niche in opposition to Android giants remains to be seen, but its combination of power, style, and smart innovation makes it one of the most exciting smartphone launches of 2025.</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-07-02', '22:33:25', 'nothing-phone-3-launches-in-india-with-flagship-upgrades', 'article/visionaries-network-nothing-phone-launches-in-india.webp', 'visionaries network: Nothing Phone 3 Launches in India With Flagship Upgrades', 'https://thesiliconreview.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-nothing-phone-launches-in-india.webp', 7, 2025, 'Visionaries network, Nothing Phone 3, Nothing Phone 3 India launch, flagship smartphone 2025, Nothing Phone specs, Nothing Phone 3 features, Carl Pei, Glyph Interface', 'Nothing Phone 3 debuts in India with major flagship upgrades, including a powerful chipset, enhanced camera, and refined Glyph Interface. Learn more.', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(261, NULL, 'Delâ€¯Monte Files for Chapterâ€¯11: Iconic 139â€‘Yearâ€‘Old Food Brand Seeks Buyer', 'Del Monte Bankruptcy: Iconic U.S. Food Brand Files for Chapter 11', 'brand management digital marketing and business', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In a move that has stunned the packaged food industry,&nbsp;<span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://www.delmontefoods.in/\">Del Monte Foods</a></span> has officially filed for Chapter 11 bankruptcy. The once-dominant player in canned fruits and vegetables has announced that it is entering a court-supervised restructuring and sale process, marking a significant turn for a brand that has fed American families for generations. The Del Monte bankruptcy underscores the severe impact of mounting debt, shifting consumer behavior, and pandemic-era miscalculations.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">According to a statement released by CEO Greg Longstreet, the company is aiming to use Chapter 11 protection to stabilize its finances and transition to new ownership. &ldquo;After a thorough evaluation of all available options, we determined that a court-supervised sale process is the most effective way to accelerate our turnaround and create a stronger and more enduring Del Monte Foods,&rdquo; he said.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Company to Continue Operations During Bankruptcy Process</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Despite the Del Monte bankruptcy filing, the company will continue normal operations through the peak canning season. Thanks to a new $912.5 million debtor-in-possession (DIP) loan, the company is expected to meet payroll, pay suppliers, and fulfill customer orders without interruption. This funding gives Del Monte the necessary breathing room to restructure while maintaining day-to-day business continuity.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Court documents filed in the bankruptcy court reveal the company holds liabilities between $1 billion and $10 billion. The massive financial strain stems from a combination of poor inventory management, soaring interest payments, and changing market dynamics.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Pandemic Demand Surge Led to Oversupply</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">At the onset of the COVID-19 pandemic, Del Monte Foods experienced a spike in sales as consumers rushed to stock up on non-perishable pantry staples. The company responded by boosting production to meet the demand. However, as consumer habits normalized, Del Monte was left with excessive inventory that eventually had to be marked down or written off.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Del Monte bankruptcy filing details how this oversupply severely impacted profitability. The company stated that it was forced to &ldquo;sell at substantial losses&rdquo; and absorb significant storage and logistics costs as a result of overproduction.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Rising Debt and Interest Rates Made Matters Worse</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Another key factor behind the Del Monte bankruptcy is its growing debt burden. Del Monte Pacific Limited acquired the U.S. division of the company in 2014, relying heavily on borrowed capital to complete the deal. Since then, the company has struggled to service this debt&mdash;especially as the U.S. Federal Reserve raised interest rates aggressively starting in 2020.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">According to internal financial disclosures, Del Monte&rsquo;s annual interest payments have nearly quadrupled in just five years. This massive jump has strained the company\'s cash flow, limiting its ability to innovate, invest in product development, or adapt to changing consumer preferences.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">CEO Longstreet emphasized that with a cleaner balance sheet and new ownership, the company will be better positioned for long-term growth. &ldquo;With an improved capital structure and enhanced financial position, we aim to build a more resilient and agile business,&rdquo; he added.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>A Legacy Brand at a Crossroads</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Founded in 1886, Del Monte Foods is deeply embedded in American food history. The company opened its famed San Francisco cannery in 1907 and claimed by 1909 to run the world&rsquo;s largest fruit and vegetable canning operation. Products like canned peaches, green beans, and fruit cocktails have made their way into millions of households across the U.S.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Now, the Del Monte bankruptcy puts that legacy in jeopardy. Industry observers believe that the brand could either reemerge under new, more agile ownership or face a potential breakup and sale of assets to competitors or private equity firms.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Consumers Unlikely to See Immediate Impact</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Despite the bankruptcy filing, Del Monte has reassured both retailers and customers that there will be no disruptions in product availability in the near term. Stores will continue to receive shipments, and consumers can still expect to see their favorite Del Monte products on grocery shelves.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">However, changes may be on the horizon. The Del Monte bankruptcy process could eventually lead to product line simplifications, pricing adjustments, or even shifts in branding strategy as the new owners focus on efficiency and profitability.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Conclusion</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Del Monte bankruptcy serves as a wake-up call for legacy <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/06/mcdonalds-to-drop-krispy-kreme-doughnuts-final-day-july22025\">food brands</a></span> struggling to adapt to today&rsquo;s economic and consumer landscape. While the company is not disappearing overnight, it faces a tough road ahead. With strong interim financing and a bold restructuring plan, there&rsquo;s a real possibility that Del Monte will survive this chapter and emerge leaner, more focused, and better prepared for the future of food retail.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-07-04', '22:53:11', 'del-monte-bankruptcy-iconic-u-s--food-brand-files-for-chapter-11', 'article/visionaries-network-delmont-bankruptcy.webp', 'visionaries network Del Monte Bankruptcy', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-delmont-bankruptcy.webp', 7, 2025, 'Delâ€¯Monte bankruptcy, visionaries network, Delâ€¯Monte Foods, canned goods industry, courtâ€‘supervised sale, food industry restructuring, Delâ€¯Monte debt, consumer preferences', 'Delâ€¯Monte Foods, the nearly 140â€‘yearâ€‘old cannedâ€‘goods company, has filed for Chapterâ€¯11 bankruptcy on Julyâ€¯1,â€¯2025. The filing includes a $912.5â€¯million financing package to maintain operations and pursue a courtâ€‘supervised sale amid declining cannedâ€‘food sales and mounting debt', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(262, NULL, 'Jurassic World: Rebirth &ndash; What the Postâ€‘Credits Scene Reveals', 'Jurassic World Rebirth Post Credit Scene: What to Expect?', 'Entertainment and Recreation', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The dinosaurs have returned, as has the thrill. Jurassic World: Rebirth is stomping into theaters with a new cast, a new thrilling location, and the same ancient danger fans adore. This sequel-reboot mashup stars Scarlett Johansson as Zora Bennett, commanding a high-risk expedition to a clandestine island complex on Ile Saint-Hubert&mdash;a shadowy spin-off of the original Jurassic Park.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Though the film offers action at the edge of your seat and a new franchise path that is popular, there is one question on everyone\'s lips once the credits roll: Is there a Jurassic World Rebirth post credit scene?</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Does Jurassic World: Rebirth Have a Post-Credits Scene?</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Let\'s have it out&mdash;the short answer is no. There is no <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jurassic_World\">Jurassic World</a></span> Rebirth post credit scene. Contrary to most modern blockbusters that lay groundwork for sequels or spin-offs following the end of the main film, this film finishes its story with the final frame before fading into the usual credit crawl.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">There is no surprise twist, no hidden recurring character at the end, and no mid-credits stage setting for the future. When the lights go down on the screen, the trip is over.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Of course, you\'re always welcome to stay seated to appreciate the work of the cast and crew&mdash;especially in a production of this magnitude. But for the rest of you rushing to the bathroom or racing to get out of the parking lot before traffic, you can leave in good conscience knowing there\'s nothing hiding behind the credits.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>What Is Jurassic World: Rebirth About? </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In Jurassic World: Rebirth, the franchise turns in a more suspenseful, spy-mission direction. Scarlett Johansson\'s Zora Bennett leads a specialized team in extracting valuable dinosaur DNA from an isolated island research facility that was originally used to study the original Jurassic Park.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The mission of the crew is noble&mdash;to acquire genetic material that holds the key to medical miracles. But the further they descend into the abandoned outpost, the darker the secrets they find. A clandestine conspiracy, concealed evidence, and explosive experiments indicate human involvement that\'s gone far beyond the cloning of dinosaurs.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Johansson is joined by a Hollywood A-list cast:</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Mahershala Ali as Duncan Kincaid, operations commander with a troubled past</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Jonathan Bailey as Dr. Henry Loomis, the team\'s senior geneticist</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Rupert Friend, Manuel Garcia-Rulfo, Luna Blaise, David Iacono, and Ed Skrein complete the cast, each bringing their own style of tension, talent, and vulnerability as things begin to spiral out of control.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>A New Era of Jurassic </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Different from the earlier movies with amusement parks turned deadly, Jurassic World: Rebirth turns the dial to a more militaristic and enigmatic tone. The <span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><a href=\"../../2025/06/28-years-later-movie-release-sparks-new-horror-frenzy\">movie</a></span> blends espionage, survival, and traditional dinosaur fright with a contemporary cinematic style. Critics are already referring to it as the most provocative installment since the original in 1993.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Nevertheless, without any Jurassic World Rebirth post-credits tag, the movie doesn\'t stake a claim to a sequel&mdash;at least, not in the conventional Marvel-style format. Perhaps that\'s intentional, so the studio gets to dip its toes in the water before taking the plunge into the next one. It also teases the fans: Is this some kind of soft reboot, a standalone adventure, or the beginning of some epic prehistoric universe?</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Fan Reactions to Missing Post-Credit Scene</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Some are surprised online that there is no Jurassic World Rebirth post-credit scene&mdash;particularly in reaction to the trend of teasing continuity between movies. Others are applauding the move, terming it a \"refreshing return to the classic movie storytelling\" that respects the self-contained quality of a finished story.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&ldquo;I was waiting for a stinger at the credits,\" quoted one Reddit commenter, \"but I like the restraint. Not every movie needs one.\"</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Final Verdict</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">If you\'re heading to the cinema this weekend, here are the facts you need to know:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Jurassic World: Rebirth is a high-energy reboot with an all-star cast and fearless direction</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->The film offers action, suspense, and an emotionally shocking center</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">There is no Jurassic World Rebirth post credit scene, so don\'t expect a final teaser or hidden message.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Whether this is a standalone adventure or the beginning of a new trilogy is not yet clear. But if box office figures roar as loudly as the dinosaurs, then there is a good chance that Universal has more prehistoric plans in development.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Until then, buckle up for two hours of gene-spliced chaos&mdash;and after the screen fades to black, you can safely leave without losing a beat.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'visionariesnetwork Team', '2025-07-04', '23:16:49', 'jurassic-world-rebirth-post-credit-scene-what-to-expect', 'article/visionaries-network-jurassic-world-rebirth.webp', 'Jurassic World Rebirth Post Credit Scene: What to Expect', 'http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/thumb/article/visionaries-network-jurassic-world-rebirth.webp', 7, 2025, 'Jurassic World Rebirth postâ€‘credits, visionaries network, Jurassic World Rebirth Easter eggs, Jurassic World Rebirth future setup, Jurassic franchise theories, Rebirth post credits future film', 'Discover what the postâ€‘credits scene in Jurassic World: Rebirth hints at&mdash;plus Easter eggs, connections to past films, and what it could mean for the franchise&rsquo;s next chapter.', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0);
