(6, 1, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong>Intelligent People: A boutique recruitment agency, with 20 years&rsquo; experience within product, marketing, eCommerce and Leadership</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In today\'s dynamic business landscape, finding the right talent is crucial for organizations aiming to thrive and innovate. Intelligent People has emerged as a beacon of excellence in the realm of recruitment, leveraging over two decades of specialized knowledge and experience. We introduce you to Intelligent People.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">Intelligent People is not your typical recruitment agency. With over 20 years of specialized knowledge in the market, the company excels in placing experienced and executive-level professionals across product management, product design &amp; UX, marketing, eCommerce, and commercial leadership roles. Operating both within the UK and internationally, it caters to scale-up ventures and enterprise-level B2B and B2C brands.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Intelligent People Specializations</strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">Intelligent People offer a range of recruitment services tailored to meet the diverse needs of its clients:</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: major-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">Retained Executive Search:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\"> The company undertakes exclusive executive search assignments, ensuring a bespoke approach to finding the right leadership talent for your organization.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: major-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">Permanent Contingency Recruitment:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\"> From mid to senior-level roles, Intelligent People matches skilled candidates with permanent positions across various domains, ensuring cultural fit and long-term success.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: major-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">Contract/Interim Placements:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\"> For temporary staffing needs, the organization provides flexible contract and interim solutions, offering immediate support during transitional periods or project demands.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Ethical and Collaborative Approach</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">Intelligent People take pride of its ethical and collaborative recruitment approach. Since its inception in 2002, it has remained committed to its mission of connecting exceptional talent with leading brands. By deeply understanding the requirements of both its clients and candidates, the company consistently achieve high success rates and have earned a reputation as a trusted recruitment partner.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Product Mentorship Scheme</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">As part of Intelligent People&rsquo;s commitment to nurturing talent within the product management industry, it has launched a comprehensive mentorship program. This initiative aims to foster professional development, facilitate networking opportunities, and provide access to valuable resources for product management professionals at all career stages.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Career Opportunities</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Intelligent People<span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\"> specialize in B2C &amp; B2B roles across product management, product design &amp; UX, marketing, and eCommerce primarily in London &amp; the South East. Its network boasts exciting vacancies with some of the most innovative and dynamic brands in the market.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: major-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">Marketing Roles:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\"> Intelligent People recruit across all online and digital marketing disciplines, placing executive-level marketers in prestigious brands.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: major-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">Product Management:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\"> The company&rsquo;s expertise lies in placing skilled product managers within scale-up and enterprise-level B2B and B2C organizations.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: major-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">eCommerce:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\"> Recognized as a leading agency in eCommerce recruitment, the company connect top professionals with prominent employers in the UK.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: major-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">Product Design &amp; UX:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\"> From Vice President Product Design to Head of UX, Intelligent People offer specialized recruitment services and market insights.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Candidate-Centric Approach</strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">At Intelligent People, the team prioritize the candidate experience. Since its inception, the team has been dedicated to building lasting relationships and ensuring that each candidate finds a role where they can thrive and achieve their full potential. The company takes pride in placing numerous senior and executive-level candidates who trust them to guide them through pivotal career moves.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Clientele and Expertise</strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">Intelligent People partner with market-leading digital scale-ups to blue-chip corporations across all industry verticals. Typical roles the company recruits for include Chief Product Officer, Chief Marketing Officer, Chief Growth Officer, Marketing Director, VP Marketing, Chief Customer Officer, Chief Commercial Officer, Chief Operations Officer, Chief Revenue Officer, General Manager, Country Manager, and Regional VP.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">Intelligent People remain committed to delivering excellence in recruitment by understanding the unique needs of both clients and candidates. Whether you are looking to fill a critical leadership position or seeking your next career opportunity, trust Intelligent People to navigate your journey with expertise, integrity, and dedication.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 1.0pt 1.0pt 1.0pt;\"><strong>About Chris Mason, Founder</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 1.0pt 1.0pt 1.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">Chris Mason, Co-Founder of Intelligent People Ltd, brings over two decades of experience as an Executive Search Consultant. His expertise spans executive, leadership, and experienced hires across various domains including Product Management, Marketing, eCommerce, Data, Design, Digital, and Commercial Leadership. With a global reach encompassing the UK, Europe, US, and beyond, Chris and his team specialize in partnering with some of the world&rsquo;s most successful consumer and tech brands.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong>&ldquo;We place experienced and executive level product management, marketing, ecommerce, and commercial leadership candidates within scale-up and enterprise B2B and B2C brands, in the UK and Internationally.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'intelligent-people-boutique-recruitment-with-20-years-experience', '2023-06-26', 'us/visionariesnetwork-chris-mason-intelligent-people.webp', 5, 'profile', 'Intelligent People A boutique recruitment agency, with 20 yearsâ€™ experience within product, marketing, eCommerce and Leadership', 'Intelligent People, best company, magazine, top magazine, best magazine, boutique recruitment', 'Intelligent People, Intelligent People boutique recruitment with 20 years&rsquo; experience', NULL, 1, 'no', 'http://www.intelligentpeople.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/intelligent-people/', 'Intelligent People', '2002', 'St. Albans, Herts'),
(7, 1, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong>Keyfactor brings digital trust to the hyper-connected world with identity-first security for every machine&nbsp;and human</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">Keyfactor&rsquo;s roots date back to 2001. What began as a PKI consulting service has evolved into a comprehensive machine identity management platform. Over the years, the company&rsquo;s focus on empowering customers to protect and manage every machine identity hasn&rsquo;t wavered. Along the way, Keyfactor brought together best-in-class companies, people, and technology.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Most recently, Keyfactor merged with PrimeKey, a pioneer in open-source public key infrastructure (PKI) and signing solutions. Bringing together the most widely used PKI and certificate authority (CA) software with end-to-end machine identity management empowers its customers to securely connect and authenticate every device, workload, and application across their business.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Establishing digital trust is the foundation of every digital transaction in today\'s interconnected world. With businesses operating across borders and industries, trust is crucial for speed, security, and compliance. However, fragmented PKI and certificate management tools can create inefficiencies, inconsistencies, and infrastructure complexity. Keyfactor\'s innovative approach to PKI and certificate management provides a single solution stack that streamlines digital trust establishment. This comprehensive solution empowers organizations to build, manage, and scale digital trust across all teams.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Keyfactor\'s solution offers automation of workflows and manual processes with automated PKI configuration, deployment, and certificate management. It also enables deployment of PKI as Code in Kubernetes or OpenShift with pre-built playbooks, integration with all major certificate authorities (CAs), HSMs, and cloud platforms, and ensures quantum-readiness with tools to discover and inventory assets, test NIST-selected PQC algorithms, and build a path toward migration.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Keyfactor provides flexible deployment options to suit every organization\'s unique needs. Choose from software appliance, hardware appliance, containers, SaaS-delivered, or fully managed, single-tenant solution deployments. Deploy your PKI on-premises, in the cloud, or in a hybrid model - the choice is yours.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">At Keyfactor, the team understands the importance of trust and compliance. Its solutions are actively maintained to meet industry standards and regulations, including Common Criteria/NIAP, ISO 27001, PCI DSS 3.2, and SOC 2 Type II for hosted customers. The company&rsquo;s open-source PKI and signing solutions are widely adopted by a global community of thousands of developers and PKI practitioners. The company&rsquo;s in-house experts develop and support the popular Bouncy Castle cryptography APIs, enabling customers to build quantum-ready and FIPS-certified applications.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Keyfactor prioritizes open standards over proprietary integrations, ensuring seamless integration with all major CAs, HSMs, and cloud platforms. Its solutions support open-source frameworks and popular protocols like ACME, EST, CMP, CMPv2, Matter, and more.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As the threat of quantum computers looms closer, Keyfactor is at the forefront of quantum-readiness. Keyfactor&rsquo;s customers are already equipped with tools to discover and inventory assets, test NIST-selected PQC algorithms, and build a path toward migration.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">EJBCA Enterprise is Keyfactor\'s flagship PKI solution that provides a complete turnkey PKI experience. With EJBCA Enterprise, organizations can deploy their PKI as a turnkey software appliance, hardware appliance, in the cloud, as a service (SaaS PKI), or in a hybrid model. They can issue identities for every device, workload, and user; integrate with any application or use case via support for multiple formats, protocols, and algorithms; configure fine-tuned controls over certificate profiles, extensions, approval workflows, and validation from one console; run their entire PKI on a single instance; scale up on-demand without infrastructure complexity; and simplify audits with detailed signed audit logs.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\"><strong>Short bio of Jordan Rackie, Chief Executive Officer</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Jordan Rackie is the chief executive officer at Keyfactor. In this role, he is responsible for setting the company vision, driving both top and bottom-line results, and managing Board relations.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Jordan has led Keyfactor as CEO since May of 2019, directly following Insight Partner&rsquo;s initial investment of $77 million into the business. During this time, Keyfactor has experienced award-winning hyper-growth and cultural achievement accolades. Jordan has championed and integrated multiple businesses into Keyfactor through M&amp;A, including Sweden-based PrimeKey and Spain-based RedTrust. Jordan holds a keen interest in the joint-value creation between employee and employer, understanding that a great organizational culture and environment creates a force multiple for business success. Jordan is an expert in developing and leading modern go-to-market teams and strategy. His previous experience includes serving as senior vice president of global revenue at Tricentis, a globally recognized leader in software test automation and software quality assurance solutions, and chief revenue officer for QASymphony (which merged with Tricentis), ranked by Inc. magazine as the 8th fastest growing software business in the U.S. in 2017. He was also a sales leader and executive for Pardot (acquired by Salesforce).</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Jordan was born, raised, and currently resides in Atlanta, along with his wife Amy, their son William, and their mini labradoodle, Charles. Jordan graduated from Georgia Tech with a Bachelor of Science in business management. In 2020, he earned the honor of being named a member of the Georgia Tech Alumni 40 Under 40. Outside of work, Jordan enjoys staying active (golf, tennis, boxing) and spending time with his family (traveling, day trips to the Georgia aquarium, time at the pool and lake), and leads by example as it relates to having a healthy work-life balance.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong>&ldquo;By simplifying PKI, automating certificate lifecycle management, and securing every device, workload, Keyfactor helps organizations move fast to establish digital trust at scale &mdash; and then maintain it.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'keyfactor-brings-digital-trust-to-the-hyper-connected-world-for-machine-and-human', '2023-06-26', 'us/visionariesnetwork-jordan-rackie-keyfactor.webp', 6, 'profile', 'Keyfactor brings digital trust to the hyper-connected world with identity-first security for every machine and human', 'Keyfactor, PrimeKey, lifecycle management, magazine, Best company, top magazine', 'Keyfactor brings digital trust to the hyper-connected world for machine and human', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.keyfactor.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/wearekeyfactor', 'Keyfactor', '2001', 'Independence, Ohio'),
(8, 1, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong>MHA Consulting is a business continuity consult to leading public and private businesses&nbsp;throughout the United States</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">As a leading provider of business continuity services, MHA Consulting helps organizations of all industries minimize the likelihood of disruptive instances and ensures proactive crisis management. With its proven methodologies, extensive experience, and commitment to long-lasting relationships, the organization has built a reputation for delivering high-quality services to its clients. MHA&rsquo;s average client relationship spans over five years, a testament to its dedication to excellence.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Streamline Your Business Continuity Program</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">MHA&rsquo;s suite of BCM software solutions enables you to:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Create a comprehensive overview of your BC and IT disaster recovery functionality</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Establish well-informed business continuity decisions based on metrics in mere minutes</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Keep your BC plans up to date with automatic software updates when standards change</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Meet the needs of all stakeholders with clearly defined reports</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Quickly get back up and running with attentive onboarding and support</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Business Continuity Services</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">At MHA Consulting, the team understands that every organization is unique, with its own set of challenges and requirements. That\'s why it offers a comprehensive range of business continuity services to assess, implement, exercise, and maintain the maturity and sophistication of your Business Continuity program.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo3;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Current State Assessment (CSA)</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">MHA&rsquo;s Current State Assessment provides an in-depth evaluation of the capability and maturity of your current Business Continuity and IT Disaster Recovery programs, based on industry best practices and standards. The assessment includes detailed findings, recommendations, and metrics defining your program\'s current maturity and recovery capability. This is an excellent first step for new and existing programs to establish a baseline of maturity and capability and develop a roadmap for future improvement.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo3;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Business Impact Analysis (BIA)</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">MHA&rsquo;s Business Impact Analysis (BIA) identifies the critical business processes and information technology that are essential to your organization\'s operations. It determines the quantitative and qualitative impacts of downtime, defining your organization\'s target Recovery Time Objectives (RTOs) and Recovery Point Objectives (RPOs).</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo3;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Threat &amp; Risk Assessment (TRA)</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">MHA&rsquo;s Threat &amp; Risk Assessment identifies the man-made, technological, and natural threats that can impact your key business and IT processing facilities. It assesses the probability and potential impact of each threat and provide prioritized recommendations for improvement.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Crisis Management Services</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">At MHA Consulting, the team believes that a strong Crisis Management Team (CMT) is crucial for effective crisis management. The company&rsquo;s team development process uses industry best practices and standards to create a CMT that is tailored to your organization\'s specific needs.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Team Plan Creation:</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"> MHA assists you in creating a Crisis Management Team (CMT) plan that outlines roles, responsibilities, and procedures for responding to crisis.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Emergency Notification System Implementation:</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"> The organization helps you select the best Emergency Notification System vendor for your organization\'s needs and manage the implementation process.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Mock Disaster Exercise:</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"> MHA performs mock disaster exercises to validate your Crisis Management Team\'s ability to respond effectively in a crisis situation.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">By partnering with MHA Consulting, you can rest assured that your business continuity program is in good hands. MHA&rsquo;s experienced professionals will work closely with you to assess, implement, exercise, and maintain your program, ensuring that you are prepared for any disruption or crisis that may arise. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Is Your Organization Suited for MHA&rsquo;s BCaaS?</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">MHA&rsquo;s BCaaS is well suited for most companies, especially those that:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Lack direction about what BCM means for the organization</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Need seasoned resources to jump start BCM efforts</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Lack a BCM program or have a program that is limited or outdated</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Expect a BCM program to be built the right way the first time</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Don&rsquo;t want to make BCM a core competency or hire additional staff</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Business Continuity Program Augmentation</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo4;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><em>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </em></strong></span></span></span><strong><em><!--[endif]-->Service Commitment</em></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">At MHA, the team has a strong track record of working with clients to elevate their business continuity management (BCM) and disaster recovery (DR) programs. Its experienced team serves as a trusted partner, providing bespoke support to organizations of all sizes, from small businesses to Fortune 20 companies. Each client is assigned a dedicated senior consultant who takes ownership of their program, ensuring seamless communication and accountability.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo4;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><em>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </em></strong></span></span></span><strong><em><!--[endif]-->Expertise</em></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">MHA&rsquo;s team consists of senior-level professionals with an average of 15 years of experience in BCM and DR. This expertise is leveraged to deliver tailored solutions that meet the unique needs of each client.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo4;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong><em>Customized Migration Plan</em></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">MHA offers a customized migration plan to transfer operational responsibility for your BCM or DR program. It begins by conducting a thorough assessment using industry best practices and its proprietary BCMMetrics tool. This evaluation identifies gaps between your current program, industry standards, and its expertise. The company then works with you to discuss areas of improvement, opportunities for growth, and any critical exposures that require immediate attention. Based on this analysis, MHA develops a tailored approach to your BCM and/or DR process, leveraging your existing capabilities while addressing necessary changes.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo4;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span><em><strong>Pricing</strong></em></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">MHA&rsquo;s pricing model is designed to provide transparency and flexibility. The initial Current State Assessment (CSA) and roadmap drive the development of a tailored annual Statement of Work (SOW), outlining specific deliverables and tasks for each quarter. The cost of MHA&rsquo;s annual outsourcing agreement is comparable to hiring a senior-level BCM or DR planner, but you benefit from access to the resources needed to achieve your goals without increasing costs. With the company&rsquo;s agreement, you pay the same price regardless of the number of resources required &ndash; whether one or three &ndash; and can expect the cost to decrease annually as components transition into maintenance mode.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\"><strong>Meet Michael Herrera, Chief Executive Officer of MHA</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Michael Herrera offers strategic leadership to the company\'s global practices and capabilities. Under his guidance, MHA has established itself as a premier provider of Business Continuity and Disaster Recovery services to organizations worldwide. Additionally, Michael founded BCMMETRICS, a cloud-based platform that assesses business continuity compliance and residual risk. As a respected industry expert, he frequently delivers keynote presentations on Business Continuity at local and national contingency planner chapter meetings and conferences. Prior to founding MHA, Michael held the position of Regional Vice President at Bank of America, where he oversaw Business Continuity initiatives across the southwest region.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">&ldquo;Our work decreases the likelihood of disruptive instances and ensures proactive crisis management for organizations of all industries.&rdquo;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'mha-consulting-is-a-leading-public-and-private-businesses-throughout-united-states', '2023-06-26', 'us/visonariesnetwork-mha-consulting-michael-herrera.webp', 3, 'profile', 'MHA Consulting is a leading public and private businesses throughout United States', 'MHA Consulting, Best company, US best company, Us magazine, best magazine', 'MHA Consulting is a leading public and private businesses throughout United States', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://mha-it.com/', 'linkedin.com/company/mha-consulting-inc', 'MHA Consulting', '1999', 'Glendale, Az'),
(9, 2, '<p><strong>Amazing Support: Award-Winning Managed IT Support &amp; Cyber Security in London, Hertfordshire &nbsp;&amp; Manchester</strong></p>', '<p dir=\"ltr\">At Amazing Support, the team is not just another IT services company. They are a Microsoft Silver accredited and HM Government Cyber Essentials certified partner that delivers tailored solutions to help businesses thrive in today\'s digital landscape. Their team of experts provides managed IT support, cyber security, business continuity, cloud solutions, and IT consultancy services that are designed to meet the unique needs of each client. The company&rsquo;s customer-centric approach sets them apart from the rest, as they strive to simplify complex technical jargon and deliver exceptional results.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>IT Support: One Size Does Not Fit All</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In an era where IT support is often met with frustration and expletives, Amazing Support is proud to hear words like <em>\"amazing\", \"brilliant\",</em> and <em>\"outstanding\"</em> used to describe its services. Why? Because it takes the time to understand each client\'s unique needs, tailoring its approach to provide a personalized experience. The company&rsquo;s onboarding process includes a thorough review of each client\'s requirements, ensuring that it is equipped to deliver the best possible outcome.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Managed IT Support</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Amazing Support&rsquo;s managed IT support services cover remote and on-site support for desktops, servers, and network equipment. It also provides regular maintenance of all systems, pro-active monitoring, managed cyber security, anti-virus, and operating system patch management. Additionally, its scheduled site visits, change requests, and full support of cloud IT platforms ensure that your technology is always running smoothly.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Cyber Security and GDPR Compliance</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In today\'s digital landscape, secure data is a must-have for any business. That\'s why Amazing Support&rsquo;s managed IT services include comprehensive cyber security and GDPR compliance. The organization will help you protect your company\'s data and that of your users, ensuring that you comply with the latest regulations.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Cyber Security Services</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Amazing Support&rsquo;s range of cyber security services includes:</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Email Protection:</strong> Utilizing Microsoft Office 365 and email security filtering with advanced threat protection, Amazing Support can ensure your business email flow is uninterrupted by spam, viruses, phishing, whaling, and cryptolocker threats.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Malware Protection:</strong> Amazing Support offers a wide range of services that can protect your system from malware and ransomware attacks.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Firewall Protection:</strong> Amazing Support installs and maintains your firewalls, constantly looking for vulnerabilities. It also sends you regular reports detailing the health of your IT system\'s security.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Threat Management:</strong> Amazing Support provides comprehensive IT system monitoring to quickly identify threats and vulnerabilities. It\'s able to dispel these threats before they wreak havoc.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Cyber Security Employee Education:</strong> Amazing Support employee IT education course includes basic training in IT systems and cyber security best practices.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Cyber Security Consultancy:</strong> Amazing Support certified experts can help you tackle any cyber security issue or set up and maintain a secure IT system.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Backup and Disaster Recovery</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Amazing Support consistently backs up your data and provides you with corresponding reports. With its backup tools in place 24/7, your critical data can be recovered should a disaster strike, as well as emergency email mailboxes available to keep your business communicating.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>GDPR Compliance</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) has been in effect since May 2018. To avoid penalties totaling 20 million euros or 4% of global turnover, it\'s essential to take data breaches seriously. Amazing Support&rsquo;s trained cyber compliance experts will guide you through 2 out of the 12 steps to becoming GDPR compliant in relation to your Cyber Security, Data Privacy, and Data Protection by Design (DPIA).</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Amazing Support, the team is committed to helping businesses adapt to the changing landscape of cyber security and data protection.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Meet David Share, Co-Founder &amp; Director</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As the Director and Co-Founder of Amazing Support, a multi-award-winning Cyber Essentials certified Managed Service Provider (MSSP), David Share has been dedicated to delivering top-notch Managed IT Support, Cyber Security, Consultancy, and Solutions to UK businesses in London and Manchester since 2007.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In David Share\'s C-Level role, David Share has extensive experience in driving the operations of the company, while also overseeing internal and external development. This includes ensuring the company\'s growth, financial control, legal and security compliance, and managing wide commercial operations and risk management. David Share works closely with the Leadership Team to collaborate on strategic direction and decision-making.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">David Share\'s responsibilities also include developing commercial strategy, conducting research and development, designing macro processes, managing operations, implementing automation, creating digital marketing campaigns, and handling human resources. As a results-driven leader, David Share makes systematic business and company decisions daily without procrastination.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">David Share\'s focus on client retention has resulted in securing additional revenue and service opportunities. David Share also prioritizes growing partnerships with top-tier industry companies. Additionally, as a UK Business Climate Leader and Member of the SME Climate Hub, David Share is committed to helping Amazing Support reach net-zero emissions by 2050.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Beyond Amazing Support, David Share has expanded into the Web3 and NFT space as an IP builder and creator. David Share collaborates with a team of experts across the UK, Europe, and the US on content creation, cross-project partnerships, events, and guest speaking engagements.</p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'amazing-support-award-winning-managed-it-support', '2023-02-08', 'us/visionaries-network-david-share-director-amazing-work.webp', 1001, 'cover', 'Amazing Support: Award-Winning Managed IT Support & Cyber Security in London, Hertfordshire  & Manchester', 'Amazing Support', 'Amazing Support', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.amazingsupport.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/the-amazing-support-company/', 'Amazing Support', '2007', 'Elstree, Hertfordshire');
