(10, 2, '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>AlphaBOLD&rsquo;s goal is to help you grow by leveraging the latest business technologies</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">AlphaBOLD believes that technology can transform lives electronically. It has been able to create solutions that give its clients and users delight while having a positive impact on its communities. It tries to build a community&mdash;what it calls the BOLDCommunity&mdash;of consultants and clients joining forces to build solutions for others. The company defines success as delivering 10x improvement&mdash;every time, and know this delivery requires two-way trust, collaboration, and willingness to push beyond. That\'s why the company grounds itself in core values of accountability, drive, and trust.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>AlphaBOLD&rsquo;s Story</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">AlphaBOLD was founded on the passion for using technology to solve complex business problems. It believes that consulting needs a new definition of success, and it is committed to making this a reality&mdash;one project at a time. It is not building a successful business; it has built a community bound together by its passion for technology.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>AlphaBOLD Values</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>AlphaBOLD lives by five core values:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Accountability: AlphaBOLD takes ownership of its actions and results</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Appreciate and Encourage: Applaud good work and encourage it in others.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Drive: To strive for the best and push past the ordinary.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Giveback: A giveback to AlphaBOLD&rsquo;s community via volunteer work and charitable initiatives.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">BOLDBelief: Knowing the company, the team, and the difference that can made.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>AlphaBOLD Team</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">AlphaBOLD has a fully staffed in-house team of over 90 full-time BOLDEnthusiasts, including experts, team leads, and project managers with global consultancy and delivery experience. Its 360-degree support team provides complete support to testing, implementation, and execution services. It operates 100% online cloud-based tools to ensure round-the-clock visibility into its projects.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Empower Your Business with AlphaBOLD</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As your partner in Microsoft Dynamics 365, AlphaBOLD is much more than your service provider; rather, it is your strategic partner. It can be engaged to activate transformational change and growth within your organization through Dynamics 365. These comprehensive business applications integrate mission-critical business functions with seamless continuity, breaking down silos that traditional ERP and CRM systems have built over time.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Your Comprehensive Partner for Dynamics 365 relation</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Microsoft Dynamics 365 shall bring the power of ERP and CRM into purpose-built applications that work seamlessly across domains. With these applications in place, AlphaBOLD shall enable your business to streamline operations, nurture richer customer experiences, and drive faster growth.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Why AlphaBOLD?</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">What sets the company apart from other Microsoft Dynamics 365 partners is its very special blend of unbeaten expertise, innovative solutions, and dedication to delivering extraordinary experiences. AlphaBOLD&rsquo;s knowledge in Dynamics 365 lets it tailor solutions that go perfectly in line with your business goals, so you can optimize your operations, enhance customer engagements, and build sustainable growth.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">AlphaBOLD maintains good relations with other Dynamics 365 partners, vendors, and customers to make sure that what it provides is up-to-date in its capabilities and gives your business a fighting chance to adapt to the constantly changing market environment. On AlphaBOLD&rsquo;s part, local knowledge and national presence are instrumental in offering solutions from San Diego across the US.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Caroline Mayou, Director of Marketing</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Caroline Mayou, a seasoned marketing professional with over 12 years of experience, leverages her technical expertise and strategic thinking to drive transformative change and growth for organizations. Caroline Mayou, as Director of Marketing, excels at developing innovative marketing strategies and optimizing e-commerce projects to generate new revenue streams. Caroline Mayou\'s accomplishments include streamlining operations to reduce costs while bridging departmental divides through seamless integrations, resulting in improved efficiency and collaboration.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We believe that by listening to your needs and by understanding your business challenges; we can apply our knowledge of technology to remove any obstacles that can slow you down.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'alphabolds-goal-is-to-help-you-grow-latest-business-technologies', '2023-02-08', 'us/Alpha_bolds.jpg', 1, 'profile', 'AlphaBOLDâ€™s goal is to help you grow by leveraging the latest business technologies', 'AlphaBOLD&rsquo;s goal', 'AlphaBOLD&rsquo;s goal', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.alphabold.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/alphabold/', 'AlphaBOLD', '2017', 'Carlsbad, California'),
(11, 2, '<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Datacate takes an objective-based approach to your IT, putting your goals and priorities first</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Datacate follows a goal-based strategy toward your information technology, placing your goals and priorities at the top of the list. Get maximum return on your IT investment. Its professionals are highly experienced and dedicated to understanding the different business requirements of its clients.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The company is based on strong partnerships and collaboration with clients in tailoring innovative solutions that will keep your business running. The team at Datacate truly believes that technology never stops evolving and is dedicated to keeping abreast of the latest developments in order to keep their clients at the forefront of IT services.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Be it cloud computing solutions, network security solutions, data backup and recovery, or any other IT services, the experience and resources are all under one roof at Datacate. It takes pride in the delivery of any kind of IT solution with its reliable, efficient, and cost-effective services that help you meet all your business-related objectives. With Datacate as your trusted IT partner, you can run your business with confidence, knowing that your technology needs are in good hands.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">SOC 2 Type I &amp; II Audit</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Datacate has completed a regular third-party audit to certify its Colocation and Cloud Services System against the SOC 2 standard. The report is an assessment of its information systems in regard to security, availability, processing integrity, and confidentiality or privacy. Its SOC 2 Type audit makes sure that its controls are suitably designed and implemented, while the Type II report gives proof of the operating effectiveness of controls over at least a six-month time frame.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>HIPAA Compliance</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">This is to say that Datacate\'s SOC 2sm has been specifically enhanced in a bid to meet the provisions in the security rule 45 CFR Section 164.308, 164.310 and 164.312 within the Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act. This essentially translates to a mapping of its controls in the relevant administrative, physical, and technical safeguards and protecting electronic protected health information. Its report bears testimony to its compliance with the requirements of both SOC 2sm and HIPAA.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>CSA STAR Attestation</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Datacate performed a CSA STAR Attestation&mdash;a collaboration between the Cloud Security Alliance and the American Institute of Certified Public Accountants. This attestation provides the rigorous third-party, independent assessment of cloud providers, ensuring that its controls align with the CSA Cloud Controls Matrix.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>NMS</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Well, the team at Datacate knows exactly how small businesses usually struggle to come up with robust and reliable networking. This company has a fully dedicated team obsessed with monitoring your network 24/7, having all kinds of advanced tools and technologies to track the health of your network in real-time. With that, they are able to track anomalies, performance bottlenecks, and a host of other impending security threats. They provide custom network management solutions that include preventative maintenance, troubleshooting, and customized networking solutions for special needs.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Benefits of Choosing Datacate for Your Network Management Solutions</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">By choosing Datacate for your network management, you will get the following benefits:</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&bull; <strong>Uptime: </strong>Proactive monitoring and maintenance provided by Datacate reduce the risk of network outages.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&bull; <strong>Security:</strong> The company takes part in constant monitoring of security threats, hearing about them in the very early stages, and protects customers\' networks from cyber-attacks.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&bull; <strong>Cost savings:</strong> This service provides enormous cost savings through the prevention of an expensive downtime and the reduction of a need for in-house IT staff.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&bull;<strong>Scalability:</strong> The organization\'s solutions grow with your business. It makes sure that your network can support increased demands placed upon it as your company grows.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&bull;<strong>Expert support:</strong> The company has an expert team of IT professionals who will always be ready to assist and advise you. Serving Northern California Service Areas</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Datacate is proud to serve small businesses across a host of service areas in the northern part of California\'s vast state. It understands the local business environment and provides person-to-person service with support to let small businesses be successful. This includes management, monitoring, preventative maintenance, and troubleshooting of a network, along with customized networking solutions.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>What Chris James, Co-founder, CEO has to say</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&ldquo;Everyone gives it their all, and it shows.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&ldquo;I oversee Datacate&rsquo;s operations and finances at the executive level. I&rsquo;m responsible for delegating and directing agendas, driving profitability, and managing company structure and strategy. I derive tremendous satisfaction from seeing our company grow and from the accolades we receive from our customers.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;Our clients benefit from infrastructure built by Datacate, owned and maintained by our team.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'datacate-takes-an-objective-based-approach-to-your-it-putting-your-goals-and-priorities-first', '2023-02-08', 'us/Datacate.jpg', 2, 'profile', 'Datacate takes an objective-based approach to your IT, putting your goals and priorities first', 'Datacate', 'Datacate', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.datacate.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/datacate-inc/', 'Datacate Inc. ', '2008', 'Rancho Cordova, CA'),
(12, 2, '<p><strong>Equilar uses AI technology to analyze executive profiles and provide personalized outreach for clients globally</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">In today\'s fast-paced and increasingly complex business landscape, having access to accurate and comprehensive information about your organization\'s relationships is more critical than ever. Effective relationship management is essential for building trust, driving growth, and staying ahead of the competition. But with the sheer volume of data available, it can be challenging to know where to start, let alone how to make sense of it all.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Equilar is the leading provider of executive intelligence solutions. Its relationship intelligence leadership fuels state-of-the-art business development and CRM applications, board and executive recruitment, and compensation and governance strategies. Equilar brings rich executive profiles in its extensive database with natural language processing and machine learning AI to provide real-time relationship analytics and targeted outreach for clientele around the world. A testament to Equilar\'s commitment to excellence, more than 1,000 corporations&mdash;including 75% of the Fortune 500, leading private equity/venture capital firms, and the top professional services organizations&mdash;are now looking to the firm for all of their needs. RainMaker: Ultimate in Data Unification.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">RainMaker is a game-changing solution that seamlessly brings all of your customer data silos into Snowflake and enriches them with Equilar\'s real-time executive data. By bringing all of your data silos into RainMaker, you will be able to tap an always-updated 360-degree view of your firm\'s network. Doing this empowers one to accelerate access to buying committees, uncovering new revenue opportunities.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>How RainMaker Works</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">RainMaker is purpose-built to turbocharge your sales and marketing initiatives, exclusively on Snowflake. Here\'s how it works:</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Integrate Data Silos:</strong> Seamlessly consolidate fragmented buyer data across your firm.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Enrich Executive Data:</strong> Layer in real-time relationship intelligence from Equilar to create a 360-degree view of your firm\'s professional connections.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Win Deals: </strong>Streamline workflows to ensure sales and marketing teams have the latest intelligence to reach target accounts.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Why RainMaker?</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">This makes RainMaker poised with several advantages over other data unification solutions: âƒ Build the Foundation: Set up RainMaker as the central hub for the aggregation of fragmented firm data silos emanating from different sources. âƒ Activate AI Initiatives: Clean CRM data that will power AI initiatives with precision, insight, and accuracy. âƒ Solve the Last Mile: Create personalized messages and engagement strategies with deep insights into executive roles, transitions, and relationships. Maximize Network Connections with Equilar</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Equilar provides strong data solutions to help maximize connections within your network and close deals. Get instant access to this vast database of executives and board members, PortCo connections, and much more to uncover the key relationships and generate new opportunities.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Available for Salesforce</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Equilar has a native integration with Salesforce, so you can create a single contact record for an executive or board member that spans multiple companies. You can draw upon Equilar rich dataset seamlessly from within Salesforce to discover hidden business opportunities and relationships.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Bring Relationship Intelligence to Life</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">By integrating Equilar data into DealCloud, firms will be able to harness both the best executive and relationship data in the industry to uncover meaningful connections and power relationship intelligence. Through DealCloud DataCortex, deal-makers can automatically populate deal associates, reports, dashboards, and tear sheets with verified contact intelligence and company affiliations directly from the Equilar database.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>David Chun, Founder and CEO</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">David has led Equilar since its inception to become one of the most trusted names in the corporate governance community. David has been recognized as one of the &ldquo;100 Most Influential Players in Corporate Governance&rdquo; by the National Association of Corporate Directors (NACD), the Disruptor Award by 2020 Women on Boards and Outstanding 50 Asian Americans in Business. David speaks publicly on corporate governance and board diversity matters, including events hosted by The Conference Board, Deloitte, EY, HR Policy Association, KPMG, NACD, NASDAQ, NYSE, The Society for Corporate Governance and Stanford&rsquo;s Directors&rsquo; College.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">David serves on the boards of the Commonwealth Club of California, PGA Reach, the Silicon Valley Leadership Group (SVLG) and is a trustee of Committee for Economic Development (CED). He is on Nasdaq&rsquo;s Center for Board Excellence Advisory Board, Catalyst&rsquo;s Women on Board Advisory Council, the Women on Boards Advisory Council of the California Partners Project and the Advisory Council of the Angel Island Immigration Station Foundation. David is a member of Young Presidents&rsquo; Organization (YPO), Past Chair of the SF Bay Chapter, a founding member of the Council of Korean Americans (CKA) and former board member of the Wharton Center for Entrepreneurship and the Asian Pacific Fund Community Foundation of San Francisco.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Prior to founding Equilar, David was a Vice President in the Investment Banking Division of Donaldson, Lufkin and Jenrette, a global investment bank that has since merged with Credit Suisse. Prior to DLJ, David was a management consultant with Bain &amp; Company and also Kenan Systems, a telecom software developer acquired by Lucent Technologies.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">David earned his M.B.A. from the Wharton School at the University of Pennsylvania and a Bachelor of Science with Honors in Systems Engineering from the University of Virginia.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;Embrace the future with superior CRM data for AI, Machine Learning, and next-gen applications. Enrich your CRM with unmatched relationship intelligence.&rdquo;</strong><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-61d98e1a-7fff-a6a4-d97b-1d84cf08083e\"></strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'equilar-uses-ai-technology-to-analyze-executive-profiles-and-provide-personalized-outreach-for-clients-globally', '2023-02-08', 'us/Equilar.jpg', 3, 'profile', 'Equilar uses AI technology to analyze executive profiles and provide personalized outreach for clients globally', 'Equilar', 'Equilar', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.equilar.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/equilar/', 'Equilar', '2000', 'Redwood City, CA'),
(13, 2, '<p><strong>BFX Commerce: A leading alcohol marketing agency based in the heart of Chicago</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">At BFX Commerce, the team prides itself on being a leading alcohol marketing agency based in the heart of Chicago. The company&rsquo;s team of innovators, trendsetters, and dedicated professionals is committed to driving growth and maximizing sales in the alcohol industry. They understand that their clients\' success is their top priority, and they strive to provide exceptional services that exceed their expectations.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">What Sets BFX Commerce Apart</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">BFX Commerce&rsquo;s foundation is built on a combination of essential elements that make it stand out from the rest. It has a team of exceptional people, a proven process, and cutting-edge technologies that drive its work. The company&rsquo;s spirit is always ready to go the extra mile for its clients, and it is competitive because it strives to be the best. They are not just a team; they&rsquo;re partners who work closely with their clients to achieve their goals.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Values BFX Commerce Brings to Every Project</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At BFX Commerce, the team brings a bold approach to every project. Their strategies are not just about making bold and well-informed choices; they\'re about envisioning the big picture and driving growth that leaps and bounds ahead of the competition. Transparency is also key to their relationships with clients. They believe in keeping them informed every step of the way, ensuring a partnership based on trust and mutual respect.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The company is also focused on results. Efficiency, resourcefulness, and a laser focus on outcomes define their approach to every campaign they undertake. Whether it\'s consulting, comprehensive digital marketing solutions, logo and label design, website development, social media management, SEO/content creation, photography, or advertisement management across Google, Facebook, and Instagram, they offer it all.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Why Choose BFX Commerce</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">When you choose BFX Commerce, you\'re partnering with an agency that knows the alcohol marketing landscape inside out. Its expertise is led by a founder with over 20 years of experience in managing digital and operations teams across notable companies within the beverage industry (Total Wine &amp; More, Spirit Hub) and retail (Bluemercury). This depth of experience combined with its team\'s innovative drive positions it uniquely to serve your brand.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">BFX Commerce Methodology</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">BFX Commerce provides expert alcohol marketing services tailored to your business. Its methodology is designed to optimize distribution channels and enhance market presence. With personalized strategies crafted for your unique needs, they&rsquo;re dedicated to driving growth and maximizing sales in the alcohol industry.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">BFX Commerce\'s marketing strategies for alcohol beverage businesses are built on three pillars: market share, operations, and goals. It empowers your business by analyzing its operations for improvement and customizing strategies to capitalize on its unique strengths and opportunities. It crafts customized plans to achieve your goals, whether it\'s enhancing distribution channels or bolstering brand visibility.</p>\r\n<p><strong><br><br></strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Creating Strategies That Work Within Compliance Guidelines</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">When it comes to alcohol marketing, BFX Commerce understands the laws and rules of the road. They create strategies that work within the guidelines of the three-tier system, including federally compliant programs and partnerships, state-compliant marketing and incentives, and platform-by-platform restrictions on what will be allowed and what isn\'t.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Products and Services</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">BFX Commerce offers a range of products and services designed to help your business thrive in the competitive world of alcohol marketing. Its services include:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Marketing Consulting: Building and managing programs to drive your business goals</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Branding: Brand design and packaging services that drive sales</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Channel Growth: Technology and services to improve your offerings to ecommerce, wholesale, and off/on-trade establishments</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Promotions: Building your brand awareness and promotions strategies online and in-person</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Not Sure What You Need?</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At BFX Commerce, the team understands that not every brand has infinite resources or knows where to start when it comes to marketing within the alcohol industry. That\'s why they offer alcohol marketing consulting services with a focus on both strategy and implementation. Their approach is straightforward and highly functional, designed to help you grow your business.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Whether you need a standard consulting engagement or an expanded consulting engagement that includes a comprehensive review of your approach and risk mitigation strategies, BFX Commerce is here to help. With its expertise in marketing essentials like channel growth strategies, brand development, promotions strategies, social media management, SEO/content creation, photography, advertising management across Google, Facebook, Instagram &ndash; you can trust us to help you achieve your goals.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At BFX Commerce, the team is committed to delivering exceptional results for its clients. Its team of experts has years of experience in the alcohol industry and is dedicated to helping you build a successful brand.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Brian Feener, CEO/Founder</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Brian is an eCommerce and marketing expert for food and beverage. After nearly 20 years of experience developing e-commerce products and supply chains for retail such as Total Wine &amp; More, Bluemercury, and Spirit Hub (where he was COO), Brian formed a marketing agency centered around his passion for food &amp; beverage. With a specialization in alcohol, he has helped numerous startups and established companies navigate the complexities of online sales, digital marketing strategies, and compliance within the highly regulated alcohol industry.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We strive to be the best, continuously pushing the boundaries to ensure your brand not only reaches its target audience but leaves a lasting impression.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'bfx-commerce-a-leading-alcohol-marketing-agency-based-in-the-heart-of-chicago', '2023-02-08', 'us/BFX-Commerce.jpg', 4, 'profile', 'BFX Commerce: A leading alcohol marketing agency based in the heart of Chicago', 'BFX Commerce', 'BFX Commerce', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://bfxcommerce.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/bfx-commerce/', 'BFX Commerce', '2022', 'Chicago, IL'),
(14, 2, '<p><strong>Hypersonix Inc. is the premier AI platform designed to propel eCommerce and retail businesses toward profitable growth</strong></p>', '<p dir=\"ltr\">In today\'s competitive landscape, eCommerce and retail businesses confront unparalleled challenges that demand not only survival but also profitable growth. Astonishingly, over 70% of these retailers face stagnation or demise, succumbing to escalating costs and unpredictable factors beyond their control. The industry grapples with persistent issues which make establishing a new normal incredibly complicated with the need for real-time identification of opportunities and risks to make faster decisions with more predictable outcomes.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">While some businesses have managed to navigate the rapid expansion of the market, their existing systems and processes are proving inadequate for profitable growth. In the face of recent market upheavals, category competitiveness, unprecedented inflation, and swiftly evolving consumer expectations, the crucial question arises: Can eCommerce and retail businesses get ahead and stay ahead?</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Enter Hypersonix, the pioneering force in addressing this critical challenge with a groundbreaking AI-driven platform that delivered actionable intelligence with its proprietary Commerce Large Language Model long before ChatGPT propelled the tech industry into a frenzy.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Hypersonix stands at the forefront as the premier AI platform meticulously designed to propel eCommerce and retail businesses toward profitable growth. The company&rsquo;s comprehensive solution offers proactive monitoring and diagnostics, analyzing every signal from sales and shipping to competition, consumer behavior, and demand forecasts. Seamlessly integrating with most eCommerce, ERP, financial, and accounting platforms, Hypersonix doesn\'t just promise results; it delivers them within weeks, not months or years.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Hypersonix, the team takes pride in crafting the future of profitable retailers using AI and ensuring eCommerce and retail businesses not only survive but thrive for years to come.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Mission&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The company&rsquo;s mission is to deliver a comprehensive, generative AI-driven operating system for every commerce business that is intelligent, predictive, prescriptive, and proactive.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Vision&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">To shape the future of eCommerce by AI-driven businesses that focus on driving profit and revenue growth, globally.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>The Future of Profit Optimization is Here</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Some pricing and inventory technologies say they drive more revenue. That\'s great, but are they constantly monitoring opportunities and risks to make you more profitable? Not really, and this is exactly why Hypersonix ProfitGPT was created. Hypersonix uses machine-learning and generative AI to give you clear recommendations on driving revenue that are profitable, giving you better cash flow. Let us show you the money!</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Proactive and Timely Monitoring Your business health requires tenacity to uncover new profit and revenue insights that need your attention and action. Hypersonix is the only solution that constantly monitors and alerts you to your opportunities to make more profit and risks to reduce your losses.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Predictive and Prescriptive Insights Hypersonix shares insights into your business health and gives you actionable insights that drive more profits and reduce your losses. Drive margin with granular, sophisticated machine-learning and generative AI-driven forecasting for pricing, promotions, inventory, and cash management.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Anomaly and Pattern Detection Implementing ProfitGPT is not a big IT project requiring a lot of resources. Hypersonix simply connects to your existing eCommerce platform and business systems. Then it uses machine-learning and generative AI to uncover insight from billions of records, in real-time. You receive actionable insights that quickly streamline your complex decision-making process.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>What is ProfitGPT?&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">ProfitGPT is the Leading Predictive Analytics Solution for Retail and DTC Brands.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">For retailers who want to fast-track their AI-driven strategies, ProfitGPT from Hypersonix simplifies the complex analysis of competitors, pricing, promotions, inventory, and forecasting to help commerce companies make better and faster decisions that grow profits.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Accelerate and Automate the Retail Decision-making Process 1000x Faster with Hypersonix AI. ProfitGPT simplifies and automates the analysis of your product\'s prices, promotions, competitors, and inventory so you can make the best decisions at a faster pace. Seamlessly integrating multiple data sources with the company&rsquo;s connected network of generative AI models will deliver actionable insights that drive product sales and margin growth.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>AI-Driven Automation&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&bull; Proactively suggest optimal price adjustments</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&bull; Work across thousands of products</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&bull; Ensure balance between growth, competitiveness, and profitability</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Smart Suggestion Rationale&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&bull; Understand the \'why\' behind every price change</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&bull; Utilize smart, AI-generated rationales for every fluctuation&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&bull; Enable quick, informed decision-making</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">CoPilot-Driven Strategy</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&bull; Integrate AI-driven recommendations</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&bull; Leverage pragmatic business rules for optimization&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&bull; Ensure optimization aligns with your preferences</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Forecasting AI</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Plan with accuracy using ProfitGPT\'s advanced double-machine learning simulator to ensure predictable and maximum sell-through strategies with visibility at the item, category, channel, and location levels.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Promo AI</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Empowers retailers to optimize their promotional strategies with data-driven insights, directly enhancing profit margins and operational efficiency. Integrating AI analytics, it refines promotional tactics to ensure maximum financial impact with minimal expenditure.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Pricing AI</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Proactively monitor, gain insights and automate pricing for maximum sales and product margin growth. Manage the optimal price point for millions of SKUs while solving any price complexity.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Competitor AI</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Having key insights on your competitors regarding their products, prices, promotions, and stock situations allows you to optimize your business strategies and gain market share.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Inventory AI&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With real-time inventory levels, demand patterns, sales velocity, and consumer buying trends at your fingertips, you can worry less about out-of-stocks and over-stocks while optimizing your cash flow.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Generative Commerce Insights and reports leverage data analysis to deliver valuable insights and actionable information. These reports are generated by the ProfitGPT AI engines, which collect, process, and analyze extensive data from different databases.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">By leveraging Hypersonix\'s cutting-edge technology, businesses can gain a competitive edge in today\'s fast-paced market. Hypersonix\'s proprietary Commerce Large Language Model enables us to deliver actionable intelligence that drives profitable growth for eCommerce and retail businesses. With Hypersonix ProfitGPT, retailers can accelerate their decision-making process 1000x faster than traditional methods.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Meet Prem Kiran, CEO&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Prem Kiran is a seasoned CEO, serial entrepreneur, and executive with a passion for building and scaling businesses. With a proven track record of founding, scaling, and exiting tech ventures, he has also held senior executive positions at SAP and STG. Notably, he was awarded the title of Youngest Senior Leader, reserved for the top 2% of global leaders. With expertise in product vision and strategy, business development and sales, product management, M&amp;A, and general management, Prem has held leadership roles at large public companies and has experience as a CEO/CSO with profit-and-loss responsibility. His focus areas include Enterprise SaaS, AI, analytics and big data, data science, business intelligence, marketing automation, B2C e-commerce, and more.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;With GenAI insights and automation from Hypersonix, your teams can make pricing, promotion, inventory, operations, and competitive decisions 1000X faster.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'hypersonix-inc--is-the-premier-ai-platform-designed-to-propel-ecommerce-and-retail-businesses-toward-profitable-growth', '2023-02-08', 'us/Hypersonixinc.jpg', 5, 'profile', 'Hypersonix Inc. is the premier AI platform designed to propel eCommerce and retail businesses toward profitable growth', 'Hypersonixinc', 'Hypersonixinc', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/hypersonix-ai/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/hypersonix-ai/', 'Hypersonix Inc.', '2019', 'San Jose, California'),
(15, 2, '<p><strong>First Orion: Top company for branded communication, handling over 6 million branded calls daily for major businesses, carriers, and developers</strong></p>', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The world of telecommunications is at the core of endless developments with new technologies and innovations mushrooming rapidly. First Orion is one of the fastest-growing, industry-leading providers of telecommunications technology, building industry-leading communication solutions, with a global staff of more than 300 employees. Our mission remains the same&mdash;to provide an exceptional mobile experience while protecting consumers from bad actors since 2008. At First Orion, we genuinely believe that the phone is a means to connect people, and being a mobile communications technology leader, we take out the worry from picking up your device and deliver confidence into every call.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Core Values</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">We believe in the great workplace, built on the principles of trust, transparency, innovation, and excellence. We also value an open and honest environment with deep passion to excel and develop world-class solutions and products. Our team gets driven by the hero mentality of Orion the Hunter, who was admired in ancient Greek culture for his bravery and cunning.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>First Orion&rsquo;s Story</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Our journey began more than a decade ago, with the aim and vision of making the process of reporting unwanted landline calls easier for consumers through the Federal Trade Commission. We founded this company to hunt down bad actors; that is why we chose the First Orion name. Today, as an international enterprise, we have grown and opened offices in such places as North Little Rock, Seattle, and Dubai.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>INFORM: Branded Calling</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">People won\'t answer unknown numbers. In fact, nearly 9 in 10 people will not answer a call from a number they don\'t know. First Orion\'s INFORM empowers businesses to enhance the customer experience and reestablish trust in the telephone call across every major mobile carrier in the U.S.&mdash;featuring aizophan up to 32-character customizable text display, businesses are able to execute clear calls that answer questions and increase customer engagement.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>The INFORM Engine</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Our innovation is built on top of our centralized technology platform, the Digital Communication Exchange. This API approach in real-time lets enterprises connect directly with solution providers and carriers, making businesses more effective at capitalizing on new technology advancements.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>&nbsp;AFFIRM: Reputation Monitoring</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Every business or call center must ensure the integrity of your brand and communicate effectively with your customers. First Orion\'s solution to this problem is AFFIRM, which keeps you updated on how your advertising outbound calls are appearing on various mobile phones. This will update you when there are proper labels and when there are undesirable tags for spam or scam. Using AFFIRM, you can perform the following functions:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Track calling number performance across all 3 major U.S. mobile networks Get alerts every time calls are tagged as SPAM or SCAM;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Minimize the occurrence of calls left unanswered and maximize interaction with customers;&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Increase productivity among agents with clear and concise communication channels;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Take control over your outbound calls with First Orion\'s INFORM and AFFIRM solutions to make sure your business communicates properly with your customer base. Try INFORM today and see how it can benefit your business.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Joe Stinziano, President &amp; Chief Executive Officer</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Joe Stinziano is President and CEO at First Orion and has a strong track record in the consumer electronics sector. At First Orion, Joe has built on this foundation, focusing on transparent communication solutions.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">He has played a key role in expanding INFORM solutions and introducing PAIRED and SENTRY, initiatives that protect against brand and call spoofing. Through partnerships with all major U.S. mobile carriers and global expansion, Joe has been actively broadening First Orion&rsquo;s impact in the field of communication, aiming to create a safer and more trustworthy environment for consumers and businesses alike.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Previously serving as the Corporate Executive Vice President for Samsung Electronics America&rsquo;s Consumer and Enterprise Business Division, Joe was instrumental in positioning Samsung as a leader in technological innovation. His efforts significantly contributed to delivering top-tier technology that has enhanced consumer and business experiences.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We&rsquo;re in the telecommunications game, elevating branded calls for all major U.S. carriers, along with Fortune 500 brands and other mobile apps. You make the call, we make the connection.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'first-orion-top-company-for-branded-communication', '2023-02-08', 'us/First-Orion.jpg', 6, 'profile', 'First Orion: Top company for branded communication, handling over 6 million branded calls daily for major businesses, carriers, and developers', 'First-Orion', 'First-Orion', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://firstorion.com/?_gl=1*2tcmaw*_up*MQ..*_gs*MQ..&gclid=CjwKCAjwruXBBhArEiwACBRtHRJG_OH5TKGrMoU8_A9UUiDqrsv0xNUAtLuIuVFBjI9OF8EX5-CvVhoCWbQQAvD_BwE&gbraid=0AAAAAD0N6dRRTFDKUkErLkBWJ8NiWHkvt', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/firstorion/', 'First Orion', '2008', 'North Little Rock, Arkansas'),
(16, 2, '<p><strong>Lightswitch produces content at scale in all 50 states for agencies, marketers, and online media</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">Video content is today part of a business since it conveys the message, engages the audience, and drives results. With an increasing demand for high-quality video production, businesses need a partner who can execute exceptional content anywhere in the world. Lightswitch is one of the leading video production companies that have been doing service to clients from San Antonio to St. Paul, Trinidad to Tokyo, Poughkeepsie to Pluto&mdash;on-location video production capabilities anywhere instantly.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Lightswitch creates videos for agencies, creatives, and marketers, further going on to partner with clients from any industry, across the board. With its global reach and expertise, the company has established itself as a trusted partner for those who want to create engaging video content that reaches audiences worldwide.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Local Video Production Solutions for Gannett</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">For nearly a decade, Lightswitch has had the pleasure of teaming up with Gannett&mdash;a Fortune 500 company&mdash;to deliver local video production solutions to thousands of small and medium-sized businesses across the United States. With a presence in more than 600 markets nationwide, Gannett\'s powerful marketing solutions demand that their video partner be not only reliable and scalable but also able to make top-notch content that truly speaks to the local markets.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As the nationwide video partner of Gannett, Lightswitch places award-winning video production in every market, at the hands of their teams&mdash;hundreds of pieces of multimedia annually in more than a dozen languages. The alliance brought, by extension, the capacity for Gannett to make local video content down to the occasion of specificity in needs and preference for each market at a very high level of engagement and ROI in any respective account.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Partnering with Zeiss: Precision at Scale Internationally</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Apart from the partnership with Gannett, some of the other noteworthy clients Lightswitch collaborates with include Zeiss, a global leadership company in technology. Zeiss is building reliance on Lightswitch expertise in industrial metrology and microscopy equipment. Zeiss needs a video partner that can deliver precision at scale internationally; Lightswitch, with their global reach and technical knowledge, makes them an ideal partner.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Award-Winning Documentary Series for The Advocate</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Another large client of Lightswitch was The Advocate, with whom the company worked on their award-winning documentary series focused on Mardi Gras by organizing over 150 shoots in just three months with local crews to produce three feature-length documentaries regarding music, culture, food, history, New Orleans, and Mardi Gras. The documentary reached upwards of 1.6 million viewers in 105 countries, featuring such guests as Hoda Kotb, Emeril Lagasse, and Jimmy Buffett.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Educating America\'s Future Technology Leaders with CompTIA</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Lightswitch works with CompTIA, the leading voice and advocate for the $5 trillion global information technology ecosystem. CompTIA has been continuously producing volumes of informational content to help them in their mission of educating America\'s future technology leaders. From here, they entrust Lightswitch with video production and other relevant materials. Lightswitch captures events, coordinates testimonials on a mass scale, and creates promotional materials that will help define new courses so CompTIA can keep ahead of the competition.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Providing the Proof of Working from Home with Kforce</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In addition to working for these notable clients, Lightswitch teamed up with Kforce&mdash;a workforce solutions company adjusting to a hybrid work environment. To help Kforce express the value of working from home, Lightswitch sent crews out locally to meet employees where they lived and worked, capturing the new aspects of life that working from home enables. With staff coast to coast, localized Lightswitch crews and project management made filming easy no matter the location.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Short background of Lynette Schwanger, CEO and Founder</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As a teen, Lynette developed an unhealthy obsession with the Lord of the Rings movies which sparked a lifelong interest in film. After graduating from Denison University with degrees in Cinema and English Writing, she worked her way through Chicago&rsquo;s film scene keen on mastering all aspects of video production, from the creative to the technical. After witnessing first-hand the always-on burnout culture that permeated the production and agency world, Lynette knew there was a better way. She co-founded Lightswitch with the belief that happy people do great work - and that employee work-life balance is essential to success</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As CEO, Lynette loves using her video expertise to help the Lightswitch team bring clients&rsquo; visions to life creatively through video. On the weekends you can find her climbing mountains with her husband, Mike, or cuddling her cat, Pierre, and dog, Voo, who hopes to be as good of a climber as&nbsp;Biscuit&nbsp;someday.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;Our producers meet you at your point of need, whether it involves conceptualization, scripting, storyboarding, or execution.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'lightswitch-produces-content-at-scale-in-all-50-states-for-agencies-marketers-and-online-media', '2023-08-02', 'us/Lynette-Schwanger-ceo.jpg', 7, 'profile', 'Lightswitch produces content at scale in all 50 states for agencies, marketers, and online media', 'Lynette-Schwanger', 'Lynette-Schwanger', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://lightswitch.net/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/lightswitchdesign/', 'Lightswitch', '1993', 'Sausalito, California');
