(17, 2, '<p><strong>Etumos is the Marketing Operations expert focused on helping clients activate the full potential of their marketing investments</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Etumos empowers marketers to create some time to focus on revenue-generating activities by giving them a reflective, data-informed framework for optimizing and measuring engagement at every step of the customer journey. Cutting through the noise and hype in today\'s martech landscape, Etumos relies on a time-tested playbook that ensures maximum effectuality of clients\' tech stacks, devoid of complexity.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Reach Your Marketing Potential</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Prove marketing ROI, justify the martech spend on the books, level up marketing operations maturity, and make sure the data flows correctly across your entire martech stack. Etumos can help.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Etumos Approach</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">How Etumos builds solutions meeting marketing operations needs of today but also anticipating the future state of business.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Etumos Philosophy</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Marketing Operations is a specialized profession with specialized skills needed.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Team &amp; Leaders</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Etumos, the team of growing Marketing Operations experts is relentless in pursuit of excellence so you smash your marketing goals.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Careers</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">If you\'re passionate about what\'s next in marketing technology and innovation, let\'s start a conversation.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>S-C-R-I-M Spells Success</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">This Etumos team seems to have a very different way of approaching how they think about the right solutions to fit business. Etumos calls these guiding principles the SCRIM Design Methodology.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">SCRIM stands for Scalable, Clear, Robust, Intelligent, and Modular. At Etumos, SCRIM is a mantra, and it\'s at the heart of how Etumos designs integration solutions, configures platforms, and architects campaign flows&hellip;. you get the picture. It is in everything.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Not quite sure what Etumos means?</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Scalable:</strong> The solution should perform similarly well at 10x the size.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Clear:</strong> How the solution has to be understandable, and reduced potential for confusion, errors built into it.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Robust: </strong>All functional requirements are covered with the solution.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Intelligent: </strong>The solution takes care of upstream and downstream processes; there is no concept of \"silent errors\" baked into it.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Modular: The solution is designed to do one function and can be easily maintained or decoupled without hurting the other componentry.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Automation and Integration Services for Marketing</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Etumos, it is known that you can\'t afford to waste hours trying to solve problems technology should solve for you. You need to go beyond those limited integrations that come with your applications. Etumos can design and deliver the right technical solutions that support better martech integration, better data flow, and more efficient campaign execution, all while providing a single source of truth for customer data.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Connect Systems</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">When integrations between your platforms don\'t quite fit your unique needs out-of-the-box, Etumos can facilitate the planning and implementation of the right structure.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Automate Everything</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Schedule data Imports, implement and manage middleware, create triggered events between systems, and reduce the team\'s manual work getting data across platforms.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Manage In-House Dev Resources</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Etumos speaks to dev and marketing ops so they can help translate marketing business requirements to the dev team and manage QA outcomes.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Use the Marketing Data You Collect and Pay For</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With great data and automation at the core of strong marketing practice, it\'s little wonder organizations are adding new technologies to their martech stacks at breakneck pace. The outcome is petabytes of valued data, captured but not necessarily making it across the stack to drive engagement and conversion. This is attributed to the fact that integration and developer resources are not available for identifying technology-centric opportunities, which can integrate martech stacks.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Preference Management Should Not Become a Full-Time Job</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Management of email preferences between systems and platforms can be an activity that turns to full-time work within a large and complex martech stack. You will then be able to centralize these preferences in one place using the iPaaS tools so you can stay in compliance with all global privacy laws while reducing manual work.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>How Etumos Helps You Get More from Your Martech Stack</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Companies are bridging this chasm&mdash;laborious manual processes&mdash;with a dearth of integration guidance and development skills, which prevents them from swinging into action effectively to engage prospects. Etumos can help get the majority of the systems to a more scalable place while removing the threat of future tech debt with technology integration services. How Etumos can help:</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&bull; Value-prioritized auditing systems and recommending opportunities for integration</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&bull; Technical and architectural guidance in vendor selection</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&bull; Creating custom integrations and workflow automation</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&bull; Better sync timing between systems</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Marketing Automation Consulting</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Etumos, it is known that you can\'t afford to waste valuable time trying to solve problems that technology should solve for you. You need to go beyond the limited integrations that come with your applications. Etumos is going to design and deliver the right technical solution that will allow you to see better martech integration, better data flow, more efficient campaign execution, and centralized customer data.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>HubSpot Consulting</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Process Creation:</strong> Etumos\' patented Framework applies team best practices to create, within HubSpot, repeatable and scalable operational processes.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Campaign Execution: </strong>Manage the end-to-end campaign build process with Etumos inside of HubSpot for repeatable and scalable processes to reduce errors and time-to-market.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Campaign Metrics &amp; Analytics:</strong> Connect your CRM to the processes in HubSpot for a complete view of your inbound pipeline.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Edward Unthank, Founder</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As a renowned marketeer, Unthank is a triple Marketo Champion, leader of the Seattle MUG, and thought-leader in the MOPs community. He is obsessed with beta releases, templates, new technologies, and anything that can make marketing more intelligent and effective.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We cut through the hype and noise of today\'s martech landscape by using proven best practices that maximize the effectiveness of our clients\' tech stacks, no matter the complexity.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'etumos-is-the-marketing-operations-expert-focused-on-helping-clients-activate-the-full-potential-of-their-marketing-investments', '2023-08-01', 'us/Etumos.jpg', 8, 'profile', 'Etumos is the Marketing Operations expert focused on helping clients activate the full potential of their marketing investments', 'Etumos', 'Etumos', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://etumos.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/etumos/', 'Etumos', '2014', 'Seattle, WA'),
(18, 2, '<p><strong>MDT Innovations: The Lead in IoT Value Chain, Intelligent Wireless Sensors, and IoT as a Service</strong></p>', '<p dir=\"ltr\">Successful companies in this technology-driven world are the ones that balance between innovation and execution. A very good example would be MDT Innovations, which is strongly committed to state-of-the-art research and development, bringing these concrete results into the real world, be it in such areas as IoT value chains, intelligent wireless sensors, or IoT as a service.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">MDT Innovations is one of the fastest-growing technology companies in the Asia Pacific region, keying into the areas of IoT value chains, intelligent wireless sensors, and IoT as a service. In particular, the company has carved a niche for itself in the industry\'s biggest players by fostering a culture of innovation and excellence.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Company History and Achievements</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">MDTi was founded in 2004 and has been profitable since its establishment. The company has grown tremendously in export sales; even to this day, accumulated export sales have been in excess of half a billion dollars. In 2017, export sales accounted for 98.5% of the total revenues, and this showed that the company had actually performed well in international businesses. MDTi has won numerous awards and accolades, including multiple Asia Pacific ICT Awards, Red Herring Asia 100 and Global 100, Deloitte Technology Fast 500 Asia Pacific, and Frost &amp; Sullivan\'s Asia Pacific IoT Solutions Competitive Strategy Innovation and Leadership Award.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>IoT Solutions</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">MDTi works in the domain of IoT on research, design, development, and deployment; after that, maintenance is provided for the IoT key components and infrastructural solutions. The engineering team is engaged in the development of IoT systems: RFID inlays, smart devices, modules, reader-writers, gateways, antennae, mobile applications, and software components.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>WIP Automation SCHOOLTRAC</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Wireless sensor-based solution which accurately detects children\'s motion in and out of school areas.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">INDUSTRY 4.0 Automation in manufacturing technologies is enabled by WIP.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>LINOTAG</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">A state-of-the-art design in RFID that involves the use of yarn as a wireless antenna which cannot be detected by any needle detector machine.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Ubiquitous Monitoring of Trolleys</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">A smart trolley system that immediately brings about stock count within areas of specification.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>RAPITA connected healthcare</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">A solution to prevent theft of hospital assets through staff warnings upon exit of equipment from the facility.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>MDT Fintech</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">MDT Fintech is an outsourcing leading service provider qualifying as Hosted payment services. The variety of products and services include:</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Immediate Payments &amp; Retail Payments Solution</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">A Payment Gateway and professional services platform for financial institutions, payment service providers and FinTech entities</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>MANAGED PAYMENT SERVICES</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">End-to-End payment processing of high reliability with predictable resource consumption</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Credit/Debit Card Management</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Accepting &amp; Processing Payments all the time</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Retail Payments Platform (RPP)</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">A generic QR code for merchant payment. PARTNERSHIP WITH ACI To expand services across the Asian region.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Values and Philosophy</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">MDT Innovations believes in enabling IoT solutions and services that empower its clients to connect with things, however insignificant the \'things\' may seem to have always wanted to connect. The company&rsquo;s culture and values are oriented around this very philosophy of innovation, collaboration, and customer satisfaction. It strives to make a difference for its partners and customers through its smartly devised innovations.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Meet Choon Lian Liew, CEO of MDT Innovations</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Choon Lian Liew, the CEO, is a well-known market research and industry analyst in New York and Tokyo. In addition to his thoughtful practice in market research, he has also had broad experience in management consultancy. With a keen knowledge base on design, development, and value engineering related to advanced analog and digital display technologies, he has a similarly good feel for the industry. Moreover, this is further supported by his especial experience in designing, development, and engineering of RFID ICs, tags, antennas and reader modules that gave him an all-rounded view of the technology sector.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;MDTi is proud of its standout engineering achievements mainly the development of world smallest NFC module, MD770R, and NFC in SIM card, which shrunk RF front end and antenna into the size of SIM card, thus empowering all mobile phones to become NFC-enabled.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'mdt-innovations-the-lead-in-iot-value-chain-intelligent-wireless-sensors-and-iot-as-a-service', '2023-02-08', 'us/MDTInnovations.jpg', 10, 'profile', 'MDT Innovations: The Lead in IoT Value Chain, Intelligent Wireless Sensors, and IoT as a Service', 'MDT Innovations', 'MDT Innovations', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://mmdt.cc/', 'Petaling Jaya, Kuala Lumpur / Selangor', 'MDT Innovations (MDTi)', '2004', 'Petaling Jaya, Kuala Lumpur / Selangor'),
(19, 2, '<p><strong>Sarah Best Strategy helps businesses and groups stand out online by offering expert help to bring your vision to life</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">At Sarah Best Strategy, the team knows that every organization has the potential to be a star in the digital space. An award-winning, certified digital marketing agency, Sarah Best Strategy assists businesses and organizations of all sizes looking to make a truthful, meaningful impact on people\'s lives and within communities. Sarah Best Strategy commits itself to unleashing the full expression of your in-house teams and talent while giving expert support in extending your bandwidth in the attainment of your goals.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With a comprehensive set of services, Sarah Best Strategy is there to help companies develop strength and overall, their digital marketing. Whether you\'re struggling to make sense of how well your social media or website content is doing, or if you\'re simply trying to determine which activities to focus on first within the confines of limited staffing or resource constraints, Sarah Best Strategy can help you in all your needs. Exteriorize confidence and clarity in your business strategy with social media, SEO, email, advertising, and inbound auditing and strategy sessions by Sarah Best Strategy; it also provides ad-hoc team training and coaching sessions and workshops.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">If you don\'t have the internal resources to reach these goals, Sarah Best Strategy can help. From end-to-end in the digital marketing spectrum, Sarah Best Strategy\'s retainer-based services include top-notch social media management and social media advertising, email marketing, Google Ad Grant management, website content strategy and copywriting, search engine optimization, and local search optimization. Sarah Best Strategy works nationally with organizations across multiple digital marketing disciplines: social media marketing, inbound marketing, content marketing, SEO/SEM, and email marketing.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Partnerships such as Sprout Social, Mailchimp, and Facebook Marketing Partners, along with WBE/WOSB/SBE certifications, flesh out Sarah Best Strategy\'s dedication to quality in service delivery. Providing clarity, easing doubts, and working better together toward KPI-focused strategies that actually work&mdash;with actual workflow challenges in mind&mdash;Sarah Best Strategy believes in your in-house team\'s potential ability to do great things.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The varied services provided by Sarah Best Strategy support your digital marketing efforts. In case you are struggling to get confidence and clarity about your existing social media or website content, then Sarah Best Strategy will help you with audits and plans. Basically, it develops confidence with digital marketing skills through coaching and consulting, via value-packed hour-long training sessions. The areas it offers services include: Content strategy planning, SEO strategy and local search optimization, Campaign creation, Inbound strategy development, and \"Same page\" content planning sessions.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">If you need ongoing support to see your vision through, Sarah Best Strategy is here for you, to extend your team. Some of the services Extelyn includes are social media management, copywriting, SEO maintenance, live social media coverage, social media advertising, Google AdWords management, creation of a lead generation path, email marketing, blogging, brand champions, and social media chatbots. Be it strategic guidance or tactical support, or both, Sarah Best Strategy is here to make your goals a reality.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Sarah Best Strategy, the team believes every organization has potential that can radiate in the digital space. Let us unlock this for you by providing knowledgeable support to empower your in-house teams and talent.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Meet Sarah Best, CEO</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Sarah Best, CEO and visionary leader, has garnered an impressive array of accolades for her innovative digital marketing strategies, including the prestigious Best Use of a Social Media Platform award from Travel + Leisure. As a recognized thought leader, Sarah has been featured in leading publications such as SUCCESS Magazine, Crain\'s Chicago Business, Mashable, TechCrunch, Chicago Tribune, National Geographic Traveler, and more.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As an esteemed guest lecturer, Sarah has shared her expertise at the University of Wisconsin-Madison School of Business and has been invited to speak at esteemed events like Social Media Week for the MacArthur Foundation and SXSW (South by Southwest) twice. A graduate of New York University, Sarah holds a Certificate in Entrepreneurship from the Goldman Sachs 10,000 Small Businesses Program at Babson College and has furthered her business education at the Tuck School of Business at Dartmouth.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Beyond her professional accomplishments, Sarah is a creative force to be reckoned with. An avid traveler and multi-talented artist, she is also a published poet whose work has appeared in The Yale Review and Painted Bride Quarterly. As a visual artist and film curator, Sarah has curated exhibitions at esteemed institutions such as the Museum of Contemporary Art (Chicago), Hyde Park Arts Center (Chicago), Mana Contemporary (Chicago/Miami/NJ), Links Hall (Chicago), Chicago Cultural Center, and Echo Park Film Center (Los Angeles).</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We build strong teams through audits of social media and search programs,&nbsp; strategy, group whiteboarding sessions, group trainings, â€‹and 1:1 coaching.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'sarah-best-strategy-helps-businesses-and-groups-stand-out-online-by-offering-expert-help-to-bring-your-vision-to-life', '2023-02-08', 'us/Sarah-Best,-CEO.jpg', 11, 'profile', 'Sarah Best Strategy helps businesses and groups stand out online by offering expert help to bring your vision to life', 'Sarah Best Strategy', 'Sarah Best Strategy', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.sarahbeststrategy.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/sarah-best-strategy/about/', 'Sarah Best Strategy', '2014', 'Middleton, Wisconsin'),
(20, 2, '<p><strong>Momentum Consulting provides one-on-one coaching, team consulting, conflict resolution, and meeting facilitation</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">At Momentum Consulting, the team is not your average consultant. They&rsquo;re driven by a mission to empower individuals and organizations to achieve breakthrough performance by fostering a culture of dignity, value, and growth. They believe that everyone deserves to succeed in their work and feel valued for their contributions.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As a high-level executive, you know what it takes to succeed in today\'s fast-paced business environment. You\'ve likely developed a keen sense of what works and what doesn\'t, and you\'re always looking for ways to improve your performance and stay ahead of the curve. But even with your expertise and experience, you may still feel like there\'s something missing. Maybe it\'s a shift in team dynamics or client needs that\'s leaving you feeling unsatisfied and uncertain about the future.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">That\'s where Momentum Consulting comes in. Its team of experts is dedicated to helping you overcome the barriers that are holding you back and achieve the breakthroughs you need to take your career and organization to the next level.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>One-on-One Coaching</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Momentum Consulting&rsquo;s one-on-one coaching services are designed to help you shift your career trajectory and accelerate your professional performance. With the guidance of its experienced coaches, you\'ll gain a new level of awareness and clarity about what\'s holding you back and how to overcome it. The company will work together to identify blind spots, change unproductive behaviours, and develop strategies for achieving your goals.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Executive Edge</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">For high-level executives, Momentum Consulting offers its Executive Edge program, a transformative 2-3 day residential experience that will help you tap into your full potential as a leader. This program is designed to help you uncover blind spots, develop new perspectives, and create a clear plan for driving innovation and growth within your organization.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Drive Cultural Change</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Building sustainable performance into an organization\'s culture is a key part of the approach at Momentum Consulting. It knows that a positive, values-driven culture is essential for long-term success, which is why it offers a range of programs and services designed to help you drive cultural change within your organization.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">From its 8-aspect cultural shift program to its company-wide perspective facilitations, Momentum Consulting can help you create a culture that aligns with your values and goals. Whether you\'re looking to improve communication, collaboration, or innovation within your organization, the company can help.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Mission Critical Initiatives</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">When it comes to important projects, every minute counts. That\'s why Momentum Consulting offers mission critical initiatives designed to help you make the most of the limited time you have for each project. Momentum Consulting&rsquo;s team will work with you to identify potential limitations, facilitate creative problem-solving sessions with decision-makers, develop solutions, and provide coaching to ensure successful implementation.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Cultural Design</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Momentum Consulting, the team believes that culture frames an organization. That\'s why they offer cultural design services designed to help you create an intentional culture that aligns with your values and goals. They will work with you to identify fundamental behaviors that drive success within your organization and integrate them into your culture.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>The Full-Service Effect</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Momentum Consulting&rsquo;s comprehensive program addresses all the internal connections necessary to shift your organization to a higher level of productivity and engagement. From discovery and discussion to building culture and coaching, the company works with you every step of the way to help you achieve breakthrough performance.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Craig Clark, Co-Founder</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Craig specializes in people. He has spent the past 40 years becoming a foremost expert on the science of human dynamics in the business world. But he is not a theorist; he is a practical change agent who goes inside organizations to drive and positively affect performance by uncovering the blind spots that constrain performance and growth.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Craig believes that dignity and respect are the birthrights of every individual. His work with people and organizations is designed to honor that conviction. He also believes that every client is entitled to a real and measurable return on the resources they expend with business consultants. Those two ideals work in partnership and are the foundation for the past and future success of Momentum.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Having led programs and workshops for individuals, Craig turned to corporate consulting, recognizing that any significant world change could occur only at an organizational level. He has since spent years developing a transformational approach to solving organizational problems with successful strategies in a variety of cultures, countries and languages.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Craig&rsquo;s r&eacute;sum&eacute; proves that techniques for improving human communications are not bound by oceans or languages. He has applied his skills across diverse groups and cultures &ndash; from Moscow to South America, from the United Kingdom to Australia, including in-residence work in Asia.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As founder and CEO, Craig oversees operations both in the U.S. and abroad. He is focused on growing Momentum&rsquo;s corporate discipline and leading teams in multi-day breakthrough programs that generate long-term, measurable results.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We help organizations, teams and individuals around the world achieve breakthrough performance.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'momentum-consulting-provides-one-on-one-coaching-team-consulting-conflict-resolution-and-meeting-facilitation', '2023-08-02', 'us/Momentum-Consulting.jpg', 12, 'profile', 'Momentum Consulting provides one-on-one coaching, team consulting, conflict resolution, and meeting facilitation', 'Momentum Consulting', 'Momentum Consulting', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.momentumconsulting.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/momentum-consulting-inc/', 'Business Consulting and Services', '', 'Austin, TX'),
(21, 2, '<p><strong>Revenue Rocket helps IT services firms with merger and acquisition (M&amp;A) initiatives and optimizing growth strategies</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">It\'s what Revenue Rocket wants for you, to help cut through the mucky water that stands between where you are and the growth of your business. You will do so via the process of the company&rsquo;s merger and acquisition expertise, coupled with growth strategy initiatives at Revenue Rocket. Don\'t make your journey to growth and profitability alone. Let Revenue Rocket help guide you to a point where you\'re ready to finally launch into a new season of organic growth through strategies that may include opening new office locations, new services, a boost in your sales efforts, and mergers and acquisition advising.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Are You Ready to Grow Your Business?</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Revenue Rocket marshals executives against the forces challenging growth with smart thinking and sound recommendations in organic growth and M&amp;A. Go for a ride with Revenue Rocket.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>IT Services Provider Contemplating a Sale?</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Deciding to sell your managed services provider &mdash;or any IT services firm &mdash; is in both regards a very big and often highly emotive decision. Of course, there\'s the great excitement of moving to newer opportunities, but it\'s also pertinent that this comes with great considerations and planning. Download Revenue Rocket\'s white paper, which gives practical advice and actionable steps to navigate this process.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Get A Deal Done with the M&amp;A Experts for IT Services Companies</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Mergers and acquisitions are the fastest path to growth, and if you\'re not participating, you\'re leaving revenue or risk on the table.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Now is the ideal time to either buy a business to bolster you through this economic downturn or take some money off the table by selling your firm.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">But don\'t try and go it alone; many twists and turns lie along the road to a successful deal. You\'ll want someone on your side who\'s been at the table for origination through closing and due diligence.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Revenue Rocket has facilitated over 200 M&amp;A Transactions within the IT services market and is ready now to reverse-engineer success for you to acquire another firm or to sell your company.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>M&amp;A Buyer Readiness: Liftoff</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">You\'ve decided to organically grow your technology-enabled services business, but don\'t know where to start. The decision to grow your business through acquisition is a big one and surely should not at all be made lightly. So many things are coming into play when getting the business ready: the right strategic fit, cultural alignment, and most importantly, the financial readiness.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With Revenue Rocket\'s seasoned management and M&amp;A Liftoff program, all sweat and uncertainty will be taken off when inorganic growth positions your business. Its seasoned experts guide the best cultural, strategic, and financial fit for your business in a unique manner.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>The 4-Step M&amp;A Liftoff</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">M&amp;A Liftoff is an end-to-end enterprise-grade service that begins with a comprehensive assessment of your business. While looking at every aspect of your business through the lens of its readiness to be acquired, Revenue Rocket brings you the important plans for improvement in order to get you ready to close the deal.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Step One: Growth Strategy Assessment with Financial Valuation&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">6 weeks</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Evaluate your business strategy, financials, corporate structure, operating model, culture, and talent.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Revenue Rocket has a number of resources to put a value on your business and to determine the proper acquisition size from a financial standpoint. It estimates points that are financially positive in nature, capital structure, and trends to enable a proper determination of your buyer ability.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">From a strategic and cultural perspective, Revenue Rocket will kick start methods&mdash;working through research and diagnostic tools, along with interviews&mdash;to provide best practices from your current state in analyzing your situation to give you recommendations on what needs to be done and by when in order to get prepared with life with a combined entity.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Step 2. Market Positioning</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Two weeks</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Revenue Rocket educates your team with rich-data insight on opportunities and advise your team on which markets are advantageous to target. Finally, Revenue Rocket works with you to act as your advisory service team to uniquely position your business to sellers to ensure you stand out favorably in a competitive market.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Step 3: Business Optimization</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Four to Six weeks</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Revenue Rocket works with you to make your business better and deliver a powerful proposition to present sellers. Taking a targeted approach to correspond to the most important opportunities for improvement and the implementation of demonstrated best practices. To transfer balancing teaching, review, and implementation of change management approaches that empower you to make the next leap to realize inorganic growth. Revenue Rocket will finish together a range of evaluations, exercises, and one-on-one coaching sessions as you work through your countdown to M&amp;A Liftoff!</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Step 4: Targeting</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Four weeks</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Here is where, in the process, when you are ready to buy, Revenue Rocket will assist you in targeting and honing your list so the potential target company\'s cultural, strategic, and financial fit may be decided on.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Let Revenue Rocket guide you with its expert experience to meet your goals, and be confident that you, your team, customers, and partners will be best prepared for exponential growth through acquisition!</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Growth Champions for Tech-Services Companies</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Would you like to take your IT services firm to a new level of revenue and profit growth? Let Revenue Rocket Consulting Group help. They are a growth strategy consulting and M&amp;A advisory firm committed to helping tech services outfits develop long-term, actionable strategies that will drive their revenues month by month.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Revenue Rocket has a team deep on subject matter expertise in the development of strategy leadership, marketing, sales, business process, financial analysis, measurement, and the study of industrial/organizational psychology. Revenue Rocket has intense domain knowledge of IT managed service providers, application development firms, application integration firms, and cybersecurity providers.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Growth Strategy Consulting</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Every day, Revenue Rocket bumps into these firms: revenue has flatlined, marketing isn\'t cranking on all cylinders, and only the CEO\'s a salesperson who can close a deal.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">You may have great people, fantastic technology chops, but running an IT services firm profitably takes effort to work ON the company &mdash;not just IN the business every day.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Revenue Rocket has crafted a proven methodology for systematic business transformation by bringing key stakeholders out of reactive mode and into a proactive view, thus enabling your firm to enjoy top-quartile performance.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Meet Mike Harvath, CEO, and President</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Revenue Rocket is led by CEO and president, Mike Harvath. Mike has spent his entire career in technology, helping those in the IT Services industry find the balance between growth and profitability. Mike has a Bachelor of Science in Electrical Engineering from the University of Minnesota, and an MBA from Harvard Business School. He lives and works in the Twin Cities metro area.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We help executives confront forces against growth with smart thinking and sound recommendations in organic growth and M&amp;A.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'revenue-rocket-helps-it-services-firms-with-merger-and-acquisition-ma-initiatives-and-optimizing-growth-strategies', '2023-02-08', 'us/Revenue-Rocket.jpg', 13, 'profile', 'Revenue Rocket helps IT services firms with merger and acquisition (M&A) initiatives and optimizing growth strategies', 'Revenue Rocket', 'Revenue Rocket', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.revenuerocket.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/revenue-rocket-consulting-group/', 'Revenue Rocket Consulting Group', '2002', 'Bloomington, MN'),
(22, 2, '<p><strong>Paradigm partners with innovative companies to build stronger, more inclusive organizations</strong></p>', '<p dir=\"ltr\">In today\'s fast-paced and ever-changing business landscape, it\'s more important than ever for organizations to prioritize diversity, equity, and inclusion (DEI). A company\'s culture is shaped by its employees, and fostering an inclusive environment where every individual can thrive is crucial for success. At Paradigm, the team understands the importance of creating a workplace where everyone feels valued, respected, and empowered to do their best work. Their comprehensive suite of technology, tools, and consulting services is designed to help organizations achieve this goal.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Paradigm\'s DEI Training programs are designed to equip employees with the skills they need to effectively hire and manage people from all backgrounds, collaborate with colleagues from diverse perspectives, and contribute to a culture where everyone can meet their potential. Its online, live, and blended learning programs address a range of topics, including unconscious bias, inclusive leadership, allyship, and more. The company also offers tools that translate learning into action.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">To build a future-ready company, organizations need an effective strategy for attracting the best people from all backgrounds and creating cultures where people can collaborate effectively.&nbsp; Paradigm&rsquo;s DEI strategy and analytics solutions help organizations benchmark their DEI maturity, use data-driven insights to make better decisions, and equip leaders with the guidance they need to take action.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Paradigm, the team understands that a company\'s DEI is shaped by both its employees and its processes and policies. Its comprehensive suite of solutions helps organizations address both aspects. The company offers DEI consulting and live training services that empower employees to incorporate inclusion into their everyday work.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">DEI Consulting and Live Training experts design DEI training programs that move the needle. Paradigm partners with clients to create impactful learning journeys, facilitate live workshops, and equip internal teams to lead discussions on diversity, equity, and inclusion.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Paradigm helps organizations meet the needs of different stakeholders by designing training programs that launch effectively, communicate with learners at key moments, deliver resources that translate learning to action, and measure impact.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Paradigm&rsquo;s expert-led workshops cover a range of topics, including:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Managing Unconscious Bias: </strong>This training helps employees understand how unconscious bias undermines effective decision-making, inclusive team dynamics, and career growth.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Inclusive Leadership:</strong> This training helps leaders build and lead teams where people from all backgrounds can do their best work and thrive.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Allyship:</strong> This training gives employees a shared definition of allyship, an understanding of how allyship creates a more inclusive culture for everyone.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Paradigm also facilitates action-oriented discussions on advanced topics such as inclusive hiring, inclusive performance management, growth mindset, belonging, anti-racism, microaggressions, championing DEI for HR professionals, understanding the employee experience and taking action, inclusion surveys, and focus groups.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Paradigm&rsquo;s Inclusion Survey uncovers how employees feel about the key themes that impact inclusion &ndash; belonging, fairness, psychological safety, commitment to diversity, and more. Their experts analyze the data to identify barriers to inclusion across different demographics and provide recommendations on how to address those barriers.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">For richer context around survey results or a deeper understanding of the experience of employees from different demographic groups, Paradigm&rsquo;s DEI experts facilitate structured conversations with employees and translate what they hear into useful insights and recommendations.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Paradigm has reimagined sexual harassment prevention training with inclusion at its core. Its online harassment training is designed to foster cultures where harassment is not tolerated and empower people who witness or experience harassment to take action.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">DEI Initiatives Your DEI strategy needs a plan. Blueprint is your architect. With Blueprint\'s online assessment tool, you can assess your organization\'s efforts, benchmark your DEI program\'s maturity, and track the metrics that matter.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Meet Joelle Emerson, Co-Founder &amp; CEO</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Joelle Emerson is the Co-Founder and CEO at Paradigm, a DEI company offering a comprehensive suite of technology, tools, and consulting to help transform organizations. Founded in 2014, Paradigm works to create cultures where people from all backgrounds and identities can do their best work and thrive. The company has partnered with over 1000 companies to design and implement DEI strategies that drive measurable impact. Learn more at www.paradigmIQ.com.<br><br>Before founding Paradigm, Joelle Emerson was a civil rights lawyer. As a Skadden Fellow at Equal Rights Advocates, I represented clients in discrimination and harassment litigation, and I advocated for policies to ensure equal pay and other workplace protections for women.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We help you design representative teams, fair talent systems and processes, and inclusive cultures that boost engagement, performance, and retention.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'paradigm-partners-with-innovative-companies-to-build-stronger-more-inclusive-organizations', '2023-02-08', 'us/Paradigm.jpg', 14, 'profile', 'Paradigm partners with innovative companies to build stronger, more inclusive organizations', 'Paradigm', 'Paradigm', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.paradigmpartner.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/paradigm-partners-llc/', 'Paradigm Partners LLC', '2001', 'Bloomington, MN');
