(23, 2, '<p><strong>The Lead Gen Specialists: Experts in Targeted Lead Generation</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In today\'s competitive business landscape, generating high-quality leads is crucial for driving growth and increasing revenue. With the right lead generation strategy, businesses can not only increase brand awareness but also establish a pipeline of prospects that are eager to engage with their products or services. The Lead Gen Specialists, a team of experienced lead generation professionals, understand the importance of generating sales-qualified leads and provide outsourced lead generation services to businesses across various sectors.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Understanding Your Business and Industry</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The Lead Gen Specialists directors have honed their expertise over three decades in the lead generation and marketing industry, giving them a deep understanding of the strategies and tactics that drive success. By leveraging this wealth of experience, the company can create tailored lead-generation programs that are specifically designed to meet the unique needs and objectives of your business.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Through a comprehensive analysis of your business goals, industry trends, and target audience demographics, the company&rsquo;s team can develop highly targeted campaigns that are optimized for maximum impact. By working closely with your sales and marketing teams, The Lead Gen Specialists ensure that its lead generation efforts are seamlessly integrated with your overall business strategy, resulting in a more cohesive and effective approach to driving growth and success.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With a focus on delivering tangible results, the company&rsquo;s lead generation programs are designed to not only generate high-quality leads, but also to nurture and convert those leads into loyal customers. By continuously monitoring and optimizing the company&rsquo;s campaigns, the company is able to adapt to changing market conditions and ensure that your business remains competitive and successful in the long term.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In essence, the firm&rsquo;s directors\' extensive experience, combined with their team\'s dedication to collaboration and innovation, allows us to deliver lead-generation solutions that are truly tailored to your business\'s unique needs and objectives. By partnering with The Lead Gen Specialists, you can be confident that you are working with a team that is committed to driving your business forward and helping you achieve your goals.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>How The Lead Gen Specialists is Different</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Unlike many lead generation agencies, The Lead Gen Specialists pride themselves on delivering exactly what clients want: a flow of sales-qualified leads with prospects looking to buy their products or services. The company doesn\'t just focus on generating leads; it also focuses on generating high-quality sales leads that your team can convert into new customers.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>B2B Telemarketing</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The Lead Gen Specialists non-scripted B2B telemarketing services provide a reliable and effective mechanism for generating high-quality sales leads that can be converted into new customers quickly. The company&rsquo;s team of dedicated B2B prospecting professionals has the ability to generate sales-qualified opportunities for your business.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Effective &amp; Professional UK B2B Telemarketing</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">When considering deploying B2B telemarketing resources, you\'re looking for a professional agency that can drive business growth and provide quality contact solutions. The Lead Gen Specialists team of experienced telemarketers can engage with prospects in your target market, identify their pain points, and put your solution forward as a viable alternative to their incumbent provider.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>LinkedIn Lead Generation</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Direct access to over 650 million LinkedIn users allows The Lead Gen Specialists to engage decision-makers in a conversation, prompting responses from those interested in buying now. Its LinkedIn automation process enables you to grow your network of decision-makers, build relationships, and generate immediate sales opportunities.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Choosing the Right Telemarketing Agency</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">When outsourcing B2B telemarketing to The Lead Gen Specialists, you can expect:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Instant Sales Leads: </strong>All leads generated are sent to you in real-time, allowing you to jump straight on them.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Detailed Reporting: </strong>The Lead Gen Specialists reports provide insights into all activity, enabling you to discuss with your dedicated Account Manager.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Non-Scripted Telemarketing: </strong>Professional, intelligent, and personal telemarketing that engages Senior Decision Makers.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Sales Qualified Leads: </strong>Sales-qualified leads with Senior Decision Makers looking to buy your products or services.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Jason Greasley, Managing Director</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Jason has over 20 years of experience working within the lead generation industry, both within agencies and directly for employers. As a skilled lead generation expert, Jason works with The Lead Gen Specialists\' clients to continue developing their lead generation and marketing strategies.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Jason\'s experience in working with leaders both within international business and local businesses has allowed The Lead Gen Specialists to work with its clients consistently each month providing them with sales-qualified leads that they are converting into new customers.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;Our non-scripted approach to telemarketing allows you to engage with decision-makers of all levels and generate high-quality sales appointments.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'the-lead-gen-specialists-experts-in-targeted-lead-generation', '2023-02-08', 'us/The-Lead-Gen-Specialists.jpg', 15, 'profile', 'The Lead Gen Specialists: Experts in Targeted Lead Generation', 'The Lead Gen Specialists', 'The Lead Gen Specialists', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://leadgenspecialists.co.uk/', 'https://leadgenspecialists.co.uk/', 'The Lead Gen Specialists', '2020', 'Witham, Essex'),
(24, 2, '<p><strong>AELOGICA: Providing Developer Team Augmentation and Innovative App Development since 2010</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The requirement of crafting a robust software application in today\'s digitally fast-moving environment is no longer associated with the case of need, but rather that of necessity. The world is getting increasingly interconnected, and it feels the absence of some online presence that might give every business, be it small or large, distinction in this competitive environment. This is what AELOGICA bases its business on: An aspiration to help entrepreneurs and progressive companies bring their vision to life.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>About AELOGICA</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">AELOGICA symbolizes honesty, transparency, and quality, and is a tenet toward which a software development company should lean. With over 25 years of combined industry experience, the company&rsquo;s team of experts has gained real insight into what truly makes an application successful. Its founder, Steven Talcott Smith, has been called a software visionary, reflecting in all his entrepreneurship the thrusting spirit through the length and breadth of the company.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>AELOGICA Mission</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">AELOGICA was established in 2010 to provide the best Ruby on Rails application development, maintenance, and support services available to entrepreneurs and businesses of all stature around the world. It brings years of experience in building complex eCommerce systems driving tens of millions of dollars in sales. This proficiency is founded upon rich entrepreneurial and development experience across multifarious industries: Travel, Healthcare, Finance, Real Estate, and e-commerce.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Team Augmentation</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At AELOGICA, the team understands that scaling your operations can be overwhelming. This is why they implement Team Augmentation services to help you scale your operations quickly and without hassle. Their team of professionals around the globe is highly qualified, and responsive, and provides a reliable extension to your resources. From jumpstarting your project to augmenting your inner processes, they are proficient in completing tasks with excellence and efficiency.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>App Development</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">AELOGICA&rsquo;s cutting-edge and in-house systems give you an upper hand in software development. From conceptualization to launch, it shall make it an enjoyable and profitable experience. It believes in delivering value not only to its clients but also to its customers. It understands that successful application development requires an in-depth understanding of the business objectives and users coupled with technical execution.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Managed Dev Ops</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Unfortunately, too many times, software projects fail or are entered into rescue mode. Whether it is the underperformance of your current development team or the trouble with your project, AELOGICA can help. It has experts at taking troubled projects and turning them into winners. Performance problems, security breaches, or delayed timelines&mdash;whatever the issue might be&mdash; AELOGICA can identify its very core and develop a plan to get you back on track.</p>\r\n<p><strong>A Unique Approach</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">What differentiates AELOGICA within the industry is its unique attitude to app development. The proprietary tools and libraries let us reach objectives with greater velocity and excellence. Tens of thousands of hours were put into the development of systems on communication and development so that its clients got outstanding results.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Why choose AELOGICA?</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At AELOGICA, the team is committed to making sure its clientele gets exceptional results by applying its unique approach to application development. The company understands pretty well how honesty and transparency can be very essential in a development process. So, it has made an investment of hundreds of hours in developing systems for communication and development. Its proprietary tools and libraries make it possible to hit objectives harder with more velocity.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>With AELOGICA, you shall get:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">A culture of excellence</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Premium communication and collaboration tools</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Expertise in Ruby on Rails Application Development</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Global Reach with Facilities in Reno, Nevada and Bonifacio Global City, Philippines</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">A Team of Experienced Developers Who are Good at Getting Projects Back on Track</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>AELOGICA Facilities</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With offices and facilities in Reno, Nevada, USA, and Bonifacio Global City, Philippines, AELOGICA delivers a series of services from two locations. AELOGICA&rsquo;s Reno facility serves as its global headquarters and is home to its executive team and key decision-makers. In Bonifacio Global City, it has been at the forefront of managing one of the country\'s premier Ruby on Rails development talent hubs.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Philosophy</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At AELOGICA, the team believes that software development should be an enjoyable experience for everybody within it. They commit to exceptional results by doing some things a little differently. Their philosophy is, that successful application development demands a depth of understanding of business objectives, users, and technical expertise in actually executing them.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>&nbsp;Short bio of Steve Talcott Smith, Founder And CEO</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Steven has earned a reputation as a software visionary with more than 25 years of experience as an entrepreneur, developer, and investor. As a longtime successful business owner, the author of the programmer&rsquo;s guidebook titled&nbsp;LevelUp, and the developer of multiple software applications himself, Steven provides crucial expertise to his clients in all aspects of the software industry.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>&ldquo;We are now positioned to serve clients on the US East Coast with round-the-clock coverage and operations support.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'aelogica-providing-developer-team-augmentation-and-innovative-app-development-since-2010', '2023-02-08', 'us/AELOGICA.jpg', 16, 'profile', 'AELOGICA: Providing Developer Team Augmentation and Innovative App Development since 2010', 'AELOGICA', 'AELOGICA', NULL, 1, 'no', 'http://aelogica.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/aelogica-llc/', 'Sarasota, FL', '2010', 'Sarasota, FL'),
(25, 2, '<p><strong>Alfafam Management Consulting: Provides operations, project management, and system implementation solutions that streamline, automate, and boost your growth</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Alfafam, the team understands what it takes to be a small or medium-sized business because they&rsquo;ve been there. That is the reason why at Alfafam, the team is dedicated to providing operation, project management, and system implementation solutions that help streamline, automate, and boost your growth. Experience the power of efficiency.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Why Choose Alfafam Management Consulting?</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Personalized solutions, just for you&mdash;every business is different. That\'s why Alfafam&rsquo;s solutions are designed to meet your unique challenges and goals. Enjoy bespoke tools that fit just right.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Cut costs, not corners: Reduce operational expenses with technology that optimizes every aspect of your business. More savings, no compromises.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Scale with confidence: Ready to grow? Alfafam&rsquo;s scalable solutions adapt to your pace. Expand your capabilities without the growing pains.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Alfafam&rsquo;s strategy is to provide small and medium-sized businesses with tailored solutions in the areas of business process management, system implementations, operations- and marketing management, strategic consulting, and project management. They tailor services to make your operations run smoother, grow business performance, and drive business growth guided by deep knowledge and passion for helping you succeed.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The company&rsquo;s substantial 4-step approach&mdash;deep analysis, customized recommendations, smooth implementation, and proactive maintenance&mdash;is incredibly powerful. Being an integral part of your team, Alfafam&rsquo;s seasoned team gets deep down into the business operations&mdash;identifying the opportunities and invisible impediments&mdash;by providing actionable strategies for process optimization, cost reduction, and revenue growth.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With Alfafam&rsquo;s experience of decade-long business experience, the company will put all its passion into helping businesses like yours. Against this backdrop, the company&rsquo;s management consulting services are tailored toward building your team with the right tools necessary to grow.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Alfafam Management Consulting, the professionals bring paramount experience from various industries with them so that every challenge can be faced with experience learned and leading-edge solutions. Such diversity enables them to recommend insights and strategies tailored specifically to every single requirement of your business setup.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Grow Your Business with Alfafam Management Consulting Management</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Benefits of a Fractional COO:</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Identify real gaps in your organization, rapidly move through key pain points, and sharpen your process for future full-time talent with the support of a Fractional Chief of Operations.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Alfafam helped all kinds of key operations that deal with supply chain management, human resources, marketing, customer service, and strategic planning. It will optimize its processes and create policies and procedures for you to ensure efficiency.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Strategy- Whether you are thinking massive business growth, market dominance, and scaling that\'s streamlined or you\'re determined to turn around declining revenue and earnings, its Fractional COOs customize strategic expertise to your goals. A fractional Chief Operations Officer actively participates in developing and implementing some of the important initiatives of a strategy, keeping the long-term vision of the company in focus with actionable plans that drive growth and success.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Expertise- Every business deserves the best management services. Alfafam&rsquo;s Fractional COOs are ultra-agile change agents who possess the expertise and know-how to drive significant transformations or reimagine stuck processes. The company does its best to realize the goals of its clients by coming up with tailored solutions that address their unique needs.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Leadership- Will work very closely with your board of directors and other C-suite leaders in implementing this roadmap, focusing on sustainable growth and execution to achieve maximum potential from your business. Fractional COO will be responsible for managing the cross-functional collaboration relating to effective communication across departments and teams to gain effective productivity, innovation, and alignment with the company goals and ideology.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Alfafam Provides Marketing Support</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">No more hassle managing hundreds of marketing tools and contractors. Alfafam combines everything into one powerful solution for small businesses. Get an optimal return on investment without extending your budget. Let the company&rsquo;s team of local and global experts become part of yours, committed to planning and delivering campaigns that truly drive success.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Marketing-Centered Approach</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Strategic Guidance- The company will provide professional guidance backed with instructions, focusing strictly on your needs. Its team works with you regarding your goals, your targeted audience, and competitors in customizing a marketing strategy to suit your needs in relation to the set objectives.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Cost-Effective Solutions- You can engage a full-time marketing professional for an expensive price. By using Alfafam&rsquo;s flexible approach, you may use all of its expertise without the large expense of employing full-time representatives, so you are guaranteed top support within your budget.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Collaborative Partnership- Alfafam doesn&rsquo;t just work for you; it works with you. Its collaborative approach indicates that there will be regular communication and updates, always keeping you up-to-date with how a campaign is faring and soliciting your input to make sure everything stays on course with your vision.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Tech Solutions- The company will enable your business to run using new technologies at breakneck speed, making your marketing supreme. From automation in marketing to efficient data analysis tools, ensure seamless integration that will optimize campaigns and drive data-backed decision-making across processes.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Social Media Management- Alfafam&rsquo;s agile team masterfully manages all aspects of your social media&mdash;from developing and scheduling your content to engaging with your audience and managing diligent reports. With a pulse on, at all times, the changing social trends, Alfafam amplifies your Brand visibility, connects with your audience at a deeper level, and builds a thriving online community that shelters unwavering brand loyalty and drives exponential business growth.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Better Branding- The company&rsquo;s marketing support also extends to the reinvigoration and amplification of your brand identity. It carefully reviews your current branding, positioning, and messaging before developing a consistent approach toward maximizing the impact of your brand. This translates into a prominent and memorable brand image that truly resonates with your audience of interest and develops long-standing relationships with them to further fuel business reputation.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Alisa Mammadova, CEO and Managing Consultant</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Over the past decade, Alisa has gained extensive expertise in various industries including beauty, retail, marketing, e-commerce, and IT. She has had the opportunity to work with Fortune 1000 companies and has also developed operational strategies for startups, small and mid-sized businesses in the technology and marketing sectors. These strategies have proven to be effective in optimizing operations and driving growth for these businesses. Through Alfafam, Alisa has collaborated with a diverse range of industries including marketing agencies, higher education supporters, non-profit organizations, law firms, logistics companies, export-import businesses, IT sector firms, and healthcare providers.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;Our experienced team delves into your business operations to pinpoint opportunities and hidden obstacles while offering actionable strategies for process optimization, cost reduction, and revenue growth.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'alfafam-management-consulting-provides-operations-project-management-and-system-implementation', '2023-02-08', 'us/Alfafam-Management-Consulting.jpg', 18, 'profile', 'Alfafam Management Consulting: Provides operations, project management, and system implementation solutions that streamline, automate, and boost your growth', 'Alfafam-Management-Consulting', 'Alfafam-Management-Consulting', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://alfafam.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/alfafammanagementconsulting/', 'Alfafam Management Consulting', '2021', 'Miami, Florida'),
(26, 2, '<p><strong>Alkira, Inc.: Network Infrastructure On-Demand for the Era of Cloud and AI</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">Amir and Atif Khan\'s vision for Alkira was to revolutionize the way businesses approach networking, making it simpler, more flexible, and more efficient. With their extensive experience in the networking industry, they understood the pain points that organizations faced when it came to managing complex networks and integrating multiple cloud environments.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">By launching Alkira, they provided a comprehensive solution that allows businesses to easily connect their on-premises data centers, branch offices, and cloud resources through a single, centralized platform. This not only simplifies network management but also improves performance and security, ensuring that data is transmitted safely and efficiently across the network.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The Alkira platform offers a range of advanced features, including real-time monitoring, automated provisioning, and customizable policies, giving businesses the flexibility to tailor their network infrastructure to meet their specific needs. By delivering these services as a subscription-based model, Alkira enables organizations to scale their network resources up or down as needed, without the need for costly hardware investments or complex configurations.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Overall, Alkira\'s innovative approach to networking has set a new standard for the industry, empowering businesses to embrace digital transformation and drive innovation with confidence. Through their dedication to customer success and commitment to excellence, Amir and Atif Khan have solidified Alkira\'s position as a leader in the networking space, paving the way for a more connected and secure future.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>A New Era of Networking</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Alkira\'s vision is nothing short of reinventing networking for the cloud era. They aim to create a multi-cloud capable network that behaves like the cloud and is consumed as-a-service like the cloud. A network that can take you to and across clouds in minutes instead of months. A network where services, like firewalls, live and scale in the cloud. A network you draw instead of build. A network with end-to-end visibility and governance. And most importantly, a network delivered as a service.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>The Power of Alkira Network as a Service</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Alkira Network as a Service is the fastest way to unify clouds, sites, and users. With its cloud-native architecture and innovative GUI-driven design, IT leaders can easily design and deploy cloud networking resources in minutes, without the need for hardware or software installations. This means that organizations can accelerate their digital transformation journey without the burden of CAPEX costs or time-consuming learning curves.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Seamless Multi-Cloud Networking: Alkira supports major cloud providers like AWS, Azure, Google Cloud Platform, Oracle Cloud, and more.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">End-to-End Security in a Flash: Gain unmatched visibility into your entire cloud network with real-time threat detection and response.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Completely Agentless: No agents to deploy or virtual overhead to manage.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">100% Delivered as a Service: No hardware to buy, no software to license, no cloud to learn &ndash; simply pay for what you use.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Transforming Networking for the Cloud Era</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Alkira\'s innovative approach to networking has transformed the way organizations connect and secure their cloud environments. With Alkira Network as a Service, IT leaders can:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Speed time to value by deploying new Azure services in minutes</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Successfully manage Azure connectivity with seamless integration</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Increase agility by pairing Azure workloads and infrastructure investments with a modernized cloud networking platform</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Simplify cloud networking with a unified platform</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Securely connect anything to Azure with end-to-end security</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Accelerate Azure deployments with networking ready in minutes</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Amir Khan, President, CEO &amp; Founder</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Amir Khan is a computer networking visionary who founded and led Viptela&rsquo;s market-leading, cloud-first, Software-Defined Wide Area Networking (SD-WAN) business before its acquisition by Cisco. As prescient as he was in identifying the $8B opportunity for SD-WAN, Amir recognized that the network hampered the cloud journey. Amir and CTO Atif Khan founded Alkira in 2018 to reinvent networking for the cloud era. Before Viptela, Amir held leadership roles at Cisco, Juniper, and Nortel. He holds 4 patents. Amir earned an MS in Electrical Engineering from the University of Colorado at Boulder, and a BS in Electrical Engineering from the University of Mississippi.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;Our vision is nothing short of the complete reinvention of networking. A vision of a multi-cloud capable network that behaves like the cloud and is consumed as-a-service like the cloud.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'alkira-inc--network-infrastructure-on-demand-for-the-era-of-cloud-and-ai', '2023-02-08', 'us/Alkira-Inc.jpg', 19, 'profile', 'Alkira, Inc.: Network Infrastructure On-Demand for the Era of Cloud and AI', 'Alkira-Inc', 'Alkira-Inc', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.alkira.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/alkiranet/', 'Alkira, Inc. ', '2018', 'San Jose, California'),
(27, 3, '<p><strong>Replicated: The best way to distribute your software to customers of every size in the most complex environments, including air-gap</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In today\'s digital age, software vendors are constantly looking for ways to improve the delivery and management of their applications to enterprise customers. Founded in 2015 by Grant and Marc, Replicated has emerged as a modern solution for delivering and managing multi-prem software. The company\'s container-based platform enables software vendors to quickly deploy cloud-native applications inside customers\' environments, providing greater security and control.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At the heart of Replicated\'s platform is the ability to distribute software to enterprise customers of all sizes, regardless of the complexity of their environments. This is achieved through a unified platform that brings together everything needed to efficiently manage, test, install, support, and measure the distribution of an application.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The Replicated Platform is designed with a comprehensive suite of features that significantly streamline the management of software applications and enhance the overall experience for software vendors. One of the standout components of this platform is the Vendor Portal, which serves as a centralized hub for vendors to efficiently oversee their applications, manage releases, and monitor customer licenses.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">This portal not only simplifies administrative tasks but also empowers vendors with valuable insights into their applications\' performance. Through the Vendor Portal, vendors can access critical data regarding uptime and usage metrics, enabling them to make informed decisions and optimize their offerings. Additionally, the platform provides tailored support packages for each customer setup, ensuring that vendors can deliver personalized assistance and maintain strong relationships with their clients.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Another key feature of the Replicated Platform is the Compatibility Matrix, which plays a crucial role in the software development lifecycle. This tool is particularly beneficial for software vendors as it allows them to rigorously test their applications in environments that closely replicate their customers\' setups. By integrating the Compatibility Matrix into their continuous integration (CI) processes, vendors can identify potential compatibility issues early on, thereby reducing the risk of deployment failures and enhancing the overall reliability of their applications.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The matrix offers a ready-made infrastructure that supports testing across a variety of Kubernetes distributions, versions, and configurations. This flexibility ensures that vendors can validate their applications against a wide range of environments, ultimately leading to a more robust and versatile product.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The process of using the Compatibility Matrix is straightforward. Software vendors can define their testing strategy by integrating Replicated\'s actions or CLI into their CI process. They can then choose combinations of distros, versions, and configurations, and set up their own smoke tests, policy tests, release tests, and canary tests on the provisioned infrastructure.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><img style=\"float: right;\" src=\"http://www.visionariesnetwork.com/story_image_upload/us/Replicated-grant-miller-founder-ceo-cover.jpg\" width=\"154\" height=\"211\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In addition to its testing capabilities, the Replicated Platform also provides a Kubernetes Installer that enables software vendors to embed Kubernetes with their application. This allows customers to install the application with a simple click-and-go operation, even in environments with VMs and bare metal hardware.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The Replicated SDK provides a way for software vendors to integrate their application with the Replicated Platform. This enables them to provide license enforcement, reporting, and update information to customers. The Customer Portal provides each customer with access-controlled instructions on how to install the latest version of the application.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Replicated\'s platform also offers a range of tools for troubleshooting issues within existing customer environments. The Compatibility Matrix can test across 65,981+ unique configuration combinations, giving software vendors complete confidence that their applications will run without issues in customers\' unique environments.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In addition to its core features, Replicated\'s platform also offers integration with Helm, a popular package manager for Kubernetes. The company\'s Enhanced Helm solution provides a unified platform that brings together everything needed to complement Helm installs, manage app lifecycles, and embed Replicated\'s advanced capabilities in an application.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The Enhanced Helm solution provides a range of benefits for software vendors, including improved install success rates, accelerated support issue resolution, and greater insights into customer usage. It also enables software vendors to embed Replicated transparently in their applications, providing a fully transparent and white-labeled application lifecycle experience for customers.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Grant Miller, Founder &amp; CEO</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We power your install options that will meet your customers&rsquo; requirements and Kubernetes comfort level (or lack thereof).&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'replicated-the-best-way-to-distribute-your-software-to-customers', '2022-05-05', 'us/visionaries-network-grant--miler-founder-ceo-replicated.webp', 1001, 'cover', 'Distribute Software Easily with Replicated', 'Replicated, software distribution, air-gap, Kubernetes, enterprise, SaaS, deployment, on-prem, DevOps, CI/CD, Docker, security, scalability, visionaries network, automation', 'Replicated simplifies software delivery to all customers, even in complex, air-gapped environments. Fast, secure, and scalable deployments.', NULL, 1, 'no', ' www.replicated.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/grantlmiller', 'Replicated', '2014', 'West Hollywood, California, USA'),
(28, 3, '<p><strong>NOBL serves ambitious leaders focused on immediate action, measurable outcomes, and internal capability-building</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Leadership looking at change and growth in the nowadays fast-paced and fast-changing business world is trying to find new ideas for the same. NOBL is a real-delivery partner of an industry where most have nothing but promises to make. NOBL has a team consisting of organizational designers, industrial psychologists, change practitioners, and category experts who help ambitious leaders achieve their goals through NOBL\'s creative approach to making change.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>A Proven Track Record</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">NOBL has been the preference for some of the most admired companies worldwide, such as Google DeepMind, Calvin Klein, Taco Bell, and Reddit. They have directly experienced how NOBL\'s approach enables them to solve intricate problems and produce measurable results.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>NOBL Method</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The NOBL approach is built on six main pillars:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Stop the Swirl: </strong>NOBL activates leaders to break strategy out from PowerPoint and into action by launching immediate pilots and programs. It ensures clarity and focus on what\'s measurable, and observable in behavior, and key initiatives.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Get Teams Moving Together: </strong>NOBL enables teams to develop consistent rhythms organization-wide. It allows teams to plan work together, coordinate efforts, share results, and harvest lessons learned.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Eliminate Artificial Barriers:</strong> NOBL uncovers structural and systems barriers within an organization and structures new solutions in place of the old ones.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Pull Conversations that are Needed out into the Open:</strong> NOBL brings executives face-to-face together to balance tough trade-offs and choices.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Establish Accountability: </strong>NOBL enables leaders to hold themselves and their peers accountable for the desired outcomes and commitments.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Grow with Feedback:</strong> NOBL moves strategies and plans to be revised based on real evidence and feedback from markets.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Bridging the Digital Divide</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">It is easy to get lost in the excitement about new technologies in the digital age. NOBL, however, understands that, in reality, there is a divide between what technology promises and reality as seen by organizations. NOBL bridges that gap by:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Outcome-based management: Engaging stakeholders around business, employee, and customer needs that technology can serve.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">First Roadmap: Plotting an ambitious yet realistic journey to experiment with new technologies and modes of work.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Teams Moving Together: An activity to develop regular rhythms of programs to develop alignment in activities throughout the organization.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Reduce Resistance: Getting people engaged and communicating on changes helps reduce the resistance to change.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Adapt: Change strategies or roadmaps based on real evidence, markets, or market feedback.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Overcoming Inertia</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Innovation always competes for all forms of resources and, therefore usually experiences a natural form of resistance in the guts of most organizations through these traditional means. NOBL:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Define the Playing Field: Define both the space for innovation (time horizons, markets, segments) as well as proactively remove the internal political boundaries.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Build Supporting Structures and Systems: Working with the teams to define the roles and processes needed in order to grow new ideas and new ways of working.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Coaching Early Attempts at Scaling: laying down an initial plan for scale and coaching alongside projects as they mature.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Engage Resistance Head-On: Train leadership on how to overcome internal opposition and build broader coalitions of support through political influence.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Bud Caddell, Founder &amp; CEO of NOBL</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">My clients have included: Warner Bros., Chipotle, Pepsi, CNN, Volkswagen, Bank of America, HBO, Nasty Gal, Calvin Klein, Levi Strauss, esurance, The College Board, Bloomin\' Brands, Ford Motor Company, GE, Nike, Taco Bell, Reddit and many others.<br><br>I\'m the founder of NOBL, a global transformation and change partner that helps leaders make real change. I grew up obsessed with technology, even serving as the Head of Technology at a venture-funded startup while attending high school. After years of helping the Fortune 500 develop innovative new products and services, I came to a realization: organizations don\'t suffer from a lack of ideas, they suffer from ways of working that kill innovative ideas. I started NOBL to help organizations respond to a world of increasing change by fusing the fields of organizational development, change management, agile methodologies, and complexity science.<br><br>Prior to NOBL Collective, I was a Partner at the management and strategic consultancy, Undercurrent. I also served as SVP of Digital Strategy and Innovation at Deutsch LA. My work has been featured in The New York Times, The Wall Street Journal, Forbes, and AdAge. I have been named &ldquo;one of the most creative people under 30&rdquo; by Business Insider and The Guardian named me as one of ten strategists to watch.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;With our Change Approaching, complex change initiatives become achievable, &ldquo;safe to try&rdquo; experiments in different ways of working.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'nobl-serves-ambitious-leaders-focused-on-immediate-action-measurable-outcomes-and-internal-capability-building', '2022-05-05', 'us/visionaries-network-bud-caddell-ceo-nobl.webp', 1, 'profile', 'NOBL Empowers Leaders for Action and Lasting Impact', 'NOBL, leadership, transformation, measurable outcomes, organizational change, capability-building, business strategy, leadership growth, team alignment, change management, agile teams, leadership coaching, visionaries network, executive support, leadership consulting', 'NOBL helps ambitious leaders take immediate action, achieve measurable results, and build lasting internal capabilities for sustainable success.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://nobl.io/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/nobl-collective/', 'NOBL', '2014', 'Los Angeles, California');
