(29, 3, '<p><strong>SingleStone: Transforming Financial Services, Insurance &amp; Government with Data Innovation, Analytics, AI, &amp; Modern Technology</strong></p>', '<p dir=\"ltr\">Founded over two decades ago, SingleStone has played an instrumental role in helping organizations untangle messy data and master emerging technologies. The company has always strived to provide ways to help organizations navigate the complex world of data-driven growth through modern transformations. Today, it continues to evolve and provides its clients with the tools and strategies needed to succeed and flourish in a fast-paced digital landscape.<br><br><strong>The Commitment of SingleStone to its Customers</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">There is a firm belief that SingleStone has at the company to blend technology with humanity, called \"Elevate Humanity,\" which underscores everything that SingleStone does. The solutions produced by this company empower the teams of their clients and delight customers-it is proof that innovation and empathy go together.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">SingleStone believes in the integrity of action towards desired outcomes and does not compromise on the same for quick solutions. SingleStone refuses to sacrifice the same with haste for readily available answers. Thus, honest analysis and bespoke solutions come from SingleStone. Examples of speed without compromise illustrate that SingleStone can deliver and hit deadlines consistently without having to settle on either factor.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Data, Analytics &amp; AI Services</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Turning data into actionable insights is a part of growth and innovation in the fast business environment today. Organizations are now aware that the tremendous volume of data they collect holds unrealized potential to help drive strategic decision-making and improve customer experiences. SingleStone is answering this significant challenge of the unused potential of data by providing a complete suite of advanced data, analytics, and AI solutions.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">These enabling tools empower client teams to design strategies and implement new experiences that are not only in step with the business objectives of their customers but also attuned to the shifting needs of customers. Modernizing the data infrastructure is one of the core services offered by SingleStone, very crucial for clients who are looking for upgradation in their operational processes.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">SingleStone will enable organizations to drive critical, real-time informed decision-making capabilities and improve performance through better data management systems and streamlined workflows. Modernization is targeted at removing inefficiency, reducing cost, and as a short-cut approach to better business outcomes.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In addition to infrastructure modernization, SingleStone offers personalized AI and machine learning discovery and experimentation services. Such services fine-tune the possibilities so that clients may tap into the potential of AI and ML properly, thus increasing efficiency in operations and deriving valuable insights from their data. A firm with knowledge in the implementation of AI can guide SingleStone\'s clients through the intricacies involved in successfully harnessing these technologies as a means of gaining an advantageous position over their competitors in their markets.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Moreover, SingleStone provides AI-driven data harmonization, which transforms clients\' data catalogs into centralized resources. This processing will make data integrations easier for analysts as the details appear to be the same and correct from all sources. Thus, with this harmonized data environment, an organization can make reliable reports and analytics that help in making strategic decisions and hence enhance overall business performance. Data Management &amp; Process&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Optimization Services</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">SingleStone helps clients build scalable solutions for improved data accuracy, transparency, and interoperability. The company\'s data management and process optimization services use human-centered automation to improve data quality at the point of collection, thus the business value of data is treated as a product.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Architecture Modernization Services</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Stunning statistics show that large IT initiatives, such as architecture modernization, are likely to fail and experience high-cost overruns. In contrast, SingleStone uses a domain-first approach in changing the architecture of clients so that it can be a strategic asset that will shield itself from costly pitfalls leading to sustained success in the long term.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Why Modernize Architecture?</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">It facilitates fast flow, accessible data, and productive teams. It also gives a competitive edge, supports innovation and adaptability for changing environments, is efficient, enhances resiliency, improves performance, and makes the teams happier.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Architecture Modernization Services Offered</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With this, SingleStone has domain-driven discovery services that allow clients to get started on a modernization journey in just 8-12 weeks. Another related service offered by the firm is domain-driven cloud services that help align the architecture of a client with AWS or Azure to the right business model. Finally, SingleStone provides continuous modernization support services so that the architecture of any client evolves to meet their needs over time.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At SingleStone, the company believes that businesses need to be supported in becoming triumphant in this rapidly changing, fast-paced world of digital change. Having expert knowledge in data-driven growth, modern tech transformation, and architecture modernization at the table, SingleStone is confident that its solutions are what help clients find their way toward even more excellent business outcomes.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Jimmy Chou, Chief Executive Officer</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Jimmy has over 20+ years of experience across multiple industries, with a particular focus on financial services and insurance. As CEO, Jimmy has been instrumental in leading the firm through transformational change since he stepped into the role in 2017.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We empower clients to bring out the best in people by delivering solutions that harness the power of data, technology, and humanity.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'singlestone-transforming-financial-services-insurance-government-with-data-innovation-analytics-ai-modern-technology', '2022-05-05', 'us/visionaries-network-jummy-chou-ceo-singlestone.webp', 2, 'profile', 'SingleStone Drives Innovation with Data, AI & Analytics', 'SingleStone, data innovation, analytics, AI, financial services, insurance, government, digital transformation, technology, modernization, IT consulting, cloud solutions, enterprise AI, visionaries network, data strategy', 'SingleStone transforms financial services, insurance, and government sectors through data innovation, advanced analytics, AI, and modern technology solutions.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.singlestoneconsulting.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/singlestone/', 'SingleStone', '1997', 'Richmond, Virginia'),
(30, 3, '<p><strong>Summit Wealth Group: Independent wealth management firm that helps clients reach their financial and personal goals</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">In 1985, Randy Morris, CEO, founded Executive Financial Planning, Inc. (EFP) with a vision to provide independent, customized financial planning advice to clients. Over the next 17 years, EFP grew to become one of the largest independent financial advisory firms in the nation. In 2002, the company expanded its vision by creating Summit Wealth Group, which is now headquartered in Colorado Springs, Colorado, with locations in five states and ten branch offices.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>A Purpose-Driven Approach</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Summit Wealth Group, the purpose is simple: to help clients navigate the path to a better, more secure future. The company\'s philosophy is built around the idea that a carefully constructed and accountability-based plan can help clients achieve their dreams. This approach enables individuals to devote their time and energy to pursuing their passions, rather than worrying about their financial security.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Core Values</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The company\'s core values are centered around exceptional client experience, teamwork and growth, ownership and accountability, and intentional relationships. These values are reflected in every aspect of the company\'s operations, from the planning process to client relationships.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Why Summit Wealth Group</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Summit Wealth Group is not just a financial services firm; it is a calling for its staff. Each member of the team is driven by a deep conviction that they are not just providing financial advice, but guiding people towards reaching their desired life. This commitment to excellence is reflected in every interaction with clients, from the initial consultation to ongoing planning and management.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Client Relationships</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Summit Wealth Group, long-term client relationships are built on trust, empathy, and integrity. The company\'s staff often develop close personal friendships with clients, frequently golfing together or serving on the same boards. Regular client events are also hosted throughout the year to foster a sense of community and connection.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Comprehensive Financial Planning</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The company\'s focus is on helping clients define what fulfillment looks like to them and providing the tools to achieve it. Comprehensive financial planning is at the heart of this approach, serving as a foundation for an individual\'s life journey. This planning process involves identifying what\'s important to the client, planning for potential headwinds, and creating a roadmap for achieving their goals.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Why Comprehensive Financial Planning Matters</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Having a comprehensive financial plan can create intentionality in one\'s life, overcome obstacles and address concerns, identify potential threats to financial goals, and empower individuals to make informed decisions. By working with a certified financial planner (CFP), clients can feel confident that they are on the right track towards achieving their financial goals.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Randy Morris, Chief Executive Officer</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Randy Morris&rsquo; early career helped prepare him as a financial planning pioneer. After graduating from the University of Colorado in 1982 with a degree in business and organizational management, he worked for two years as Vice President of Executive Economic Services, Inc., in Denver, Colorado.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In 1985, Randy founded Executive Financial Planning, Inc. (EFP), one of Mississippi\'s first financial planning firms. During his tenure as founder and CEO, EFP became one of the nation\'s largest financial planning firms.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In 2002, he created Summit Wealth Group (SWG) out of a desire to provide additional wealth management services for clients. Randy serves as the firm\'s CEO. SWG currently works with clients in 46 states with client assets under advisement of $2.007 billion as of April 2024.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Peers in the financial industry have recognized Randy&rsquo;s skills and accomplishments by electing him as a past President of the Mississippi Chapter of the Financial Planning Association (FPA). Randy is a Chartered Financial Consultant (ChFC-1985), and a CERTIFIED FINANCIAL PLANNER&trade; Practitioner (1987). He is also a Registered Representative, an Investment Adviser Representative, and a Registered Securities Principal with Commonwealth Financial Network&reg;&nbsp;(a registered broker/dealer, member FINRA/SIPC). Additionally, he has assisted the CFP&reg;&nbsp;Board of Examiners as an exam reviewer.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Randy has served on numerous boards, including Barge Timberlands International, Camp Lake Forest Ranch, Southeast Regional Committee for Young Life, Military Community Youth Ministries (MCYM), and the World Vision Leadership Council. Randy lives with his wife, Nancy, in Scottsdale, Arizona, where they attend Scottsdale Bible Church. They have six children: Joy, Jesse, Hannah, Scott, Randy, and Ryan, as well as 12 grandchildren.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Randy&rsquo;s accolades include being recognized by Forbes Magazine in each of the past 7 years, making its&nbsp;\"Best-In-State Wealth Advisors\"&nbsp;list for the state of Arizona. Randy has also been recognized as a Chairman&rsquo;s Level advisor through Commonwealth every year since 2007. This is a distinction based on annual production attained by just 3 percent of advisors affiliated with Commonwealth Financial Network.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We help our clients navigate through the critical financial decisions they might face throughout life with confidence.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'summit-wealth-group-independent-wealth-management-firm-that-helps-clients-reach-their-financial-and-personal-goals', '2022-05-05', 'us/visionaries-network-summit-wealth-managemnet-randy-morris-ceo.webp', 3, 'profile', 'Summit Wealth Group: Independent Financial Planning Experts', 'Summit Wealth Group, wealth management, financial planning, retirement planning, investment advice, independent advisors, personal goals, financial goals, fiduciary, estate planning, portfolio management, money management, financial security, asset management, visionaries network', 'Summit Wealth Group is an independent wealth management firm helping clients achieve financial security and personal goals through tailored financial planning and advice.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.summitwealthgroup.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/summitwealthgroup/', 'Summit Wealth Group', '2002', 'Colorado Springs, Colorado'),
(31, 3, '<p><strong>Peaks Digital Marketing is a full-service SEO &amp; Digital Marketing Firm</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Peaks Digital Marketing is a full-service SEO and digital marketing firm located in Denver, Colorado, and it helps businesses and organizations expand their online presence and achieve their goals. The company&rsquo;s team of experts delivers an unparalleled level of value and expertise to help your brand reach its digital summit.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Primary mission</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Peaks Digital Marketing helps push your brand to the Digital Summit with innovative, lead-generating strategies that are focused on ROI and Data-Driven Expectations Here, the company marries cutting-edge SEO, SEM, and omnichannel marketing campaigns that increase call volume, sales, impressions, and appointments.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>What Makes Peaks Digital Marketing Awesome</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Peaks Digital Marketing prides itself on dedicated support, deep knowledge of best practices in SEO, custom lead generation with easy onboarding, and a focus on building inherent value back into your business. Its team is laser-focused on providing exceptional personal experiences for its valued clients.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Dedicated Support</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Peaks Digital Marketing will ensure the right support team working for you. This is why it offers 7:30 AM - 6:30 PM, 5-day-a-week support so that your questions are addressed promptly and efficiently. The organization&rsquo;s mission is to provide an experience that exceeds your expectations.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Extensive SEO Best Practices Knowledge</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Peaks Digital Marketing has expert knowledge of Google algorithms, technical SEO strategies, content marketing, and more. And it applies that expertise to give you timely targeted advice to safeguard your website for the future and to start building momentum in your marketplace.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Custom Lead Generation</strong><br>No two niches or markets are alike and that is why Peaks Digital Marketing develops specifically customized strategies for the needs that your organization. The company will easily fit into your team and offer targeted, itemized strategies toward success.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Building Inherent Value</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Peaks Digital Marketing&rsquo;s objective is to maximize your value and profit by creating marketing campaigns based on hard data points and proven metrics. They build lists and apply strategies to drive future organic growth, with tangible returns on investment.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Core Values</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Peaks Digital Marketing works to enable you to have the presence your organization deserves online. It partners with companies like yours to become a member of your team. Together, it will watch your business take off to new heights with proven data-driven analytics, seasoned digital marketing strategies, and an advanced knowledge of SEO best practices.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>AdWords &amp; PPC Services</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">If you want results right away, then Google AdWords (Pay Per Click) is the way. Peaks Digital Marketing&rsquo;s trained, professional staff in AdWords can ensure you start getting new business right now, catapulting your message to the top. We offer competitor and market analysis, keyword research, ad copywriting and multivariate testing, and reporting and lead tracking.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>SEO Content Marketing Services</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Proper SEO goes with quality content. Peaks Digital Marketing&rsquo;s in-house writers can assist your business in creating optimized content that resonates with your target ideal, which would rank higher on the Google results page for top search terms. It can assist you in digitizing your in-person sales and discovery process as well as making it generate much more traffic and improving conversions.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Content Marketing</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Peaks Digital Marketing is aware of the significance of quality content in driving SEO success. All its content is branded as well as SEO/SEM-optimized to make sure it attracts more views and gets people engaged. So, its services ensure retaining reputation, relating to customers, and increasing ROI.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">You will be secure in knowing your brand is in great hands as you work with Peaks Digital Marketing. Peaks Digital Marketing&rsquo;s team of experts works day and night to help you reach digital summits and fulfill all your online success goals.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>David A. Finberg, CEO &amp; Owner</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">David Finberg is the Founder and Managing Member of Peaks Digital Marketing and has SEO &amp; SEM successes on both local and nationwide scales. After pursuing a degree in Applied Information Technology at George Mason University, and working at several startups, Mr. Finberg decided to venture fully into the digital marketing industry.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">David has generated tens of millions of dollars in revenue for clients, ranked thousands of first page search terms on Google, and grown numerous corporations and businesses through effective SEO + SEM-based digital marketing campaigns.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;Our team of SEO experts come from diverse backgrounds with seasoned knowledge of best practices for medical, financial, and other business services.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'peaks-digital-marketing-is-a-full-service-seodigital-marketing-firm', '2022-05-05', 'us/visionaries-network-david-a-finberg.webp', 4, 'profile', 'Peaks Digital Marketing is a full-service SEOÂ &Â Digital Marketing Firm', 'Peaks Digital Marketing', 'Peaks Digital Marketing', NULL, 1, 'no', '', '', '', '', ''),
(32, 3, '<p><strong>Waters Business Consulting Group, LLC helps business owners--large and small--improve their cash flow, reduce their costs, and work more efficiently</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Waters Business Consulting Group is dedicated to helping entrepreneurs like you achieve their goals and fulfill their life\'s purpose. Whether you\'re looking to retire on a beach, spend more time with family, pursue a hobby, or make a positive impact through mentoring or charity, the team of seasoned consultants at Waters Business Consulting Group is here to guide you every step of the way.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With years of experience in helping businesses grow and thrive, Waters Business Consulting Group\'s team of consultants combines expertise with proven models to transform businesses and lives. They take a hands-on approach, working closely with clients to understand their goals and develop tailored strategies to help them achieve success. Unlike many competitors, Waters Business Consulting Group doesn\'t just offer high-level advice &ndash; they roll up their sleeves to help clients complete action items and implement strategies designed to grow their business.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Waters Business Consulting Group, experience is one of the most valuable assets a business can have. That\'s why the team has years of experience in helping businesses overcome obstacles and achieve their goals. Whether you\'re struggling to increase sales, improve profitability, or expand your operations, Waters Business Consulting Group has the skills and expertise to help you achieve your goals.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Waters Business Consulting Group offers a range of comprehensive business consulting services designed to help businesses thrive, whether you\'re starting out, struggling to survive, or growing rapidly. The Growth Accelerator Program is designed to help businesses accelerate their growth by developing a strategic plan, implementing marketing strategies, and streamlining operations. The Growth Management and Exit Program is ideal for businesses looking to manage their growth and increase their asset value in preparation for an eventual exit. And the Tiered Performance Program is designed for emerging entrepreneurs and small businesses with limited resources and capital, offering a tiered fee structure tied to actual performance improvement in the business.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With a proven track record of helping businesses achieve success, Waters Business Consulting Group is confident in its ability to help entrepreneurs like you achieve your goals and fulfill your personal aspirations. The team is dedicated to helping entrepreneurs like you succeed and achieve their dreams.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Waters Business Consulting Group believes that every business owner deserves to achieve their goals and fulfill their personal aspirations. Whether you\'re looking to increase your income, reduce your workload, or pursue a passion outside of work, Waters Business Consulting Group is here to help you achieve your goals. The team is committed to helping entrepreneurs like you succeed and achieve their dreams.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">For entrepreneurs like you who are looking for a trusted partner to help them achieve their business goals and fulfill their personal aspirations, Waters Business Consulting Group is the perfect choice. With its team of experienced consultants and comprehensive business consulting services, Waters Business Consulting Group is dedicated to helping entrepreneurs like you succeed and achieve their dreams.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">If you\'re looking for a trusted partner to help you achieve your business goals and fulfill your personal aspirations, contact Waters Business Consulting Group today. Learn more about its comprehensive business consulting services and how it can help you unlock your business growth and fulfill your personal aspirations.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Waters Business Consulting Group, the team is passionate about helping entrepreneurs like you achieve their goals and fulfill their life\'s purpose. With years of experience in helping businesses grow and thrive, the team is dedicated to helping entrepreneurs like you succeed and achieve their dreams. Contact Waters Business Consulting Group today to learn more about its comprehensive business consulting services and how it can help you unlock your business growth and fulfill your personal aspirations.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>John Waters, Founder of Waters Business Consulting Group</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">John Waters brings trusted experience, proven strategies, and notable results to his clients. As a young entrepreneur, John started his first business venture, a lemonade stand, at the age of 10. After 30 years of experience and developing various programs, he realized that his expertise would greatly benefit other business owners in achieving their goals and dreams.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">During his tenure as CEO of Creative Environments Design &amp; Landscape Inc., John\'s team successfully increased annual revenue from $7.5 million to $42 million in just seven years.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">John\'s success was marked by overcoming challenges in nine different business partnerships across various industries, including commercial janitorial, residential real estate, technology and stocks &amp; commodities investment brokerage, and landscape design and construction.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Later, John stepped down as CEO to pursue his passion for helping entrepreneurs improve their business and life as a business owner.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Today, Waters Business Consulting Group has helped hundreds of business owners achieve significant success in business, utilizing John\'s experience and proven programs. Throughout his 35 years of business and research experience, John has learned that scaling a business requires four key elements: People, Strategy, Execution, and Capital.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Waters Business Consulting Group, John provides professional, tailored business consulting and coaching services to help clients leverage their unique business model for improved infrastructure and team accountability. His team\'s focus is on providing long-term sustained growth in sales, profits, and asset value of the business.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We Help business owners achieve their dreams by providing HOPE, a PLAN, RESULTS, and FREEDOM.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'waters-business-consulting-group-llc-helps-business-owners--large-and-small--improve', '2022-05-05', 'us/visionaries-network-john-waters-founder1.webp', 5, 'profile', 'Waters Business Consulting Group, LLC helps business owners--large and small--improve their cash flow, reduce their costs, and work more efficiently', 'Waters Business Consulting Group, LLC helps business owners--large and small--improve', 'Waters Business Consulting Group, LLC helps business owners--large and small--improve', NULL, 1, 'no', '', '', '', '', ''),
(33, 3, '<p><strong>&nbsp;Tech Group&rsquo;s expertise is vigilant monitoring and seamless maintenance of your computer network</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In today\'s fast-paced digital landscape, technology is the backbone of any successful organization. A reliable and efficient IT infrastructure is crucial for businesses to stay competitive, innovative, and ahead of the curve. At The Tech Group, the team understands the importance of this and is dedicated to providing top-notch IT services to help its clients achieve their goals.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With over 100 years of combined professional IT experience, The Tech Group&rsquo;s team of experts is equipped to support clients across a wide range of industries, from small to medium-sized businesses to enterprise organizations. Its diverse backgrounds, training, and education enable it to provide tailored solutions that cater to each client\'s unique needs and requirements.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Full Network Assessment: Understanding Your IT Infrastructure</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Before upgrading or expanding your network, it\'s essential to understand the capabilities and shortcomings of your existing infrastructure. Its Full Network Assessment provides a comprehensive analysis of your IT network, including an on-site evaluation by a senior network engineer, backup and security assessment, and recommendations for future upgrades.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Managed Services: Proactive IT Support</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The Tech Group understands the importance of responsive and reliable IT support. Its Managed Services solution provides three levels of support to meet the needs of SMBs to enterprise customers, as well as government, education, and healthcare segments. Its services include system monitoring, patch management, anti-virus/spyware management, backup management, server and desktop support, network management, monthly executive summaries, and bi-annual reports.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>IT Professional Services: Expert Technical Support</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Tech Group&rsquo;s IT Professional Services team provides expert technical support for all your IT needs, including technical support, software updates, patch management, vulnerability management, virus/spyware/spam protection, data backup/disaster preparation/business continuity, network administration, hardware maintenance, and more.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Network Upgrades and Support Services: Expert On-Site and Remote Support</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Tech Group&rsquo;s experienced technicians provide both remote support and on-site service as needed. Its services include installation, upgrades, system administration services, network server support, firewall management, internet/email management, network security general maintenance support.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Project Services: Customized IT Solutions</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Tech Group&rsquo;s Project Services team offers customized IT solutions for your unique needs. Its services include initial consultation and project design, product procurement and installation, ongoing support project assistance, and staff augmentation.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>The Human Side of IT: Personalized Approach</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Tech Group prides itself on its personalized approach to IT services. Its team is dedicated to understanding your business goals and objectives and providing tailored solutions that meet your specific needs. The company believes in building strong relationships with its clients and is committed to helping you achieve your IT objectives.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Co-Managed IT Services: Enhance Efficiency and Security</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Tech Group&rsquo;s Co-Managed IT Services offer unparalleled support and expertise for modern businesses. Its structured approach includes enhanced cyber and network security, strategic planning and guidance, empowering your internal team, compliance assurance, and data management to drive revenue growth.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Enhanced Cyber and Network Security: Protect Your Business</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Tech Group&rsquo;s Co-Managed IT support includes robust security measures to safeguard your business against cyber threats. Its team employs proactive monitoring and advanced threat detection tools to identify and mitigate security risks before they can impact your operations.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Strategic Planning and Guidance: Align Technology with Business Goals</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Tech Group&rsquo;s Co-Managed Care service provides strategic guidance tailored to support your business goals. Its expert team collaborates closely with your organization to offer proactive IT solutions and personalized support to align technology with your company\'s strategic vision.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Empower Your Internal Team: Collaboration for Success</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Tech Group Co-Managed Care service empowers your internal IT team by providing seamless collaboration with its experienced MSP experts. Together, it provides unparalleled support and expertise to optimize your IT operations.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Compliance Assurance: Safeguard Your Business</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Tech Group Co-Managed IT support ensures compliance with industry regulations and standards. It offers comprehensive compliance support with tailored solutions to optimize your efforts while minimizing risks.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Data Management: Secure Critical Data</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Tech Group&rsquo;s data management services provide comprehensive storage protection backup solutions for all your vital files. It prioritizes securing critical data including employee records and customer information.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Drive Revenue Growth: Boost Productivity and Revenue</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Tech Group&rsquo;s Co-Managed IT support boosts your business by saving you time for core activities offering expert technology strategies for growth adaptation to industry changes. Regular infrastructure analysis keeps you ahead optimizing performance and positioning you for success.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Steve Loyer, President and CEO</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With over 25 years of sales and service experience in network and network security solutions, Steve has earned technical and sales certificates from Microsoft, Cisco, Hewlett Packard, Citrix, Sonicwall, Symantec, McAfee, Barracuda, and American Power Conversion. Steve graduated from Vermont Technical College with a degree in Electrical and Electronics Engineering Technology.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We prioritize personal connections through face-to-face interactions because we believe in understanding you and your business. Our commitment to customer service goes beyond the virtual realm.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'tech-groups-expertise-is-vigilant-monitoring-and-seamless-maintenance-of-your-computer-network', '2022-05-05', 'us/visionaries-network-steve-loyer-techgroup.webp', 6, 'profile', 'Â Tech Groupâ€™s expertise is vigilant monitoring and seamless maintenance of your computer network', '&nbsp;Tech Group', '&nbsp;Tech Group', NULL, 1, 'no', '', '', '', '', ''),
(34, 3, '<p><strong>FIT Solutions offers managed IT services and cybersecurity services to help organizations reduce IT costs and downtime</strong></p>', '<p dir=\"ltr\">FIT Solutions understands that IT services are not just about providing technical expertise, but about building relationships and understanding the needs of clients. The company\'s approach is centered around providing a personalized experience, with a focus on quality, dedication, and proactive planning. This approach has allowed FIT Solutions to establish a reputation as a trusted business partner, rather than just a technology provider.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>The FIT Difference</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At the core of FIT Solutions\' approach is its commitment to quality service. The company prides itself on providing elite, white-glove service to its clients, with the goal of creating a raving-fan culture. FIT Solutions believes that this approach sets it apart from other IT service providers, and has contributed to its consistently high customer satisfaction scores.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">A major advantage of partnering with FIT Solutions is its committed engineering team, which serves as the backbone of the company\'s service offerings. This team is composed of highly skilled and experienced experts who bring a wealth of knowledge to the table. They are not just technicians; they are professionals who take the time to deeply understand the unique intricacies of each client\'s business operations and network infrastructure.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">By investing this time and effort into understanding the specific challenges and goals of their clients, FIT Solutions is able to deliver tailored solutions that are not only effective but also aligned with the strategic objectives of each organization. This personalized approach ensures that clients receive services that are specifically designed to address their individual needs, leading to enhanced operational efficiency and improved overall performance. Another significant advantage of partnering with FIT Solutions is its distinctive approach to customer support.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Unlike many other IT service providers that employ a tiered help desk system, which can often lead to frustration and delays, FIT Solutions offers a more streamlined and direct support experience. Clients have the opportunity to interact directly with a dedicated group of engineers who are not only well-versed in their systems but also familiar with the history and context of their specific issues. This direct line of communication fosters a collaborative environment where engineers can quickly diagnose problems and implement effective solutions without the need for lengthy escalations or handoffs.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As a result, clients benefit from faster response times and more effective problem resolution, ultimately leading to minimized downtime and enhanced productivity. This commitment to personalized service and direct engagement sets FIT Solutions apart in the competitive landscape of IT service providers, making it a preferred partner for businesses seeking reliable and responsive support.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>24/7/365 Cyber Team</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In addition to its technical expertise, FIT Solutions also offers a 24/7/365 cyber team that provides monitoring and securing services for its clients. The analysts investigate alerts, assess risk levels, and take the necessary steps to escalate or dismiss them. This ensures that clients\' environments are always secure and up-to-date.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Proactive Planning</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">FIT Solutions believes that proactive planning is essential for success. That\'s why it offers quarterly Technology Business Planning documents, which provide a roadmap for how IT will support business objectives over the next 3-24 months. This approach allows FIT Solutions to help its clients anticipate and prepare for future challenges, rather than simply reacting to them.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Managed Cybersecurity Services</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In addition to its proactive planning services, FIT Solutions also offers a range of managed cybersecurity services. These services include Security as a Service, which provides 24/7 monitoring and response to cyber threats. FIT Solutions also offers Managed SIEM &amp; Traffic Monitoring, which provides real-time analysis of security alerts generated within an environment. The company\'s consulting services provide monthly reports of incidents, as well as a real-time security dashboard.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Penetration Testing</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">FIT Solutions\' penetration testing services simulate various types of real-world attacks, allowing it to assess the security posture of an environment. The team delivers a report with industry risk analysis and remediation suggestions, providing valuable insights for improving security.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>External Testing</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">FIT Solutions\' external testing services simulate an attack from outside the network, imitating a criminal with no knowledge of the environment.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Internal Testing</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">FIT Solutions\' internal testing services simulate an internal attack, possibly from a criminal who has gained access to the network or obtained stolen credentials.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Social Engineering</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">FIT Solutions\' social engineering services use emails, phone calls, and in-person visits to identify opportunities to educate users and strengthen their defenses against these attacks.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Compliance Audits &amp; Assessments</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">For organizations under compliance regulations, FIT Solutions offers compliance audits and assessments. The company is familiar with a variety of regulatory requirements, including NIST, FINRA, PCI-DSS, HIPAA, HITECH, SEC, GLBA, and more. These thorough security assessments enable organizations to understand their risk profile.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We understand that IT is constantly evolving, and staying ahead of the curve can be a challenge.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'fit-solutions-offers-managed-it-services-and-cybersecurity-services-to-help-organizations-reduce-it-costs-and-downtime', '2022-05-05', 'us/visionaries-network-ephraim-ebstein-ceo-fit-solution.webp', 7, 'profile', 'FIT Solutions: Managed IT & Cybersecurity Services', 'FIT Solutions, managed IT services, cybersecurity, IT support, reduce downtime, IT cost savings, network security, data protection, tech support, cloud services, IT management, MSP, ransomware protection, visionaries network, secure infrastructure', 'FIT Solutions provides managed IT and cybersecurity services to help businesses cut IT costs, reduce downtime, and improve security and performance.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://fitsolutions.biz/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/fit-solutions.biz/', 'FIT Solutions ', '2012', 'San Diego, CA'),
(35, 3, '<p><strong>Glorium Technologies is a top-shelf bespoke software development firm</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">Glorium Technologies is a full-cycle app and software development company specializing in solutions specifically designed to fulfill the needs of a client\'s individual business. This company has been around for a number of years, with a stable and strong reputation as a provider of high-quality, custom software solutions aimed at catering to each individual client\'s unique requirements.<br><br>Custom software development services offered by the company include web app development, e-commerce solutions, content management systems, enterprise application integration, customer relationship management (CRM) solutions, as well as API development and integration services. All these aim to assist businesses in simplifying operations and improving profit by enhancing their customers\' experience.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Full-cycle development for custom web applications forms an integral part of Glorium Technologies\' approach. Idea road mapping forms the primary aspect of this company, where clients sit with consultants and business analysts to brainstorm on their web app ideas and custom needs. Based on those discussions, designers create an intuitive interface, and the web development team turns that intuitive interface into a web app.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The company also offers integration and migration services so that there is always seamless integration with what they have in place or third-party services. Finally, the support and maintenance group monitors and tracks all problems involving software for problems associated with the web application, thus ensuring stability and security.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Its other services include mobile apps, also adding the opportunity of custom software development services. The company specializes in both native mobile applications for iOS and Android systems and cross-platform applications suitable for different systems. They also offer progressive web apps that provide an app-like user experience and interface and hybrid apps that combine native and web technologies.<br>The company, Glorium Technologies, also focuses on the development of artificial intelligence. The company\'s services include developing custom AI technology using machine learning algorithms, image processing, natural language processing, and other advanced technologies.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Apart from this, predictive analytics enhances intelligence in terms of decision-making and planning, and computer vision enables advanced image processing and analysis. Apart from this, the company provides services concerning data engineering for acquiring, cleaning, preprocessing, and analyzing clients\' data.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">By partnering with Glorium Technologies, businesses can gain many benefits. To name a few: by getting custom software development services from the company, the businesses can gain an operational efficiency of 40%, reduce time to market by 30%, cut the time to insight down by 65%, and through automation recover 36% of their work week. Besides, because of the Glorium Technologies technological and AI development capability, firms can also further insights into customer behavior, preferences, and needs, thus helping firms make better decisions and pull ahead of others.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Andrei Kasyanau, CEO</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As CEO of Glorium Technologies, Andrei Kasyanau enables tech startups to accelerate their growth with on-demand agile product development services. His company\'s tailored approach enables companies to reach the market up to 30% faster and save 40% compared to maintaining an in-house team.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As a seasoned professional, Andrei has had the privilege of navigating both corporate environments with financial giants and entrepreneurial ventures, where he built his company from the ground up in an agile setting. This diverse experience has given him a unique perspective on driving innovation and success.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Outside of the office, Andrei is a family man with four kids who help him maintain a healthy work-life balance. When he\'s not traveling (pre-COVID), he\'s had the opportunity to visit over 30 countries and immerse himself in various cultures and traditions. He\'s also an adventure enthusiast, enjoying extreme activities like skiing, hiking, sailing, flying, and kite surfing. Andrei is always eager to connect with like-minded individuals who share his passion for exploring new horizons and taking breaks from the office grind.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We work closely with VC-backed startups and expanding tech companies, developing custom solutions that help them grow.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'glorium-technologies-is-a-top-shelf-bespoke-software-development-firm', '2022-05-05', 'us/visionaries-network-adrei-kasyanau-ceo.webp', 8, 'profile', 'Glorium Technologies: Custom Software Development Experts', 'Glorium Technologies, software development, custom software, bespoke solutions, app development, tech partner, enterprise software, product development, software engineering, IT services, scalable software, healthcare software, visionaries network, SaaS development, software firm', 'Glorium Technologies is a top-tier bespoke software development firm delivering tailored, scalable solutions to meet complex business needs across industries.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://gloriumtech.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/glorium-technologies/', 'Glorium Technologies', '2010', 'Princeton, New Jersey');
