(36, 3, '<p><strong>Navigator Business Solutions: Delivering SAP cloud ERP solutions that make you and your company better</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">Growth-focused organizations come to Navigator Business Solutions when they find their ability to grow and adapt is being limited by their current business processes and systems. Navigator helps companies conquer their industry and business complexity by implementing and supporting the best fit SAP Cloud-ERP systems and processes.<br><br>Navigator uses an optimized approach to deploying solutions using a combination of Fit-to-Standard best practices and an innovative, workshop-based implementation methodology that helps accelerate the delivery of SAP ERP as a core element in a company&rsquo;s digital transformation. This approach delivers a rapid time to value and rapid time to benefit, enabling the companies&rsquo; resources to be better spent on analyzing and transforming their businesses to meet today&rsquo;s demanding market challenges.<br><br>While not all company needs are the same, they do need a common set of standard ERP features to achieve optimal performance. Navigator has developed solutions consisting of these features and benefits that meet the needs of industry customers out of the box. This solution-set has been developed through more than 15 years of industry experience, delivering integrated SAP ERP offerings for growth-focused companies, configured to Navigator&rsquo;s clients\' current and future needs.<br><br>With more than&nbsp;300+ SAP Cloud ERP implementations, Navigator has a proven track record of on-time, and on-budget, implementations. This has made Navigator a top SAP partner for the past 15+ years, and the obvious choice for businesses that are looking for improved operations and greater revenue growth.<br><br>As an SAP Gold Partner and one of the top SAP implementation partners in the world, Navigator focuses on helping growth-focused companies deploy cost-effective, cloud-based ERP solutions based on the market-leading&nbsp;SAP S/4HANA Cloud Public Edition&nbsp;platform, as well as helping clients optimize and support their&nbsp;SAP Business One, and&nbsp;SAP Business ByDesign&nbsp;platforms. Navigator is a partner for life providing award-winning ERP professional services and support, including project planning, implementation, consulting, training, and US-based development and client support.<br><br>Navigator&rsquo;s vision is cutting the cost and headaches of ERP systems by focusing on time-tested, industry-standard best practices and then either configuring or adding pre-built integrations and extensions for client-specific industry functionality. This reduces implementation and operational costs, improves deployment speeds, and ensures best practices for firms of all sizes and industries.<br><br>Navigator is one of the few select, active&nbsp;GROW with SAP Partners. Its SAP-qualified partner-packaged solutions are integrated solutions that leverage market-leading SAP software and innovations, together with industry-specific additions, to deliver low-risk, predictable projects at attractive price points &ndash; for a rapid time to value.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>What is Cloud ERP?</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">ERP is a Unified Solution to Manage Your Business From Anywhere</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Cloud ERP is a rapidly growing approach to enterprise resource planning (ERP) that makes use of Software as a Service (SaaS) business model to provide companies with more flexible business management solutions. Readily scalable, add new users and functionality &ndash; all without the need for expensive IT resources. The SAP ERP Solutions delivered by Navigator Business Solutions provide predictable pricing, seen as an operating expense, not a capital expense. All so you can focus on your business growth &ndash; and not on IT and back office processes.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">ERP is an industry term for the broad suite of completely integrated solutions that help businesses manage the central functions of their business such as purchasing and inventory management. SAP applications SAP Business One, SAP Business ByDesign, and SAP S/4HANA Cloud Public Edition, go well beyond the basic core functions of accounting and inventory, delivering a complete, robust suite covering all aspects of business management including Human Resources, Financials, Analytics, Supply Chain, Project Management, CRM, and more.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The industry is moving quickly to cloud computing as it provides a greater opportunity for businesses to completely transform how they use and pay for information technology. For example, cloud-based (SaaS) ERP applications eliminate the need for a business to purchase additional servers and storage hardware and maintain them on-site which, in turn, reduces operational expenses.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Chris M. Nielsen, President &amp; Chief Executive Officer</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Chris Nielsen has over 20 years of hands-on experience as head of finance, operations, and technology for various divisions of global corporations. Chris&nbsp;has&nbsp;led the implementation of ERP, and other key IT, systems in several countries and understands the critical impact of these projects and decisions. Chris received his Bachelor of Science degree from the University of Utah and holds an MBA from Westminster College with the final year, and course work, completed at the University of Chicago.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;Our SAP-certified consulting services team has earned a reputation as a leader in providing technical and process solutions.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'navigator-business-solutions-delivering-sap-cloud-erp-solutions-that-make-you-and-your-company-better', '2022-05-05', 'us/visionaries-network-chris-m-nielson-navigator-ceo-president.webp', 9, 'profile', 'Navigator: SAP Cloud ERP Solutions for Business Growth', 'Navigator Business Solutions, SAP ERP, cloud ERP, business solutions, enterprise software, ERP implementation, digital transformation, SAP partner, cloud solutions, scalable ERP, visionaries network, ERP provider, ERP consulting, supply chain software, financial management', 'Navigator Business Solutions delivers SAP cloud ERP systems that streamline operations, drive growth, and make businesses more efficient and competitive.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.nbs-us.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/navigator-business-solutions/', 'Navigator Business Solutions', '2005', 'Lehi, Utah'),
