k\" rel=\"noopener\">equilar.com</a></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 14.542%;\">David Chun,&nbsp;<br>Founder &amp; CEO</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 68.7752%;\">Equilar.com provides corporate leadership data, offering insights into executive compensation, board governance, and shareholder engagement. It supports benchmarking, succession planning, and recruitment, helping organizations improve transparency and performance.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 125.6px;\">\r\n<td style=\"width: 16.6616%;\" bgcolor=\"#CCCCCC\"><a title=\"BFX Commerce\" href=\"https://bfxcommerce.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">BFX Commerce</a><br><a title=\"bfxcommerce.com\" href=\"https://bfxcommerce.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">bfxcommerce.com</a></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 14.542%;\">Brian Feener,&nbsp;<br>CEO/Founder</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 68.7752%;\">BFXCommerce.com is an e-commerce platform designed to provide seamless shopping experiences, offering a wide range of products across various categories. The site emphasizes convenience, affordability, and secure transactions, catering to diverse customer needs with efficient delivery services and excellent customer support.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', '20-business-experts-2023', '2023-10-02', 'us/20-business experts-2023.png', 1002, 'listing', '20 Business Experts 2023', 'business experts, business, best business magazine, best magazine', '20 Business Experts 2023', NULL, 1, 'no', '', '', '', '', ''),
(38, 4, '<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Ignite Visibility: A top digital marketing agency that focuses on performance and aims to provide clarity in digital marketing<strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-776e40fc-7fff-afd3-8d56-b8ebcf499a7d\"></strong></strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">Ignite Visibility, a premier full-service digital marketing agency with offices in San Diego, CA, and Orlando, FL, is committed to delivering exceptional results for its clients. With over 30 years of combined industry experience, Ignite Visibility\'s co-founders, John and Krish, set out to create an agency that truly puts its clients first.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Ignite Visibility\'s unique approach to digital marketing sets it apart from other agencies. The team of experts utilizes a unified cross-channel marketing strategy driven by best-in-class creative minds. They provide thought leadership, expertise, and industry research to keep their clients\' brands on the cutting edge of their industry. Monthly and quarterly business strategy reports detail their work, results, and how to reach newly identified goals. Additionally, they offer proprietary software-driven and source-based forecasting built on competitive analysis and business data.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Ignite Visibility\'s commitment to quality service, communication, and customer success is unparalleled. They believe in building relationships, celebrating success, scaling what works, testing for new solutions, and celebrating all over again. Their real-time communication via Slack and other project management systems ensures seamless collaboration between teams.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In 2013, John and Krish set out to create an agency that would over-deliver for its clients. They attracted the best subject-matter experts for each service and established a reliable system for consistently growing businesses online. In February 2023, Ignite Visibility partnered with Mountaingate Capital, a private equity firm based in Denver, Colorado. This partnership further solidified their commitment to client-centric culture.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In December 2023, Ignite Visibility acquired Orlando-based Integrated Digital Strategies (IDS), a prominent digital marketing agency specializing in the franchisor/franchisee industry. This acquisition strengthened their commitment to high-quality service that puts the client first.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Today, Ignite Visibility is a 100% remote team with over 200 full-time employees worldwide. They have worked with over 160 happy clients and manage approximately $100 million in advertising dollars annually.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Ignite Visibility\'s SEO company executes unique strategic plans to achieve their clients\' business goals. They offer a range of services, including local SEO, keyword research, analytics and reporting, digital PR and link building, content creation, ecommerce SEO, lead generation SEO, and SEO for all industries.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The team at Ignite Visibility prides itself on transparency, nationally recognized excellence, various industries served, clear ROI reporting, custom strategy development, achievable goals, flexibility, and strategic blueprint implementation. They believe in delivering quantifiable results that have a tangible impact on their clients\' businesses.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">For businesses looking for a partner that can deliver exceptional results and put their needs first, Ignite Visibility is the perfect choice. With over a decade of experience in the industry, they have honed their expertise in infusing industry best practices to find the success their clients are after.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>John Lincoln, CEO of Ignite Visibility</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">John Lincoln, a seasoned digital marketing expert with an MBA, is the CEO of Ignite Visibility, a renowned agency that offers a comprehensive range of services, including multichannel digital strategy, SEO, paid media, social media, creative, email, PR, and CRO. With a strong focus on relationships, responsiveness, and results, Ignite Visibility has consistently been recognized as one of the top digital marketing agencies in the United States by Clutch.co.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Lincoln\'s business philosophy is centered around helping others through digital marketing and using the profits to invest in his clients\' success, employees\' success, and his community. With nearly two decades of experience, he has worked with over 1,000 online businesses, achieving remarkable results. He has helped numerous clients take their websites to the #1 position in Google for competitive keywords, built social media communities with millions of followers, and strategized record-breaking advertising campaigns.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Lincoln is a prolific author and has written thousands of articles and videos. He has been featured in prominent publications such as Forbes and The New York Times. He has also authored three books: \"Advolution\" (2022), \"The Forecaster Method\" (2019), and \"Digital Influencer\" (2016). Additionally, he has produced and directed two documentaries: \"SEO: The Movie\" and \"Social Media Marketing: The Movie\".</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Lincoln has received numerous accolades for his work, including being recognized as a Most Admired CEO and Top Business Leader Under 40 by the San Diego Business Journal. He has spoken at prestigious conferences and events such as Web Summit, SMX, and Pubcon. Prior to his entrepreneurial endeavors, Lincoln taught Web Analytics, SEO, and Paid Media at UC San Diego from 2010 to 2018.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;Ignite Visibility has had the pleasure to work with some of the biggest brands in the world and currently represents 150 clients.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'ignite-visibility-performance-driven-marketing-agency', '2025-01-04', 'us/visionaries-network-john-lincoin-ceo-ignite-visibility.webp', 1001, 'cover', 'Ignite Visibility | Performance-Driven Marketing Agency', 'Ignite Visibility, digital marketing, SEO, PPC, performance marketing, content strategy, marketing agency, online growth, conversion optimization, visionaries network, email marketing, social media, paid ads, lead generation, digital strategy', 'Ignite Visibility is a top digital marketing agency focused on performance, providing clarity and results-driven strategies.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://ignitevisibility.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ignite-visibility/', 'Ignite Visibility', '2012', 'San Diego, California'),
(39, 4, '<p><strong>NanoImaging Services uses cryo-EM technology to accelerate drug discovery and development for pharmaceutical and biotech companies</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">NIS (NanoImaging Services) is a pioneering Contract Research Organization (CRO) that has been at the forefront of cryo-electron microscopy (cryo-EM) services since 2007. With a diverse range of skill sets and state-of-the-art technology, including more transmission electron microscopes than any provider in North America, NIS has made cryo-EM imaging and analysis accessible to companies of all sizes, and teams across the drug discovery pipeline.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">NIS\'s commitment to quality results and collaboration with clients has enabled them to accelerate the development of new and life-changing therapeutics. By leveraging cutting-edge technologies and expertise, NIS helps clients overcome the historical bottlenecks associated with sample preparation, including sample suitability, stability, and reproducibility.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">One of the key areas where NIS excels is in sample preparation. Their team of experts uses optimized methods to assess sample suitability and stability for cryo-EM, including negative stain analyses to evaluate sample quality. They also offer advanced services such as protein purification, grid substrate preparation, and vitrification and plunge freezing to optimize the output of cryo-EM studies.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">NIS\'s protein purification capabilities include buffer exchange and removal of soluble aggregates from samples using their microvolume AKTA Go equipped with Superose 6, Sephadex 200, and desalting columns. This service is available at their East Coast site and requires advance request.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Their expertise in grid substrates is another area where NIS stands out. They have developed innovative methods for deploying grid variations to solve complex sample challenges. For example, they often use continuous support grids to optimize the distribution and orientation of difficult samples. They also prepare continuous carbon grids and have developed a reliable method for preparing graphene oxide grids, which are ideal for biological macromolecules due to their hydrophilicity and minimal background in cryo-EM imaging.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">NIS\'s sample vitrification and plunge freezing capabilities are also unparalleled. They have accumulated decades of experience and established reliable standard operating procedures for both Vitrobot and manual plunging devices. They can vitrify a wide range of samples, including soluble proteins, membrane proteins stabilized by detergents, nanodiscs, and amphipols.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In addition to their expertise in sample preparation and vitrification, NIS also has a state-of-the-art computational infrastructure that supports both on-site and co-localized high-speed computing resources. This includes over 500 processing cores, 50 GPUs, and six petabytes of storage space, all located within secure facilities behind multiple high availability firewalls and following NIST security guidelines.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">NIS\'s commitment to innovation is evident in their deployment of the latest generation transmission electron microscopes across their San Diego and Boston sites. They are constantly acquiring new technologies to remain at the forefront of the field.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Overall, NIS is a leading provider of cryo-EM services that enables companies to accelerate the development of new and life-changing therapeutics. With their expertise in sample preparation, vitrification, plunge freezing, and computational infrastructure, NIS is well-positioned to help clients overcome the challenges associated with cryo-EM imaging and analysis.</p>\r\n<p><strong>John Rigg, Chief Executive Officer</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">John Rigg brings over 20 years of leadership experience within the pharmaceutical and biomanufacturing industries to NIS.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Most recently, he served as Chief Executive Officer of Exelead Biopharma, a biopharmaceutical contract development and manufacturing organization specializing in complex injectable formulations, including lipid nanoparticle (LNP) based drug delivery.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Prior to joining Exelead in June 2014, John served as the Vice President of Manufacturing for Ventria Bioscience, Fort Collins Co., a progressive bioscience company specializing in developing and commercializing proteins expressed in rice. Prior to Ventria, John spent 25 years at Eli Lilly and Company with a multitude of assignments across manufacturing sites in the US, Puerto Rico and the United Kingdom. John has extensive knowledge and experience with the development, scale up, and commercialization of therapeutic proteins.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Originally from Liverpool, England, John attended Liverpool University where he graduated with a BSc (Hons) in Applied Chemistry.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;NanoImaging Services (NIS) is the industry leader with the longest history in cryo-EM.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'nanoimaging-services-uses-cryo-em-technology-to-accelerate-drug-discovery-and-development-for-pharmaceutical-and-biotech-companies', '2023-06-11', 'us/visionaries-network-john-rigg-ceo.webp', 1, 'profile', 'Cryo-EM Drug Discovery | NanoImaging Services for Pharma', 'cryo-EM, drug discovery, drug development, biotech, pharmaceuticals, visionaries network, structural biology, nanotechnology, microscopy, protein analysis, 3D imaging, cryo-electron microscopy, molecular structure, pharma research, biomedical', 'Accelerate drug discovery with cryo-EM. NanoImaging Services delivers advanced imaging for biotech and pharmaceutical development and structural analysis.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.nanoimagingservices.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/nanoimaging-services/', 'NanoImaging Services', '2007', 'San Diego, CA'),
(40, 4, '<p><strong>eStruxture Data Centers: The largest Canadian cloud and carrier-neutral data center provider</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">eStruxture Data Centers, the largest Canadian-owned and operated data center provider, offers high-density data centers located in the major Canadian markets. It adopts a customized approach in offering businesses the most efficient combination of space, power, cooling, and connectivity to suit the particular needs of every business.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The services provided by eStruxture Data Centers will be designed based on the specific demands of businesses that depend on mission-critical IT infrastructure. The services offered include cloud and carrier-neutral colocation alternatives, plus customized data center colocation solutions to fit the unique needs of any given business.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">One of the major strengths of eStruxture is its highly connected ecosystem, offering access to over 50 network providers and 900 business-critical networks. This allows enterprise customers to connect to major cloud service providers such as AWS, Azure, and Google Cloud through its Cloud Connect platform.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Cloud Connect is a reliable cloud interconnection platform serving securely and dependably interconnected environments between eStruxture and major cloud service providers. The platform is developed through strategic partnerships with leading NaaS providers, Megaport, and Console Connect.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">This appointment would further solidify the leading position of eStruxture in the Canadian Data Center market by appointing Taylor Hammond as the Vice President, Head of Corporate Development and Capital Markets. With Hammond\'s expertise in Corporate Development and Capital Markets, the company is well-placed to drive its growth and expansion over the coming years.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Hammond\'s corporate development and capital market experience have bolstered these capabilities in the new role. Hammond brings an accomplished record of accomplishment in leading growth and expansion for a variety of industries, including technology and telecommunications.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In this new role, Hammond will lead the corporate development and capital markets for eStruxture. He will lead the leadership team in identifying strategic growth opportunities through partnerships that help develop and foster expansion plans.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The appointment of Taylor Hammond to the position of Vice President, Head of Corporate Development and Capital Markets indeed marks a major leap forward for eStruxture Data Centers in the right direction. With his experience and expertise, the company is all set for further growth and expansion in the Canadian data center market.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As one of Canada\'s largest data center operators, eStruxture Data Centers offers a set of data center services focused on the needs of businesses dependent on mission-critical IT infrastructure. With its very connected ecosystem that comprises more than 50 network providers and over 900 business-critical networks, the company is so well-positioned that it can be a partner of choice for all secure and reliable connectivity needs.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Todd Coleman, Founder, President and Chief Executive Officer</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Todd Coleman is the Founder, President, and CEO of eStruxture. Todd brings more than 25 years of experience in the IT, data center, and telecommunications industries. Most recently, Todd was the Chief Operating Officer and co-founder of Cologix.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Todd has also held several senior positions at Level 3 Communications, a global telecommunications company, including Senior Vice President of Data Centers, Senior Vice President of Media Operations, and President of Level 3 Communications Europe. Todd holds a juris doctorate and a bachelor&rsquo;s degree in computer information systems.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&ldquo;We offer colocation, cloud connectivity, bandwidth, and security and support services to customers across Canada in its carrier and cloud-neutral facilities.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;Our solutions are designed to give you more: more locations, more capacity, more connections that enable you to run modern, demanding enterprise applications, and offer your business the control to rapidly scale in response to unpredictable changes in business processes.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'estruxture-data-centers-the-largest-canadian-cloud-and-carrier-neutral-data-center-provider', '2023-05-11', 'us/visionaries-network-todd-coleman-ceo-estruxture.webp', 2, 'profile', 'eStruxture: Canada\'s Largest Carrier-Neutral Data Centers', 'data centers, cloud services, eStruxture, carrier-neutral, colocation, visionaries network, cloud storage, IT infrastructure, hybrid cloud, secure hosting, connectivity, enterprise cloud, network solutions, green data centers, data security', 'eStruxture is Canada&#039;s largest cloud and carrier-neutral data center provider, offering secure, scalable, and sustainable infrastructure for all your IT needs.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.estruxture.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/estruxture/', 'eStruxture Data Centers', '2017', 'Montreal, Quebec'),
(41, 4, '<p><strong>Cynoteck is a Microsoft Solution Partner and Salesforce Consulting Partner Company</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">Cynoteck believes in the power of technology and provides exceptional experiences. The right teams can take care of their technological aspects and amplify their business productivity.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Cynoteck is a dynamic and professional IT services provider that serves enterprises and individuals, helping them meet the challenges of the global economy. They offer services in the area of CRM Consultation and Implementation, Application Development, Mobile Application Development, Web Development, and Offshore Development. Their experienced Project Managers apply a mature development methodology, continuously exceeding their clients\' business expectations and ensuring the success of off-shoring projects. They have expertise ranging from consulting on business and technology to creating innovative technology solutions. Their vision shapes the culture at Cynoteck, which lays a strong emphasis on innovation and thought processes.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Cynoteck\'s name is derived from Cynosure + Technology + Knowledge. They deliver value to their customers by utilizing their technology and knowledge. They believe that IT should be a highly value-adding asset to businesses that rely on technology to provide a competitive advantage in their industry. To do so, IT must be treated as an integral part of the business. To be successful as a business, IT must have a clear vision and a realistic plan that is aligned with corporate goals. It also must have an IT organization that is able to leverage the infrastructure to execute those plans and manage them effectively.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Cynoteck undertook its journey in 2008 with a humble team of three individuals and two determined founders, Udit Handa and Anshul Verma. Their collective vision was to establish a world-class IT service company, choosing Dehradun as one of the locations for their delivery center due to the city\'s abundant talent pool and potential for growth despite limited opportunities. Headquartered in Minnesota, USA, the company strategically set up its offshore center in Dehradun, India, and Dubai, UAE to leverage the skilled workforce and promote global collaboration.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Over the years, Cynoteck\'s team of dedicated consultants has made significant strides, undertaking numerous globally recognized software implementations and pioneering innovations. This continuous progress has enriched their expertise, enabling them to craft exceptional outsourced solutions and top-notch product development services.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Cynoteck\'s uncompromising dedication to excellence has made them earn prestigious awards and valuable partnerships since their start. The company proudly holds the prestigious Gold Partner status with Microsoft and has become a member of NASSCOM, a testament to their dedication and contribution to the IT industry. As Cynoteck continues its journey, it remains focused on providing innovative solutions while maintaining its position as a trusted and reliable partner for businesses worldwide.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In 2023, Cynoteck was honored to be recognized as the \"Top Salesforce Lightning\" company by Clutch, a testament to their expertise and proficiency in Salesforce\'s innovative technology. They have also been awarded as the \"Top Salesforce Company in UAE 2023,\" solidifying their position as a key player in the UAE\'s Salesforce market. Additionally, their commitment to excellence has earned them the title of \"Top Microsoft Dynamics ERP Company 2023,\" highlighting their proficiency in Microsoft\'s powerful ERP solutions.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Their expertise extends beyond Salesforce and Microsoft Dynamics ERP. They have been recognized as the \"Top CRM Consulting Company 2023,\" \"Top ERP Consulting Company 2023,\" and \"Top Salesforce Consulting Partner\" for their comprehensive expertise in customer relationship management.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Cynoteck, they believe that IT should be a highly value-adding asset to businesses that rely on technology to provide a competitive advantage in their industry. To achieve this, they have developed a strong emphasis on innovation and thought process within their organization. Their vision is to shape the culture at Cynoteck, which lays a strong foundation for success.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">What makes Cynoteck your best CRM Consulting partner?</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Cynoteck, they have worked with both B2B and B2C businesses for over a decade, resolving all possible CRM challenges that they faced. Their CRM consultants help businesses choose and implement an ideal CRM solution for their industry and needs. They have experience working with various industries such as healthcare, retail, real estate, and others where you have important customer data.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Whether you need a new CRM or want to improve your existing one, they can help. They assist in mapping out CRM implementation as per your customer management strategy, developing custom CRM systems and functionalities for the optimization of your existing CRM solutions. Their CRM experts understand CRM processes for different industries where you have important customer data.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Their consultants are always up-to-date with the latest technologies and can help you deal with any complex tasks like CRM audit and optimization, CRM upgrade, configuration, and integration. They are a long-term Microsoft Solutions Partner and a Salesforce Registered Consulting Partner Company that focuses on your business needs primarily, suggesting the best CRM solutions that work for your business practice.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Cynoteck, they are committed to providing exceptional IT services that meet the evolving needs of enterprises and individuals alike. With their expertise in CRM Consultation and Implementation, Application Development, Mobile Application Development, Web Development, and Offshore Development, they are confident that they can help you unlock your business potential. Contact them today to learn more about how they can help you achieve your business goals.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Udit Handa, CEO</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Udit Handa, a multifaceted individual with a passion for technology, has made a name for himself in the industry. With a background that includes working with renowned companies like Microsoft and JLL, Udit\'s journey began in his hometown of Dehradun, India.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">After gaining experience as a software engineer and developer, he discovered his true calling as an entrepreneur. In 2009, he took the leap and founded Cynoteck Technology Solutions, which has since grown from a team of two to a company of over 200 talented professionals. In addition to his role as CEO, Udit has expanded his expertise by acquiring certifications in blockchain architecture, Ethereum development, digital marketing, and more.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Following the success of Cynoteck, he went on to establish Petofy, a platform that connects pet owners with pet-related service providers. As a skilled business leader and family man, Udit has mastered the art of balancing work and family life. In his free time, he engages in volunteer work and advocates for Indie Dog Breed adoption campaigns.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">He is also an avid runner and promotes fitness activities within Cynoteck and his community. Udit\'s accomplishments have earned him numerous accolades, including the 2022 Uttarakhand ICON Award for Best IT Company in the region. He has also been featured in the book \"The Art of Starting Up.\"</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;Our client list includes Fortune 500 companies like Microsoft and JLL. We have maintained a healthy and successful relationship with our clients.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'cynoteck-is-a-microsoft-solution-partner-and-salesforce-consulting-partner-company', '2023-05-11', 'us/visionaries-network-udit-handa-ceo-cyboteck.webp', 3, 'profile', 'Cynoteck | Microsoft & Salesforce Consulting Partner', 'Cynoteck, Microsoft Partner, Salesforce Consulting, CRM solutions, cloud services, app development, Dynamics 365, Salesforce integration, IT consulting, business solutions, Azure, Power BI, Salesforce partner, visionaries network, digital transformation', 'Cynoteck is a trusted Microsoft Solution &amp; Salesforce Consulting Partner offering CRM, cloud, and IT services globally.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://cynoteck.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/cynoteck-technology-solutions-private-limited/', 'Cynoteck Technology Solutions', '2008', 'DehraDun, Uttarakhand'),
(42, 4, '<p><strong>Hollman Media provides expert website development and digital marketing services to boost your online presence</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In these fast-paced digital times, an online presence is crucial to the success of businesses. Hollman Media is a full-service web development and digital marketing company that takes a business further in creatively enhancing its online presence through website design and digital marketing. With highly qualified professionals committed to the delivery of customized solutions, Hollman Media is the perfect partner to help businesses maximize their online reach.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Amplify Your Reach through Targeted Digital Advertising</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Hollman Media offers targeted digital advertising services that drive traffic, generate leads, and convert customers for your business. The company&rsquo;s team brings exceptional experience in Google, Facebook, and Instagram Ads to zero in on your target audience with pinpoint targeting capabilities. It provides two influential digital advertising solutions: Google Ads and Facebook and Instagram Ads.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Excel with Google Ads</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Google Ads are perfection in the field of digital marketing for businesses, enabling them to connect with their ideal audience at precisely the right moment. Advanced analytics, optimization tools, and measurable results ensure maximum ROI in driving qualified traffic and conversions. Starting from as low as $300 a month, Google Ads unlocks the power of growth and success in the competitive online marketplace.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Leveraging the full potential of Facebook and Instagram Ads, these two ad options are game-changers for businesses in the digital world of marketing. Reaching as many as 2.8 billion active users each month is an enormous audience to tap into. Advanced audience insights, robust targeting options, and visually appealing ad formats ensure businesses reach the right audience with compelling stories. From $400 a month, Facebook and Instagram Ads are an extremely affordable solution for businesses who want to maximize their online presence and drive meaningful engagement with their target audience.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Google Partner and Ads Certifications</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Hollman Media has earned the prestigious Google Partner badge to show the world that they know their stuff and will truly be able to drive success home for their clients. Their Google Partner certification provides assurance that they have the knowledge and skills needed to deliver quality results for their clients.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Why Google Business Profile Matters</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Amplify your local presence through Google Business Profile, henceforth referred to as GBP. At Hollman Media, it assists companies in optimizing their profiles by improving customer links and adding more credibility. The only thing standing between one and his or her local online presence is a GBP - this is what will show directly in the results of Google Search or Maps when someone is searching for either your business or services.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Why is Google Business Profile Important?</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&bull; Improved Local Visibility: Appears within Google\'s local pack when users search for your business for more website and physical traffic. Engage Directly with Google Business Profile by posting updates, responding to reviews, answering customer questions, showing your business through photos and videos, and offering booking options.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&bull; Increased Credibility: A maintained GBP represents an active, reliable, and engaging business to customers.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Maximize Your Google Ads with Google Business Profile</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Google Business Profile and Google Ads go hand in hand. When both are appropriately maintained, amplified online visibility, increased customer engagement, and higher ROI on advertising spend will come into view for your business.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Expert Search Engine Optimization Services</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Hollman Media, the team understands the relevance of SEO in today\'s world. From a team of highly experienced SEO consultants, they offer fully integrated services to enhance your website rankings and give you maximum online visibility. The company&rsquo;s philosophy behind SEO is based on sound knowledge of search engine algorithms but also the best practices the industry offers.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Why Choose Hollman Media&rsquo;s SEO Services?</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Be it a small business wanting to set up on the web or a large enterprise looking to conquer the search engines, Hollman Media&rsquo;s SEO expert services will help meet your goals. With a proven track record of success and keeping its expertise updated with the latest trends in SEO, Hollman Media is committed to driving measurable results for its clients.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Enhance Your Online Visibility with Hollman Media</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Hollman Media, the team commits ourselves to helping a business reach its goals through professional web development and digital marketing services. With the full-service, targeted digital advertising, Google Business Profile optimization, and expert SEO services the company offers, Hollman Media is ready to be your partner in making the most of your online presence.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;Our team comprises highly skilled professionals dedicated to delivering customized solutions tailored to meet your unique needs. Partner with us and unlock the true potential of your online presence.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'hollman-media-provides-expert-website-development-and-digital-marketing-services-to-boost-your-online-presence', '2023-05-11', 'us/visionaries-network-travis-hollman-founder.webp', 4, 'profile', 'Hollman Media | Web Development & Digital Marketing', 'Hollman Media, web development, digital marketing, SEO, visionaries network, online presence, branding, PPC, content marketing, social media, responsive design, eCommerce, local SEO, UX design, web solutions', 'Hollman Media offers professional website development and digital marketing services to enhance your brand&rsquo;s online presence and drive results.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://techharbordigital.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/tech-harbor-digital/', 'Hollman Media/Tech Harbor Digital', '2000', 'Norfolk, Nebraska');
