(43, 4, '<p><strong>Riverleaf Biotech Industries, LLC: Herbal extraction and product manufacturer, specializing in hemp extraction and CBD wellness and skin care products</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">In recent years, the CBD industry has experienced rapid growth and widespread acceptance, driven in part by the increasing recognition of the benefits of cannabidiol (CBD) for human health. As the market continues to evolve, companies are seeking innovative ways to stay ahead of the curve and provide high-quality products that meet the growing demands of consumers. Riverleaf Biotech Industries LLC, a leading provider of hemp-derived products and extracts, is poised to play a significant role in shaping the future of the CBD industry through its commitment to collaboration, innovation, and quality.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Riverleaf Biotech Industries LLC, the team is dedicated to creating a new standard for CBD products by mirroring the standards of production found in pharmaceutical laboratories. By controlling every step of the process, from plant to product, the company ensures that a strict level of quality control is implemented at all stages. This commitment to quality is reflected in the company\'s adherence to Good Manufacturing Practices (GMP), ISO, USDA, and FDA standards, as well as its pursuit of certifications in these areas.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">One of the key ways that Riverleaf Biotech Industries LLC is working to shape the future of the CBD industry is through its wholesale partnership options. The company offers a range of made-to-order cannabinoid-infused products, including custom formulations, private label options, and Serenital Distribution. Each of these options allows customers to benefit from Riverleaf Biotech Industries LLC\'s expertise in hemp extraction and product development, while also providing them with the flexibility to tailor their products to meet their specific needs and branding goals.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Riverleaf Biotech Industries LLC is a leading provider of white labeling services tailored specifically for businesses looking to establish or expand their CBD brand. By offering a comprehensive suite of solutions, Riverleaf enables companies to streamline their product development processes, ultimately saving them both time and financial resources.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With their white labeling services, businesses can take advantage of ready-made CBD products that are already formulated and tested, allowing them to quickly enter the market without the lengthy and often costly process of product development. This is particularly beneficial for startups or smaller companies that may not have the resources to invest in extensive research and development.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Furthermore, Riverleaf also collaborates with clients to create custom private label CBD items, leveraging their expertise in formulation and compliance to ensure that the final product meets the specific needs and branding of the client. In addition to white labeling, Riverleaf Biotech Industries offers a hemp toll processing service, which provides a flexible and cost-effective solution for customers looking to convert their hemp biomass into high-quality CBD extracts. This service allows businesses to utilize their own raw materials while benefiting from Riverleaf\'s advanced processing capabilities and industry knowledge.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">By outsourcing the extraction process, companies can focus on their core competencies, such as marketing and distribution, while ensuring that they receive premium CBD extracts that meet industry standards.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In addition to its wholesale partnership options, Riverleaf Biotech Industries LLC is also committed to supporting research and development in the CBD industry. The company\'s product development laboratory is equipped to experiment with various herbal formulations and provides customers with access to expert formulation specialists who can help them develop new products or improve their manufacturing processes.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Ultimately, Riverleaf Biotech Industries LLC\'s commitment to collaboration, innovation, and quality makes it an ideal partner for companies looking to stay ahead of the curve in the rapidly evolving CBD industry. By working together with Riverleaf Biotech Industries LLC, companies can gain access to expertise in hemp extraction and product development, as well as a range of innovative solutions that can help them succeed in this exciting and rapidly growing market.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Gabriel R. Haddad, CEO &amp; Founder</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Wanting to make the purest concentrated plant essences, Gabriel founded Riverleaf Biotech Industries LLC in 2014. Riverleaf began providing research and development (R&amp;D) services for the extraction of a wide variety ofâ€¯high-qualityâ€¯plant, fungus, and algaeâ€¯materials. When the Agriculture Improvement Act of 2018 went into effect, the company expanded and started specializing in hemp extraction services.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;Riverleaf aims to enrich the community by sharing our resources and building strong connections with our peers.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'riverleaf-biotech-industries-llc-herbal-extraction-and-product-manufacturer-specializing-in-hemp-extraction-and-cbd-wellness-and-skin-care-products', '2023-05-11', 'us/visionaries-network-gabriel-haddab-ceo-founder.webp', 5, 'profile', 'Riverleaf Biotech | Hemp & CBD Product Manufacturer', 'Riverleaf Biotech, CBD products, hemp extraction, herbal extraction, skincare, wellness, CBD oil, natural remedies, CBD skincare, visionaries network, organic CBD, hemp wellness, CBD manufacturing, CBD tinctures, CBD topicals', 'Riverleaf Biotech specializes in premium hemp extraction and CBD wellness products, including skincare, oils, and herbal-based solutions.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://riverleafbiotech.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/riverleafbiotech/', 'Riverleaf Biotech Industries, LLC', '2014', 'Eugene, Oregon'),
(44, 4, '<p><strong>Storm Cloud Marketing helps your business discover, execute, and optimize effective marketing strategies</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">The fast-moving, constant shifts in today\'s marketing landscape can leave a person reeling with the myriad of options available. In truth, there are literally thousands of marketing channels and strategies a business can follow. No wonder most businesses do not know where to begin in making it all make any sense. What if you could tame the monster of marketing and be confident about meeting your objectives? Welcome to Storm Cloud Marketing.<br><br>Storm Cloud Marketing has been a trusted partner for businesses since 1998, guiding them through the often complex and challenging landscape of marketing. With over two decades of experience under Storm Cloud Marketing&rsquo;s belt, it has accumulated a wealth of valuable data and insights that empower the company to assist its clients in sidestepping the common pitfalls that can lead to wasted time and financial resources.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">So, how exactly does Storm Cloud Marketing help businesses tackle their marketing challenges? The process begins with a simple yet crucial step: a straightforward phone call. During this initial conversation, the company takes the time to listen carefully to your specific goals, concerns, and unique circumstances. It believes that understanding your vision is essential to crafting an effective marketing strategy. Once Storm Cloud Marketing has a clear understanding of your objectives, its dedicated team of marketing professionals springs into action.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Storm Cloud Marketing analyses your current marketing efforts, identifies areas for improvement, and leverages its extensive experience to develop a customized action plan tailored specifically to your needs. This plan is designed not only to address your immediate challenges but also to set you on a path toward long-term success. The organization&rsquo;s approach is collaborative and transparent; it keeps you informed every step of the way, ensuring that you feel confident and engaged in the process.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Whether you are looking to enhance your brand visibility, increase customer engagement, or drive sales, Storm Cloud Marketing is committed to providing you with the tools and strategies necessary to achieve your aims.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Once you approve an action plan, then Storm Cloud Marketing gets to work. Using marketing research, the Storm Cloud Marketing team develops a thoughtful and customized strategy for your business. It finds time to understand the target audience of the customer and then work out a way to show areas whereby one can improve the marketing flow. Then, the company maps out your current marketing flow by marking out some areas you can optimize and improve.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The result of this: A fully tailored marketing strategy in digital, creative, and website recommendations. Storm Cloud Marketing presents this strategy in a very clear, actionable plan, full of steps toward the implementation of your new marketing approach over time.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">But why is having a decent marketing strategy important? Without a roadmap, it\'s very easy to go through your marketing resources without any kind of movement toward desired goals. When too many options are available, it is very distracting and often causes you to lose track of what is working and what isn\'t.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The proper strategy in marketing will ensure that you\'re using targeting with a purpose to reach your goals and that you have systems in place to monitor and measure results. This way, as your business grows and changes, you can course-correct if or when necessary.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Storm Cloud Marketing, the team believes strategy underpins everything it does. Whether you need advertising, website design, or even a promotional video, be sure the company will be talking strategy before it gets down to it. It will not give you anything that looks good but give you something that works.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We\'ve been a partner to hundreds of businesses from global brands to local shops, helping them fight and tame the marketing monster as a comprehensive, long-term partner, OR by executing a single piece of their marketing strategy.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'storm-cloud-marketing-helps-your-business-discover-execute-and-optimize-effective-marketing-strategies', '2023-05-11', 'us/visionaries-network-dustin-storm-co-owner-storm-cloud-marketing.webp', 6, 'profile', 'Storm Cloud Marketing | Strategy & Growth Experts', 'Storm Cloud Marketing, marketing strategy, business growth, digital marketing, SEO, branding, content creation, PPC, social media, marketing agency, campaign optimization, visionaries network, creative services, marketing consulting, online marketing', 'Storm Cloud Marketing helps your business discover, execute, and optimize powerful strategies for growth and success.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.stormcloud.marketing/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/storm-cloud-marketing/', 'Storm Cloud Marketing', '1998', 'Joplin, Missouri'),
(45, 4, '<p><strong>Consultus Digital will generate more leads, sales, and revenue for your business than you thought possible</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">More than ever, today\'s fast-paced digital landscape demands the generation of leads, sales, and revenues that keep businesses thriving. Consultus Digital is the leading innovator in the digital marketing and sales enablement space; it renews how businesses look toward growth by offering pioneering solutions with results. Its unique blend of data, technology, and psychology powers Consultus Digital in accelerating business growth and reaching revenue targets for businesses.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Breaking Away from the Traditional Model</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Until Consultus Digital came up with this innovative approach, the conventional way of growing revenues was to generate more leads through different marketing strategies. Often, conventional ways bore little fruit. After having worked for years with hundreds of companies, one thing was clear: an increase in the volume of leads did not actually mean an increase in either sales or revenue. The reason was simple: antiquated sales systems were letting leads go to waste.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Consultus Digital knew developing a modern, scalable digital sales model complements digital marketing strategies. Since the company also has solutions for both digital marketing and sales functions, the two strategies could be aligned, ensuring performance in an optimal manner.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Digital Strategy Services that Steal the Spotlight</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Consultus Digital offers bespoke digital marketing strategies to help businesses stay ahead of the competition. A wide array of services is provided by the team at Consultus Digital, including:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Development of a Digital Marketing Strategy: An approach to traffic and lead generation, tailored.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Marketing Service: An integrated solution covering the development of websites and landing pages, search engine optimization, paid search management, conversion rate optimization, social media marketing, and robust measurement solutions.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Enablement of Sales: A progressive, technology-enabled approach to turbocharging the performance of sales.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>The Consultus Digital Process</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Consultus Digital invests a lot in each of their customer organizations to gain an understanding of their needs and goals. The company then looks for experts who can assist the client in laying a foundation by developing a website, among other things, and creating an overall digital marketing strategy.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Once the ground is laid, Consultus Digital works on lead acquisition through integrated inbound marketing strategies: search engine optimization, Google Ads, social media, and reputation management. The only thing that this company focuses on is performance marketing to increase leads and sales.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Selling and Modifying</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">After a lead generation, Consultus Digital undertakes the work of optimizing sales performance for clients. The organization introduces modern sales methodologies and technologies for the sales teams that provide the resources they need to close deals at a better rate.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">This incorporation of the whole practice within the CRM sales data of clients allows Consultus Digital to measure each and every campaign\'s effectiveness and to further evolve their strategies toward optimal performance.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Jake Matzanke, Director of Strategy</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Jake Matzanke, Director of Strategy and Partner at Consultus Digital, has spent over a decade in digital marketing and sales, working with hundreds of organizations. However, he has come to realize that there is a significant gap in his industry.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">What\'s that gap, you ask? It\'s the fact that many businesses he has worked with focus solely on generating leads, hoping that this will lead to increased revenue. But, all too often, new leads don\'t necessarily translate to increased sales or revenue. Jake has discovered that many of these companies lack modern sales processes, such as CRM systems, lead-flow routing, and automation. Additionally, they often miss opportunities to generate significant returns through cross-selling and up-selling to existing clients.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Jake has found that the traditional agency-client model only scratches the surface of what\'s needed to drive meaningful growth for these businesses. That\'s why he founded Consultus Digital - a unique blend of agency and consultancy services.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Consultus Digital, Jake takes a holistic approach to business growth. He immerses himself in his clients\' operations, transforming their sales and marketing strategies from the ground up. From inbound lead generation to sales enablement services (including CRM implementations and lead flow routing), Consultus Digital offers a comprehensive solution for businesses seeking sustainable growth and increased revenue.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;Our sales enablement arm supercharges how an organization sells by implementing modern technologies and methodologies such as chatbots, CRMs, proposal-building software, sales collateral, and much more.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'consultus-digital-will-generate-more-leads-sales-and-revenue-for-your-business-than-you-thought-possible', '2023-05-11', 'us/visionaries-network-jake-matzanke-director-consultus-digital.webp', 7, 'profile', 'Consultus Digital | Lead Generation & Revenue Growth', 'Consultus Digital, lead generation, digital marketing, sales growth, visionaries network, PPC, content marketing, online advertising, conversion optimization, social media, marketing agency, business growth, revenue boost, email marketing, digital strategy', 'Consultus Digital drives more leads, sales, and revenue for your business with expert marketing and growth strategies.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://consultusdigital.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/consultus-digital/', 'Consultus Digital', '2017', 'Toronto, ON'),
(46, 4, '<p><strong>Summit Digital Marketing\'s mission is to help its clients get found online and increase their reach, revenue, and impact</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">In today\'s digital age, having a strong online presence is crucial for businesses of all sizes and industries. With the rise of the internet and social media, customers are now more likely to search for products and services online rather than relying on traditional methods such as word of mouth or print advertisements. As a result, businesses that don\'t have a solid digital marketing strategy in place are at risk of falling behind their competitors and losing potential customers.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>The Benefits of Digital Marketing</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Digital marketing offers numerous benefits for businesses, including increased brand awareness, improved website traffic, and enhanced customer engagement. By having a professional website and engaging in various digital marketing activities, businesses can showcase their products and services to a wider audience, increasing their chances of attracting new customers and driving sales. Additionally, digital marketing provides businesses with valuable insights into customer behavior, allowing them to make data-driven decisions and optimize their marketing strategies for better results.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Pay-Per-Click Advertising (PPC)</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">One of the most effective forms of digital marketing is pay-per-click (PPC) advertising. PPC allows businesses to create targeted ads that appear on search engines and other websites, directing users to their website. With PPC, businesses only pay when a user clicks on their ad, making it a cost-effective way to generate leads and drive sales. By using keywords and targeting specific demographics, PPC campaigns can be highly targeted, allowing businesses to reach their ideal audience and increase their chances of conversion.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Search Engine Optimization (SEO)</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Another important aspect of digital marketing is search engine optimization (SEO). SEO involves optimizing a website\'s content and structure to improve its visibility in search engine results pages (SERPs). By using keywords and phrases strategically, creating high-quality content, and building high-quality backlinks, businesses can improve their website\'s ranking on search engines and increase their visibility to potential customers. With SEO, businesses can attract organic traffic and establish themselves as authority figures in their industry.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Google Ads Management</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Google Ads is one of the most popular forms of PPC advertising, allowing businesses to create targeted ads that appear on Google search results pages. With Google Ads management, businesses can create custom campaigns that target specific demographics, interests, and behaviors. By using Google Ads analytics tools, businesses can track the performance of their campaigns and make data-driven decisions to optimize their ads for better results.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Paid Media Marketing</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Paid media marketing involves using paid advertising channels such as social media platforms, online directories, and email marketing to promote a business\'s products or services. With paid media marketing, businesses can reach a wider audience and increase their brand awareness by targeting specific demographics and interests. By using paid media marketing analytics tools, businesses can track the performance of their campaigns and make data-driven decisions to optimize their ads for better results.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Digital Marketing Consulting</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Finally, digital marketing consulting involves providing expert advice and guidance to businesses looking to improve their digital marketing strategies. With digital marketing consulting, businesses can get personalized recommendations for improving their online presence, increasing their website traffic, and driving sales. By working with experienced digital marketing consultants, businesses can gain valuable insights into the latest digital marketing trends and best practices.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Roman, Founder &amp; CEO</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Ten years ago, Summit Digital Marketing was a one-Roman show! Fueled by his vision to change lives through marketing, Roman created Summit with no intention of hiring employees (and yet here Summit Digital Marketing is!). Like any Founder and CEO, Roman has worn a lot of hats over the years. After graduating from the Moody Bible Institute in Chicago with the intent to become a youth pastor, Roman felt called by God instead to help people through entrepreneurship and business.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Today he&rsquo;s doing just that and is beyond grateful for the relationships, impact, and opportunities that have come with this journey. Outside of Summit, Roman is a loving husband and father of two girls. He loves snowboarding, golfing, hosting parties, and rooting for the Vikings. His perfect day? Waking up early, spending a quiet morning by the fire praying and reading, followed by hitting the slopes snowboarding with his family! Roman is an entrepreneur who stays up to date on emerging tech and marketing trends to help clients and companies succeed.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We are a digital marketing agency based out of Denver, Colorado, that specializes in search engine optimization (SEO) and pay-per-click (PPC) advertising services, such as Google Ads and Facebook Advertising.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'summit-digital-marketings-mission-is-to-help-its-clients-get-found-online-and-increase-their-reach-revenue-and-impact', '2023-05-11', 'us/visionaries-network-roman-ceo-summit-digital-marketing.webp', 8, 'profile', 'Summit Digital Marketing | Grow Your Online Reach', 'Summit Digital Marketing, SEO, PPC, digital strategy, online visibility, lead generation, content marketing, paid ads, marketing agency, search marketing, website traffic, digital growth, business impact, visionaries network, revenue growth', 'Summit Digital Marketing helps you get found online and grow your reach, revenue, and impact through proven digital strategies.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.summitdigitalmarketing.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/summitdigitalmarketing/', 'Summit Digital Marketing', '2013', 'Colorado Springs, Colorado'),
(47, 4, '<p><strong>PeoplActive is an Anti-threat Cyber Squad dedicated to safeguarding your organization from the ever-evolving landscape of cyber threats</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">PeoplActive is a dedicated anti-threat cyber squad and cloud development partner that provides comprehensive solutions to safeguard your organization from cyber threats and help you achieve your cloud development goals. The company&rsquo;s team of experts is bold enough to confront the audacity of threat actors head-on and wise enough to stop threats by building a defense system that turns your organization\'s vulnerabilities into strengths. With their managed service model and deep subject matter expertise, they ensure that they keep you compliant and ready to tackle any cyber threat.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Precaution is the first step in counteracting ransomware attacks, and the company is here to guide you through the process.&nbsp; PeoplActive&rsquo;s team will work with you to identify potential vulnerabilities, implement robust security measures, and provide ongoing monitoring and maintenance to ensure your organization\'s safety. The company understands that every organization is unique, and its approach is tailored to meet your specific needs and requirements. From assessing your current security posture to developing a customized incident response plan, PeoplActive is committed to helping you stay ahead of the ever-evolving threat landscape.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In the world of cloud project development, unpredictability can be a major challenge. A new project\'s intricacy can snowball into an unmanageable job requiring extra hands. That\'s where PeoplActive\'s flexible hiring model comes in. It offers a pool of the top 5% of cloud developers from 150+ countries who have applied to its platform. Its rigorous vetting process ensures that its candidates have the skills and expertise required to deliver high-quality results. Its hiring model includes a high-quality/cost ratio, rigorous vetting, seniority tests, effective collaboration, and matching your timezone.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At PeoplActive, the team is proud to work with some of the world\'s most successful companies. Their clients appreciate their access to the latest technology, hassle-free management, client-specific offerings, and qualified and certified developers. The company offers customizable cloud staffing solutions tailored to your unique business requirements, making them the go-to partner for your digital transformation goals. Whether you\'re looking to modernize your cloud architecture, build secure and scalable cloud environments, or simply want to secure your applications and infrastructure, PeoplActive is here to help.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Finding the right talent is crucial to your project\'s success. That\'s why the organization developed a unique approach to talent sourcing. PeoplActive team of experts will work with you to understand your goals, technical needs, and team dynamics within 1 hour. They will then introduce you to the right talent for your project within 48 hours, with an average time to match of under 24 hours. You\'ll have the opportunity to get a first-hand understanding of their capabilities or skip to a small trial of hours to see if the fit is right.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At PeoplActive, the team is committed to delivering exceptional results that meet your unique business needs. Their team of experts has extensive experience in managed services, cloud consulting, and staffing, making them the perfect partner for your digital transformation goals. Whether you\'re looking for guidance on implementing a cloud strategy, building a secure cloud environment, or simply need help with day-to-day operations, PeoplActive here to help.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Kartik Donga, Founder</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Kartik Donga has been a pioneer in delivering innovative and forward-thinking solutions to clients across the globe, seamlessly combining technological expertise with business acumen. With over 20 years of experience, he has revolutionized the digital and cybersecurity sectors, leveraging Silicon Valley-caliber talent in Cloud, Cybersecurity, and DevOps to drive business transformation.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As the visionary leader behind Communication Crafts and PeoplActive, Kartik has spearheaded the growth of Fortune-500 companies and startups across the US, UK, Middle East, Australia, India, and APAC, driving 5X revenue growth from their tech operations.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Under his leadership, PeoplActive has established a robust foundation for its current focus on managed cybersecurity services, providing scalable and long-term solutions to empower brands. Specifically, PeoplActive has specialized in protecting sensitive data and ensuring operational integrity for healthcare providers worldwide.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In addition to his work at PeoplActive, Kartik is also leading Communication Crafts, guiding teams to deliver vision-led digital transformation services. His expertise spans technology product development, e-commerce platforms, and workforce solutions. With his unique blend of technological expertise and business acumen, Kartik has become a driving force in the industry, transforming the way businesses approach digital transformation.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;Our team is bold enough to confront the audacity of threat actors head-on and wise enough to stop threats by building a defense system that turns your organization&rsquo;s vulnerabilities into strengths.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'peoplactive-is-an-anti-threat-cyber-squad-dedicated-to-safeguarding-your-organization', '2023-05-11', 'us/visionaries-network-kartik-donga-founder-peoplactive.webp', 8, 'profile', 'PeoplActive | Cybersecurity & Threat Protection Experts', 'PeoplActive, cybersecurity, threat protection, cyber threats, network security, data protection, cyber defense, IT security, anti-threat solutions, cyber risk, endpoint security, visionaries network, cyber monitoring, breach prevention, cyber squad', 'PeoplActive is a dedicated Cyber Squad protecting your organization from evolving cyber threats with advanced security solutions.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://peoplactive.com/', 'https://peoplactive.com/', 'PeoplActive', '2020', 'Ahmedabad, Gujarat'),
(48, 5, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong>Steve Brown AI Futurist: Steve Brown assists businesses in developing AI transformation plans, leveraging his expertise as an AI specialist, futurist, and entrepreneur</strong></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As the world continues to grapple with the rapidly evolving landscape of artificial intelligence (AI), it\'s essential for companies to develop a comprehensive AI transformation strategy that harnesses the power of this technology to drive growth, innovation, and competitiveness. Steve Brown, a renowned AI expert, futurist, and entrepreneur, is at the forefront of this movement, helping organizations navigate the complexities of AI and its potential impact on various industries.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With over 30 years of experience in high-tech, including 25 years at Intel, where he served as Chief Evangelist and a futurist in Intel Labs, Brown has developed a unique understanding of the AI landscape. He has also worked at Google\'s AI research lab, DeepMind, where he led marketing, communications, and public affairs teams as Senior Director and served as the company\'s in-house futurist.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In his latest book, \"The Innovation Ultimatum: How Six Strategic Technologies Will Reshape Every Business in the 2020s\", Brown provides a comprehensive guide to digital transformation and innovation, offering practical advice on how companies can ride the AI wave and accelerate their AI transformation.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">As a thought leader on AI\'s impact on business, education, and society, Brown has spoken at numerous industry events and has appeared on major media outlets, including CNN, BBC, Bloomberg TV, ABC, NBC, CBS News, and Forbes. He is also an advisor to several companies, including Analog Computation Enterprises, a stealth startup building analog chips and AI software to significantly reduce energy consumption while delivering breakthrough performance.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In his keynotes and innovation workshops, Brown helps companies understand how generative AI, autonomous AI assistants, worker augmentation, and digital transformation will reshape various aspects of their business, including R&amp;D, sales &amp; marketing, operations, and customer service. He also explores the longer-term societal implications of the dawning of the Intelligence Era and the opportunities and risks presented by powerful new AI technologies.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Key Takeaways from Steve Brown\'s Keynotes</strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0cm;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\">Learn how to build an AI transformation strategy for your business</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\">Discover how companies use AI to elevate customer experience, streamline operations, and boost employee skills</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\">Understand the vital impact of AI on business and what you should do right now</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\">Explore the future trajectory of AI and its significance for us all</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\">Get practical advice to harness AI for competitive advantage and personal growth</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Whether you\'re looking to understand the basics of AI or navigate the complexities of AI transformation, Steve Brown\'s keynotes and innovation workshops offer valuable insights and practical advice to help you stay ahead of the curve. As a visionary AI futurist and expert in generative AI and machine learning, Brown is poised to help you unlock the full potential of AI and transform your business for the future.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\"><strong>Steve Brown, founder of Steve Brown AI Futurist</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Steve Brown brings a wealth of experience as a seasoned leader who has successfully driven digital transformation and innovation at top-tier tech companies, startups, and Fortune 100 corporations. With a proven track record of building high-performing teams and driving innovation, Steve is confident in his ability to lead meaningful change and growth for a purpose-driven organization.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Throughout his career, Steve has developed a unique skill set that combines technical expertise, business acumen, market insights, and people leadership skills. He has successfully led business transformation and managed global teams, leveraging his expertise in digital transformation, ideation, foresight, communication, and the latest artificial intelligence technologies, including transformers, LLMs, diffusion, and AI assistants. Steve\'s passion for harnessing the power of artificial intelligence to make a positive impact on people\'s lives drives him to continuously develop innovative solutions that improve daily life through digital technology.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">As a seasoned leader with a broad range of experience, Steve possesses a unique set of skills that enable him to drive digital transformation and innovation. He is skilled in applying cutting-edge artificial intelligence, machine learning, blockchain, and IoT technologies to drive business growth and improvement. Steve also excels in ideation and creative thinking, strategic planning and visioning, innovation leadership, and change management, global operations leadership and future casting, keynote speaking, and corporate spokesperson roles. His expertise spans multiple industries, allowing him to bring a unique perspective to any organization.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'steve-brown-ai-futurist', '2023-05-20', 'us/visionaries-network-steve-brown-ai-futurist.webp', 1001, 'cover', 'AI Futurist & Innovation Strategist | Steve Brown', 'Steve Brown, AI futurist, AI transformation, digital strategy, business innovation, AI specialist, keynote speaker, entrepreneur, future tech, AI consulting, emerging technology, tech trends, digital transformation, visionaries network, AI planning', 'Steve Brown helps businesses build AI transformation plans, bringing deep expertise as an AI futurist, specialist, and visionary entrepreneur.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.stevebrown.ai/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/aitransformation/', 'Steve Brown AI Futurist', '2014', 'Portland, Oregon'),
(49, 5, '<p><strong>Mindbreeze is a leading international provider of appliances and cloud services for enterprise search, applied artificial intelligence, and knowledge management</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">Mindbreeze is recognized as a leading global supplier of advanced appliances and cloud services, with a specialized focus on enterprise search, applied artificial intelligence (AI), and comprehensive knowledge management solutions. The company is dedicated to empowering international businesses by enhancing their operational processes, thereby driving efficiency and productivity. Headquartered in Chicago, Illinois, Mindbreeze also maintains a significant European presence with its headquarters located in Linz, Austria.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">This strategic positioning allows the company to effectively support clients across various time zones, ensuring that businesses receive timely assistance and solutions tailored to their unique needs. Mindbreeze\'s innovative offerings are trusted by major corporations worldwide, including industry giants such as Lufthansa, Daimler AG, Air France, and Freddie Mac.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">These organizations utilize Mindbreeze InSpire, the company&rsquo;s flagship product, to streamline essential business operations, improve decision-making, and harness the power of their data. The company is committed to staying at the forefront of technological advancements, continuously developing and refining its solutions to meet the evolving demands of the market.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">By focusing on innovation, Mindbreeze not only enhances the capabilities of its clients but also contributes to their long-term success and competitiveness in an increasingly digital landscape. As a result, Mindbreeze remains a pivotal player in the realm of enterprise search and knowledge management, consistently delivering value and driving transformation for its customers.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Data Protection and Security</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Data protection and security are of utmost importance at Mindbreeze. Being part of the Fabasoft Group, at Mindbreeze, the highest level of security and reliability is guaranteed by using the Fabasoft Cloud Services. Aside from the various international recognitions and awards it has gained so far, the company has obtained important international certifications in data protection and security, among others.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Web Accessibility Certificate</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Mindbreeze was therefore honored with the Web Accessibility Certificate (WACA), the first and only quality seal in Austria recognizing accessibility on the web in accordance with international W3C guidelines for the best web accessibility. For this reason, the website highly complies with the WCAG 2.1 - AA and therefore is silver awarded.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>K&uuml;nstliche Intelligenz</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Mindbreeze InSpire relies on artificial intelligence to extend knowledge acquisition through immersive presentation of customized and contextual results and process optimization. The company makes use of a wide variety of artificial intelligence techniques, from deep science to large language models, to enable interaction with employees and customers in a deeply personalized fashion.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Open Standards</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Mindbreeze trusts and supports open standards, such as ONNX, Open Neural Network Exchange, allowing the company to combine its enterprise search engine with large language models of various leading providers like DeepAI, Meta, or HuggingFace. This allows customers to create answers and insights from internal company data in a remarkably human-like manner.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Continuous Improvement</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Mindbreeze InSpire learns from user behavior and adapts to user needs over time. The company\'s relevance model relies on machine learning and neural networks to understand user behavior with a view to predicting which content is relevant.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Knowledge Management</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Mindbreeze InSpire also brings knowledge management features into the limelight, enabling enterprises to reveal insights into their data and knowledge. In fact, its solution enriches and extracts data from a diverse range of sources; analyzes the ingested content; and offers personalized, all-encompassing 360-degree views as ready-cooked presentations of the right information in the right context at just the right time.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Daniel Fallmann, Founder &amp; CEO&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Daniel Fallmann founded Mindbreeze in 2005 and as its CEO he is a living example of high quality and innovation standards. From the company&rsquo;s very beginning, Fallmann, together with his team, laid the foundation for the highly scalable and intelligent Mindbreeze InSpire appliance. His passion for enterprise search and machine learning in a big data environment fascinated not only the Mindbreeze employees but also their customers.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>\"Our aim is to offer the best total package for content analytics and enterprise search needs available on the market. We love to surprise and captivate our customers time and again with outstanding innovations.\"</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'mindbreeze-is-a-leading-international-provider-of-appliances-and-cloud-services-for-enterprise-search-applied-artificial-intelligence-and-knowledge-management', '2023-05-20', 'us/visionaries-network-daniel-fallman-founder-mindbreeze.webp', 1, 'profile', 'Enterprise Search & AI Solutions | Mindbreeze', 'Mindbreeze, enterprise search, AI solutions, cloud services, knowledge management, applied AI, data insights, search appliances, business intelligence, information retrieval, digital transformation, AI software, cloud computing, enterprise tools,visionaries network', 'Mindbreeze delivers advanced enterprise search, AI, and knowledge management through powerful appliances and cloud-based services for smarter business decisions.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://inspire.mindbreeze.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/mindbreeze', 'Mindbreeze', '2005', ' Linz, Upper Austria');
