(50, 5, '<p><strong>Quansight: Turning Data into Insights with Open-Source Software</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">Within the fast pace of change in the realms of artificial intelligence and machine learning, businesses are looking to new technologies as a way of innovating and keeping ahead of their competition. The open-source community and software developers worldwide working together on building and enhancing software that empowers AI and ML are at the heart of this process.<br><br>Quansight is a Data Science and Engineering company created by Travis Oliphant, one of the leading public figures in the Python data community, with prior key leadership and vision behind industry cornerstones like NumPy, SciPy, Conda, and Numba, and he has also greatly contributed to shaping NumFOCUS and the PyData Conference Series.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Travis\'s experience in the open-source community has given him the vantage point needed to build a team of top talent in the industry. More than half of the full-time technical staff at Quansight includes active contributors to open-source data projects, many of these contributors acting in leadership roles within their project communities. Lead contributors to the PyTorch project and one of the leading open-source machine-learning frameworks for building and training AI models, respectively, Quansight is building one of the largest teams of industry professionals in creating impactful software.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Quansight is committing to providing the highest level of custom support to its clients in succeeding with open-source software. Some of the kinds of services they are offering are PyTorch Quickstart, PyTorch Optimization, and PyTorch Training. Clients could build and optimize AI/ML systems with these services toward a newly created system or optimize existing systems.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Quansight leverages scientific Python plus its extensive library and tool ecosystem to deliver custom solutions that truly realize value out of data. The company empowers its clients and strengthens the open-source projects these leading technologies depend on with critical business insight and actionable knowledge.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Large Language Models are Revolutionizing AI</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Large language models are a hot topic across the AI industry, where companies are striving to glean competitive advantages from their capabilities. The implementation of LLMs could be an intense and intimidating job for newbies. Quansight\'s decades of experience within the Python data ecosystem put us in good stead to help clients navigate the pathway.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The company offers numerous services aimed at guiding clients on how to begin LLMs, in which LLMs can add the most value, the current LLMs assessment, and how to tune the existing LLMs. Whether the client needs help in developing an LLM system or tuning one, the company\'s team of experts is available to guide the client accordingly.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Preserving Privacy through Nebari</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">A major concern with most organizations that are deploying AI is how to keep privacy and security maintained. The Quansight Nebari platform is an enterprise data science and MLOps platform that is designed to be highly customizable for use in maintaining control over data. The use of Nebari to build AI workflows in-house lets clients keep data in-house, instead of risking privacy and using third-party vendors.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Nebari is built out as a managed integration of open-source technologies&mdash;Jupyter, Conda, Dask, and more. Following an infrastructure-as-code approach and abstracting away all the DevOps details, it gives a seamless way to deploying and maintaining a shared data science environment. Nebari gives a flexible solution that meets your needs, whether you deploy your AI workflows for on-site or cloud use.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Travis Oliphant, CEO</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Travis Oliphant, CEO of OpenTeams and Quansight, leads two companies that specialize in connecting companies with open-source communities and experts, enabling them to harness the power of data science, artificial intelligence, and machine learning. With over 20 years of experience in scientific computing, he has created and contributed to several widely used Python libraries and tools, including NumPy, SciPy, Numba, Conda, and Jupyter.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Travis\'s mission is to build successful businesses based on open-source principles while improving the way programs are written and data is analyzed. He enjoys taking complex concepts and bringing them to life by marshaling resources and people, simplifying complex ideas with programming, and developing products that make it easy for scientists, engineers, and others to leverage their domain expertise and utilize the computer as a general-purpose tool.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In addition to his roles at OpenTeams and Quansight, Travis serves as a strategic advisor to several startups and organizations in the data science and open-source space, including bodo.ai, Saturn Cloud, and NumFOCUS.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;Quansight&rsquo;s staff includes seasoned scientists, engineers, and developers with advanced degrees, and diverse and specialized domain expertise.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'quansight-turning-data-into-insights-with-open-source-software', '2023-05-20', 'us/visionaries-network-travis-oliphant-ceo-quansight.webp', 2, 'profile', 'Data Insights with Open-Source Tools | Quansight', 'Quansight, data insights, open-source software, data science, analytics, machine learning, Python, visionaries network, big data, open source, software development, data engineering, tech consulting, predictive analytics, scientific computing', 'Quansight transforms data into actionable insights using open-source software, empowering innovation in science, AI, and enterprise analytics.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://quansight.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/quansight/', 'Quansight', '2018', ' Austin, Texas'),
(51, 5, '<p><strong>Nerdery is a leading digital product consulting firm with strategists, designers, tech experts, and passionate Nerds</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">For two decades, Nerdery has blazed a trail in technology, driven by an unyielding fire for innovation and a relentless commitment to delivering game-changing business benefits for its clients. The company has always been guided by a bunch of nerds passionate about blowing beyond limits to help clients set sail on their more digital futures fueled by data-learned insights, AI, and multidisciplinary knowledge.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The mission, success, and driving engine at Nerdery are the core values of integrity, curiosity, and collaboration. They shape how the company delivers original solutions for its partners to set them apart in times of saturated markets. Nerdery empowers its team to act with ownership and drive progress and growth for not only the company but also its clients through the empowerment of their specialists with the establishment of a culture of adaptability, creativity, and continuous learning.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">One of the key differentiating characteristics of Nerdery can be found in its flexible engagement models, by design and for the nature of each client. Whether it is rendering the services of expert talents to work with an already existing team or being a full-service digital transformation solution, Nerdery approaches it with a view toward fulfilling the unique needs of each client.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Nerdery\'s flexible partnership model is very able to fit with existing teams offering clients the needed expert talent and cross-industry expertise, all matched with flexibility and scalability, in actuality not interrupting operations. This approach largely facilitates accelerated speed to impact and guaranteed development predictability through an agile methodology that otherwise helps in optimizing every resource.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Conversely, Nerdery offers them a full-service approach that gives clients a deep bench of experts who will take their vision from app, website, or major undertaking from concept to market. By offering strategy, delivery, and optimization services tailored to each specific use case, Nerds enables customers to take their digital products to market faster and with more confidence.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">So, what truly sets Nerdery apart from the rest? For one, the company is second to none in its ability to adapt to the new marketplace with its signature blend of speed and flexibility. In tune with its strategy to answer the peculiar needs of a client, Nerdery makes sure its approaches and teams are always appropriate to the current trajectory at any moment in time for a project.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Moreover, nobody else delivers every leg of the journey with measurable impact from the first sprint. With quick wins and constant progress, Nerdery drives deliverables and measurable business value in every step the client takes so that vetted investments can be realized and all established goals can be met.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With more than 20 years of proven digital expertise under its belt, Nerdery is well-poised to have a sense of what is next for its clients\' industries. Merging industry best practices with the latest in technology, Nerdery empowers clients to innovate and stay ahead of the curve.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Michael Schmidt, CEO</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Michael Schmidt is a seasoned leader with 20 years of experience in digital business consulting, where he is best known for solving complex business challenges and maximizing client outcomes through technology. He co-founded Nerdery in 2003, serving as CIO and then Chairman of Nerdery&rsquo;s Board of Directors until being named CEO in 2020.<br><br>During his tenure at Nerdery, Michael has helped organizations across a variety of industries make long-lasting, transformational change. As CEO, Michael is passionate about guiding clients in making an impact through digital technology &mdash; ultimately, improving the lives of their end-users while growing their business.<br><br>In 2014, Michael co-founded Prime Digital Academy, a full-stack engineering and UX bootcamp, and has also guided various startups across industries.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We work alongside our clients to understand their goals and build digital products that transform business, create enduring customer connections, and elevate the human experience.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'nerdery-is-a-leading-digital-product-consulting-firm-with-strategists-designers-tech-experts-and-passionate-nerds', '2023-05-20', 'us/visionaries-network-michael-schmidt-ceo-nerdery.webp', 3, 'profile', 'Digital Product Consulting Experts | Nerdery', 'Nerdery, digital consulting, product strategy, UX design, tech experts, innovation, software development, agile teams, digital transformation, product design, developers, user experience, consulting firm, technology solutions, digital strategy', 'Nerdery is a top digital product consulting firm, blending strategy, design, and tech expertise to build impactful digital experiences.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.nerdery.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/nerdery/', 'Nerdery', '2003', ' Edina, Minnesota'),
(52, 5, '<p><strong>Pendulum: Proactively identify risks and opportunities to provide actionable insights for brand, security, and government teams</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">Pendulum is a mission-driven company, deeply invested in making sure that its customers are proactively informed about online narratives. Since its founding, Pendulum has been about disrupting harmful threats to society. Indeed, such core tenets have remained central to Pendulum\'s mission even as the company itself evolved to take on the broader implications of a digital, interwoven world.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At the core of the Pendulum platform is a deep knowledge of the power of audio and video content in shaping public opinion. In today\'s digital age, where text is increasingly yesterday\'s news, Pendulum delivers the most unique insights into critical topics, communities, narratives, and claims they appear, how they spread, and what they mean-enabling customers to respond early and effectively to emerging trends and risks.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Pendulum\'s sophisticated AI makes the conversations of the internet a place where corporations are most vulnerable in a way no other technology has matched. By monitoring the social media platforms-from TikTok and YouTube to BitChute and Instagram- the platform identifies with precision where content travels at speed and rapidly processes with velocity high-volume data to summarize and report automatically.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">This will let communication teams be more proactive: plan for crises much in advance and accelerate decision-making. With Pendulum, it would be easy for teams to monitor broader brand discussions on multiple platforms and get key insights into main communities, audiences, and influencers.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Pendulum is designed with government agencies and risk intelligence departments in mind. Done using protected ML machinery, Pendulum processes huge datasets to identify critical intel and bring harmful content to the surface for better decision insights, which ensures organizations are always one step ahead.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Among its major features, Pendulum boasts its product RiskWand, which automates the work of horizon scanning by surfacing potential threats and synthesizing information into digestible stories. It will make rapid judgments about the importance of the latter to allow one to make better decisions in the process. Further, Pendulum\'s ElectionIQ solution offers a granular view of the online stories that define the 2024 US election and, in turn, shows how organizations can keep track of key issues, voices, and policy influencers.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">To that end, Pendulum has developed a platform to enable customers to take an active understanding of online narratives. Powered by leading-edge AI technology and a suite of proprietary ML algorithms, Pendulum provides unparalleled visibility of critical topics, communities, narratives, and claims. With Pendulum, an organization\'s corporate communications, public affairs, government agencies, or risk intelligence teams are empowered to remove their blind spots-to provide actionable insight that empowers better decision-making.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With comprehensive coverage across video, audio, and text content, Pendulum empowers organizations to pre-empt both risk and opportunity, stay ahead of the competition, and gain advantage. Automating horizon scanning and synthesizing insight data into digestible stories, Pendulum\'s platform modernizes the way organizations approach online narratives, making it easier for them to make informed decisions in today\'s fast-paced digital landscape.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Mark Listes, Chief Executive Officer and Co-Founder</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Mark Listes specializes in building and growing companies and organizations that address complex problems. As the current leader of Pendulum, he is focused on providing a real solution to mitigate the risks associated with harmful narratives. The company is currently hiring, and Mark encourages individuals with a passion for solving hard problems, combating mis/disinformation, or open-source intelligence to reach out.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Prior to his current role, Mark had a track record of building and growing organizations that tackled challenging problems in Defense Innovation, Nation-State Election Interference, early-stage company growth, and Civil/Voting Rights.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We operate across 75 different languages, supporting both search and result translation.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'pendulum-proactively-identify-risks-and-opportunities-to-provide-actionable-insights-for-brand-security-and-government-teams', '2023-05-20', 'us/visionaries-network-ceo-mark-listes-pendulum-intelligence.webp', 4, 'profile', 'Actionable Risk Insights Platform | Pendulum', 'Pendulum, risk detection, threat intelligence, brand protection, security insights, government tools, AI monitoring, proactive analysis, misinformation, social listening, reputation management, data insights, crisis response, visionaries network, predictive analytics', 'Pendulum helps brand, security, and government teams proactively identify risks and opportunities with AI-powered, actionable intelligence and insights.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://pendulumintel.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/pendulumintel/', 'Pendulum Intelligence, Inc.', '2021', ' Seattle'),
(53, 5, '<p><strong>Mavenoid is the Intelligent Support Platform specifically designed for products and devices</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">Today\'s fast-moving digital ecosystem has set the bar high for receiving seamless and effective support from the brands customers put their trust in. However, many organizations fail to offer timely and effective help, especially when it comes to hard, technically demanding issues that are too complicated for chatbots and too simple for a live agent. Enter Mavenoid&mdash;an AI-powered support solution that has revolutionized support since 2017&mdash;empowering leading product brands around the world.<br><br>The Mavenoid Virtual Assistant automates product support by surfacing the exact content to solve each customer\'s question&mdash;whether they\'re looking for a new product, troubleshooting, or ordering replacement parts. The result is an amazing 58%-plus self-service resolution rate, leaving customers satisfied and empowered to find answers for themselves.<br><br>But what truly sets Mavenoid apart is that it has the real ability for a successful understanding of how products and devices work so that customers can successfully troubleshoot&mdash;without any problems or a stuck customer-service loop due to a chatbot. The AI guiding all this has been specifically trained on the vagaries of product manufacture and maintenance, as well as conversation, to ensure that customers receive just the right information in very plain speech.<br><br>One of the features of the support solution through Mavenoid is its possibility to answer based on already existing support content or to design guided flows that would give detailed step-by-step instructions. This is an option of flexibility in the approach, letting the brand go for the one that suits the needs and preferences of its customers.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Another interesting feature is Vision Assist, which gives the user ability to simply scan ingeniously a product label through their phone or tablet to accurately identify the product when troubleshooting, registering for warranties, or ordering replacement parts.<br><br>For those issues that are more complicated and require human intervention, Mavenoid\'s Virtual Assistant easily fits into the ticketing workflows from platforms such as Zendesk, Salesforce, and others. This empowers agents to take over from where the AI has left off or continue to work with customers using their favorite channels.<br><br>The AI-powered content retrieval enables Mavenoid to help customers more effectively search through product documentation for the answers they need, saving them more than 50% on time per ticket. Therefore, the customer dissatisfaction reduces and it increases the productivity and efficiency level of the agent.<br><br>The feedback of agents is ingested by the Mavenoid AI while tickets are being resolved, in order to self-develop customer support flows in the direction of more self-service and the further elevation of resolution rates from automated tickets. A constant feedback loop ensures the continuous development and improvement of the support experience.<br><br>Another game-changer in the Mavenoid arsenal is One-Click Interactive Video Support. The agents can pause, zoom, and draw on a feed so that they can intuitively walk customers through complicated instructions. In summary, this makes the complex troubleshooting a breeze.<br><br>Use of a Dynamic Help Center will enable the management of problems before they turn into tickets: access to personalized support content&mdash;as necessitated by any customer&mdash;refers to FAQs, product manuals, video tutorials, and step-by-step guides.<br><br>And because global brands need to localize and create content in over 50 languages, Dynamic Help Center eases their burdens of managing support knowledge. Agents can also log into their own Help Center to be able to share personalized solutions with customers in a snap.<br><br>Beyond that, with this AI-based support solution, you can get insights into customer behavior and preferences that often only other brands would dream of. They can track cases of self-service and live support resolution, the performance of each piece of support content, and when customers abandon a troubleshooting flow&mdash;all from one dashboard.<br><br>Besides, the Insights module of Mavenoid provides valuable data on customer behavior, which will help in identifying common anomalies in product operation or issues about which customers are getting confused. That information can be used to improve products and services geared toward customer support, changing this cost into a profit generator.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;Our purpose-built technology delivers best-in-class customer support with intelligent troubleshooting and personalized remote support that delivers resolution rates of 58% and up.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'mavenoid-is-the-intelligent-support-platform-specifically-designed-for-products-and-devices', '2023-05-20', 'us/visionaries-network-gintautas-miliauskas-ceo.webp', 5, 'profile', 'Intelligent Product Support Platform | Mavenoid', 'Mavenoid, intelligent support, product support, device support, AI support platform, customer service, automated help, troubleshooting, technical support, self-service, chatbot, support tools, tech support, visionaries network, product assistance', 'Mavenoid is the intelligent support platform built for products and devices, enabling fast, automated, and scalable customer support solutions.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.mavenoid.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/mavenoid/', 'Mavenoid', '2017', 'Stockholm'),
(54, 5, '<p><strong>Satori: A Data Security Platform that allows data teams to enable users with fast data and meet security and compliance requirements</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">In today\'s fast-paced digital landscape, organizations must be agile and adaptable to remain competitive. This is particularly true for companies seeking to become AI-ready. To achieve this, organizations need to implement data security controls that enable them to move quickly while maintaining control over sensitive data. This is where Satori, a data security platform comes in.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Unlike other solutions that manage security controls on the underlying data stores, Satori\'s innovative platform doesn\'t require any changes to your data, schema, or user interactions with data. This means that organizations can implement data security controls quickly and easily, without disrupting their operations.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>AI and Data Compliance: A Perfect Pair</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Compliance requirements can be a significant obstacle to implementing AI and data analytics projects. However, with Satori\'s Data Security Platform, organizations can disarm compliance requirements out of the box. By gaining visibility into where sensitive data is stored, who can access it, and why, organizations can ensure complete control over sensitive data access.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Moreover, Satori\'s platform enables organizations to set dynamic security policies that govern access to sensitive data. This includes redacting sensitive data and enforcing policies that ensure compliance with regulatory requirements.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Fast AI Reliability: The Key to Success</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Building and maintaining AI models requires fast and reliable access to data. Satori\'s Data Security Platform provides the visibility and policy enforcement needed to ensure that AI models are built on a foundation of secure and governed data.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">By using Satori\'s platform, organizations can gain real-time insights into their data and ensure that AI models are trained on accurate and reliable data. This enables organizations to make informed decisions quickly and confidently.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>The Power of Data Governance</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Data governance is critical for organizations seeking to become AI Ready. By providing a single platform for managing data access, security, and compliance, Satori\'s Data Security Platform enables organizations to govern their data effectively.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With Satori\'s platform, organizations can set access and security policies once and then sit back and let users use the Data Portal to access data immediately. This ensures that data is accessed securely and compliantly, while also providing visibility into who has accessed what data and when.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Key Capabilities</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Satori\'s Data Security Platform offers a range of key capabilities that make it an ideal solution for organizations seeking to become AI-ready. These include:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Access Management: Automatic access management that simplifies permissions over all diverse ML and BI stacks.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Privacy Policies: Continuously classify and tag sensitive data and implement security and privacy policies dynamically.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Data Activity Audit &amp; Monitoring: Not knowing who is accessing what data and when creates a security and compliance risk.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Universal Data Access Audit: Simplified setup with a single location for data access logs even across multiple data stores.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Eldad Chai, Co-Founder and Chief Executive Officer</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Before establishing Satori, Eldad served as the Senior Vice President of Product Management and a member of the senior leadership team at Imperva. Prior to this, he was one of the founding members of Incapsula, a cloud-based web applications security and acceleration company, where he led the product, research, and sales divisions until the company was acquired by Imperva in 2014.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In his personal life, Eldad is an avid learner who spends most of his free time reading books, learning from people and experiences, and exploring new ideas. He enjoys spending time outdoors with his family, whether it\'s trekking in Nepal, taking an RV trip in Austria, or relaxing on the beach in Thailand.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Eldad holds a Bachelor\'s and Master\'s degree in Communication Systems Engineering from Ben-Gurion University.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We continuously discover sensitive data across data stores and dynamically track data usage while applying relevant security policies.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'satori-a-data-security-platform-that-allows-data-teams-to-enable-users-with-fast-data-and-meet-security-and-compliance-requirements', '2023-05-20', 'us/visionaries-network-eldad-chai-ceo.webp', 6, 'profile', 'Secure Data Access Made Easy | Satori', 'Satori, data security, data access, compliance, data governance, privacy, security platform, fast data, secure analytics, user access control, data protection, regulatory compliance, secure sharing, visionaries network, cloud security', 'Satori is a data security platform that empowers teams to deliver fast, secure data access while ensuring compliance and governance.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://satoricyber.com/', 'https://il.linkedin.com/company/satori', 'Satori Cyber', '2019', ' Rehovot'),
(55, 5, '<p><strong>Glorium Technologies is a full-service app and software development company that meets unique client needs with top technology solutions</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">Glorium Technologies is developing apps and software up to the point of delivery on concrete business goals for a client using the most suitable technology solutions. Custom software development services offer an opportunity to get an off-the-shelf product that is sure to cover all the particular needs of the company. This, in turn, presents such advantages as personalization, cost-effectiveness, scalability, improved security, and strategic competitive advantages over off-the-shelf software.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Custom software development is the process of conceptualizing software in a way that exactly matches a company\'s requirements. Custom software is not like other generic software applications on the market. It is a special design addressed to a certain business activity to serve a particular role in concretizing made operations better and achieving a competitive business advantage through a rare application. Developing such software is a specialty that the custom software development agencies concentrate on by providing unique solutions to businesses, taking into account the cost for developing custom software.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>The Process of Solving Custom Software</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The process of solving custom software is multi-faceted and incorporates several pivotal stages in the said process. All stages have their role in play at what they are supposed to do. It is from there that the outcome of a software project remains successful. These stages encompass:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Requirement Analysis</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Design and Architecture</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Development and Testing</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Deployment</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Maintenance</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">By following these stages, you can ensure that your custom software project is well-planned, well-executed, and meets the needs of your business.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Choosing the Right Custom Software Development Company</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Selecting the right custom software development company is a strategic decision that can either make or break the success of the software project. In the process of hiring a custom software development company, there are a number of factors to take into consideration which include:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Technologies, programming languages, and areas of specialization of the company</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The general experience of the industry</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Work portfolio and feedback from previous clients as testimonials</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Various pricing models</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Geographical location</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">And almost every other possible factor that could impact the output of the software project.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>The Role of Agile Methodology in Custom Software Development</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">An agile methodology plays an immense role in the creation of customized software by the means of flexibility, adaptability, and constant improvement. Agile development methodology is indicated by being swift in practice, flexible in its adaptability, and adaptive with the need for transparent communication to breed collective responsibility and progress.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Emerging technologies in artificial intelligence, IoT, and cloud computing are redesigning the landscape for custom software development with smart capabilities and increased connectivity. New capabilities include the ability to learn and self-correct through data interactions over time, enable real-time monitoring, and automation, and incorporate scalability together with cutting-edge security.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Real-World Examples of Successful Custom Software Development Projects</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Custom software development has been at the core of the innovation and efficiency paramount to myriad industries. From increasing sales productivity within the tile manufacturing industry to promoting better patient engagement within the healthcare sector, custom software development has enabled creativity and enhanced activity in production.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Andrei Kasyanau, Co-founder and CEO</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As the co-founder and CEO of Glorium Technologies, Andrei Kasyanau brings a unique blend of corporate and entrepreneurial experience to the table. Having worked with financial giants and built his own business from the ground up, he understands the importance of agile product development.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Glorium, Kasyanau\'s team specializes in providing tech startups with on-demand agile product development services, enabling them to reduce their time to market by up to 30% and save 40% compared to in-house teams.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As a devoted father of four, Kasyanau is known for his passion for family and adventure. When he\'s not working, he can be found exploring new cultures and traditions as a seasoned traveler, having visited over 30 countries before COVID.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Kasyanau is also an adrenaline junkie who enjoys extreme activities like skiing, hiking, sailing, flying, and kite-surfing. He\'s always looking for someone to join him on these adventures and drag him away from his desk!</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We understand that your business is constantly evolving and dynamic, and we\'re here to help you keep up. Our solutions are flexible and scalable, thanks to the collaborative environment we\'ve created for developing business innovations.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'glorium-technologies-is-a-full-service-app-and-software-development-company-that-meets-unique-client-needs-with-top-technology-solutions', '2023-05-20', 'us/visionaries-network-adrei-kasyanau-ceo.webp', 7, 'profile', 'Custom App & Software Development | Glorium', 'Glorium Technologies, software development, visionaries network, custom solutions, tech company, full-service IT, mobile apps, web development, SaaS, product design, technology partner, enterprise software, software solutions, digital transformation, development services', 'Glorium Technologies delivers full-service app and software development, providing custom tech solutions tailored to each client&rsquo;s unique needs.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://gloriumtech.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/glorium-technologies/', 'Glorium Technologies ', '2010', ' Princeton, New Jersey'),
(56, 5, '<p><strong>Access Infinity aims to streamline decision-making and strategy development across a pharma product&rsquo;s life cycle</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">The pharmaceutical industry is indeed going through a phase of great change, mainly due to increasing demand for better efficiency and effectiveness in developing and distributing medicines. This is what several factors bring about: the escalations of cost in healthcare, the need for personalized medicine, and the enhanced importance of regulatory compliance. In such a scenario, pharmaceutical companies have no choice but to rethink their century-old practices and implement innovative strategies to compete in the market.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">One of the significant reasons for this shift is the pressure to reduce the time and cost involved in bringing new drugs into the market. It is estimated that the time needed to bring drugs to the market exceeds ten years, which is also expensive and runs into billions of dollars.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In this way, companies have to make their operations faster and more efficient. This has led to the adaptation of sophisticated technologies such as artificial intelligence machine learning, and big data analytics as R&amp;D processes can be greatly improved using these technologies. Companies can quickly identify potential drug candidates and optimize the design of clinical trials, enhancing recruitment as well as retention of patients.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The company Access Infinity is a consultancy firm that initially began offering services in 2014 for pharmaceutical firms to find their way in the path that will propel them forward into new challenges. It started by providing the strategies and means of attaining market access as well as its appropriate pricing for pharma businesses. As the company progressed, so did its offerings; over the years, Access Infinity expanded for innovative digital tools-from Access Hub, and Evidence Hub, to Nuro-to aid decisions and strategy development at every stage of a product\'s life cycle.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The heart of Access Infinity\'s approach is built upon a foundation of collaboration, excellence, and care. The company values are encapsulated in this trinity, guiding it in work with clients and employees in the same manner. Whether it\'s culture-building, hard work dedicated to excellence, or being really concerned about the well-being of both its employees and clients, Access Infinity has only the best of results in store.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The innovation that Access Infinity introduces to the market, in relation to a powerful digital platform, involves eliciting data-based insights on everything from pricing to clinical trials to HTA, or Health Technology Assessment. Users can access all the information in one place, compare and contrast the data points side by side, and export insights in a range of formats. It is a very potent tool meant to support pharma companies in making more informed decisions and ultimately in staying ahead of their competition.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Yet another addition to the Access Infinity portfolio is Evidence Hub, the continuously updated library of value messages and evidence. Through that channel, users collect and catalog all the support evidence of an asset\'s value story: getting automatic updates and a living evidence base for your asset. Such innovative solution helps streamline processes in evidence management by pharma companies while they make more informed choices about their products.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As one of the leading market access consultancy firms, Infinity has an exceptionally good experience working with its customers to deliver over 1,500 projects and support over 250 brands that have entered the market. The firm extends its reach across three continents and currently engages more than 40 market access consultants in over 40 countries. The strong network of this firm therefore provides it with unmatched insights and support supplied to the clients.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Not only does Access Infinity\'s team consist of experts and global reach, but also great skills and attention to detail. The company conducts interviews in-house with a talented multi-lingual team and can, therefore, provide an accurate transcript and soundbites that are useful for decision-making purposes for the clients.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Shrinivas Rao Mukku, Founding Director</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Shri has over 14 years of industry experience, working with firms like Merck and Lundbeck, Access Partnership, and Double Helix. Shri has a PhD from the Asian Institute of Technology and an MPhil from the University of Cambridge.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We believe in recognizing achievements, big or small, and fostering a culture of celebration that motivates our team to progress together as a collective.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'access-infinity-aims-to-streamline-decision-making-and-strategy-development-across-a-pharma-products-life-cycle', '2023-05-20', 'us/visionaries-network-shrinivas-rao-founding director-access-infinity.webp', 8, 'profile', 'Pharma Strategy & Insights Platform | Access Infinity', 'Access Infinity, pharma strategy, decision-making, product lifecycle, market access, healthcare analytics, pharmaceutical insights, drug development, pricing strategy, pharma consulting, data-driven decisions, lifecycle management, visionaries network, market intelligence, biopharma solutions', 'Access Infinity streamlines pharma decision-making and strategy development across the entire product life cycle with data-driven insights.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://accessinfinity.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/accessinfinity/', 'Access Infinity', '2014', 'London, England'),
(57, 5, '<p><strong>Hammerspace: A High Performance, Global Data Environment connecting data with users and applications, anywhere, anytime</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Hammerspace is a ground-breaking software company practically re-setting how data can be used and maintained. The Global Data Platform integrates unstructured data from sites, clouds, and storage systems with extreme parallel performance for AI, GPU, and high-speed analytics to transform how unstructured data is stored. With Hammerspace, organizations stop the miseries of data silos, and its data can become an instantly available resource no matter where users or applications reside.<br><br><strong>Electronic Design Automation (EDA)</strong><br><br>The EDA is one of those industries that are well-renowned for their dynamic and performance-driven environment. With the increasing complexity in semiconductor designs, the need for EDA teams to rapidly access storage and compute that is high-bandwidth and low-latency becomes inherent for meeting demanding power and performance goals. However, traditional IT infrastructure and legacy solutions fall short in handling these demands.<br><br>Hammerspace addresses these challenges with its leading-edge solution for a high-performance global file system, combined with flexibility in cloud compute and storage resourcing. EDA teams can now quickly provision and scale pipelines as demands change with high-performance application workloads. Hammerspace nodes are designed to push data through at the maximum instance and network infrastructure throughput, while the Hammerspace cluster dynamically scales out to concurrently handle any volume of workloads.<br><br><strong>The Hammerspace Difference</strong><br><br>The Hammerspace solution delivers a number of benefits for EDA teams:<br><br>Remote workforce: Utilize heterogeneous HPC cluster and cloud compute resources with linear performance scalability.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Iteration acceleration: Empower the creative departments using a single data set to shrink the cycle of production.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Hybrid cloud: Automate orchestration and data management across data center and cloud region.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Life Sciences</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Finally, data management and infrastructure issues in most of the Life Sciences form the biggest challenge ever. With the genomically related decoding complexity, Cryo-EM microscopy, imaging devices, and many others, researchers require access to huge volumes of data to support discovery processes. Traditional storage often struggles to meet these demands, leading to delays.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The Hammerspace solution eliminates all these challenges by providing a latently coherent data environment that allows users, applications, and cloud services to always access appropriate data wherever it is. This will provide further power and allow researchers to create, analyze, and manage creative projects throughout the project lifecycle: from origin through collaborative to archive longitudinally in a distributed environment.<br><br><strong>Hammerspace Solution</strong><br><br>While being the enabler for Life Sciences researchers, Hammerspace offers the following advantages or benefits:<br><br><strong>Create: </strong>High-performance data creation maintains the instruments operating at full speed.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Analyze: </strong>Share datasets over multiple file protocols and allow different application workflows to simultaneously modify them.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Collaborate: </strong>Automated data orchestration to remote teams and distributed data services in the cloud without making multiple copies of data.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Retain: Secure, policy-driven data tiering and data protection.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>David Flynn, Chief Executive Officer</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Hammerspace Co-founder and Chief Executive Officer David Flynn is a recognized leader in IT innovation who has been architecting disruptive computing platforms since his early work in supercomputing and Linux systems.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">David pioneered the use of flash for enterprise application acceleration as founder and former CEO of Fusion-io, which was acquired by SanDisk in 2014. He served as Fusion-io President and CEO until May 2013 and board member until July 2013. As Fusion-io CEO, David was responsible for the company&rsquo;s strategic direction, oversaw all operations and was the visionary behind the company&rsquo;s innovative technology and market strategy. Preceding his position as CEO, David was Fusion-io technical found and CTO, where he created the company&rsquo;s foundational research and development efforts, as well as the development of short- and long-term technological roadmaps.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Previously, David served as Chief-Architect at Linux Networx where he was instrumental in the creation of the OpenFabrics stack and designed several of the world&rsquo;s largest supercomputers leveraging Linux clustering, InfiniBand, RDMA-based technologies. Also, David served as Project BlackDog&rsquo;s Chief Scientist and Vice President of Engineering. He has also held positions Network Computer Inc and Liberate Technologies, a spin-off of Oracle Corporation, developing thin-client solutions.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">David holds more than 100 patents in areas across web browser technologies, mobile device management, network switching and protocols to distributed storage systems. He earned a bachelor&rsquo;s degree in computer science at Brigham Young University and serves on boards for several organizations and startup companies.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;Hammerspace is radically changing how unstructured data is used and preserved. Our Global Data Platform unifies unstructured data across edge, data centers, and clouds.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'hammerspace-a-high-performance-global-data-environment-connecting-data-with-users-and-applications-anywhere-anytime', '2023-05-20', 'us/visionaries-network-david-flynn-ceo-hammerspace.webp', 9, 'profile', 'High-Performance Global Data Platform | Hammerspace', 'Hammerspace, global data, data environment, high performance, data access, hybrid cloud, data orchestration, file system, data mobility, storage solution, cloud storage, distributed data, visionaries network, IT infrastructure, unified data', 'Hammerspace delivers a high-performance global data environment, connecting data to users and applications anytime, anywhere across hybrid and multi-cloud systems.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://hammerspace.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/hammerspace/', 'Hammerspace', '2018', 'San Mateo, California');
