(58, 6, '<p><strong>RTS transforms industries with high-quality IT services, consulting, and implementation solutions</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Resolve Tech Solutions (RTS) prides itself on being the pioneer of tomorrow\'s technology landscape. Their mission goes beyond modernization and transformation; it\'s about breathing new life into industries and redefining what\'s possible. As a trusted IT partner for many businesses, RTS caters to a diverse range of industries, including utilities, oil &amp; gas, telecom, retail, government, aerospace, defense, finance, and real estate.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At the heart of RTS lies its dedication to customer success and its collaborative, transparent culture. This ethos drives them to deliver innovative and effective solutions that keep their clients at the forefront of their industries. RTS\' prowess in SAP services and cloud technology has earned them the title of the largest SAP services partner in North America for seven consecutive years.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>RTS Vision and Mission</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">RTS envisions a world where digital and AI technologies drive limitless possibilities. They believe in enabling their customers to realize the full potential of transforming into a digital enterprise. RTS\' mission is to accelerate their customers\' technology transition with their commitment to continuous innovation, cutting-edge solutions, and developing and retaining the best talent.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>How Can RTS Help Your Business?</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Resolve Tech Solutions is an award-winning mid-sized consulting and IT services firm, headquartered in Dallas, Texas. They specialize in helping organizations achieve their IT modernization goals through core business system modernization and migrations, digital transformation services such as custom application modernization, data modernization, cloud-native and mobile development, and AI/ML and RPA enablement.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><img style=\"float: right;\" src=\"../../story_image_upload/us/Resolve-Tech-Solutions_cover.jpg\" alt=\"image\" width=\"197\" height=\"259\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">RTS Core Values</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">RTS\' core values define their culture and the behaviors needed to drive success in their organization:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Customer Centricity:</strong> RTS is unwavering in their commitment to placing their customers at the center of everything they do. They actively listen to their needs, understand their challenges, and tailor their solutions to exceed their expectations.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Resiliency:</strong> In an ever-evolving landscape, RTS embraces change and adapts with agility. They view challenges as opportunities for growth and learning.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Trust:</strong> Trust is the bedrock of RTS\' relationships&mdash;with their clients, partners, and colleagues. They foster trust through transparency, integrity, data-driven decisions, and consistently delivering on their promises.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Collaboration:</strong> RTS believes in the power of collaboration. Together, they achieve more. They encourage an inclusive and collaborative work culture where diverse perspectives are valued.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Innovation: </strong>RTS fosters a culture that encourages creativity and the pursuit of groundbreaking solutions. Using data-driven decisions, they are unafraid to challenge the status quo and explore new frontiers in technology.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Intelligent Enterprise Transformation</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">SAP S/4HANA can transform all critical enterprise functions from finance and supply chain to customer service and marketing. It enables businesses to transact, analyze, and predict in real-time, in an increasingly unpredictable world. RTS is SAP\'s leading business partner and the first to work with SAP end-to-end from product innovation to development and delivery of SAP S/4HANA and new industry solutions.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Explore and Employ Novel Ways to Stay Competitive and Grow</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The pressure to innovate groundbreaking, sustainable value for customers and the business is relentless&mdash;and it\'s not going away anytime soon. RTS\' S/4HANA Migration Advisory Services helps solve business challenges quickly with less costs and risk by fostering innovation, nurturing new ideas, and building strong offerings&mdash;all while they reap the full value of their investment in SAP solutions.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>AWS Cloud</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Managing a large number of cloud instances can be a daunting task. As companies scale and expand their cloud infrastructure, it becomes essential to optimize costs, ensure performance, and maintain security across their AWS environment. That\'s where RTS\' AWS Cloud Management Services come in. With robust experience in cloud management, RTS specializes in helping companies like theirs efficiently manage and maximize the potential of their AWS infrastructure.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Cloud Migration Made Easy for Government Agencies</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Tarrant County is part of the Dallas&ndash;Fort Worth metroplex, the fourth-largest metropolitan area in the United States. The county is home to a diverse economy, with major industries including aerospace, defense, energy, healthcare, and logistics. In 2022 Tarrant County, Texas, was facing a challenge: one of their existing on-premises applications was outdated and no longer meeting their needs. They needed to find a way to transition to a cloud-hosted environment, but they needed a company with expertise in AWS GovCloud that was ITAR compliant.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Benefits of Moving to the Cloud with RTS</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">By partnering with RTS for your cloud migration needs, you can enjoy:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Efficient Cost Optimization:</strong> RTS\' experts will conduct a thorough analysis of your AWS usage, identifying cost-saving opportunities without compromising performance.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Performance Monitoring and Optimization:</strong> RTS\' team will proactively monitor your AWS infrastructure, utilizing advanced monitoring tools to identify performance bottlenecks and address them promptly.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Security and Compliance: </strong>RTS has extensive expertise in AWS security best practices and can assist you in implementing robust security measures to safeguard your sensitive information.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Automation and Scalability: </strong>RTS\' team specializes in designing and implementing automated solutions that enable rapid scalability, ensuring that your AWS environment can keep up with your organization\'s evolving demands.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>24/7 Support and Expert Guidance:</strong> RTS\' team of AWS experts is available round-the-clock to provide support, answer your questions, and offer expert guidance whenever you need it.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">By partnering with Resolve Tech Solutions (RTS), you can revolutionize your digital landscape by leveraging cutting-edge technology solutions that drive limitless possibilities.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We envision a world where digital and AI technologies drive limitless possibilities. We believe in enabling our customers to realize the full potential of transforming into a digital enterprise.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'rts-transforms-industries-with-high-quality-it-services-consulting-and-implementation-solutions', '2025-01-19', 'us/visionaries-network-vinod-ceo-rts.webp', 1001, 'cover', 'IT Services & Consulting Solutions | RTS', 'RTS, IT services, consulting, implementation, digital transformation, tech solutions, enterprise IT, managed services, system integration, cloud services, IT strategy, business technology, software solutions, visionaries network, IT support', 'RTS transforms industries with top-tier IT services, expert consulting, and implementation solutions that drive innovation and efficiency.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.resolvetech.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/resolve-tech-solutions/', 'Resolve Tech Solutions', '2010', ' Addison, TX'),
(59, 6, '<p><strong>Vertical Motion: A trusted Canadian software development and entrepreneur assistance company</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">A highly respected, award-winning leader in technology, Vertical Motion has supported the global initiatives of startups, non-profits, and B2B and B2C businesses since 2006. Headquartered in Calgary and Kelowna with team members coast to coast, the firm has established a position of leadership as a partner of choice within software development and support for entrepreneurs.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">For the team at Vertical Motion, success is over and above. This, they achieved in an attempt to always leave anything better than the way they find it by streamlining processes, empowering employees, and strengthening entrepreneurs. They <em>\"Fight for Clarity\" </em>with a vital and meaningful understanding of their clients and their problems.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The core values it upholds include creating passionately, speaking with its actions, innovating empathetically, achieving quality through persistence, and showing dauntless curiosity. These fuel the commitment to deliver high-value solutions to the needs of their clients.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Vertical Motion proudly supports the Coalition for App Fairness seeking a level playing field for the app business and giving people freedom of choice on devices. This coalition unites all innovators from startups to small developers, indie studios, and first-time creators with one goal in mind: to create equal opportunities for all app developers to innovate and engage in commerce.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The software development team develops native, cross-platform, and PWA for B2B and B2C customers. By gathering more than a decade of industry experience, they have developed custom web, iPhone, Android, and Windows solutions across various industries.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Apart from software development, Vertical Motion also presents AI integration services. They support customers in implementing AI to rationalize operations, and customer experiences, exploiting data analytics, or introducing unparalleled innovation. Through the Canada Digital Adoption Program (CDAP), qualified Canadian organizations could receive non-dilutive funding up to a maximum of $15,000, 0% interest loans up to $100,000, and $7,300 in wage subsidies.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The mobile app development team in the company helps its clients plan, design, develop, and test mobile applications to improve enterprise productivity, efficiency, and employee satisfaction. Equipped with unrivaled functionality and seamless integration, businesses can have confidence that their employees are set up for success from anywhere.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Vertical Motion works to keep up with the latest technologies and trends within the industry. They are quite aware of how innovation helps to power business growth and take it very seriously that their customers have goals they want to accomplish. Whether it\'s taking new products to market for a startup or streamlining internal operations for an established business, Vertical Motion is ready to help.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Jason Jones, President</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Jason launched Vertical Motion in 2006 and has since grown the business to be one of Canada&rsquo;s top software and application developers. Besides running and managing his business, Jason predominantly dedicates his time to advising founders and entrepreneurs through Vertical Motion\'s Product Launch and C-Suite on-demand services.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As a well-regarded member of the entrepreneur community, Jason plays a pivotal role in shaping the next generation of startups as an Executive in Residence (EiR) at Foresight Canada and a Business Mentor at Futurpreneur Canada. Jason is regarded by his peers as a practiced leader, self-starter, and visionary who effectively articulates both high-level business concepts and intricate technical details in a way that experienced and novice founders can comprehend. His strong commitment to supporting his clients coupled with his genuine care for their business creates an open space for creativity, innovation, and growth.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;Our team of executive advisors, project managers, software developers, business analysts, marketing specialists, and graphic designers have extensive experience in several industries.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'vertical-motion-a-trusted-canadian-software-development-and-entrepreneur-assistance-company', '2025-01-19', 'us/visionaries-network-president-jason-jones.webp', 1, 'profile', 'Trusted Canadian Software & Startup Support | Vertical Motion', 'Vertical Motion, software development, Canada tech, startup support, entrepreneur services, app development, custom software, IT consulting, business growth, tech solutions, visionaries network, mobile apps, digital strategy, product design, tech partner', 'Vertical Motion is a trusted Canadian company offering software development and entrepreneur assistance to drive innovation and business success.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.verticalmotion.ca/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/verticalmotion', 'Vertical Motion', '2006', ' Calgary, Alberta'),
(60, 6, '<p><strong>Deep Fork Technology helps businesses break through barriers with affordable custom software solutions</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">In 2013, Deep Fork Technology opened its doors to help business owners navigate the complex world of technology. Unlike many vendors who only see clients as a means to increase their bottom line, Deep Fork Technology takes a different approach. The company believes in joining your team, working together to drive your business forward, and celebrating your successes.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With over 9 years of experience, Deep Fork Technology has helped countless small and medium-sized businesses overcome the growing pains that hold them back from achieving their goals. Whether you\'re looking to simplify your process, keep up with growth, or move away from spreadsheets, Deep Fork Technology is the right partner for you.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Why Choose Deep Fork Technology?</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Deep Fork Technology, the team prides themself on their unique approach to software development. The company crafts custom solutions grounded in reliable technology and tailored to meet the specific needs of your business. Its collaborative approach ensures that you\'re always in the loop, and its transparent communication style makes it easy to understand the progress of your project.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Deep Fork Technology also believes in keeping things simple. It avoids using complex tech jargon and instead focuses on speaking your language, ensuring that you\'re always informed and in control.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Deep Fork Technology&rsquo;s Future Focus</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Deep Fork Technology, the team is committed to fostering long-lasting relationships with their clients. They believe that by working together, they can help you achieve your goals in the most efficient way possible.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Is Your Business Having Growing Pains?</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">If you\'re experiencing growing pains in your business, Deep Fork Technology is here to help. It&rsquo;s custom solutions can help simplify your process, keep up with growth, and move away from spreadsheets.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Simplifying Your Process</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">When starting out, businesses often use multiple pre-built solutions to manage different aspects of their process. However, as they grow, these solutions can become restrictive and difficult to manage. Deep Fork Technology&rsquo;s custom solutions can help you streamline your process, eliminating the need for multiple software solutions.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Keeping Up with Growth</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As your business grows, it\'s essential to have a scalable platform that can keep up with your needs. Deep Fork Technology can help you build an employee management, onboarding, or time management platform that will be adaptable to your future growth.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Moving Away from Spreadsheets</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Spreadsheets are often used to track data when businesses are starting out. However, as they grow, these spreadsheets can become cumbersome and difficult to manage. Deep Fork Technology can help you build a centralized portal where you can organize and track data from anywhere.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Why Build Applications in 2023?</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In today\'s market, mobile and web applications are crucial for success. Having an easily accessible platform that connects employees, manages processes, and generates sales on any device means business efficiency can be at an all-time high.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Reasons to Build Applications in 2023:</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">A Scalable Platform for Future Integrations: Having a simple platform that covers only a small portion of your process is restrictive. That\'s why Deep Fork Technology delivers a sturdy platform for future features to easily fit into.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Better Experience for Customers: Having services available on both mobile and desktop devices is a great way to engage with more customers. Web application development allows for better user experience and access to more complex functionality than normal web pages allow.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Easy Access to Business Data While Offline: Having a system like time-tracking or job management that can be done offline is perfect for businesses that need to track data in an offline environment.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Needing Functionality Only an App Can Handle: Native mobile apps offer access to native device features like geolocation, notifications, local storage, and more!</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">A Service Targeted to Mobile Users: Sometimes businesses like Uber offer a service that is only available on mobile devices. If you have a great app idea, having a free consultation with people who were once in your shoes is a great idea.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Why Get Web Design &amp; Development in 2023?</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">There\'s no question that your website is one of the most important aspects of business marketing today. But just having a website isn\'t enough. According to web credibility research from Stanford University, 75% of consumers judge a company\'s credibility based on the company\'s web design.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Reasons to Get Web Design &amp; Development in 2023</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The site is Not Mobile-Friendly: Over 55% of internet browsing occurs on mobile devices, and according to Google, 61% of users are unlikely to return to a site on mobile if it isn\'t fully responsive.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Ranking Very Low in Search Engines: One of the most important parts of a website is Search Engine Optimization (SEO). If users can\'t find your site, it won\'t matter how much great content is found on it.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The site is Loading Very Slowly: According to researchers, slow-loading websites cost retailers $2.6 billion in lost sales each year. Site speed is vital when trying to convert and keep users engaged.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Conversions are Low</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Needing to increase your conversion rate is a great reason to create or update an existing website. Once Deep Fork Technology has a clear understanding of who your target audience is, it can work to figure out the best way to convert them.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Needing a Slick Template</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">A big portion of Deep Fork Technology web design clients come to us with an outdated-looking site. Researchers found that 38% of users will stop engaging with a website that has an unattractive layout. If your website looks like it was made in the early 2000\'s, you are losing out on sales.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Kris Dillon, Founder</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Coming from a background of holding a CEO position for multiple corporate-sized companies, over time I felt that something just wasn\'t right. There was so much \'fluff\' stuffed into projects that it was hard for small businesses to purchase custom software. That\'s why I started Deep Fork.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We focus on building business relationships with the power of software, that last a lifetime.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'deep-fork-technology-helps-businesses-break-through-barriers-with-affordable-custom-software-solutions', '2025-01-19', 'us/visionaries-network-kris-dillon-founder-deep-fork.webp', 2, 'profile', 'Affordable Custom Software Solutions | Deep Fork Technology', 'custom software, Deep Fork Technology, business solutions, software development, tech partner, app development, affordable software, digital transformation, automation, IT services, system integration, technology consulting, software design, visionaries network, scalable solutions', 'Deep Fork Technology helps businesses overcome challenges with affordable, custom software solutions tailored to their unique needs.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://deepforktechnology.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/deepforktechnology', 'Deep Fork Technology ', '2011', ' Oklahoma City, OK'),
(61, 6, '<p><strong>Welcome Tech is the first digital platform providing immigrants the resources needed to thrive in a new country</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">America has been a land of opportunity for many, but most immigrants find their way in life around the States a bit difficult. Even though they can work and believe they can contribute to society, much of the products and services put forth for them are inadequate, miscalculated, and unrepresentative. This is where Welcome Tech jumps in: the company committed to building a future for immigration with complete solutions for immigrants and equipping them with what they need to succeed.<br><br>Welcome Technologies is in the business of understanding that immigrants have a resolve to conquer uncertainty and build a life full of possibility. The company further marries the breadth of its offerings with the depth of experience in building a trusted, community-powered solution tailored to their needs. This approach helps not only the immigrant but also encourages all Americans to share in the success of integrating immigrants into their cultural fabric.<br><br>Finally, Welcome Tech enables the potential of immigrants to strengthen society through delivering the services and support needed by millions to confidently settle in a new country. Its flagship platform, SABEResPODER, was designed to respond to just about any day-in-and-day-out practical need with which immigrants-whether due to language or cultural barriers-might be confronted in the United States.<br><br>SABEResPODER, Welcome Tech&rsquo;s community platform offers a range of services and tools: language classes, cultural orientation, and access to top-rated services. With more than 4 million Latinos who can genuinely rely on the website as a source of trusted information, education, and service, SABEResPODER has been the guiding portal for immigrants\' questions seeking answers and leadership.<br><br>Values of empathy, purpose, courage, trust, innovation, and honor are placed within Welcome Tech. It guides them in their mission to understand the needs of immigrants through changing and building a better society. How these values are plugged into the company is shown by its engagement to the quality of service and resources given out to its members.<br><br>One of the broad areas in which Welcome Tech provides support is in healthcare. This health and wellness program, named PODERsalud, offers hassle-free and reasonably priced medical services across the country, with discounts on dental care, prescription medications, and a host of other health-related expenses. With PODERsalud, members can have in-person and on-demand virtual consultations, besides saving money on various health services.<br><br>Welcome Tech is committed to creating a world with more approachable and hassle-free healthcare, while being on a simple pricing model that ensures considerable value and savings for its members. It is focused on allowing members to take responsibility for their health and well-being, no matter their situation.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Amir Hemmat, Co-Founder and CEO</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Amir Hemmat is the Co-Founder and CEO of Welcome Technologies, the &ldquo;digital Ellis Island&rdquo; and future global platform for immigration. Welcome is a venture-funded mobile tech platform helping immigrant communities connect to opportunity including the optimal information, products, and services they need to succeed in a new country. Welcome is currently focused on the U.S. Hispanic community, the largest immigrant community in the world, through its community platform SABEResPODER&reg; (SEP). The SEP brand and services reach over 9M community members a year across 50 US markets.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&ldquo;Welcome Tech\'s unparalleled consumer insights, first-party data, and proprietary technology to inform affordable, fair, and best-in-market custom solutions across key services.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We empower lives and communities for a better world through our trusted community-powered solution.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'welcome-tech-is-the-first-digital-platform-providing-immigrants-the-resources-needed-to-thrive-in-a-new-country', '2025-01-19', 'us/visionaries-network-welcome-tech-ceo.webp', 4, 'profile', 'Digital Platform for Immigrants | Welcome Tech', 'Welcome Tech, immigrant resources, digital platform, new country support, immigration help, cultural integration, financial services, legal support, housing, job search, visionaries network, healthcare access, community support, language tools, technology for immigrants', 'Welcome Tech is the first digital platform offering immigrants essential resources to succeed and thrive in a new country.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://welcome.tech/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/welcome-technologies-us', 'Welcome Technologies', '2010', 'Los Angeles, California'),
(62, 6, '<p><strong>Take control of your IT and technology security with iTology&rsquo;s managed IT services, robust cloud offerings, and proactive cybersecurity</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">Business is a very fast-moving process; security and efficiency are indispensable in it. iTology firmly believes that business growth relies on trustworthy and innovative technology as the leading IT solutions provider. By focusing on the security of IT solutions onsite and in the cloud, iTology offers security and peace to Oklahoma City and Tulsa metro businesses, knowing their data and operations are safeguarded.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At iTology, the team takes the necessary time to genuinely comprehend the unique needs of every business and develop customized IT solutions that fit those needs. They are committed to your business\'s success through innovative yet reliable IT services. In this way, business owners and managers are able to free up more time to focus on what they do best: running their businesses.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Data Management and Security: </strong>Over the past times, it has arisen that any organization grows with a single concern about data management and security. According to research, every company has an average storage of over 1,000 sensitive files, which include passwords, credit card numbers, and personal information. iTology provides enterprise-class password policies and two-factor authentication to guarantee that communication and data are secured.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Microsoft Suite Services:</strong> iTology provides collaborative document management and enhanced communication solutions for businesses in Oklahoma City, as a Microsoft Preferred Partner. iTology&rsquo;s Microsoft Suite Services will allow your organization to collaborate both internally and externally seamlessly.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Hardware as a Service:</strong> With iTology\'s Hardware as a Service solution, your organization will never have to purchase new hardware again. In the unlikely event of hardware downtime, the company will replace it at no extra charge, keeping you up and running.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>VoIP Services:</strong> Modern telephone service at its best, iTology&rsquo;s VoIP services offer the latest and greatest in Voice over the Internet Protocol (VoIP). This advanced technology permits seamless communications, better cost efficiency, and increased productivity altogether.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>E-Mail Management:</strong> iTology\'s E-Mail Management solution securely communicates your business from the inside out, keeping your business protected against today\'s cyber threats.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Network Management:</strong> iTology monitors your network constantly to make sure it\'s always secure and that you will have very little chance of any downtime. Their team of experts works around the clock to identify and respond to any potential threats before they become an issue.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Security:</strong> The best proactive ways to protect the network are the key approaches to managed IT services. Along with close interaction with the employees, iTology makes them understand how to protect data and implement the latest industry-standard security policies.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>iTology Backup and File Management:</strong> With image-based backups combined with file and folder-based backups, iTology\'s Backup and File Management solution ensures infallible data loss protection.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Ease of Mind and Functionality:</strong> iTology is aware that every business is unique and its goal is to find what makes your business unique. It designs smooth networking processes and data storage and access that give far more than a return on investment: it gives peace of mind.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Family-Owned and Operated:</strong> Because iTology is a family-owned and operated IT company in Oklahoma, you will never have to call someone on the other side of the world to get your technology fixed. iTology&rsquo;s team works to offer superior service to the Oklahoma City and Tulsa metro businesses.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Industry-Specific Solutions:</strong> iTology offers customized solutions for various industries, including energy, environmental, education, construction, financial, hospitality, medical, non-profit, professional services, small business, and more.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Business Continuity Planning (BCP):</strong> Business Continuity Planning (BCP) is the process of creating a system for prevention and recovery from cyber threats and other technological disasters that a business may face. At iTology, the team understands the importance of BCP for Oklahoma businesses. Their experienced team helps you determine the best backup methods for your business, including onsite and offsite support, cloud, and fully managed IT services.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Cloud Services for Your Oklahoma Business Needs&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">iTology provides cloud services that cater to your business needs. Its experienced team helps you:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Migrate to the cloud</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Optimize your existing cloud infrastructure</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Manage successful backups</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Reduce data loss</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Free up on-site storage</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Cloud Migration: Moving to the cloud can be a daunting task for businesses like yours. iTology streamlines the entire process with seamless cloud migration solutions that keep your data safe, reduce downtime, and save money.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Hosted Servers: iTology&rsquo;s customized hosted server solution improves productivity and performance in your organization. Benefits include enhanced privacy, more control, less downtime, and better resource allocation.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We stay up to date on the latest IT trends and topics so that we can make the most informed decision when it comes to what your business requires.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'take-control-of-your-it-and-technology-security-with-itologysmanaged-it-services-robustcloud-offerings-and-proactivecybersecurity', '2025-01-19', 'us/visionaries-network-ceo-itology.webp', 3, 'profile', 'Managed IT & Cybersecurity Services | iTology', 'iTology, managed IT, cybersecurity, cloud services, IT security, tech support, IT management, network security, cloud computing, data protection, proactive IT, visionaries network, IT consulting, business IT, technology services', 'Take control of your IT and tech security with iTology&rsquo;s managed services, robust cloud solutions, and proactive cybersecurity strategies.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://itology.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/itologyok/', ' iTology', '2007', 'Bethany, Oklahoma'),
(63, 6, '<p><strong>Yseop leads in Generative AI for regulated sectors, transforming content automation with a human-focused AI platform</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">The next industrial revolution is being led by artificial intelligence and the automation of repetitive tasks to enhance human capacity in the workplace. At Yseop, the team is pioneering this revolution by empowering people to work smarter and faster, liberating them from tedious, repetitive tasks, and automating complex business processes. Their vision is to make a significant impact on the way businesses operate, and they believe that their advanced Natural Language Generation (NLG) technology and suite of specialist tools are key to achieving this.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Yseop&rsquo;s passion for language and technology expertise underpins everything it does. The company has built a strong global team of linguists and AI specialists to develop its technology, ensuring that its written narratives are always high-quality, across all 7 languages. As Yseop continues to grow, it will accelerate speed and accuracy, while maintaining a natural written style.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Whether you are looking for help to identify your first business use case or have a specific need in mind, Yseop can help you seize the opportunities of this next-generation AI technology and drive real business improvement. Yseop&rsquo;s NLG solutions can be applied across various industries, including medical and regulatory writing, corporate finance document automation, and more.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In the medical and regulatory writing space, Yseop&rsquo;s pre-trained generative AI model, Yseop Copilot, empowers top BioPharma companies to automate content outputs for key regulatory documentation and medical writing workflows. By integrating directly into Microsoft Word, the company&rsquo;s solution enables medical writers to work where they are comfortable while increasing productivity and getting therapies to market faster. With Yseop Copilot, medical writing teams can focus on scientific, more complex work, rather than tedious administrative tasks.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Automating Medical Writing Workflows</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Yseop Copilot automates time-consuming tasks to enable regulatory documents to be delivered faster and more efficiently. By producing first drafts of reports like the clinical study report (CSR) and clinical trial narrative (CTN), medical writing teams can focus on scientific, more complex work. With Yseop Copilot, medical writers can:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Increase productivity efficiency by 50%</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Remove tedious administrative work like importing and transforming tables</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Ensure FDA &amp; EMA compliance</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Regulatory Document Automation</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Yseop Copilot\'s automation packs automate the critical chain of preclinical documents to deliver a comprehensive level of report automation for highly accurate narratives. By automating core regulatory report documents across the eCTD pyramid, Yseop&rsquo;s solution dramatically accelerates submission timelines.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Corporate Finance Document Automation</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Yseop\'s NLG solutions can transform corporate finance departments\' business data into written narratives. Its automated reporting solutions provide expert-level financial reporting and analysis, all within the bounds of compliance requirements. By automating financial reporting with scale and accuracy, corporate finance teams can:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Remove tedious administrative work like importing and transforming tables</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Save time and resources</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Empower themselves with actionable insights to drive better decisions</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In addition to automating medical writing workflows and regulatory document automation, Yseop&rsquo;s NLG solutions can also be applied to corporate finance document automation. Its automated reporting solutions provide expert-level financial reporting and analysis, all within the bounds of compliance requirements.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Yseop, the team is committed to empowering people to work smarter and faster, while automating complex business processes. The company&rsquo;s NLG technology and suite of specialist tools are designed to make a significant impact on the way businesses operate. Whether you are looking to automate medical writing workflows, regulatory authoring processes, or corporate finance document automation, Yseop can help you seize the opportunities of this next-generation AI technology and drive real business improvement.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">By automating repetitive tasks and freeing up human capital for more strategic and creative work, Yseop&rsquo;s NLG solutions can help businesses achieve significant productivity gains and improved operational efficiency. With its advanced technology and expertise in language and AI, Yseop is poised to revolutionize the way businesses operate in the future.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Alain Kaeser, Founder &amp; Chief Strategy Officer</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Alain co-founded Yseop in 2007 after many years of extensive research and testing into artificial intelligence, knowledge engineering, and the science of languages.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">His first exploration into the application of NLG in finance came in 1985 when Alain created a software program that helped accountants make financial decisions through language generation and the management of business rules. The program was extremely successful and won a CPA Golden Disk award, encouraging him to pursue further research surrounding artificial intelligence and making an inference engine &ldquo;talk&rdquo;. This was when Alain began to expand the technology&rsquo;s focus to include domains such as marketing and sales, which ultimately led Yseop to where it is today.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Alain received his diploma in mathematics from the prestigious Ecole Normale Sup&eacute;rieure of Cachan (France), where he also taught for two years, and has a postgraduate degree in computer science from the University of Paris VI.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;Yseop is reimagining the future of scientific writing to get medicine into the hands of those who need it faster.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'yseop-leads-in-generative-ai-for-regulated-sectors-transforming-content-automation-with-a-human-focused-ai-platform', '2025-01-19', 'us/visionries-network-alain-kaeser0ceo-yseop.jpg', 5, 'profile', 'Generative AI for Regulated Industries | Yseop', 'Yseop, generative AI, regulated sectors, content automation, AI platform, compliance, life sciences, finance, automation tools, human-centric AI, enterprise AI, natural language generation, AI writing, visionaries network, digital transformation', 'Yseop leads in generative AI for regulated industries, transforming content automation with a human-centric, compliant AI platform.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://yseop.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/yseop', 'Yseop', '2007', 'New York, NY'),
(64, 6, '<p><strong>Agile has enterprise-level software systems, state-of-the-art facilities, and innovative solutions to fit just about any need</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">Agile prides itself in being the Supply Chain Sherpas. It was the first to chart a path to e-commerce fulfillment success, blazing the trail with state-of-the-art solutions. Well aware is the fact that e-commerce fulfillment entails more than pick, pack, and ship; it is about seamless customer experiences across all channels of an online marketplace, through social media, and in-store shopping. Services of Omnichannel Support by Agile ensure that whatever channel they may use, your customer gets their product in the most functional manner.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As one of the largest e-commerce fulfillment service providers, the requirement for Agile was to create a comprehensive approach to meet the special needs of their customers. A team of expert Supply Chain Sherpas collaborates with you to identify your pain points and develops customized solutions to meet your specific needs.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Whether you want to improve your inventory management, streamline your shipping operations, or enhance your customer service, Agile is here to help.<br><br>Its e-commerce fulfillment services include an e-commerce shopping cart and channel integration to receiving and inventory management, order fulfillment services, and returns processing. Inventory management is also done for online businesses where the company will ensure that advertised products are in stock within the warehouse while at the same time maintaining minimum stockouts and overselling. Agile\'s team works hand in glove with you to manage your inventory levels, avoid stockouts, and maximize customer satisfaction.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The Agile team knows technology is the secret to successful e-commerce fulfillment. Their business intelligence and technology solutions will give you full view of visibility into your supply chain operations that empower data-driven decisions and optimization of your business processes. Agile uses the most up-to-date SCS software such as the WMS, TMS, and shipping software. Agile\'s technology solutions help customers make their operations more efficient, reduce costs, and improve customer service.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">But Agile provides more than just e-commerce fulfillment services; it also provides a range of transport management services that will enable you to optimize your shipping operations. The agile team will work with you to find the best shipping method to suit your business: weight, zone-based pricing, flat rate, regional rate, and express. The company provides customers with shipping alternatives, including mail, parcel, LTL/truckload, ocean, air, and intermodal transportation. With their wide network of carriers and logistics partners, the team at Agile can offer flexible and cost-effective shipping alternatives with unique solutions to fit each customer\'s specific needs.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Agile is committed to taking your enterprise to the next level in e-commerce fulfillment. Agile is seasoned Supply Chain Sherpas, elbow to elbow with you through the pain points of finding solutions tailored to your very specific needs. With modern technology and expertise, one can trust that one\'s e-commerce business is in good hands. Agile is committed to the success of your competitive e-commerce business.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Drew Eastman, CEO</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With over 19 years of experience in various fields of business, Drew Eastman is a passionate and driven leader who strives to create innovative and progressive solutions for emerging brands. His core competencies include operations management, new business development, international business, and e-commerce fulfillment. As the CEO of Agile Supply Chain Strategies, he leads a team of dedicated operators who share his vision of delivering elite customer service, scaling businesses, and working with like-minded companies. Agile values innovation, collaboration, and integrity, and he seeks to empower his clients and partners with the best supply chain strategy and technology.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As the CEO of Agile Supply Chain Strategies, Agile oversees all aspects of the company\'s operations, sales, and growth. He works closely with clients to understand their needs, challenges, and goals and provides them with customized and flexible solutions to best operate their emerging brand. Drew also leverages his domestic and international business skills and network to expand the company\'s reach and opportunities in new markets.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We have all the top tech and the right systems but what makes it all come together and succeed is our exceptional team. Our team simply makes Agile the very best in the business.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'agile-has-enterprise-level-software-systems-state-of-the-art-facilities-and-innovative-solutions-to-fit-just-about-any-need', '2025-01-19', 'us/visionaries-network-ceo-agile-supply-chain-strategies.webp', 7, 'profile', 'Enterprise Software & Innovative Solutions | Agile', 'Agile, enterprise software, innovative solutions, IT services, custom systems, software development, tech solutions, digital transformation, state-of-the-art facilities, cloud services, visionaries network, agile development, business technology, system integration, software platforms', 'Agile delivers enterprise-level software, cutting-edge facilities, and innovative tech solutions tailored to meet virtually any business need.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.agilescs.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/agile-supply-chain-strategies?trk=public_profile_topcard-current-company', 'Agile Supply Chain Strategies', '2006', ' Salt Lake City, Utah');
