(65, 6, '<p><strong>Aclymate is the easy and affordable climate solution to find, reduce, report, and offset your company\'s carbon footprint</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Aclymate\'s mission is to create a world where everyone is educated about and empowered to act for humanity\'s best climate future. In service of this, the company is committed to inspiring and equipping small businesses to lead on climate mitigation. Pioneering climate solutions, Aclymate has created a holistic platform for small-to-mid-sized businesses (SMBs) to measure, track, offset, reduce, and report on their emissions in pursuit of a net-zero future.<br><br><strong>The Beginning of the Journey</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Aclymate co-founder and CEO, Mike Smith, began his journey with Aclymate when, as a young lad, he had an awakening about the forces of climate change. He watched forests burn down in his backyard as a child and was told that nature would slowly heal itself; but when he returned to his childhood hometown, 20 years later, the forests hadn\'t grown back. This made Mike feel urgent and responsible to do something; thus, he turned into an advocate for mitigating climate change.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Finally, Mike\'s journey introduced him to William Loopesko, the co-founder and Chief Technology Officer at Aclymate. Will loved animals and the outdoors and had a developing product that had to do with measuring the temperature of dogs. The two entrepreneurs met through an entrepreneurs\' group, and hit it off, with a common dream of making climate change accessible to all.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Solution Aclymate</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Aclymate\'s platform is designed especially for SMBs needing an all-in-one climate solution. At the core of the platform lie the three steps: Measure, Reduce, and Offset.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Measure: Aclymate\'s carbon accounting tool makes use of the GHG to measure and track emissions. The platform is integrated with major accounting software and utility companies for ease of gathering data. Users can also upload spreadsheets of additional information as needed.<br>Thanks to Aclymate\'s class-leading reporting functionality, enterprises are able to find hotspots-quick, easy reductions can be made. The intuitive reports present actionable insights for enterprises in light of decisions taken in consonance with real data.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Offset: Aclymate\'s marketplace presents a wide range of offset options from around the world. Users are free to browse and select offsets that are in tandem with their values and goals.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Certifications and Compliance</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Aclymate\'s solution provides a way for businesses to achieve a number of certifications and compliances: for example, B Corp. The carbon accounting feature with Aclymate and the reporting feature help an organization in quantifying Scopes 1, 2, and 3 under the GHG protocol and reporting it. Third-party verification of the emission reports features on the platform; it also enables setting a net-zero target and defining the climate transition plan.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&bull; Ecovadis: Aclymate, with the help of customized reporting, helped clients increase their assessment scores in Ecovadis and achieve the Platinum level of such a prominent certification.<br>&bull; Green Business Benchmark: The reporting required for GBB Certification is included out-of-the-box within the Aclymate solution, and hence it is easy for any organization to get points toward GBB certification.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Values at Aclymate</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Aclymate, integrity, equality, balance, and action are the guiding stars. Sustainability for this company is not only the reduction of emissions but also respect for people, and their empowerment to make decisions. Aclymate has a low hierarchy that pretty much allows team members to work collaboratively and innovatively, and pays balanced attention to work-life balance.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Mike Smith, Founder &amp; CEO</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&ldquo;We measure the emissions across your life - at work, home, and events - to help you identify, reduce, offset, and report your climate pollution. Our product is powerfully detailed, yet remains affordable and easy to use.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;Aclymate provides the climate solution built for the 99+% of us who don\'t run sustainability teams for large corporations.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'aclymate-is-the-easy-and-affordable-climate-solution-to-find-reduce-report-and-offset-your-companys-carbon-footprint', '2025-01-19', 'us/visionaries-network-mike-smith-ceo-founder-aclymate.webp', 8, 'profile', 'Affordable Carbon Footprint Solution | Aclymate', 'Aclymate, carbon footprint, climate solution, carbon offset, sustainability, emissions tracking, environmental impact, green business, visionaries network, climate reporting, reduce emissions, carbon accounting, eco-friendly, ESG, carbon reduction', 'Aclymate offers an easy, affordable way to find, reduce, report, and offset your company&rsquo;s carbon footprint for a sustainable future.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://aclymate.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/aclymate/', 'Aclymate', '', ' Denver, Colorado'),
(66, 6, '<p><strong>Dealer OMG revolutionizes dealership advertising by eliminating generic, cookie-cutter ads</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">In today\'s competitive automotive industry, dealerships are constantly seeking innovative ways to stand out from the crowd and attract potential customers. One company that is leading the charge is Dealer OMG, a cutting-edge digital marketing firm that has made it its mission to revolutionize dealership advertising by eliminating generic, cookie-cutter ads.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Founded by former Meta employees and seasoned dealership experts, Dealer OMG leverages its award-winning adtech, vinAMP, to craft personalized, attention-grabbing advertisements that are tailored to each dealership\'s unique needs. With a team of experts who understand the intricacies of the automotive industry, Dealer OMG empowers dealerships to expand their market share and forge lasting relationships with customers.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Meet the Best Social Ads in Auto</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Dealer OMG knows that cookie-cutter ads are no longer enough to capture the attention of today\'s consumers. That\'s why they have developed a range of innovative marketing strategies designed to help dealerships stand out from the competition. From scalable and flexible solutions to sales, fixed ops, acquisition, branding, and recruiting strategies, Dealer OMG has a solution for every dealership\'s unique needs.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Scalability and Flexibility</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">One of the key benefits of working with Dealer OMG is its ability to scale its marketing strategies to meet the needs of any dealership. Whether you\'re looking to target a small audience or a large one, Dealer OMG\'s platform can handle it. Additionally, its flexible approach allows dealerships to customize their marketing strategies to fit their unique brand and goals.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Sales Strategy</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Dealer OMG\'s sales strategy is designed to engage customers at every stage of their car buying journey. Using customer lifecycle strategies alongside industry-leading creative, the company creates custom audiences that are tailored to each dealership\'s specific needs. From lead form abandoners to behavioral retargeting and unsold leads, Dealer OMG\'s sales strategy is designed to maximize conversions and drive revenue.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Fixed Ops Strategy</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In addition to its sales strategy, Dealer OMG also offers a fixed ops strategy designed to unlock the full potential of your service department. By targeting past customers and local drivers for conquesting opportunities, the company helps dealerships increase their sales-to-service retention and drive revenue.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Acquisition Strategy</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Dealer OMG\'s acquisition strategy is designed to help dealerships acquire new inventory. By targeting past customers and DMV conquest YMM audiences, the company creates a pipeline of potential customers who are interested in purchasing a new vehicle.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Branding Strategy</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In today\'s crowded digital landscape, it\'s more important than ever for dealerships to have a strong brand identity. Dealer OMG\'s branding strategy is designed to deliver an experience for customers in their newsfeeds and stories, helping dealerships build awareness and drive engagement.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Recruiting Strategy</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Finally, Dealer OMG also offers a recruiting strategy designed to help dealerships tap into the right audiences and leverage their networks for hiring opportunities. By targeting blue-collar school grads, recent college grads, and sales professionals, the company helps dealerships find the talent they need to succeed.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Dealer OMG