(67, 7, '<p><strong>Pickaxe helps executives in marketing, product, engineering, and analytics build the future</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">Pickaxe is a collective of Makers, Strategists, Developers, Data Scientists, Designers, and more, with a diversity of skills but driven by a like core: Accuracy, Empathy, Utility. This keen sincerity is revealed in its take on marketing technology (martech) and data science.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At the heart of the Pickaxe mission is the desire to help companies be successful in achieving the building of trust between a company and its customers. The team understands the need for accuracy in everything from business marketing to analytics. With this vision, they do their best to provide correct solutions that meet the requirements for clients.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Empathy is one more principal value that guides Pickaxe. The company is aware that the success of their customers will hitch a direct ride with their success as a group and, therefore, are committed to making their business, work, and lives better. It is this light that they use to design solutions that answer to the need of each individual client.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Third is utility, for Pickaxe. They think that solutions must be practical and useful to truly impact a business. It\'s this very focus on utility that defines the martech and data science approaches of Pickaxe&mdash;always centered on functional results.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><img style=\"float: right;\" src=\"../../story_image_upload/us/Pickaxe_Joshua-Dern,-Co-founder_CEO_cover.jpg\" alt=\"image\" width=\"200\" height=\"262\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Their Marketing Systems Optimization practice is aimed at addressing the improvement of martech stacks for any company toward maximum ROI realization. Everything from attribution improvement and fixing data silos to aligning KPIs and reporting conflicts from ad networks is included. The expertise lies in the entire customer journey, from Customer Acquisition and Customer Retention to Engagement and Growth.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Besides marketing optimization, Pickaxe also deals in the services of data science and machine learning. Their team of experts will help companies solve complex data challenges, find new avenues for growth, and develop custom ML models. Scaling data capabilities, building custom ML models, and synthesizing analysis on large datasets, Pickaxe approaches every question with rich business acumen. Context and outputs as the critical competitive anchors.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Data schema and preparation are important areas of expertise for Pickaxe. Business-focused data cleaning and joining, plus processing of the data, ensure a truly real-world impact on the running of the particular business. This contains internal knowledge and metadata baked into models to help make more accurate predictions and hence better decision-making.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Anotherprit area where Pickaxe really excels is data pipelines. Their team will help your business access data in such a way that it becomes instantly actionable and available across all necessary platforms. Using the query tool from Pickaxe, marketing and business teams can get access to data without requiring special skills or technical expertise.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Finally, Pickaxe stands for codeless insights which offer so much more than simple data analysis. From day one, their training included business sense, which makes them able to identify anomalies and foresee future outcomes with a high degree of correctness. Lastly, with Pickaxe\'s tools, companies can go ahead and act upon decisions taken in a data-driven way, confident that both the insights are not only out of the box but also based on real data.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Joshua Dern, Co-founder &amp; CEO</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With over 20+ years of leading digital strategy, content, and transformation in emerging technologies at leading major media corporations and building startups, Joshua loves figuring out the hard stuff. Formerly he was SVP/GM Social Media @Viacom Media Networks/MTVN, CPO @Bedrocket Media Ventures, award-winning product head @Huge for HBO GO, TMN, and more, and former VP Digital @Atlantic Records / WMG.<br><br>Joshua lives in the intersection of design, content, technology, and strategy, and he\'s proud to have overseen so many products that people love and use every day. In his off time you can find him skateboarding, mountain biking, making silly movies, and otherwise spending time with his dog Shmee, and his wife and son.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We solve your biggest problems and deliver solutions custom-designed for your business without the fluff.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'pickaxe-helps-executives-in-marketing-product-engineering-and-analytics-build-the-future', '2022-07-14', 'us/visionaries-network-joshua-dern-ceo-pickaxe.webp', 1001, 'cover', 'Build the Future with Pickaxe | Executive Solutions', 'Pickaxe, marketing strategy, product development, engineering, analytics, innovation, executive tools, data insights, digital transformation, business intelligence, visionaries network, future planning, tech solutions, collaboration, decision-making', 'Pickaxe empowers executives in marketing, product, engineering, and analytics with tools and insights to build the future.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://pickaxe.ai/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/pickaxe-foundry', 'Pickaxe', '2015', ' New York, NY'),
(68, 7, '<p><strong>Network Handlers: Provides Web &amp; Digital Solutions to Exponentially Grow Your Business</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In today\'s fast-paced and rapidly changing business landscape, staying ahead of the competition requires more than just a good product or service. It demands innovative solutions, cutting-edge technology, and a deep understanding of customer needs. For businesses looking to drive growth, improve efficiency, and stay competitive, partnering with the right technology partner is crucial. That\'s where Network Handlers comes in.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Network Handlers is a team of skilled and dedicated software developers and implementation consultants who help fast-growing startups and innovative enterprises drive impact and achieve their goals. The company is a one-stop resource for custom development needs in Finance, HR, Education, Non-Profit, e-commerce, and more. With over 17 years of experience, Network Handlers has remained at the forefront of innovation, implementing solutions to serve clients\' unique needs.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Network Handlers is a team of skilled and dedicated software developers and implementation consultants who help fast-growing startups and innovative enterprises drive impact and achieve their goals. The company is a one-stop resource for custom development needs in Finance, HR, Education, Non-Profit, e-commerce, and more. With over 17 years of experience, Network Handlers has remained at the forefront of innovation, implementing solutions to serve clients\' unique needs.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The company is committed to customer success, offering personal customer support that is always available to help with any software project. Whether it\'s customizing a product, fixing bugs on a website, integrating e-commerce with ERP, migrating data, or handling complex shipping or tax API integrations, Network Handlers acts as an in-house development team, allowing businesses to focus on what they do best - running their operations.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Network Handlers is a leader in web services solutions, having developed its own proprietary suite of tools and platforms called Missio Solutions. This allows the company to effectively develop and deploy solutions quickly and efficiently. From donor CRM solutions to marketplaces and customer portals, Network Handlers helps shorten time-to-market and provide all the tools needed for rapid deployment.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The company\'s expertise extends to enterprise product development, where experienced product development teams work on all sorts of enterprise-level projects, including B2B and B2C trading. Network Handlers offers highly skilled and professional solutions for each development project.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Enterprise product development refers to the process of creating and enhancing software solutions tailored specifically for large organizations or enterprises. These solutions address the complex needs and requirements of businesses operating at scale. User experience is the most important factor in enterprise product development, as it delivers a great user experience to consumers through customized software.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Network Handlers\' skilled experts understand the complex needs and challenges of enterprise-level businesses and offer tailored services to develop custom software products that meet their specific requirements. The company provides services such as product strategy, software development, quality assurance, and ongoing support to help enterprises optimize their operations and achieve their business goals.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Some of the services offered by Network Handlers include SaaS integration services, CRM integration services, cloud service integration services, CMS integration services, mobility integration services, and reporting system integration services.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">When it comes to choosing a partner for enterprise product development, Network Handlers stands out due to its commitment to timely delivery, appealing appearance, business updates and upgrades, and more. The company\'s approach ensures that each project is completed within the expected timeframe without compromising on quality. With a focus on delivering visually appealing software that offers the best user experience, Network Handlers is an ideal partner for businesses looking to drive impact and achieve their goals.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;Our mission is to be the partner of choice from #startups to grown-up companies. We are committed to understanding the user and business goals so we can implement design principles essential to creating the best customer experiences and products our clients and their customers will love.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'network-handlers-provides-web-digital-solutions-to-exponentially-grow-your-business', '2022-05-14', 'us/Ria-Nancoo-CEO-Network-Handlers.jpg', 1, 'profile', 'Network Handlers: Web & Digital Growth Solutions', 'Network Handlers, web solutions, digital marketing, SEO, web design, branding, visionaries network, business, development, online presence, strategy, UX, content, social media, tech', 'Network Handlers delivers innovative web and digital solutions designed to boost your online presence and grow your business exponentially.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.networkhandlers.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/networkhandlers', 'Network Handlers', '2008', 'New York, United States '),
(69, 7, '<p><strong>Rembrand is the world\'s leading platform for Enhanced In-Scene Advertising</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Rembrand is a global innovator in radically reappraising how brands and creators interconnect with audiences. The company is headquartered across three countries with a go-to-market team located in the U.S. for developing a pioneer solution targeted at opening up this subsequent era of non-interruptive video ads. Rembrand empowers creators to unlock new value from the content they share without having to compromise on viewer experience through seamless integration of AI-driven technology.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In the vision of Rembrand, there is something that remains central: to inlay brands in people\'s favorite content in a way that would offer a much more sustainable, effective form of advertising to both brands and consumers. It is based on imagination, creativity, and passion for innovation, and Rembrand believes AI can unlock new possibilities within the process of content creation.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">This way, brands reach out to their target audiences in ways that respect the audiences\' attention. Its values are seen in the commitment to respect the viewers\' experience by ensuring that ads are not disruptive or annoying but become a part of the content. It is from this innovative venture that the Rembrand Marketplace is born, in which the best worldwide creators provide high-quality content for any brand.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">This once-in-a-lifetime opportunity allows brands to weave their message or product into powerful videos using special animations to grab attention and narrate a story. It is never possible to skip, ignore or be distracted if it\'s Rembrand\'s creative units; they will always create maximum impact. By using AI-driven technology, the company allows brands to reach their target audience very precisely: it aggregates the free flow of high-quality content created by top creators around the world that serves niche markets and demographics.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">\"Rembrand\'s platform monetizes for creators: the ability to supplement sponsored posts with targeted in-scene media. Target media can be embedded post-production, and with the Rembrand post-production solution, this can be done across their entire content library. This creates greater chances to generate more revenue for the creators and gives them greater content flexibility, where they can really focus on storytelling rather than being limited by commercial considerations.\".&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">For brands, Rembrand enables targeted reach with high-quality, resonant content; the ability to insert a message or a product within engaging videos without disturbing the viewer experience; and measurable results through advanced analytics and reporting. AI technology found at the heart of Rembrand is what drives innovation in speed, scale, realism, and efficiency within video advertising.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Traditional VFX product insertion can take weeks; Rembrand\'s AI does it in hours. The platform processes huge volumes of content, doncipi thousands of creators and brands a day. What\'s more, Rembrand\'s AI is not only tradable with the laws of physics but also understands the detection of the environment, surfaces, and camera angles to realistically place media objects within a video scene. This level of realism ensures that the ads are indistinguishable from the content they interrupt and, as a result, reduces the time and cost spent on production while interest is heightened.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As Rembrand continues to raise the bar for innovation in AI-driven video advertising, this one looks fixed to define the industry\'s future. With its innovative approach and cutting-edge technology, Rembrand is changing the way brands engage with audiences and creators monetize audience content. Whether a brand wants to connect with its target audience or a creator is looking for additional monetization opportunities, Rembrand will introduce new ways of thinking about video advertising. It accomplishes this by taking advantage of the best that AI and groundbreaking technology have to offer, allowing Rembrand to set the place and definition of what is possible in video advertising.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Omar Tawakol, Chief Executive Officer</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Rembrand is co-founded by 20-year tech executive, Omar Tawakol, who also serves as the company\'s seasoned leadership. He has held several notable positions, including Vice President and General Manager of Cisco\'s Contact Center business unit. Before that, he founded and led Voicea, a pioneering voice-based AI assistant platform that was recently acquired by Cisco. His entrepreneurship drive is further exhibited in the founding and chieftaincy of BlueKai&mdash;the largest consumer data marketplace globally&mdash;acquired by Oracle in 2014. Before that, he had robust experience in tech while working in industry giants like Google, Salesforce, and Microsoft. He has an MSc in Computer Science from Stanford and an undergraduate degree from Massachusetts Institute of Technology.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We offer a Marketplace and a Platform that enables advertisers to become part of the story, rather than interrupting it.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'rembrand-is-the-worlds-leading-platform-for-enhanced-in-scene-advertising', '2022-05-14', 'us/visionaries-network-omar-tawakol-ceo-rembrand.webp', 2, 'profile', 'Rembrand: Leader in Enhanced In-Scene Advertising', 'Rembrand, in-scene advertising, digital ads, AI, marketing tech, virtual ads, media, innovation, branding, visionaries network, content monetization, advertising platform, real-time, immersive, technology', 'Rembrand is the global leader in enhanced in-scene advertising, using AI to deliver immersive, real-time brand integration across digital content.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.rembrand.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/getrembrand/?viewAsMember=true', 'Rembrand', '2022', 'Los Altos, California, USA'),
(70, 7, '<p><strong>Seal Global provides AI-driven digital transformation solutions &amp; builds global teams to enhance profits &amp; reduce costs</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">In today\'s fast-paced digital landscape, Startups and Small Enterprises (SMBs) are facing unprecedented challenges in navigating the complex journey of digital transformation. At Seal Global, the team understands the importance of leveraging Artificial Intelligence (AI) to unlock opportunities for growth and scalability. The company&rsquo;s Applied Generative AI solutions are designed to empower businesses to streamline their operations, liberate knowledge, amplify efficiency, and exceed their digital marketing aspirations.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Why Seal Global?</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Seal Global&rsquo;s team of experts has navigated the ambiguities of AI implementation, providing comprehensive solutions to help businesses overcome the complexities of digital transformation. With its expertise in AI-driven digital transformation services, it sculpts information assets, liberates knowledge, and amplifies efficiency to drive business growth.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Seal Global and AI in a Nutshell</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Seal Global, the team integrated Artificial Intelligence with essential Digital Transformation Services. Applied Generative AI solutions are designed to enhance 360-degree productivity by custom-building intelligent Generative AI models. The company&rsquo;s services include:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Prompt Engineering as a Service (PEaaS): </strong>Work directly with Seal Global&rsquo;s talented pool of Prompt Engineers to experience the power of prompt engineering on AI platforms that create excellence at scale.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>SEER:</strong> Unlock information automation with SEER, Seal Global&rsquo;s customer interaction service that transforms business information into actionable insights, automation, and leads.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>SAVANT: </strong>Liberate knowledge, scale efficiency &amp; profit with SAVANT, your knowledge buddy, a knowledge liberation agent that harnesses Custom AI to increase efficiency.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>LUMOS:</strong> Illuminate your digital presence with LUMOS, Seal Global&rsquo;s AI-enhanced digital marketing service that offers personalized content creation to campaign optimization.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Other Competencies</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">While Seal Global&rsquo;s AI-driven capabilities set us apart, at the heart of Seal Global lies a robust foundation of legacy competencies that have been the bedrock of its success. The company&rsquo;s comprehensive suite of services includes:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">eCommerce and Multichannel Business Consultancy: As your Outsourced Director of eCommerce, Seal Global navigates the options-bloated, guidance-anemic landscape of the industry, helping you make informed choices and implement effective strategies.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Strategy, Technology, Marketing, Operations, and Organization: Seal Global&rsquo;s comprehensive suite of services encompasses every facet of your business, covering strategy development, technology implementation, marketing campaigns, operations optimization, and organizational structure.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Financial Planning and Profitability Enhancement: Seal Global delves deep into financial planning, identifying cost reduction and revenue maximization opportunities to ensure your business thrives in a competitive digital environment.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Outsourced Director of eCommerce Services: Seal Global extends its role beyond consultancy to become an integral part of your team as your outsourced director of eCommerce.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>What Seal Global Brings to the Table</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Seal Global brings cutting-edge technology skills, deep domain expertise, and standardized delivery methodology to address the complexities of today\'s commerce. From planning the front end of your online store to back-end technologies and processes, Seal Global will hand-hold you through every stage of your implementation.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Tracking and Analytics Implementation</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Seal Global offers a range of services designed to track and analyze your business performance:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Targeted SEO campaigns for Shopify stores</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Analytics/data reporting</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Implementation of Google Analytics, Webmaster Tool, and Merchant Center</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Digital marketing campaigns through search engines, social networks, and online ad networks</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Search Engine Marketing (SEM) and Search Engine Optimization (SEO)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Social Media marketing campaigns and content on FB, Twitter, Google+, Blogs</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Email marketing including maintaining email calendar, campaign set-up, list segmentation, product selection, email delivery, and performance analysis</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Building Global Teams for the Healthcare Industry</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Seal Global\'s non-clinical healthcare outsourcing services empower healthcare organizations to streamline operations and reduce costs while maintaining exceptional customer service. The company&rsquo;s competitive offshore rates for U.S. work hours ensure cost-effectiveness without compromising quality.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Seal Global, the team is committed to empowering businesses with cutting-edge AI capabilities and expert guidance to navigate the complexities of digital transformation.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Oney Seal, Founder and CEO</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Oney Seal is the founder and CEO at Seal Global Holdings, a Miami headquartered technology consulting and investment firm that specializes in building and operating internet retail, fintech, and technology companies on a turnkey basis. Seal Global&rsquo;s client and investee companies are in a wide variety of technology sectors such as online retail, fintech, AI/ML, travel &amp; hospitality, outsourcing, and media &amp; entertainment. Oney is a distinguished member of The American Society for AI ( ASFAI).<br><br>Oney holds executive management or board positions in most of the portfolio companies and is a successful, results-driven, entrepreneurial CEO, with a proven track record in starting and building an Internet Retailer 500-ranked e-commerce company, a boutique outsourcing company, and a pioneering IPTV/OTT company.<br><br>- Specialized in leading growth and profit performance in multi-channel environments.<br><br>- Ability to develop and manage high-performance cross-border teams, and specialize in leading all aspects of an e-commerce business and multi-channel digital strategy.<br><br>- Provide hands-on e-commerce, digital transformation, and AI consulting to boards and VCs of technology and internet retail companies.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We help you build exceptional customer experiences, get the technology right, and extend your consumer reach with our Offshore Outsourcing Services.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'seal-global-provides-ai-driven-digital-transformation-solutions-builds-global-teams-to-enhance-profits-reduce-costs', '2022-05-14', 'us/visionaries-network-oney-seal-founder-seal-global.webp', 3, 'profile', 'Seal Global: AI Solutions for Growth & Cost Efficiency', 'Seal Global, AI-driven, digital transformation, global teams, cost reduction, profit growth, automation, visionaries network, technology, business solutions, outsourcing, strategy, scalability, efficiency, enterprise', 'Seal Global delivers AI-powered digital transformation and builds global teams to boost profits, streamline operations, and cut business costs efficiently.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.sealglobalholdings.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/sealglobalusa?trk=public_profile_topcard-current-company', 'Seal Global Holdings', '2006', 'Florida, United States');
