(71, 1, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Micro Pro: Your One-Stop Shop for IT Support and Solutions</span></strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">As a small to medium-sized business, managing your IT infrastructure can be a daunting task. With the ever-evolving technology landscape, it\'s easy to get overwhelmed by the numerous options and complexities. That\'s where Micro Pro comes in - a team of experienced experts dedicated to providing comprehensive IT support and solutions to businesses in Surrey, London, and beyond.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">IT Support that Solves Your Challenges</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">At Micro Pro, the team understands that IT problems can arise at any moment, disrupting your business operations and causing unnecessary stress. The company&rsquo;s team of skilled experts is just a phone call or email away, ready to provide fast and efficient solutions to your IT challenges. Whether you need help with hardware, software, or networking issues, Micro Pro got you covered.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Proactive Approach</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">The company&rsquo;s approach is proactive, not reactive. It takes the time to get to know your business, people, process, and ethos, allowing it to provide tailored IT support that meets your unique needs. Micro Pro believes in building strong relationships with its clients, becoming an integral part of their operation and helping them achieve long-term success.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Full-Service IT Support</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Micro Pro&rsquo;s comprehensive IT support services include:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Managed IT services for businesses and professionals</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Office relocation support</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Hardware supply and deployment</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Computer and laptop installation</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Repairs, servicing, and upgrades</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Data backup and recovery</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Virus removal</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Installation of CAT6A data cabling</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Unified wireless deployment</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Broadband help</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">GDPR Compliance</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">In today\'s digital age, data protection is more important than ever. The General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) came into effect in 2018, enshrining individuals\' right to data privacy in EU law. The company&rsquo;s team of experts is ready to help you achieve GDPR compliance and create a strategy for maintaining compliance in the future. They will assign a dedicated data privacy consultant to guide you through the process, ensuring it\'s as streamlined and easy as possible.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">IT Strategy</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">At Micro Pro, the team develops IT strategies that align with your business objectives. It uses the latest technology and best practices to ensure you\'re well-prepared to meet your goals. Its team will evaluate potential options and choose solutions that best suit your business needs.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Microsoft 365</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Microsoft 365 (formerly Office 365) is a comprehensive suite of essential business tools that can help drive excellence. With its expertise, you can optimize your operations by choosing the right M365 bundle for your business needs, ramp up cybersecurity, establish GDPR compliance, and avoid the pitfalls of optimizing cloud-based SaaS on your own.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Cloud Backup</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">A solid backup strategy is critical to the operation of any business. Cloud Backup provides an offsite repository for your data that\'s available 24/7 from any location. Micro Pro&rsquo;s fully managed Cloud Backups are encrypted for absolute security and comply with GDPR regulations. It\'s a cost-effective solution that reduces local IT infrastructure costs and scales with your business needs.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">At Micro Pro, the team is committed to providing exceptional IT support and solutions that help businesses succeed. Whether you\'re in Surrey, London, or beyond, the company&rsquo;s team of experts is here to remove obstacles and frustrations, delivering expedient IT support and secure solutions that help your business grow.<br><br></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\"><strong>Meet James Kirby, Managing Director</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">The founder of Micro Pro. He is an experienced IT professional, who has specialised in helping professional service companies and their stakeholders overcome IT challenges and efficiently embrace technology while scaling from SME to Enterprise.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">He has 20 years of IT solution design, deployment, support, consultancy and project management experience, gained in a diverse range of industry sectors, including Legal, Expert Witness, Accountancy, Managed Workspaces and Care.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">His experience encompasses design, costing, implementation, project management and support. He has been relied upon for decades by key stakeholders in growing businesses as someone who can provide authentic, impartial, expert advice and strategy and then deliver on time and on budget, time after time.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong>&ldquo;Micro Pro offer thorough audits and reviews for companies based in London and the surrounding areas. Our experienced team provide an objective audit and review of IT systems, helping our clients to improve their operations and add value.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'micro-pro-your-one-stop-shop-for-it-support-and-solutions', '2023-07-06', 'us/visionariesnetwork-micro-pro-james-kirby.webp', 7, 'profile7', 'Micro Pro: Your One-Stop Shop for IT Support and Solutions', 'Micro Pro, Your One-Stop Shop, IT Support and Solutions, best companies', 'Micro Pro: Your One-Stop Shop for IT Support and Solutions', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://micropro.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/micro-pro-ltd/', 'Micro Pro', '2008', 'Addlestone, Surrey'),
(72, 1, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>Nitrogen: Empowering Advisors and Firms to Deliver Exceptional Results</span></strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">In the world of financial advising, it\'s not uncommon to encounter investors who make poor decisions due to fear and uncertainty. This can lead to subpar outcomes and a lack of confidence in the advisory process. However, with Nitrogen, advisors and firms can transform these fearful investors into fearless ones, making informed decisions that drive long-term financial success.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">At the heart of this platform is a customer-driven approach, where firms prioritize delivering exceptional results and exceeding client expectations. This means being bold in their approach, thinking from the perspective of fearless investing, and focusing on making a meaningful impact on both firms and investors.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">The platform is built on the principles of the Heart of a Champion, which includes executing with a growth mindset, innovating, being curious, and compounding every day. This mindset is driven by a passion for winning for customers, teammates, and investors. The team is comprised of leaders who own quality outcomes, prioritize team over ego, and are all-in when it comes to achieving a common goal.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Authentic transparency is also a core value of Nitrogen. This means open, direct, respectful, and transparent communication that sets the right expectations and builds trust with clients. The platform\'s reputation is built on objective methodology, never compromising on its values or principles.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">One of the key features of the Nitrogen is the Risk Number, which provides a scientific framework for assessing risk tolerance. This framework won the Nobel Prize for Economics and helps investors understand the relationship between risk and reward. By providing this information, advisors can set better expectations with clients and demonstrate alignment with their goals.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">For financial advisors, the Risk Number enables them to make informed investment decisions and demonstrate alignment with prospects, clients, and regulators. Clients can see their Risk Number on a scale of 1-99 and understand how much risk they\'re willing to take on to achieve their goals.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Compliance personnel benefit from the Risk Tolerance Questionnaire, which provides a repeatable process for assessing risk tolerance and capacity. This helps ensure that investors are treated as individuals and not stereotyped based on age or other factors.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Firm executives can leverage the Client Engagement Platform for Wealth Management Firms to equip their teams with the tools needed to assess risk tolerance and capacity. This platform also includes a proposal engine that enables advisors to create personalized proposals that demonstrate their commitment to their clients\' best interests.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">The proposal engine is designed to be easy to use and provides a seamless experience for clients. Advisors can quickly close deals and grow assets under management (AUM) by leveraging the platform\'s features. Clients benefit from seeing how their advisor is acting in their best interests and are more likely to invest fearlessly for the long haul.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">For compliance personnel, the Proposals Dashboard provides a book-of-business view of all clients, reports, and proposals. This allows them to track which clients have received their Risk Number, who has received Form CRS, and where advisors need assistance building proposals.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Firm executives can roll out a consistent proposal process that both advisors and prospects love, leading to improved close rates and client satisfaction. By leveraging the four most powerful words in the profession &ndash; <em>\"What\'s Your Risk Number?\"</em> &ndash; advisors can quickly capture leads and create ACAT form moments that drive growth.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">In conclusion, the Nitrogen is designed to empower advisors and firms to deliver exceptional results by transforming fearful investors into fearless ones. By leveraging its customer-driven approach, Heart of a Champion mindset, authentic transparency, and innovative technology features, firms can create a unique prospecting process that drives growth and success.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\"><strong>The Visionary Behind Nitrogen: Dan Zitting\'s Journey to Revolutionize Financial Advisory</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">As the CEO of Nitrogen, Dan Zitting brings his extensive experience as a SaaS entrepreneur and operator to the table. With a passion for software that enables bold visions, he is dedicated to empowering the world to invest fearlessly. Prior to joining Nitrogen, Dan spent 13 years in the enterprise SaaS space, focusing on governance, risk management, and compliance (GRC).</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">During this time, Dan co-founded Workpapers.com, a cloud software for audit and compliance management, which was acquired by Galvanize (then ACL) in 2011. He then led Galvanize, growing the company into an industry-recognized leader in GRC, recognized by analysts, investors, and most importantly, customers. The company was ultimately acquired by Diligent in a $1 billion transaction, creating the world\'s largest GRC software company with a $650 million+ revenue SaaS business serving over 25,000 customers in 130+ countries.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Dan\'s experiences have been featured in various publications, including Forbes, The Wall Street Journal, Bloomberg, Business Week, Reuters, The Street, and CNBC, as well as hundreds of professional speaking events.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Dan holds a BSBA in Information Systems and Finance from Colorado State University and a Master of Accountancy from the University of Notre Dame. He believes that his purpose is to challenge organizations to maximize their impact by operating with a conscience, and he sees cloud software as his best contribution to this mission</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong>&ldquo;We create a common language between advisors and clients, allowing you to spend more time building your business and less time managing it.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'nitrogen-empowering-advisors-and-firms-to-deliver-exceptional-results', '2023-07-06', 'us/visonariesnetwork-dan-zitting-nitrogen.webp', 8, 'Profile8', 'Nitrogen: Empowering Advisors and Firms to Deliver Exceptional Results', 'Nitrogen, Empowering Advisors, Firms to Deliver Exceptional Results, best companies, best magazine', '&nbsp;Nitrogen: Empowering Advisors and Firms to Deliver Exceptional Results', NULL, 1, 'no', 'http://www.nitrogenwealth.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/nitrogenwealth/', 'Nitrogen', '2011', 'Auburn, California'),
(73, 1, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong>Overdrive IOT is a Real time Asset Management IOT company,&nbsp;monitoring assets in real-time with industry-leading accuracy</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">In today\'s fast-paced digital landscape, where the pace of technological change is accelerating at an unprecedented rate, businesses and individuals alike are constantly seeking innovative solutions to streamline operations, optimize resources, and gain a competitive edge. The rise of the Internet of Things (IoT) has opened up new opportunities for companies to leverage data-driven insights and automation to drive efficiency, reduce costs, and improve customer experiences. At Overdrive, the team specializes in providing cutting-edge IoT solutions that enable real-time asset monitoring, empowering its clients to make data-driven decisions and stay ahead of the curve.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Overdrive, a leading IoT company in Singapore and Asia, has established itself as a prominent player in the industry with its expertise in real-time asset monitoring. With a team of highly skilled and tech-savvy professionals, it is dedicated to developing innovative solutions that cater to its clients\' specific requirements.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">At Overdrive, the team understands the importance of customization and tailoring its services to meet the unique needs of each client. The company&rsquo;s team of experts works closely with its clients to understand their objectives and challenges, allowing them to create special formulas that address their specific pain points. By leveraging the company&rsquo;s deep understanding of IoT technologies and its ability to analyze data in real-time, the company is able to provide its clients with actionable insights and valuable information. As Overdrive continues to expand its presence in Asia, its primary focus is on monitoring people, vehicles, and facilities simultaneously.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This comprehensive approach allows the company to offer its clients unparalleled visibility and control over their assets. By monitoring people, the company can ensure their safety and security, while also optimizing their productivity. Monitoring vehicles enables the company to track their location, performance, and maintenance needs, leading to improved efficiency and cost savings.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Additionally, monitoring facilities allows the firm to identify potential issues, such as equipment failures or security breaches, in real-time, enabling proactive measures to be taken. Overdrive&rsquo;s commitment to delivering top-notch visibility and control sets them apart from their competitors. The organization utilizes cutting-edge technologies and advanced analytics to provide its clients with real-time updates and actionable insights. By harnessing the power of IoT, Overdrive enables its clients to make informed decisions, optimize their operations, and drive business growth.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Overdrive&rsquo;s flagship solution is OverWheels, a comprehensive fleet tracking system designed to provide real-time data on vehicle location, speed, fuel levels, and technical details. With OverWheels, fleet managers can take proactive measures to optimize their operations, reducing costs and improving efficiency. For instance, the company&rsquo;s solution allows fleet owners to monitor temperature-sensitive cargo and maintain a suitable environment for perishable goods. Overdrive also offers trailer tracking applications for high-precision data and visibility into the entire yard operation, as well as real-time coverage of airside vehicles to prevent accidents and promote a safe driving culture.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">At Overdrive, the team understands that every business has unique requirements. That\'s why the company offers custom software product development services tailored to meet your specific needs. Overdrive expert team will guide you in creating a growth-oriented strategy and roadmap to achieve your business objectives. Its software product development services include end-to-end software product development, dedicated IoT tech teams and designated points of contact, software consultancy, software modernization, and full-cycle IoT AI development.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Overdrive&rsquo;s car-sharing solution is specifically designed for fleet owners in Singapore. With its GPS-based car tracker solution, fleet managers can track the real-time location of each vehicle on a map, analyze routes taken by drivers, and identify opportunities for optimization. This leads to reduced fuel costs, improved delivery times, and increased overall efficiency. The benefits of the company&rsquo;s car-sharing solution include optimized fleet utilization, enhanced safety and route planning, improved customer and driver experience, reduced fuel and operation costs, and improved overall vehicle health.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">At Overdrive, the team believes that real-time asset monitoring is the key to unlocking the full potential of your business. With its cutting-edge IoT solutions, you can gain unparalleled visibility and control over your assets, streamline operations, and make data-driven decisions.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\"><strong>Aston Chia, CEO, Co-Founder</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\"><em>&ldquo;Our tech is unique because it features both an open architecture to ingest both in-house and partnered intelligence modules as well as an ability to tweak device-level firmware and connectivity &mdash; making the platform highly robust and scalable.&rdquo;</em></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'overdrive-iot-is-a-real-time-asset-management-iot-company', '2023-07-06', 'us/visionariesnetwork-aston-chia-overdrive.webp', 9, 'Profile9', 'Overdrive IOT is a Real time Asset Management IOT company,  monitoring assets in real-time with industry-leading accuracy', 'Overdrive IOT,Real time Asset Management, IOT company,  monitoring assets, real-time with industry-leading accuracy, best companies, best magazine, visionariesnetwork', 'Overdrive IOT is a Real time Asset Management IOT company,  monitoring assets in real-time with industry-leading accuracy', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://overdriveiot.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/overdriveiot/', 'Overdrive IOT', '2015', 'Singapore'),
(74, 1, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong>Palmetto makes it affordable for homeowners to source their energy from renewables like solar power</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">At Palmetto, the team is dedicated to making clean energy accessible to everyone. Their innovative platform solutions empower homeowners to go solar, enable businesses to grow, and drive environmental impact at scale. The company believes that the future of energy is cleaner, greener, and more sustainable.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">The Palmetto Clean Energy Operating Platform</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">The company&rsquo;s proprietary platform technology and energy intelligence solutions accelerate the sale and adoption of clean energy, such as residential solar power. It offers an end-to-end clean energy experience that makes it easy for homeowners to go solar and enjoy long-term maintenance, insights, and support.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">National Fulfilment Network</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Palmetto&rsquo;s nationwide fulfilment network connects homeowners with local sales and installation specialists, advancing the clean energy economy in communities across the United States. With Palmetto, you can trust that your clean energy needs will be met with expertise and professionalism.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Integrated Partner Solutions</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Established consumer brands can now expand into the clean energy market and generate new revenue streams with the company&rsquo;s integrated partner solutions. By partnering with Palmetto, you can drive growth, increase customer engagement, and contribute to a sustainable future.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">A New Ecosystem for Clean Energy</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">The Palmetto Clean Energy Operating Platform offers a suite of innovative resources that empower homeowners and businesses alike to realize the benefits of solar. The firm&rsquo;s platform mobilizes a new energy ecosystem to meet the needs of the company&rsquo;s global environment.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Philanthropic Efforts</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">In 2021, the firm launched \'Get Solar, Give Solar\' with a $5M, multi-year commitment to Solar Sister - a women-owned training and entrepreneurship program advancing the distribution of solar energy in developing countries. This program funds philanthropic partnerships in the fight against climate change, providing underserved communities with access to solar energy.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Why Switch to Solar?</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Technology has advanced dramatically in the last 20 years, and solar is no exception. Yet, many homeowners continue to rely on outdated electricity grids and plans. By switching to solar, you can unlock a host of benefits that fossil fuels simply can\'t provide:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Boost your energy independence</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Save money on your electricity bill</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Earn credits and incentives</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Increase the value of your home</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Palmetto Protect</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Palmetto understands that investing in solar can be a significant decision. That\'s why it offers Palmetto Protect - comprehensive coverage that safeguards your investment. With proactive monitoring, intelligent issue detection, 5-star service and support, and an available 95% Performance Guarantee and labor coverage with Palmetto Protect Performance powered by Omnidian, your system can run at peak efficiency while your mind can rest at ease.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">LightReach</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Want the benefits of solar without the cost of investment? Choose a no-buy LightReach energy plan and power your home with low rates, clean energy, and instant solar savings. LightReach offers an innovative approach to home energy management for those who value the financial and environmental benefits of rooftop solar but want the ease of an affordable monthly plan.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">With LightReach, you\'ll enjoy:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Predictable monthly payments</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Installation and maintenance included</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">90% production guarantee</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">25-year protection program</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Christopher Kemper, Chairman, Founder &amp; CEO Journey: A Mission-Oriented Leader in Clean Technology</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Chris is the Chairman, Founder and Chief Executive Officer of Palmetto Clean Technology, Inc. He is a mission-oriented leader focused on technology solutions to climate change. Chris&rsquo; approach blends capitalism with environmentalism, focusing on re-imagining decentralized energy systems and a decarbonized future.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">As outlined in his manifesto, the New Utility Revolution, technological advancements and economic advantages created by clean technology are approaching a tipping point in the global energy infrastructure. The need to democratize access to clean energy and the need to reduce global warming and emissions is quickly driving the realization that clean energy now makes good business sense for the planet&rsquo;s survival.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Chris originally started Palmetto in London after refining his skillset in both policy and finance from organizations including Compagnie Financiere Tradition and the United Nations. In both capacities, he worked primarily with, and in, developing countries to deliver clean technologies in an effort to leapfrog and work outside of an antiquated centralized utility grid structure. In those early days, Palmetto was focused on sourcing, financing, and developing renewable energy projects around the world, but primarily in the least developed countries.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Chris continues to lead the company toward the marketplace, energy-as-a-service model, while ensuring the company is grounded by two major principles - building trust with Palmetto&rsquo;s customers and driving as much transparency as is possible. As a result of Chris&rsquo; hard learned experiences and his vision, today, Palmetto is one of the leading clean technology marketplaces and stands as one of the largest job creators (direct and indirect) in the sector.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">With his graduate degrees in hand, Chris aspires to complete his doctorate-level coursework in environmental economics, which he plans to use to continue educating populations about the environment and the ramifications of climate change. Chris is an avid hiker, a struggling fly fisherman, and is active in charitable giving through his foundation that focuses on supporting early-stage companies, entrepreneurs, and mission driven organizations. He lives in Charlotte, North Carolina.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong>&ldquo;Our Clean Energy Operating Platform enables end-to-end sales, financing, fulfilment, permitting, energy intelligence insights, digital sales funnel and a digital customer experience.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'palmetto-makes-it-affordable-for-homeowners', '2023-07-06', 'us/visionariesnetwork-palmetto-christopher-kemper.webp', 10, 'Profile10', 'Palmetto makes it affordable for homeowners to source their energy from renewables like solar power', 'Palmetto, affordable for homeowners, energy, solar power, best magazine, best companies', 'Palmetto makes it affordable for homeowners to source their energy from renewables like solar power', NULL, 1, 'no', '', '', '', '', '');
