(75, 1, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Phosphorus Cybersecurity Inc. Eliminating IoT Security Gaps with Active Discovery</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In today\'s rapidly evolving digital landscape, the Internet of Things (IoT) has become an integral part of our daily lives. From smart home devices to industrial control systems, the number of connected devices is staggering. In fact, there are now more IoT devices in the world than there are people. This proliferation of connected devices has created a massive attack surface, leaving organizations vulnerable to security breaches and threats.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">At Phosphorus, the team understands the critical need for a comprehensive approach to IoT security. That\'s why they&rsquo;ve developed the industry\'s first and only remediation platform that finds every IoT device, fixes every device, and brings every device into compliance. The company&rsquo;s platform is designed to eliminate the IoT security gap by providing real-time visibility, deep discovery, and zero disruption.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">The Challenge</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">The healthcare industry is particularly vulnerable to IoT security threats. With an increasing number of connected devices, hospitals and medical facilities face a daunting task in monitoring, patching, and remediating these devices. The lack of visibility and control over these devices creates a significant risk to patient care and data confidentiality.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Legacy passive discovery solutions rely on network monitoring to perform discovery, resulting in limited visibility, inaccurate inventory, long mean-time-to-inventory, and high network performance impact. Meanwhile, legacy active solutions fail with IoT assets due to their intrusive, brute-force device polling approaches that disrupt or dramatically degrade operations.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Intelligent Active Discovery</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Phosphorus\'s Intelligent Active Discovery (IAD) solution is designed to overcome these limitations. Its patented IAD approach intelligently calibrates the platform\'s device interactions, dynamically adjusting discovery parameters such as probe sequencing, packet rates, ports in scope, and more &ndash; all while ensuring that assets are fully classified with speed, safety, and minimal network impact.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">With Phosphorus IAD, you can:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Discover all IoT devices without traffic monitoring</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Achieve deterministic discovery with first-time and accurate classification</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Gain unmatched high-resolution device detail with granular risk assessment and deep device metadata</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Ensure zero disruption to operational devices</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Benefits</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">By using Phosphorus IAD, you can:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Reduce Mean Time to Inventory (MTTI) by up to 98%</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Increase efficiency by up to 95% compared to legacy active scanners</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Gain complete visibility into your IoT estate</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Prioritize remediation efforts with accurate risk assessment</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Minimize network performance impact</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Phosphorus Solution</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">The company&rsquo;s solution is designed to address the unique challenges of healthcare organizations. With Phosphorus IAD, you can:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo3;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Discover and track constantly moving devices across floors and patient rooms</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo3;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Monitor and rotate passwords for all assets within your organization</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo3;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Update firmware on IoT, OT, and IoMT devices without disrupting operations</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Conclusion</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Phosphorus is dedicated to eliminating the IoT security gap with its Intelligent Active Discovery solution. Its platform provides a comprehensive approach to IoT security, enabling you to gain real-time visibility, deep discovery, and zero disruption. By leveraging Phosphorus IAD, you can reduce your organization\'s risk exposure and ensure the confidentiality and integrity of your data.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Don\'t let IoT security threats compromise your organization\'s operations or patient care. Choose Phosphorus IAD today and take the first step towards a more secure future.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Chris Rouland</span>, </strong><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">CEO &amp; Board Member</span>: A Visionary Leader in Cybersecurity Innovation </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Chris Rouland is a visionary leader and pioneer in the field of cybersecurity, with an impressive track record of founding multiple multi-million-dollar companies that have revolutionized the way they approach internet security. His entrepreneurial ventures include Bastille, a groundbreaking company that pioneered the assessment and mitigation of risks associated with the Internet of Radios, and Endgame, a leading provider of endpoint security solutions.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Prior to his entrepreneurial pursuits, Chris held senior leadership positions at industry giants IBM and Internet Security Systems (ISS), where he served as Chief Technology Officer and Distinguished Engineer, respectively. As Director of X-Force for ISS, he played a key role in driving innovation and strategic direction for the company\'s internet security offerings.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Throughout his career, Chris has amassed an impressive portfolio of over 20 patents and holds a Master\'s degree from the prestigious Georgia Institute of Technology. His unique blend of technical expertise, business acumen, and leadership skills has enabled him to make a lasting impact on the cybersecurity landscape.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong>&ldquo;Safely FIND, FIX, and MANAGE every&nbsp;IoT,&nbsp;OT,&nbsp;IIoT, and&nbsp;IoMT&nbsp;device with our leading CPS Protection Platform.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'phosphorus-cybersecurity-inc--eliminating-iot-security-gaps-with-active-discovery', '2023-06-06', 'us/visionariesnetwork-chris-rouland-phosphorus-cybersecurity.webp', 11, 'Profile11', 'Phosphorus Cybersecurity Inc.: Eliminating IoT Security Gaps with Active Discovery', 'Phosphorus Cybersecurity Inc., IoT Security, best IoT company, best company, best magazine, visionaries network', 'Phosphorus Cybersecurity Inc.: Eliminating IoT Security Gaps with Active Discovery', NULL, 1, 'no', '', '', '', '', ''),
(76, 1, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong>project44 is on a mission - to make supply chains work</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">project44 is on a quest to revolutionize the way supply chains operate, making them more efficient, resilient, and sustainable. As the only High-Velocity Supply Chain Platform, project44 provides shippers, logistics service providers (LSPs), and carriers with the technology and expertise to optimize their operations, reduce costs, and deliver exceptional customer experiences.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">The Visionary Behind the Movement</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Jett McCandless, founder and CEO of project44, has spent over 25 years working in the logistics and delivery space. He has witnessed firsthand the challenges that shippers and carriers face in managing complex supply chains. With a vision to transform the industry, McCandless set out to create a platform that would provide real-time visibility, transparency, and optimization capabilities.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">The Birth of project44</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">The name \"project44\" is inspired by Route 66, a legendary American highway that connects Chicago, Illinois, to Los Angeles, California. In the 1950s, Route 66 was bypassed by Highway 44, which was designed to accommodate the growing demand for transportation infrastructure. This new highway became the catalyst for connecting a growing nation and supply chain. McCandless saw parallels between this historical event and his vision for project44 &ndash; connecting shippers, carriers, and consumers through a seamless supply chain experience.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">A Team of Industry Experts</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">McCandless assembled a team of industry experts, technology visionaries, and ambitious individuals to bring his vision to life. Since its inception, project44 has remained committed to its mission of making supply chains work. The company has received numerous awards and recognition for its innovative approach to supply chain management.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Awards and Recognition</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">project44 has been named a multi-year leader in the Gartner Magic Quadrant and the \"Customer\'s Choice\" in Gartner\'s Voice of the Customer report. The company is also an eleven-time leader on G2\'s Supply Chain Visibility Grid and has won three SAP Pinnacle Awards. Additionally, project44 was awarded Google Cloud Partner of the Year.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Transforming Supply Chains</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">project44\'s High-Velocity Supply Chain Platform empowers shippers to transform their supply chains from cost centers into revenue generators. By leveraging AI-powered insights, customers can improve customer experiences, decrease transportation costs, and increase cash flow.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Benefits of project44</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Increase revenue through better customer experiences</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Decrease logistics costs by avoiding unnecessary expenses</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Increase cash flow by reducing inventory costs</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Delight customers by reducing product waste</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Industry-Specific Solutions</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">project44 offers tailored solutions for various industries, including:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Food and Beverage:</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"> Eliminate stockouts and shortages by using real-time order-level visibility and predictive insights.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Retail:</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"> Improve on-time performance by making smarter decisions with historical data about every route used.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Life Sciences:</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"> Maintain product integrity and deliver goods quickly, including perishable and temperature-controlled shipments.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">End-to-End Visibility</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Movement by project44 sets a new standard for end-to-end visibility. The platform connects shippers to every order and every shipment on any mode of transportation, anywhere in the world. By bringing predictability to supply chains, project44 enables businesses to make informed decisions and optimize their operations.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Global Reach</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">project44 seamlessly connects with all carriers, forwarders, and facilities, eliminating visibility gaps common with simple tracking and single-mode visibility. Whether it\'s air, land, or sea transportation, project44 has you covered.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">In conclusion, project44 is on a mission to revolutionize supply chains worldwide. With its High-Velocity Supply Chain Platform, the company is empowering shippers to transform their operations from cost centers into revenue generators. By providing real-time visibility, transparency, and optimization capabilities, project44 is helping businesses improve customer experiences, reduce costs, and increase cash flow. Join the movement today!<br></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\"><strong>Jett McCandless, Founder and CEO: Visionary Leader of project44, a Global Logistics Technology Pioneer</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Jett McCandless is founder and CEO of project44, the world&rsquo;s leading High-Velocity Supply Chain Platform. Under Jett&rsquo;s leadership, project44 has grown into a $2.7 billion &ldquo;unicorn&rdquo; that tracks over 1 billion shipments annually in 185+ countries for over 1,300 leading brands. The company generates more than $100 million in annual recurring revenue (ARR), the largest SaaS generation 2 logistics tech in the world.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">An entrepreneur with over 20 years of transportation and logistics experience, Jett has guided multiple early-stage companies from ideation, startup, expansion through to maturity. Jett previously founded Metafora (formerly CarrierDirect), an Inc 500-listed advisory firm, after selling his stake in GlobalTranz, a $2+ billion 3PL where he was Executive Vice President and Principal. A longtime adrenaline seeker, Jett gets his thrills from whitewater SUP, heli-skiing, downhill mountain biking, and parenting.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong>&ldquo;We operate the most trusted end-to-end visibility platform that tracks more than 1 billion shipments annually for the world&rsquo;s leading brands.&rdquo;</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">&nbsp;</span></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'project44-is-on-a-mission-to-make-supply-chains-work', '2023-07-06', 'us/visionariesnetwork-jett-mccandless-project44.webp', 12, 'Profile12', 'project44 is on a mission - to make supply chains work', 'project44, supply chains, best companies, best magazine, visionariesnetwork', 'project44 is on a mission - to make supply chains work', NULL, 1, 'no', '', '', '', '', ''),
(77, 1, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong>Remedy Payment Solutions aims to offer transparent pricing and personalized service</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">At</span> Remedy Payment Solutions, the team believes that taking care of the company&rsquo;s clients is the key to building long-term relationships. Their mission is to provide competitive pricing and exceptional service to merchants who accept electronic payments, setting them apart from other payment processing companies. With over 15 years of experience in the industry, Remedy has established itself as a trusted and knowledgeable partner for businesses of all sizes. The company&rsquo;s goal is to be your \"partner in success,\" using its expertise to help you grow your business while reducing your processing fees.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Retail</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">For retail businesses, Remedy offers a range of solutions to streamline credit card processing and improve efficiency. Its countertop terminals, point of sale systems, and online reporting tools make it easy to manage transactions and track sales. Plus, its PCI and EMV compliant systems ensure that your customers\' sensitive information is protected.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Card Not Present</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">For businesses that process payments remotely, such as phone or email transactions, Remedy offers virtual terminals, recurring billing, customer profile management, and payment links. It&rsquo;s simple-to-use solutions make it easy to automate monthly payments and reduce errors.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Mobile Payments</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Remedy&rsquo;s mobile payment solutions allow you to accept payments on the go, using EMV/swipe card readers, Bluetooth connectivity, reliable hardware, and contactless payments. Whether you\'re a food truck or a travel company, Remedy&rsquo;s mobile payment solutions are designed to keep you moving.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Integrated Payments</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">For businesses with e-commerce platforms or software applications, </span>Remedy Payment Solutions<span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"> offer seamless integration with its transaction tokenization, SDKs and APIs, gateway integration, and experienced developers. The company&rsquo;s solution-based approach ensures that your payment processing is efficient and secure.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">What Separates </span>Remedy Payment Solutions?</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">At Remedy Payment Solutions, the team dedicated to making a positive impact in the payment processing industry. With over 15 years of experience, it saved clients over $1 million annually in processing fees. Remedy is one of the most trusted and knowledgeable credit card processors in the industry, and its solution-based partnership approach has earned us the endorsement of software providers, state and national associations.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Why Merchants Choose Remedy</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Business owners choose Remedy because it is honest and accessible whenever they need something. Its services include:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Chargeback support with monitoring, email notifications, and personalized support</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Guaranteed savings: If </span>Remedy Payment Solutions<span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"> can\'t save you money on your processing fees, they&rsquo;ll give you $500</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">PCI compliance: Remedy does the heavy lifting to ensure payment compliance</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">No cancellation fee: Cancel at any time with zero early termination fees</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Payment concierge: 24/7 personalized customer support</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Integration specialists: In-house software and e-commerce integration experts</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Next day deposits: Batch as late as 10pm EST and receive funds the next business day</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 5.25pt 0cm .0001pt 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; color: #4a4a4a;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\"><strong>Meet Alex Dimitracopoulos, Founder and CEO</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Alex Dimitracopoulos is a seasoned CEO and Founder with a proven track record of success in the financial services, moving and storage, and telecommunications industries. With over many years of experience, Alex has developed a unique blend of skills that enable him to drive business growth, build strong relationships, and develop effective strategies.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Throughout his career, Alex has held various leadership positions, including CEO, where he has been responsible for setting the overall vision and direction of the organization. He has a proven ability to lead cross-functional teams, develop and execute business plans, and drive revenue growth through strategic partnerships and innovative solutions.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Alex\'s expertise spans sales, sales management, people management, strategic partnerships, product development, operations management, and contract negotiation. He has a deep understanding of the importance of building strong relationships with clients and partners, and has developed a reputation for being a trusted advisor and thought leader in his industry.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">As a results-driven executive, Alex is known for his ability to drive business results through data-driven decision making and a focus on continuous improvement. He is well-versed in market trends and technologies, and is always looking for ways to leverage innovation to stay ahead of the competition.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Alex holds a Bachelor\'s degree in Economics where he developed a strong foundation in financial analysis, economic theory, and business strategy. He is a passionate advocate for professional development and continuous learning, and has completed various courses and certifications in leadership, sales, and marketing.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong>&ldquo;We\'ve saved companies over $1,000,000 in processing fees while providing unrivaled solutions and support.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'remedy-payment-solutions-aims-to-offer-transparent-pricing-and-personalized-service', '2023-07-06', 'us/visionariesnetwork-alex-dimitracopoulos-remedy.webp', 14, 'Profile14', 'Remedy Payment Solutions aims to offer transparent pricing and personalized service', 'Remedy Payment Solutions,  transparent pricing, personalized service, best magazine, best company', 'Remedy Payment Solutions aims to offer transparent pricing and personalized service', NULL, 1, 'no', '', '', '', '', ''),
(78, 1, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong>Scytale is the global leader in security compliance automation, helping companies get compliant and stay&nbsp;compliant with security frameworks</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">As a SaaS company, you know how important compliance is. You\'ve probably spent countless hours pouring over complex regulations, gathering evidence, and dealing with auditors\' requests for additional information. It\'s a tedious and time-consuming process that takes away from your core business operations. But what if you could simplify this process and free up more time to focus on what matters most - growing your company?</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">That\'s exactly what Scytale does. It saw the struggles that SaaS companies were facing with compliance and decided to do something about it. They brought together a team of experts in compliance and technology to create a platform that automates compliance requirements, making it easy for companies to stay compliant without sacrificing their precious time.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Scytale&rsquo;s journey began with a simple observation: compliance is not fun. In fact, it\'s often tedious, administrative, and lengthy. But they believed that with their expertise and passion, they could totally transform the way SaaS companies deal with compliance. The company designed its platform to be next-generation, carefully crafting each feature to simplify the process and make it more efficient.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Scytale&rsquo;s platform is built around the concept of \"compliance as a service.\" With Scytale, you\'ll have your very own dedicated compliance expert who will guide you through every step of the compliance process. You\'ll receive weekly meetings with your expert, hands-on support to navigate the company&rsquo;s automation tool, advisory from industry veterans, and tailored guidance to help you build a robust information security system.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">But that\'s not all. Scytale also knows how painful audits can be, with endless emails and Zoom meetings with auditors requesting additional information or evidence. That\'s why Scytale offers a unique service where it takes over full management of your audit process with your chosen auditor, freeing you up to focus on your actual job.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Penetration testing is another area where Scytale excels. Scytale helps you streamline the process of identifying security vulnerabilities and document how they can be exploited by an attacker. You\'ll no longer have to worry about managing multiple tools and spreadsheets; Scytale&rsquo;s platform will do it all for you.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Vendor risk management is another area where Scytale has seen significant pain points in the market. Its automated vendor risk management feature allows you to simplify the process of onboarding new vendors, conducting risk assessments, and tracking risks associated with each vendor. You\'ll no longer have to juggle multiple spreadsheets or tools; Scytale&rsquo;s platform will do it all for you.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">At Scytale, the team understands that every company is unique, which is why it offers a customized approach to your needs from day one. The company&rsquo;s platform is designed to integrate seamlessly into your existing workflows, ensuring a smooth transition into the world of compliance.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">So why let compliance get in the way of your business? With Scytale, you can focus on what matters most - growing your company - while they handle the complexities of compliance for you. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Here are some key features that set Scytale apart:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Dedicated compliance expert:</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"> Your very own expert who will guide you through every step of the compliance process.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Automation:</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"> Scytale&rsquo;s platform automates compliance requirements, making it easy for you to stay compliant without sacrificing precious time.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Penetration testing:</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"> Scytale helps you streamline the process of identifying security vulnerabilities and document how they can be exploited by an attacker.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Vendor risk management:</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"> Simplify the process of onboarding new vendors, conducting risk assessments, and tracking risks associated with each vendor.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Customized approach:</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"> Scytale understands that every company is unique, which is why it offers a customized approach to your needs from day one.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Seamless integration: </span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Scytale&rsquo;s platform is designed to integrate seamlessly into your existing workflows.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">At Scytale, the team is committed to revolutionizing the way SaaS companies approach compliance. They believe that with their expertise and passion, they can make compliance easier, faster, and more efficient.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Short bio of Meiran Galis, CEO</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">&ldquo;We test web applications, mobile applications, API testing, infrastructure (internal and external networks), and more.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'scytale-is-the-global-leader-in-security-compliance-automation', '2023-07-06', 'us/visionariesnetwork-scytale-meiran-galis.webp', 15, 'profile15', 'Scytale is the global leader in security compliance automation, helping companies get compliant and stay compliant with security frameworks', 'Scytale, global leader, security compliance automation, security frameworks, best magazine, best company', 'Scytale is the global leader in security compliance automation, helping companies get compliant and stay compliant with security frameworks', NULL, 1, 'no', '', '', '', '', '');
