(79, 1, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">SIMETRY: Your Partner in IoT Deployment and Management</span></strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">SIMETRY understands the complexities and challenges that come with running an IoT deployment. With over two decades of experience working alongside Stallion Infrastructure Services, their parent company, they have honed their expertise in providing solutions for remote connectivity in challenging environments.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Through their partnership with Stallion Infrastructure Services, SIMETRY has gained valuable insights into the intricacies of IoT management and has developed a dedicated team to address these challenges head-on. Their team is equipped with the knowledge and skills necessary to navigate the complexities of IoT deployments and ensure their success.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">By leveraging their extensive experience and expertise, SIMETRY is able to offer comprehensive solutions that address the unique needs of each IoT deployment. Whether it\'s overcoming connectivity issues in remote locations or managing large-scale deployments, SIMETRY is committed to providing reliable and effective solutions that meet the demands of today\'s interconnected world.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Secure Your Wireless IoT Network</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">SIMETRY</span> <span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">suite of cellular cybersecurity features protects against network vulnerabilities, excessive data usage, and spend. With SIMETRY, you can rest assured that your network is secure and reliable.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">What is Private APN?</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">A Private APN (Access Point Name) offers a secure point of entry onto an IP network for a cellular device. Unlike traditional network setups that use a Public APN shared with users from inside and outside your organization, a Private APN provides a dedicated access point to an isolated network for your organization.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Benefits of Private APN with SIMETRY</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">With SIMETRY\'s Private APN, your devices access the carrier networks through private IPsec tunnels, creating a secure and reliable private network for your data.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Use any device with a SIM:</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"> Combine your total cellular data usage from all carriers into one plan.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">End-to-End Encryption:</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"> Get tier-1 data from major carriers and superior support from SIMETRY.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Control Data Use &amp; Costs:</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"> Track and control your fleet of IoT devices from one unified platform.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Complete M2M Connectivity Solutions</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">SIMETRY is the M2M extension your organization needs. It offers M2M SIM cards and M2M data plans from major carriers with exceptional customer support. Using SIMETRY as your complete M2M vendor helps you deploy faster, control cost, and save time with M2M data services from a single contact and bill.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">The SIMETRY Advantage</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Tier-1 Business Data:</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"> Get reliable, optimized wireless connectivity from the major carriers &ndash; free of throttling.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">In-House 24/7 Support:</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"> Support your organization with a dedicated, reliable M2M connectivity support team.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Ensuring Connectivity to Healthcare Devices:</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"> Connect all of your healthcare IoT devices to a safe and secure cellular connection that keeps patients visible and your operation running smoothly and efficiently.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Limited Carrier Usage</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Other companies may lock you into a specific carrier, but not SIMETRY. The company allows multiple carriers on one plan and SIM card, so you experience failover and flexible data wherever you go. Don\'t lose connectivity again.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Payment Flexibility</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Don\'t get roped into prepaid data plans. With SIMETRY, you only pay for what you use. You can easily access your billing and data from any of your devices through its customer portal.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Out of the Box Connectivity</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">With SIMETRY, there\'s no downtime with out-of-the-box connectivity implementation. No need for manual configuration on your side. Leave it all to SIMETRY and experience the SIMETRY difference in no time.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">24/7 Support</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">With SIMETRY, you have access to the knowledge of its support team around the clock. They are there to support your IoT data needs when you need them.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">At SIMETRY, the team is committed to helping you overcome the challenges of IoT deployment and management. The company&rsquo;s team is here to provide you with the expertise and support you need to keep your operations running smoothly and efficiently.&nbsp;<br></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\"><strong>Cash Blackburn, General Manager</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">&ldquo;Simplify IoT data plans, device management, and support with our IoT service provider.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong>&ldquo;SIMETRY began as a solution for IoT management problems. Now, we help our customers eliminate them.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'simetry-your-partner-in-iot-deployment-and-management', '2023-07-06', 'us/visionariesnetwork-simetry-cash-blackburn.webp', 16, 'Profile16', 'SIMETRY: Your Partner in IoT Deployment and Management', 'SIMETRY: Your Partner in IoT Deployment and Management', 'SIMETRY: Your Partner in IoT Deployment and Management', NULL, 1, 'no', '', '', '', '', ''),
(80, 1, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong>Revolutionizing Education with VictoryXR: Bringing Immersive Learning to the Forefront</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">In today\'s rapidly evolving educational landscape, traditional teaching methods are being challenged by the emergence of innovative technologies. One company, VictoryXR, is at the forefront of this revolution, introducing virtual and augmented reality to the classroom to enhance student learning experiences. Founded in 2016 by Steve Grubbs, VictoryXR has grown from a small startup to a company with over 25 employees and a presence in two offices in Davenport, Iowa, and Austin, Texas.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>The Problem with Traditional Online Education</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Online education has become increasingly popular, but traditional online classrooms often fall short in providing an engaging and interactive experience for students. Video conferencing can be dull and unengaging, leading to decreased student focus and motivation. This is where VictoryXR comes in, offering immersive classrooms and campuses through virtual reality (VR). Their platforms enable students to interact with educators and peers in a synchronous yet virtual environment, making learning more enjoyable and effective.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>The Benefits of VictoryXR</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">VictoryXR\'s platforms have been shown to increase student grades, focus, and enjoyment. With over 6,000 3D objects available for teaching various subjects, educators have access to a vast library of resources to create engaging lessons. The company\'s commitment to accessibility ensures that students with disabilities can also participate in these immersive experiences.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Accessibility and ADA Compliance</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">VictoryXR takes accessibility seriously, recognizing that not all users may be able to access their platforms using assistive devices. While VR technology may not be ideal for all users, the company acknowledges its limitations and is committed to improving accessibility as the technology develops.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Unlock the Power of Immersive Education with VictoryXR</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">VictoryXR is revolutionizing the way students learn with its cutting-edge virtual and augmented reality platforms, VXRLabs and VXRWeb. With these innovative tools, students can experience immersive learning like never before, engaging in interactive simulations, field trips, and hands-on activities that make learning fun and effective.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">VXRLabs: A Turnkey Solution for Immersive Learning</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">VXRLabs is a VR platform that offers a wide range of interactive simulations and lab experiences for learning, covering various subjects such as CTE, history, science, math, literature, and more. The platform is designed to be multiplayer and synchronous, allowing students to collaborate with classmates and peers from around the world in a fun and engaging way.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">VXRWeb: High-Definition Immersive Learning</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">VXRWeb is a web-based platform that offers high-definition immersive learning experiences on Mac, Chromebook, or PC. Students can access dozens of 360&ordm; field trips in the VictoryXR: Global Traveler app, interactive literature and museum experiences, and more.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">VictoryXR License: The Best Immersive Education Bundle</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">The VictoryXR License is the best immersive education bundle on the market. It includes a license for both VXRLabs and VXRWeb, allowing two students to benefit from one subscription.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Immersive Learning Opportunities</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">VictoryXR offers a range of immersive learning opportunities for students, including:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Conducting mess-free animal dissections and chemistry experiments</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Studying astronomy with a trip to space</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Exploring pivotal moments in history</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Going on job shadows</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Conducting science experiments with unlimited practice</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Forklift Simulator Training</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">The forklift trainer simulation is perfect for companies that hire forklift drivers. The simulation prepares users for national forklift driver certification and provides low-stakes learning.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Fire Extinguisher Simulation</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">The Fire Extinguisher Simulator trains users in fire event evaluation, the fire safety triangle, types of fires, extinguishers to use, and extinguisher technique and best practices.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">Experience the Future of Education with VictoryXR</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: EN-IN;\">VictoryXR is changing the face of education by providing immersive learning experiences that engage students and make learning fun. With its innovative platforms and tools, VictoryXR is helping to create a global learning community that is connected, collaborative, and effective.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\"><strong>Meet Steve Grubbs, CEO and Co-Founder of VictoryXR</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">As a visionary leader in the VR education industry, Steve Grubbs is dedicated to revolutionizing the way people learn and teach. With over 6 years of experience, he has assembled a team of educators, developers, and designers to create cutting-edge, AI-powered learning experiences for schools, corporations, and colleges.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Steve&rsquo;s entrepreneurial spirit has driven him to found and lead several successful ventures. He owns VictoryStore.com, a leading online retailer of custom products and promotional items. He also founded Victory Enterprises, a technology services and IT consulting firm, where he served as past chair. Additionally, he created ChalkBites, a mobile app connecting businesses with immersive training.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Steve holds a J.D. from the University of Iowa College of Law and was a former chairman of the House Education Committee in the Iowa House of Representatives. He is an active member of YPO, the global leadership community of chief executives, and chaired the YPO Technology Network for two years.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Through his work at VictoryXR, Steve is committed to leveraging technology, innovation, and education to make a positive impact on the world. His team and he are dedicated to creating immersive learning experiences that transform the way people learn and teach.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong>&ldquo;We provide AI and XR (VR, AR, MR) services for businesses and schools which include labs, digital twin campuses, global field trips and simulators. Our 3D spatial AI avatars are changing the world of training and learning.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'revolutionizing-education-with-victoryxr-bringing-immersive-learning-to-the-forefront', '2023-07-06', 'us/visionariesnetwork-victoryxr-steve-grubbs.webp', 17, 'Profile17', 'VictoryXR Brings Immersive Learning to Education', 'VictoryXR, immersive learning, virtual reality, education tech, VR classrooms, metaverse learning, EdTech, visionaries network, digital learning, online education, VR in schools, future of education, VictoryXR platform, 3D learning, educational innovation', 'VictoryXR is transforming education with immersive learning experiences using virtual and augmented reality for next-gen classrooms and training environments.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.victoryxr.com/', 'https://www.victoryxr.com/', 'VictoryXR', '2016', 'Davenpt, Iowa'),
(81, 7, '<p><strong>Peasum is a consulting firm that primarily builds synergy between people, products, processes &amp; providers</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In today\'s fast-paced and ever-changing business landscape, companies must be agile, innovative, and customer-centric to stay ahead of the competition. At Peasum, the team specialize in business transformation, leveraging strategic insights and cutting-edge methods to drive growth, efficiency, and excellence. The company&rsquo;s team of experts is dedicated to helping organizations like yours thrive in the market by fostering strategic partnerships, prioritizing continuous improvement, and delivering tailored solutions that meet unique customer needs.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Fostering Strategic Partnerships</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Peasum, the team believes that strategic partnerships are the key to achieving exceptional results. They work closely with their clients to understand their goals, challenges, and aspirations, and develop customized solutions that align with their business objectives.&nbsp; Peasum&rsquo;s partnership approach ensures seamless collaboration, open communication, and a shared commitment to success.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Continuous Improvement</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Peasum is committed to continuous improvement, constantly enhancing its strategies and methodologies to deliver long-lasting results. Its team of experts stays up-to-date with the latest trends, technologies, and best practices in the industry, ensuring that its clients receive the most effective and efficient solutions possible.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Business Operations</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Excellent business operations are essential for driving efficiency, effectiveness, and success. At Peasum, the team prioritizes process optimization, ensuring that its clients\' businesses run smoothly and efficiently. They identify areas for improvement, streamline processes, and implement scalable solutions that drive growth and profitability.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Solution Delivery</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Peasum&rsquo;s expertise lies in delivering precise, timely, and tailored solutions that meet its clients\' specific needs and expectations. It leverages its extensive network of technology partners to provide innovative solutions that drive business outcomes. Its solution delivery process is designed to ensure seamless integration with existing systems and processes.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Customer Satisfaction</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Peasum, customer satisfaction is their top priority. They strive to deliver exceptional service through personalized support and innovative solutions that exceed their clients\' expectations. The company listens carefully to their needs, understands their goals, and works collaboratively to develop solutions that meet their unique requirements.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Preparing for the Future</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In today\'s digital age, businesses must be prepared to adapt quickly to changing market conditions, technological advancements, and shifting employee expectations. At Peasum, the team helps organizations align their business goals with technology and inspire employee engagement through innovative thinking, skill development, and supportive organizational structures.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Tailored Solutions for Unique Customer Needs</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Peasum understands that every business is unique, with its own set of challenges and opportunities. That\'s why they start by understanding their clients\' needs and then use their expertise and extensive network of technology partners to deliver efficient, tailored solutions that meet their specific requirements.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Turning Strategy into Success Together</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Peasum, the team believes that strategy must be translated into tangible results. They work closely with their clients to align their operating models with their strategic goals, streamline processes, and enhance efficiency. Through careful listening and drawing on cross-industry expertise, the company tailors and implements solutions that enable their clients\' strategic objectives.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Drive Your Business Growth</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Peasum partners with its clients to quickly develop products that advance their business goals. Its strategies focus on reducing time-to-market and improving features while upskilling teams to ensure ongoing success after project completion.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Prioritizing People in Design</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Peasum, the team believes that people are at the heart of every successful business. They develop integrated solutions that consistently deliver experiences everyone loves by staying ahead of evolving trends and technologies while driven by their clients\' needs.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Free Consultation</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Peasum, the team offers a free consultation to help you identify the right combination of services needed to drive efficient, faster, and better results.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Peasum Process</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Peasum&rsquo;s process is designed to deliver exceptional results:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Analysis: Peasum deeply understands your \"what\" and \"why\".</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Collaboration: The company works with you to design your \"how\".</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Delivery: Peasum employs its services in end-to-end solutions to deliver your \"wow\".</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>UCHE OTI, Senior Partner</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With 20 years of experience, Uche leads Peasum&rsquo;s Business Transformation team as a Senior Partner. He specializes in enhancing service delivery within social housing and public sectors through strategic and analytical expertise. His leadership drives projects to successful outcomes and fosters solutions that address the dynamic needs of public entities.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We excel in delivering expert business solutions that are precise, timely, and tailored to meet your client&rsquo;s expectations and their business requirements.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'peasum-is-a-consulting-firm-that-primarily-builds-synergy-between-people-products-processes-providers', '2022-05-14', 'us/visionaries-networ-ucheti-kayo-peasum-senior-partner.webp', 4, 'profile', 'Peasum: Synergy-Driven Consulting for Business Success', 'Peasum, consulting, synergy, people, products, processes, providers, business strategy, optimization, innovation, growth, transformation, collaboration, operations, visionaries-network', 'Peasum is a consulting firm focused on creating synergy between people, products, processes, and providers to drive sustainable business success.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.peasum.com/', 'https://uk.linkedin.com/company/peasum-consults?trk=public_profile_topcard-current-company', 'Peasum', ' 2019', 'London'),
(82, 7, '<p><strong>Swarm Digital Marketing is a boutique digital marketing agency that specializes specifically in website development and search engine optimization</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Since 2019, Swarm Digital Marketing has been making a digital swagger, if you will, within the boundaries set by the industry. With locations in New York City and Tampa, Florida, the company has grown from its founders\' combined experience of 25 years in the digital market.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Swarm Digital, they are dedicated to building a digital marketing agency that truly works for the client. Leveraging their vast network of marketing geniuses at their fingertips, they were able to come up with truly innovative solutions that help businesses succeed amid constant change within the digital space.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">One of Swarm Digital\'s most innovative solutions is SwarmSEO&mdash;a WordPress plug-in that drives local visitors to client websites. This technology maximizes on the fact that 4 out of every 5 searches locally end with a sale&mdash;a fact where proximity or location is commonly plugged into this search. SwarmSEO helps businesses to capture such opportunities by optimizing websites for local SEO.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Web Design and Development are also key services provided by Swarm Digital. The business represents customers in building websites, redesigning previously existing sites, and providing subsequent maintenance with updates to ensure flawless performance. Having custom WordPress theme design and development expertise, Swarm Digital is able to create custom solutions to deal with specific needs for clients.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Another area of attention that Swarm Digital puts forward is e-commerce. Their experience includes building an online storefront using WordPress, Shopify, and Magento. Be it placing orders and processing online payments or enhancing the existing capabilities of e-commerce, Swarm Digital has the right expertise to get things done.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The list of Swarm Digital\'s expertise includes website development, web application, and software development. Custom software development is realized by developing solutions that satisfy customers\' special needs for either internal purposes or as a service-based product.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Mobile app development is another mastery area that Swarm Digital can boast about. The demand for mobile applications these days keeps growing, hence the company develops apps that often help businesses operate more effectively or give their customers services in the best way possible.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">SEO forms a very important part of any digital marketing strategy. Swarm Digital has a team of veteran SEO experts who help clients rank organically for relevant keywords. Swarm Digital achieves this by applying techniques such as keyword research, on-page optimization, and link building to ensure organic traffic to their clients\' websites.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Logo design services by Swarm Digital provide top-notch logos, followed by a \"logo package\" of that logo in many different file types and colors. These logos can be used on many diverse platforms from screen and print to signage.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Lastly, Swarm Digital has Search Engine Marketing, or SEM, as its final service in this category. The company manages campaigns containing Display Ads, YouTube Pre-rolls, Extended Network Placements, and PPC campaigns on Google and Bing.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Apart from these services, Swarm Digital offers brand development services to help clients in their effort to position their brands within the market. The swarm digital branding expert would help a particular business in attaining its goal by producing a comprehensive understanding of a brand\'s identity and messaging.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Swarm Digital Marketing is an all-in-one solution for any businesses intending to create or improve an online presence. This innovative agency is sure to continue making waves in the digital marketing sector, with new solutions, a great deal of experience, and a commitment to customer satisfaction.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Matthew Weitzman, Co-Founder</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Matthew is Swarm Digital Marketing\'s resident tech expert with a whopping 12 years of experience in the industry. His impressive background spans web application architecture, WordPress development, HTML, PHP, and API integration. Be prepared to geek out with him on topics like mark-up, tracking codes, security protocols, and database architecture - he\'s a true tech aficionado! When not conjuring up innovative digital solutions, Matt can be found whipping up gourmet meals, playing with his adorable Frenchie pup, or taking a run along the scenic East River in New York City.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;Swarm has in turn developed a proprietary automated inbound marketing platform that is changing the way local SEO is done for all businesses.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'swarm-digital-marketing-is-a-boutique-digital-marketing-agency-that-specializes-specifically-in-website', '2022-05-14', 'us/visionaries-network-mathew-co-founder-swarm-digital.webp', 5, 'profile', 'Swarm Digital: SEO & Website Development Experts', 'Swarm Digital, digital marketing, SEO, website development, boutique agency, web design, search engine optimization, online presence, branding, visionaries network, conversion, UX, strategy, growth', 'Swarm Digital Marketing is a boutique agency specializing in website development and SEO to help businesses grow online and boost search visibility.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.swarmdigital.io/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/64961299/admin/', 'Swarm Digital Marketing', '2019', 'New York, USA'),
(83, 7, '<p><strong>Total Expert unifies data, marketing, sales, and compliance solutions to deliver the perfect customer journey across every financial milestone</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In an increasingly competitive landscape, financial institutions are recognizing the importance of creating deeper, human-first connections with modern consumers. At Total Expert, the team believes that empowering banks, credit unions, lenders, insurance agencies, and other financial services firms to do so will create a financially healthier world.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Total Expert&rsquo;s team has spent years studying the banking and lending industries to develop a platform that is grounded in real needs. The result is the most innovative, integrated technology in the industry &ndash; and the only one that puts customer experience first.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">To achieve this, the company has created an all-in-one customer engagement platform that unites internal teams and fosters communication, collaboration, and better outcomes for customers. With its platform, financial institutions can redefine sales and marketing collaboration, streamline customer engagement, and drive more referrals from professional relationships.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The platform is designed to help financial institutions maximize productivity and streamline customer engagement by providing prioritized lead lists, a 360-degree customer view, co-marketing capabilities, lead management, workflow management, dashboards and pipeline views, and more.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">One of the key features of Total Expert&rsquo;s platform is its ability to help financial institutions identify the leads and customers that their teams should engage with first. This is achieved through prioritized lead lists, which quickly identify which customers and opportunities to engage with. The platform also provides a single source for all customer and engagement information, making it easier for financial institutions to initiate the next best discussion or present the most relevant product for each customer\'s financial journey.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Another important aspect of Total Expert&rsquo;s platform is its ability to drive more referrals from professional relationships. This is achieved through co-marketing capabilities that tap into professional networks to create engaging co-marketing assets with built-in compliance workflows.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In addition to these features, the company&rsquo;s platform also includes lead generation and routing capabilities that help financial institutions generate more loans in any market. This is achieved through targeted messaging that gets in front of every borrower, quickly connecting them to the right loan officer to support their homebuying needs.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The platform also includes tools that help reduce the administrative burden on teams by categorizing leads and prioritizing opportunities. This ensures that financial institutions can focus on what matters most &ndash; providing exceptional customer service and building strong relationships with their customers.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In today\'s digital age, consumers have come to expect a seamless and personalized experience when interacting with financial institutions. Total Expert&rsquo;s platform is designed to meet this expectation by providing a single source for all customer and engagement information, making it easier for financial institutions to initiate the next best discussion or present the most relevant product for each customer\'s financial journey.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The mortgage industry is particularly ripe for disruption. According to recent research, a record number of consumers pounced on fleeting interest rates in the first half of 2021 to purchase new homes or refinance existing mortgages. And many of these consumers did it online.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As the mortgage market continues to evolve, financial institutions must adapt to meet the changing needs of their customers. Total Expert&rsquo;s platform is designed to help them do just that by providing a comprehensive solution for sales and marketing needs.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Joe Welu, Founder &amp; CEO</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Joe Welu is the founder and CEO of Total Expert, the fintech software leader that launched the first customer experience platform purpose-built for modern financial institutions. Since 2012, Joe has led Total Expert&rsquo;s vision, culture, and growth to more than 300 employees today. The company powers CRM, marketing, and customer engagement for more than 170 financial institutions&mdash;from leading community banks and credit unions to 15 of the top 25 U.S. banks and lenders. Total Expert&rsquo;s growth has skyrocketed since its inception, being named the #1 CRM platform by STRATMOR Group and earning top spots on the Inc. 5000 and HousingWire Tech100.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We turn customer insights into actions to increase loyalty and drive growth for banks, lenders, credit unions, and insurance companies.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'total-expert-unifies-data-marketing-sales-and-compliance-solutions-to-deliver-the-perfect-customer-journey-across-every-financial-milestone', '2022-05-14', 'us/visionaries-network-joe-welu-total-expert-founder.webp', 6, 'profile', 'Total Expert: Unified Marketing & Sales for Finance', 'Total Expert, customer journey, data, marketing, sales, compliance, finance, CRM, automation, customer experience, financial services, milestones, visionaries network, fintech, personalization', 'Total Expert connects data, marketing, sales, and compliance to create seamless customer journeys across key financial milestones with powerful automation and insights.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://totalexpert.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/total-expert/', 'Total Expert', '2012 ', 'St. Louis Park, Minnesota'),
(84, 7, '<p><strong>TUCU stands for Tech U Can Use. That&rsquo;s what it delivers. Tech you can use to protect your data, support your team, and grow your business</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">In the current dynamic digital world, technology forms an integral part of any business. When technology adds to the woes by performing below expectations, frustration sets in and results in irritating stress and loss of productivity. TUCU calls this \"techaches.\" TUCU understands how mission-critical seamless and secure IT operations are and is committed to delivering end-to-end tech support and new solutions to eradicate techaches and bring productivity to the forefront.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Why TUCU?</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">TUCU knows each business is different and so are your IT requirements&mdash;special. Therefore, it takes some time to understand your business goals and challenges before rushing into recommending solutions. Its expert team keeps up-to-date on the very latest trends and best practices in technology to ensure that your IT systems are always running smoothly and are really secure.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Aside from this continuous IT support, TUCU also provides proactive monitoring and maintenance in search of issues to solve before they actually occur. Its vision is to become your trusted partner in IT, assisting in understanding the ever-changing technology world and how one benefits from it. Be it a small startup or an established business, TUCU has the experience and expertise to help in achieving the desired IT goals.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Cybersecurity Solutions</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Effective cybersecurity for a small business is fundamental to this information digital ecosystem. TUCU offers end-to-end comprehensive cybersecurity solutions, covering all those aspects that could grant a business the best form of protection. This includes managed endpoint detection and repair tools for threat prevention and ransomware, identity management solutions to regain the control of your company\'s information and secure remote work setup to protect company data while providing flexibility to employees.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Azure Management &amp; Support Services</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">TUCU, a Microsoft Certified Consultants since 2003, lends it years of experience with Azure Cloud Solutions. Its Azure Cloud Consultants can therefore assist in realizing all of the above-mentioned benefits through the complete migration of IT systems in the cloud, retirement of your server, increasing mobility, and reducing hardware costs. It also offers Azure Cloud Support Services whereby outsourcing of Azure Cloud management and IT will enable you to focus on what you do best.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Strategic IT Advisory</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Cybersecurity does not live in a vacuum. Your business is dynamic, and new challenges or new opportunities seem to appear at a moment\'s notice. TUCU is always available to provide strategic IT consulting to help review your needs, implement changes as required, and manage every other technology field.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In summary, TUCU is the backbone in all aspects of technology for any small business operating in Toronto and its environments. These are innovative solutions that will rid your company of techaches through comprehensive tech support. Let it be cybersecurity solutions, Azure management services, strategic IT advisory, or any general help needed to progress your company&mdash;TUCU has all needed help available. Let the company handle your technology so you will be free to do what best suits your purpose.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Adam Thorn, Founder</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Adam Thorn has been providing expert IT security and technology management services to small business owners since 2003. Prior to establishing his freelance IT consulting career and later becoming the president of TUCU Managed IT Services in Toronto, he worked in Network Security at CIBC and HP Canada.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Since 2003, Adam has been dedicated to assisting small and mid-sized companies, as well as non-profit organizations, in building and securing their networks and servers, migrating to the cloud, virtualizing servers, protecting data, and keeping pace with the ever-changing technology and cybersecurity landscape.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As a seasoned IT consultant, Adam is committed to helping clients reduce risk, safeguard data, manage devices and accounts, support their teams, and drive business growth. His team is dedicated to providing comprehensive IT management services to fill the critical gaps in an organization\'s IT department.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;Our services range from computer support and cybersecurity to InfoSec screenings and IT compliance, all tailored to your needs.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'tucu-stands-for-tech-u-can-use--thats-what-it-delivers--tech-you-can-use-to-protect-your-data-support-your-team-and-grow-your-business', '2022-05-14', 'us/visionaries-network-adamthorn-tucu-founder.webp', 7, 'profile', 'TUCU: Tech You Can Use to Grow & Protect', 'TUCU, Tech U Can Use, IT support, cybersecurity, data protection, business growth, MSP, tech solutions, managed services, cloud, visionaries network, IT services, secure, team support, scalable', 'TUCU delivers Tech You Can Use&mdash;smart IT solutions to protect your data, support your team, and help your business grow securely and efficiently.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://tucu.ca/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/tucu', 'TUCU Managed IT Services Inc', '2003', 'Toronto, Ontario');
