(85, 7, '<p><strong>TBAT Innovation Ltd: A value-led independent consultancy working with technology &amp; research and development organizations all over the UK</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">In today\'s fast-paced business environment, innovation is the key to success. For technology and research and development organizations, securing the necessary funds to drive innovation is crucial. TBAT Innovation Ltd, a value-led independent consultancy with over 20 years of experience, understands the importance of offering a wide range of innovation support services to help companies succeed with their R&amp;D projects and add value to their clients. In this article, Visionaries Network will delve into the services offered by TBAT Innovation Ltd and explore the benefits of their expertise in grant funding and R&amp;D tax credits.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Core Values</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At TBAT Innovation Ltd, the team&rsquo;s core values are built around four key principles: Vibrant, Integrity, Collaboration, and Respect. Their enthusiastic business advisors are passionate about supporting growth through innovation and research &amp; development, ensuring that their services are delivered with trust, transparency, and honesty. They foster a collaborative environment, working closely with clients and stakeholders to ensure that their services meet their needs.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>TBAT Innovation Promises to You</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">TBAT&rsquo;s approach each client and project with utmost care and attention, treating them as their own. To ensure quality and compliance, they have implemented various processes, including ISO9001 Accreditation and Anti-Money Laundering Checks. TBAT&rsquo;s in-house accountants review all financial reports before submitting data to HMRC, and provide HMRC Enquiry Support to ensure that their clients receive the credit they deserve.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>R&amp;D Tax Credits</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The R&amp;D Tax Credits scheme is an HMRC incentive designed to encourage innovation and increased spending on R&amp;D activities by UK businesses. Claiming R&amp;D Tax Credits can be a complex process, but TBAT Innovation Ltd.&rsquo;s expert consultants can guide you through it. TBAT&rsquo;s aim is to simplify the process with minimal disruption to your business, ensuring that you receive the credit you deserve.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>R&amp;D Tax Credit Calculator</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">TBAT&rsquo;s R&amp;D Tax Credit Calculator provides an indicative figure on how much R&amp;D Tax Relief you could receive from HMRC. This can be done for the current financial year and the two previous years.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>R&amp;D Tax Credits Schemes</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The UK government offers various R&amp;D tax credit schemes, including the SME R&amp;D tax credit scheme and the R&amp;D expenditure credit (RDEC) scheme for larger companies. These schemes aim to stimulate technological advancement and drive economic growth by supporting businesses in their pursuit of innovation and development.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Online R&amp;D Tax Portal</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">TBAT Innovation Ltd.&rsquo;s Online R&amp;D Tax Portal is an expert-supported, interactive online system that allows you to process your own claim hassle-free. This innovative system provides increased visibility of your claim from start to finish, allowing you to provide information at anytime from anywhere.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>How the Online Portal Works</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The Online Portal is designed for all manner of claim sizes and complexity. Depending on your preference, you can input key company, financial, or technical information yourself or work with an R&amp;D Tax Consultant to complete the claim. The system is flexible and adaptable, allowing you to work with your accountant or invite key individuals to specific sections of the claim.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Sam Stephens, Director</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Sam Stephens, Director of TBAT, founded the company in 2002 as a comprehensive consultancy, dedicated to supporting small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs). Over the course of the next five years, TBAT evolved into the innovation-driven enterprise it is today, with a focus on guiding companies through the entire lifecycle of new product and process innovation.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As a passionate engineer, Stephens has been fascinated by mechanical innovation from a young age, having spent his childhood tinkering with lawnmower-powered go-karts and radio-controlled aircraft. This passion still remains strong today, as he enjoys vintage and classic car restoration.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Stephens began his career as a graduate and manufacturing engineer at Rolls-Royce Aerospace before moving to Rolls-Royce and Associates as a Development and Project Engineer. During his four-year tenure, he designed and implemented repairs to the UK\'s nuclear submarine fleet, gaining valuable experience in engineering and an appreciation for the deployment of new technology in demanding environments. Later, he spent three years as a project manager at Alstom, overseeing gas turbine development and testing, which further expanded his skill set and knowledge. Currently, Stephens heads up Business Development and R&amp;D Tax Credits at TBAT.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We can help you access Grant Funding, R&amp;D Tax Credits, Video Games Tax Relief, SEIS / EIS, Capital Allowances, and Patent Box.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'tbat-innovation-ltd-a-value-led-independent-consultancy-working-with-technology-research-and-development-organizations-all-over-the-uk', '2022-05-14', 'us/visionaries-network-sam-stephens-director-tbat-innovation.webp', 8, 'profile', 'TBAT Innovation: UK R&D and Tech Consultancy', 'TBAT Innovation, consultancy, R&amp;D, technology, visionaries network, funding, research, grants, tax credits, business growth, value-led, independent, development', 'TBAT Innovation Ltd is a UK-based consultancy supporting technology and R&amp;D organizations with funding, strategy, and growth through expert, value-led services.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://tbat.co.uk/', 'https://uk.linkedin.com/company/tbat-innovation-ltd', 'TBAT Innovation Ltd', ' 2002', ' Derbyshire, United Kingdom'),
(86, 7, '<p><strong>From Web Design and Development to Media Production and Public Relations, Twelve12 does all the work so you focus on your customers</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">Twelve12 is a full-service branding, marketing, and sales agency that has built a concrete position within the industry through new effective solutions for small businesses. Backed by a robust team of professionals with an eagerness to help business growth empower and see entrepreneurship thrive in the true sense, Twelve12 provides its clients with comprehensive services to achieve their goals.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Therefore, Twelve12 delivery is deeply founded on the notion of branding. It reckons that a business cannot dream of emerging as an industry leader unless it has in place a well-threshold identity. Be that as it may, Twelve12 offers a wide array of branding services geared towards giving clients a strong brand identity bound to communicate, inspire, and resonate with their target audience.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Twelve12 finalizes logo design as part of twelve key services. The group of in-house experienced designers works very closely with clients to come up with logos that are not only memorable but also unique and reflective of the brand values and personality. From concept to completion, Twelve12\'s logo design process ensures a final product that clients will love.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">This is not all, as Twelve12 will also help to come up with a name for your company apart from the logo design. Experts from this agency will help provide a brand a name that best suits its values, personality, and mission. That includes researching existing trademarks, conducting market research, and recommending the perfect name.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Twelve12 also offers services in visual identity&mdash;from developing color schemes and typography to imagery related to the brand\'s overall aesthetic. Their team is involved with clients in creating a visual identity that is going to be used throughout all marketing channels and platforms.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Another key offering Twelve12 has is creative strategy. Their team of experts comes up with comprehensive creative strategies pointing out how the brand will communicate its message down to its target audience. This would involve determining channels that would best do the communication to the target audience, developing messaging they can really relate to, and creating content to drive results.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Twelve12 Marketing specializes in lead-based and sales-first services. These include lead generation, leadership training, advertisement, and campaign development.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">One of the most critical facets of the marketing services offered at Twelve12 is lead generation. The company will help the clients look for leads, whether through online landing pages, traditional mail campaigns, or any other means possible. This means the identification of potential customers who would have a likely interest in the product being offered and developing campaigns to target them.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Other important aspects of Twelve12\'s marketing services include leadership training. However, the company offers trainings for its leadership teams in leading teams towards execution and data-driven decisions. These trainings cover areas such as marketing analytics, campaign optimization, and communication strategies.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Twelve12 also offers paid social media, Google Ads, and display advertising. The group partners with clients in creating effective campaigns and delivering results.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Apart from all these, Twelve12 has included the service of campaign development in its kitty. The experienced team at this company creates end-to-end campaigns to drive results by fusing multiple marketing channels and tactics. This includes messaging frameworks, content calendars, and campaign execution management.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Twelve12 gives small businesses the digital marketing services necessary for their online establishment. This includes SEO, content creation, social media marketing, and internet marketing.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">SEO is one of the significant constituents of digital marketing. Twelve12 optimizes the website for clients with the help of experts in SEO to enhance online presence and drive organic traffic. It contains keyword research, on-page optimization, and link building.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Other key areas in Twelve12\'s digital marketing services include creative, quality content development that engages audiences and delivers results. These include but are not limited to blog posts, social media posts, email newsletters, and so on.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Another important area of Twelve12\'s digital marketing services is social media marketing. The firm helps clients build robust social media presences through content calendars, management of social media accounts, and engaging with followers.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Another service Twelve12 does is Internet marketing. The team at Twelve12 produces high-quality internet marketing strategies that drive targeted traffic to the websites of their clients and include pay-per-click advertising, email marketing, and retargeting techniques.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We&rsquo;re not very rigid about the way we work. The only thing we don&rsquo;t compromise is quality.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'from-web-design-and-development-to-media-production-and-public-relations-twelve12-does-all-the-work-so-you-focus-on-your-customers', '2022-05-14', 'us/visionaries-network-ike-elimsa-director-twelve12.webp', 9, 'profile', 'Twelve12: Full-Service Marketing & Media Agency', 'Twelve12, web design, development, media production, public relations, branding, marketing, digital agency, PR, visionaries network, customer focus, Irvine', 'Twelve12 handles web design, development, media production, and PR&mdash;so you can focus on what matters most: your customers and business growth.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.twelve12.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/twelve12/about/', 'Twelve12', '2015', ' Irvine, California, USA'),
(87, 7, '<p><strong>Brainiest.ai provides small and medium business marketers with creative, strategic, and analytic AI tools that help brands connect with target audiences</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In the current, fast-moving digital environment, businesses of all sizes find new ways to seek a competitive edge and get the most bang for their marketing buck. Enter Brainiest: a cutting-edge AI marketing platform designed to get great results without tricky prompts. Attune the power of artificial intelligence in users\' hands, and Brainiest unleashes the ability of mid-sized and small business marketers to achieve their goals.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>The Brainiest Team</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The Brainiest team includes marketing and technology experts who understand how technology can help better real-world experiences in their undertakings. Through their career, they have been assessing how technology is impacting organization businesses and different facets of life, hence developing solutions that apply technology to make a difference. From the first 32-bit microprocessor to big data systems and AI in marketing, this team has always been on the leading edge of technology.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Brainiest Story</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Brainiest was born over lunch at a Cheesecake Factory in Arizona as friends and former Intel colleagues Alan Steinberg and Mike McGowan discussed the emergence of AI. Mike, with previous work providing machine learning consulting services across a host of industries, had an epiphany for an AI platform to create marketing content for small and mid-sized businesses. And thus, Brainiest was born.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>What is an Applet?</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">An applet is a small application designed to perform some specific function in a larger platform. Brainiest is comprised of multiple dozens of AI-powered applets, each specifically purpose-built for a particular marketing function, such as generative, strategic, analytic, or predictive. These applets facilitate a myriad of marketing capabilities at users\' fingertips without requiring detailed technical knowledge.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>The Brainiest Advantage</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">This is unlike other AI tools that basically do nothing but give a prompt box. Brainiest comes with a set of pre-built questions that must be answered to ensure quality results. These questions collect relevant meaningful information that one would expect to be asked if using a good marketing consultant, and are developed by expert marketers. There is no need for specialized training to use the product, and thus users are able to get valuable results right from the word go.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Brainiest Applet Categories</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Brainiest offers a number of applets across categories, which include: Audio &amp; Video: Get maximum mileage out of your audio and video assets by transcription, translation, Text&ndash;to&ndash;Speech audio, and action items from meeting recordings. Brand Development: Compare brand logos; get a full brand guide drawn up, look out for your brand voice, know all about it with recommendations for implementation.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Content Creation: AI-powered tools can enable one to generate text, images, and video for SEO marketing, social media posts, and ad campaigns.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Customer Insight: What customer feedback really means for your business, crafting customer personas, beating sales objections, generating sales scripts, and actionable insight.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Marketing Strategy: The AIDA marketing framework enhances the knowledge of a customer journey in making informed decisions about marketing plans.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Promotion tools: Crank out email subject lines, news releases, product descriptions and promotional e-mail and sms/text messaging campaigns. Why Small Businesses Love Brainiest</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Dozens of marketing functions in one platform. No prompting expertise is needed; see better results right away. Made for Small Businesses, Not Big Businesses, it delivers generative AI plus creativity and strategy insights. More time to focus on human creativity and innovation. More chances of generating more revenue with greater efficiency.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Providing an AI marketing platform that helps to empower goal attainment without complex prompting, Brainiest is changing the way businesses do their marketing. Offering a user-friendly interface with a number of applets in various categories, Brainiest becomes just the right partner for any business looking to drive growth smoothly through leaner marketing operations.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Alan Steinberg, CEO</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Alan Steinberg has been driving innovative technology to market for 50 years. In his role as Brainiest CEO, Alan is steering the ship as lead strategist and key spokesman to ensure Brainiest continues to deliver maximum value for small and mid-sized business marketers.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Prior to developing Brainiest, Alan was responsible for a series of landmark &ldquo;firsts&rdquo; as a senior product marketing and strategic planning executive with Intel and CEO and Director of Strategic Planning for DevelopOnline (cloud-based software development):</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">-The first university microprocessor course at Temple University</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">-The industry&rsquo;s largest-volume Microcontroller 8051</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">-The first 32-bit embedded microprocessor</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">-The first SuperScalar embedded microprocessor</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">-The first online advanced software development program for microprocessors</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Alan has also served as CEO and Director of Strategic Planning for Deepdive Technologies (electronic discovery and big data) and Customer Loyalty Accelerator. His journey with Brainiest is the latest and perhaps the most rewarding chapter in a storied career highlighted by the development of technological breakthroughs that changed the game for organizations and people around the world.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">An avid runner, Alan runs 10-plus miles a day to stay in shape while thinking through what&rsquo;s next for Brainiest.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We bring out the inner marketing genius inside everyone! Whether you&rsquo;re a business owner, entrepreneur, or marketing person, Brainiest pulls your ideas to the forefront!&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'brainiest-ai-provides-small-and-medium-business-marketers-with-creative-strategic-and-analytic-ai-tools-that-help-brands-connect-with-target-audiences', '2022-05-14', 'us/visionaries-network-alan-steinberg-ceo-brainiest.webp', 10, 'profile', 'Brainiest.ai: Smart AI Tools for SMB Marketers', 'Brainiest.ai, AI tools, small business, marketing, analytics, strategy, creativity, branding, audience targeting, SMB, digital marketing, automation, visionaries network, insights, campaigns', 'Brainiest.ai equips small and medium business marketers with AI-powered creative, strategic, and analytic tools to connect brands with their target audiences effectively.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.brainiest.ai/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/brainiest-ai', 'Brainiest AI', '2024â€‹', 'Phoenix, Arizona, USA'),
(88, 7, '<p><strong>ChannelMix is the only Marketing Impact Modeling&trade; platform to deliver revenue-generating media mix predictions in under 24 hours from initial data connection</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As a marketer, there\'s nothing more frustrating than wrestling with data that seems to be out of control. You know the feeling - hours spent gathering numbers, only to discover that they\'re incomplete, inconsistent, or just plain wrong. It\'s enough to make you want to pull your hair out!</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At ChannelMix, the team understands this pain all too well. That\'s why it sets out to create a solution that would help marketers like you take control of their data, and gain the insights they need to make informed decisions.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>The Importance of Data Control</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In today\'s digital age, data is more important than ever. With the rise of social media, search engines, and other digital channels, marketers have access to more data than ever before. But with this increased availability comes increased complexity. Data can be overwhelming, fragmented, and difficult to make sense of.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Without a clear understanding of your marketing data, you\'re left making guesses rather than informed decisions. This can lead to wasted resources, missed opportunities, and a general sense of frustration.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">That\'s where ChannelMix comes in. Its platform is designed to help marketers like you take control of their data, and gain the insights they need to make informed decisions.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">ChannelMix founders, Michelle Jacobs and Matt Hertig, were marketing analysts who were tired of the manual process of data gathering. They decided to build their own solution, one that would automate the collection and visualization of marketing data from any source. And so, ChannelMix platform was born.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>How ChannelMix Works</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">ChannelMix is a data management platform designed for marketers by marketers. It collects marketing data from any source, store it in a scalable data warehouse, and provides users with easy access to analytics and reporting tools.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The company&rsquo;s Automated Marketing Reports give you a clear view of your marketing performance across multiple channels. You can track engagement metrics, analyze sales and revenue, and plan your budget with confidence.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">But that\'s not all. Its Marketing Impact Modeling tool uses AI-driven predictive analytics to help you optimize your media mix. With ChannelMix platform, you can:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Measure the impact of your marketing campaigns on leads, sales, and revenue</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Plan your budget based on past campaign results</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Predict the best media mix for your target audience</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Reduce media waste by up to 75%</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">And with ChannelMix Client Success Team Support, you\'ll always have access to expert guidance and training.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Why Choose ChannelMix?</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">So why choose ChannelMix? Here are just a few reasons:</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Accuracy:</strong> The company&rsquo;s AI-powered recommendation engine predicts optimal media mix in real-time, with an accuracy rate of 93%.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Comprehensive Data Integration:</strong> ChannelMix includes all performance-related data in its models, including online and offline media, events, lead and sales data.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Continuous Learning:</strong> ChannelMix AI learns from each campaign, offering increasingly accurate predictions and recommendations.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>24-Hour Model Activation:</strong> The company&rsquo;s models are ready the next day and updated nightly, so you can start making decisions quickly.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Client Success Team Support:</strong> ChannelMix\'s dedicated team is always available to help you maximize the potential of its platform.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Real-World Results</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">But don\'t just take ChannelMix\'s word for it. Its clients have seen real-world results with ChannelMix. Here are a few examples:</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Mattel:</strong> With ChannelMix, Mattel was able to reduce media waste by 75% and increase ROI by 20%.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Maui Jim:</strong> Maui Jim used ChannelMix to optimize their media mix and saw a 30% increase in sales.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Attane:</strong> Attane used ChannelMix to measure the impact of their marketing campaigns on leads and saw a 50% increase in conversions.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Matt Hertig, CEO/Co-Founder</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Matt Hertig is the CEO, CTO, and co-founder of ChannelMix. Matt has been at the helm as ChannelMix has evolved from a small analytics consultancy to a six-time Inc. 5000 honoree.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">One of the biggest drivers of ChannelMix&rsquo;s growth is its technology solution, ChannelMix, the first data management platform designed for marketing. ChannelMix eliminates cumbersome data gathering by systematically combining online data, offline data, sales data, and custom data sources, reducing the hours that marketers spend each day prepping data for reporting.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We help reduce wasted spend by identifying inefficiencies and improving marketing efficiency, protecting budgets with real-time scenarios that display the impact on revenue, sales, and leads.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'channelmix-is-the-only-marketing-impact-modeling-platform-to-deliver-revenue-generating-media-mixpredictions-in-under-24-hours-from-initial-data-connection', '2022-05-14', 'us/visionaries-network-matt-hartig-ceo-co-founder-channelmix.webp', 11, 'profile', 'Marketing Impact Modeling in Under 24 Hours | ChannelMix', 'marketing impact, media mix, attribution, analytics, revenue, predictions, visionaries network, modeling, ROI, ChannelMix, performance, optimization, advertising, insights, marketing tech', 'ChannelMix delivers fast, revenue-driving media mix predictions with Marketing Impact Modeling&trade; in under 24 hours. Connect your data and see results fast.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://channelmix.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/channel-mix', 'ChannelMix', '2007', 'Kansas City, Missouri, United States'),
(89, 7, '<p><strong>Equivity provides dedicated virtual assistant services to individuals, to entrepreneurs, and businesses</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In the busy business world today, every company wants to strive and improve their productivity to accelerate growth while reducing operational stress. Equivity believes a business needs a strong support system in order to be able to do this. It works in tandem with its clients from its different lines of business to increase productivity and accelerate growth through scalable strategic outsourcing and virtual support.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Equivity\'s Vision</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Equivity\'s team envisions itself to achieve the goal of becoming the No.1 Service Provider of Virtual Support Services for its clients and promises that with the alliance, Equivity clients would be enabled to grow and attain sustainable success. Its vision is thus to provide outsourcing solutions that shall meet clients\' distinguished needs, allowing them to focus on what they do best: growing their business.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Business Outsourcing and Virtual Support</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Equivity offers a host of virtual support services designed to assist any business like yours in finding success. Administrative, marketing, and paralegal support&mdash;name it&mdash;they have both the expertise and tools to help one realize their goals. Their services include virtual executive assistants, whereby workload is simplified by saving money through the outsourcing of routine administrative tasks to their pool of skilled virtual assistants.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Retain Equivity to take your reach to an entirely new level of engagement with target audiences through their inventive marketing consultants. Allow Equivity\'s veteran customer service professionals to fill a customer service position or build an entire team for you. Use Equivity to assemble an efficient team of administrative assistants, receptionists, project managers, accounting professionals, or other office support staff. Strengthen your sales team or fill particular sales positions by using Equivity\'s experienced sales professionals.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>How Can a Virtual Assistant Help You?</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">A Virtual Assistant can assist you in a lot of areas, from the tasks mentioned to items such as:</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&bull; Data Entry</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&bull; Proof-reading and Editing</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&bull; Transcription</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&bull; Illustration Research</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&bull; Travel Arrangements</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Why Choose Equivity?</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Equivity, the team understands that no two businesses are alike. That is why they provide a fully tailored experience that caters to your particular needs. Its services are engineered for scalability, allowing you to grow or downsize when you consider appropriate. Their dedicated Client Experience Managers will work on a one-to-one basis to ensure you realize the maximum value from its services.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Build Your Dream Team</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With Equivity, you can select from its team of heterogeneous assistants to get precisely what you want. The company knows how to get the perfect team for you from any of its business units.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>No Limits, Only Possibilities</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Equivity does not just stop at offering you standard solutions; the company will come up with customized solutions to meet your unique needs. Be it any kind of challenge or an idea that calls for something way out of ordinary norms, the company will take up the challenge and work together to find a solution.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Aldo Bettoni, CEO</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Aldo is an expert in the virtual workspace. He has been working in strategy as well as running, growing and leading businesses for over 15 years. He is the co-founder of a successful BPO/outsourcing company, bringing his technological and innovation skills to Equivity\'s clients and helping them find a smarter way to work.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Aldo also created a fully virtual start-up in the financial services industry, lending his experience to his goal as Equivity\'s CEO of providing businesses and entrepreneurs with the virtual resources they need to grow and achieve their professional goals.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Aldo brings a diverse background to the company, having worked in Chile, Costa Rica and Mexico as well as Michigan, California and Texas. He received his MBA from the Kenan Flagler Business School at the University of North Carolina at Chapel Hill. Aldo lives in Orange County with his wife and daughter Olivia. He is a diehard soccer fan and loves traveling the world and enjoying new cuisines.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We offer a wide range of scalable plans so that you can increase your hours as your business grows and the need arises.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'equivity-provides-dedicated-virtual-assistant-services-to-individuals-to-entrepreneurs-and-businesses', '2022-05-14', 'us/visionaries-network-aldo-bettoni-ceo.webp', 12, 'profile', 'Virtual Assistant Services for Professionals | Equivity', 'virtual assistant, remote assistant, business support, admin help, Equivity, entrepreneurs, executive assistant, scheduling, email management, marketing support, legal assistant, virtual help, visionaries network, dedicated assistant, remote services', 'Equivity offers dedicated virtual assistant services for individuals, entrepreneurs, and businesses to boost productivity and streamline operations.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://equivityva.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/equivity-vpa/', 'Equivity', '2014', 'Las Vegas, NV'),
(90, 7, '<p><strong>Grayce: Change and transformation for the world\'s most ambitious organizations</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">The delivery of change and transformation is a huge task in a fast-paced changing business environment. In a fast-changing technological world, spiraling costs, and leaking knowledge pose a challenge to remain ahead of competition; therefore, an organization has to move very fast. Grayce is a leading provider of high-performing talent, with over a decade\'s experience in the development and deployment of top-notch professionals to help organizations realize their objectives. Through collaboration with ambitious organizations, Grayce provides low-risk and scalable solutions to build capability for the long term.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Accelerated Development Programme</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Grayce\'s Accelerated Development Programme has been specially developed to provide work experience, mentorship, and training in most areas of business. It empowers participants with the competence and confidence to acquire their skills and knowledge through the combination of project work, workshops, and networking opportunities within a supportively challenging environment.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The program has been quite successful in placing people into successful positions within a very broad spectrum of industries, from finance and consulting to technology. Indeed, so many past participants have moved into leading companies to great positions and credited Grayce\'s program for their professional success.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The system Grayce has developed focuses on high potentials to fast-track talented people for leadership within their organizations. It helps participants gain not only the technical know-how necessary to succeed in a chosen field but also the soft skills&mdash;communications, teamwork, and problem-solving&mdash;which are equally important in making a difference.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Grayce Analysts work closely with the client to understand their needs and goals, providing relevant, bespoke solutions to tackle them. This may entail an in-depth analysis of existing processes and systems, defining areas for improvement, and designing new strategies and technologies to drive change and deliver preferred outcomes.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Through effective communication and collaboration, Grayce&rsquo;s analysts will ensure that during the project life cycle, all stakeholders remain engaged and informed. Further, they continue supporting and advising clients in the process of change by surmounting all difficulties and other hindrances. Finally, the company&rsquo;s analysts work tirelessly for the delivery of organizational objectives for clients and the attainment of sustainable growth and success.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With their competence and experience, they put clients at the forefront of changing market conditions, changing regulatory requirements, and customer demands within the dynamic competitive business environment of today.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Sourcing of Talent</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Grayce Analysts are trained to synthesize professional and technical expertise to meet the most imperative needs of the clients. With flexible, new-thinking talent, they bring innovation in change and transformation. Grayce&rsquo;s analysts deliver excellence in the roles of Junior Project Manager, Business Analyst, Project Management Officer, Product Owner, Data Analyst, Software Developer, Cyber Security Analyst, Software Tester, Data Engineer, DevOps Analyst, and so on.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Digital solutions</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Grayce analysts are focused on empowering clients with the power of data and technology to drive their business. Equipped with these programming languages, such as Python, JavaScript, AWS, and Tableau, analysts develop a great deal of innovative solutions catering to the needs of each client.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Grayce Analysts will work as Software Developers, Cyber Security Analysts, Data Engineers or Software Testers. They are conversant with agile methodologies, thus able to flex quickly on changing requirements. They liaison closely with the clients to make sure that the technology solutions that are developed are not only effective but also align to the organization\'s overall goals and objectives.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">After delivering technology solutions, Grayce Analysts move inside clients\' teams to continue their support in data-driven decision-making and during digital transformation. Equipped with skills and experience, Grayce Analysts enable clients to stay ahead of the curve and drive success in an increasingly digital world.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Jeff Hewitt, Executive Chair</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Jeff is Grayce\'s Executive Chair and a member of the board. Jeff has spent over 25 years in the technology sector, working for HSBC bank originally, but spending most of his career at Civica delivering technology solutions to the public sector and helping to improve citizens\' lives. Jeff is passionate about career development, having sponsored the apprentice scheme at Civica since its inception, and is a great believer in nurturing and growing talent to contribute to the future of society. Jeff has successfully grown Civica from 400 people to 6000 in his tenure.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;Our Accelerated Development Programme has enabled thousands of talented individuals to launch successful careers and, coupled with our proven delivery model, has seen Grayce support over 2000 projects across more than 100 organizations.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'grayce-change-and-transformation-for-the-worlds-most-ambitious-organizations', '2022-05-14', 'us/visionaries-network-jeff-hewitt-executive-chai-grayce.webp', 13, 'profile', 'Change & Transformation Experts | Grayce', 'transformation, Grayce, business growth, strategy, digital change, talent, agile delivery, program management, project support, future leaders, consulting, visionaries network, enterprise, business solutions', 'Grayce drives change and transformation for ambitious organizations, delivering future-ready talent and strategic business solutions for lasting impact.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.grayce.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/grayce', 'Grayce', '2019', 'Manchester'),
(91, 7, '<p><strong>Hozio specializes in all phases of website design and development as well as full search engine optimization services</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Since its inception, Hozio has worked with a diverse range of clients, from small local businesses to large corporations, helping them navigate the ever-changing landscape of digital marketing. The company offers a wide range of services, including search engine optimization, pay-per-click advertising, social media marketing, and website design. Hozio\'s success can be attributed to its commitment to staying ahead of the curve when it comes to digital marketing trends and technologies.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The company\'s team of experts constantly monitors industry developments and adapts their strategies accordingly to ensure their clients achieve maximum results. In addition to providing top-notch digital marketing services, Hozio also prides itself on its exceptional customer service. The company takes the time to understand each client\'s unique needs and goals and works closely with them to develop customized marketing strategies that drive results.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Overall, Hozio\'s dedication to excellence, innovation, and customer satisfaction has solidified its reputation as a leader in the digital marketing industry. With 15 years of experience under their belt, Steven Orandello and John Bosco continue to lead the company to new heights, helping businesses of all sizes achieve their marketing goals and grow their online presence.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Hozio understands that if your website is hidden, it\'s an opportunity lost. Your ideal customers might be searching for what you do; they just need to find you. A good ranking at Google means better visibility and more visibility usually drives more sales. That\'s where proper search engine optimization, SEO, enters the picture at Hozio.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Hozio optimizes clients\' websites, frontend and backend, to help them rank high in search results, making them one of the potential customers\' first choices. Its strategy for local SEO will most wanting buyers in the area, and with time-tested tactics joined by fresh insights, it ensures a first-page result for desired keywords.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Gazing across the SEO service range, Hozio has services that contain keyword research, on-page optimization, link building, technical SEO, content strategy, and reporting with analytics. The company does not believe in one-size-fits-all approaches toward SEO, so its experts take time to get an insight into every client\'s business goals, industry, and competition to design a customized plan that suits the needs of the business.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">What sets the company apart from any other SEO company is the fact that it is committed to providing personalized service. Their goal at Hozio is to ensure that the results they deliver truly reflect each client\'s brand identity and unique business goals. With Hozio by their side, businesses will be able to reset the course of their digital journey toward long-term online success.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Besides this, Hozio offers Google PPC services to get organizations directly in the middle of visibility on digital marketplaces. Hozio feels that visibility is only half the tough battle, for it holds within every click an optional investment that should be studied and optimized i.e., Hozio\'s qualities through data, user behavior, and enhanced strategy to make sure that these investments clients put into Google Ads convert to real-time contacts and business growth.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Hozio also hosts leading web design solutions that can make or break any online presence of a business. The company obtains the idea that a website leaving people in confusion or frustrated can harm a brand. Its web design and development solutions, therefore, focus on the creation of a smooth and engaging experience.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">By using AI technology and time-tested psychological tactics built up over a period of more than 40 years, Hozio makes sure that every website visitor creates a positive first impression. Its web design solution strives for greater visibility, higher conversion rates, and increased sales with value-driven content that accelerates the pace of any buyer\'s journey.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We are an internet marketing agency based in Long Island, NY, with clients ranging from small individuals to large corporations and private equity groups.&rdquo;</strong><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-dbc3db14-7fff-abde-3940-60c8f90d8c5b\"></strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'hozio-specializes-in-all-phases-of-website-design-and-development-as-well-as-full-search-engine-optimization-services', '2022-05-14', 'us/visionaries-network-john-bosco-founder-hozio.webp', 15, 'profile', 'Web Design & SEO Services Experts | Hozio', 'web design, website development, search engine optimization, Hozio, digital marketing, responsive design, visionaries network, UX design, local SEO, keyword research, content strategy, web solutions, on-page SEO, custom websites', 'Hozio offers expert website design, development, and full SEO services to boost your online visibility and grow your business.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.hozio.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/hozio', 'Hozio', '2009', 'Holbrook, New York');
