(92, 7, '<p><strong>JCM Business Solutions: Experts in business development and CRM software solutions</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In 2010, JCM was launched by Chris Moran&mdash;a business consultancy firm, and its design theory was based on one simple maxim: \"Business First, Software Later.\" This is the model that has guided the development of the firm\'s approach to business and CRM software delivery over the years. What started as a small start-up, JCM today is a thriving business known for its Zoho software solutions, embodying greatness in numbers and excellence in delivery through a team of technology-savvy and dedicated consultants.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Over the years, JCM has grown its services to be the local premium partner of ZOHO, working hand in hand with the company in bringing quality business management software for small businesses. The company\'s partnership with Zoho has therefore enabled JCM to deliver innovative solutions to its clients so as to streamline their operations and to ensure that they are able to meet their objectives.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The success of JCM is due in no small measure to the fact that it is dedicated to the hallowed values enunciated above. The company believes that employees are the most valuable assets it has and provides an environment for growth, learning, and development. This is reflected in the company\'s approach to work-life balance, encouraging flexibility and honesty.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The commitment to excellence at JCM is not just limited to internal practices. Consultants at the firm are challenged to look way much above the normal ways of delivering top-of-the-market products and services. It is through such an approach that innovation has developed, bringing positive change within the business. That is also what gave it the ability to keep up with many changing trends and offer customers cutting-edge solutions.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">There is also the issue of the company\'s focus on profitability. To JCM, the company exists to provide jobs and employment opportunities for his colleague, make a reasonable profit from its customers and provide a fair return to its investors. Those who drive and create profit should benefit from it, reflecting the company\'s commitment to fairness and transparency.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Growth and Achievement HISTORY</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Growth and achievements of JCM underline its commitment towards quality. The company has experienced an exceptional growth over the years, and this has helped it to get new premises based on the increased requirement of the human resource and office-space needs. JCM started in a new premise in 2014, and then, later in 2015, it moved into a bigger office space.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In 2016, the company rebranded with the new motto: \"Business First, Software Later,\" where one understands what clients really need in their business prior to suggesting software solutions. This is what has given JCM an opportunity to build relations with clients and deliver oriented solutions that would meet their unique requirements.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">JCM was awarded Zoho Advanced Partner in 2017, and this can give the company recognition in having the strength in developing Zoho software solutions. Since then, the company has been a crucial part of expanding services to other partnerships, which include Severnside and LRComms, giving full IT support and comprehensive voice solutions.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Awards and Recognition</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">JCM has always strived to bring the best together with quality service; hence, it has gained multiple awards and accolades. Last year, the business acquired the Business Heroes Award by the British Chambers of Commerce for what it has done during the lockdown in support of small businesses. That award testifies to the commitment JCM has to empower small businesses to strive in the face of this adversity.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Added to this accolade, JCM is today also recognized as one of the top partners within the UK of Zoho software solutions. The expert handling with Zoho CRM has placed the company as one of the go-to partners for any business wishing a tailored CRM solution.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>The Future Ahead</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Expect, then, that JCM\'s message will remain the same into the sunset: People first, productivity second, and profitability third. Innovation will remain JCM\'s hallmark in seeking and finding new, improved ways to produce quality products and services.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Supported by a heavyweight consultant and business partner team, JCM is well-situated for continued growth and success with the business community. Business development and CRM software solutions are all available under one roof in JCM.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Chris Moran, Founder/Managing Director</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Chris formed JCM in 2010 and now heads up the company\'s Sales and Business Development Teams.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>&ldquo;We believe that the most important part of any business is its people.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'jcm-business-solutions-experts-in-business-development-and-crm-software-solutions', '2022-05-14', 'us/visionaries-network-chris-moran-founder-managing-director-jcm.webp', 14, 'profile', 'JCM Business Solutions: Experts in business development and CRM software solutions', 'JCM Business Solutions', 'JCM Business Solutions', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://jcmbusinesssolution.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/jcm-business-solutions-llc', 'JCM Business Solutions', '2009', 'Seaford, New York'),
(93, 7, '<p><strong>Maxsource Technologies is a digital marketing partner of choice for many businesses across the world</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">Maxsource Technologies is a digital marketing partner of choice for many businesses across the world. Founded in 2013, Maxsource has grown from a small team of web design and development professionals to a vibrant group of experts in web design, development, and digital marketing. Its journey has not been easy, but with a team of super-fresh brains and super-experienced ninjas, the company has made itself a known name in the industry. They have developed custom-made Shopify and WordPress sites, dynamic Digital Marketing strategies, Data Entry, Data Mining, and Internet Research Services for their customers worldwide.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Maxsource&rsquo;s vision is to become the USA\'s most valuable web design and development company through ultimate performance and uniqueness in every project they undertake. Their mission is to make technology a blessing for your business by creating leading-edge products and providing unique services that prioritize quality and customer satisfaction.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The company prides itself on developing and sustaining customer relationships, delivering great digital products, and enjoying its work. They never compromise on quality, stay updated on the latest technologies and trends, do solid research, complete projects strongly and uniquely, and deliver on time.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As a company that specializes in digital marketing solutions, Maxsource understands the importance of staying ahead of the curve in today\'s fast-paced digital landscape. That\'s why it invests heavily in training its team members to stay updated on the latest technologies and trends. From artificial intelligence to machine learning, blockchain to IoT, Maxsource stays ahead of the curve to provide cutting-edge solutions for its clients.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">One of Maxsource&rsquo;s core services is iPhone app development. It offers iPhone app development services for the entire Apple device family, including smartphones, tablets, TVs, and wearables. Its team of experienced developers can help you turn your company idea into a working iOS application. Maxsource believes that ideation is key to innovative results, planning is essential to maximize output results with minimal input within an optimal timeline, and testing ensures that the final product is free from any glitches. Its designers focus on creating iOS apps with one goal: increasing conversions.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Another area of expertise for Maxsource is e-commerce development. It provides comprehensive Magento development and e-commerce strategy services to ensure that your e-commerce website provides a premium branded and customer-centric experience that engages and generates revenue. Maxsource&rsquo;s Magento experts have enviable competence in the Magento platform, from design and architecture to delivery and optimization to continuous support and maintenance. It believes that optimizing site performance is equally important as making it look reasonable.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In addition to these services, Maxsource also offers Virtual Marketing Strategist Service. This service provides a clear strategy tailored to your business needs. Whether you operate or run a small to medium-sized business without an in-house marketing team or need help with specific tasks, their virtual marketing professionals deliver the skills, experience, and insights you require without the full-time expenses associated with full-time employees.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Maxsource Technologies, the team understands that every business is unique, with its own set of challenges and goals. That\'s why it takes time to understand your specific needs and develop customized solutions that meet those needs. Whether you\'re looking to launch a new product or service, improve your online presence, or increase sales and revenue, it can help you achieve your goals.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Maxsource Technologies, the team believes that technology should be a blessing for your business. That\'s why they strive to create leading-edge products and provide unique services that prioritize quality and customer satisfaction. Whether you\'re looking for web design and development services or digital marketing solutions, Maxsource is here to help you achieve your goals</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Navdeep Sethi, Founder and CEO</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Navdeep is a serial entrepreneur who leverages his experiences and expertise in cutting-edge and emerging technology, business operations, and brand strategy to create a diverse portfolio of brands.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With a passion for utilizing technology to create impact, he harnesses his deep understanding of technology to provide much-needed services for communities. As a successful serial entrepreneur, Navdeep has the ability to develop visionary \"next-level\" ideas and deliver them to the marketplace with precision timing, meeting end-user needs with precision.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">He has extensive experience in all aspects of operations, including human resource management, organizational process development, and infrastructure expansion, which enables him to drive sales and revenues for profitability.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">By leveraging his technical expertise and entrepreneurial spirit, Navdeep harnessed the power of web technology to create diverse brands that offered well-needed products and services. He builds companies that create change.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Throughout his career, Navdeep has built a diverse business presence across the Information Technology, Human Resources, Entertainment, and Real Estate sectors. The companies he has founded have an impressive track record of value creation, which compares well with their respective industry peers.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Navdeep\'s companies strive to bring the latest innovations and best value offerings to all consumers in their quest to deliver the best-in-class results.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As a committed leader, Navdeep is dedicated to each and every client, promising to listen to their goals, objectives, and unique needs; communicate with them through each step of the process; and achieve the best possible result for them.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We are no beginners, but we still hold the curiosity and excitement of a beginner. With the wrestling struggles and uncertainty, Maxsource has come across multiple frameworks that have increased our learning curve and guided us to the path of improvement.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'maxsource-technologies-is-a-digital-marketing-partner-of-choice-for-many-businesses-across-the-world', '2022-05-14', 'us/visionaries-network-navdeep-sethi-ceo-maxsource.webp', 16, 'profile', 'Global Digital Marketing Partner | Maxsource Technologies', 'digital marketing, Maxsource, SEO, PPC, social media, content marketing, email marketing, web design,visionaries network, marketing agency, lead generation, online strategy, global marketing, marketing partner, digital solutions', 'Maxsource Technologies is the trusted digital marketing partner for businesses worldwide, delivering tailored strategies and measurable results.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.maxsourceworld.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/maxsource-technologies', 'Maxsource Technologies ', '2013', ' New York, New York'),
(94, 7, '<p><strong>KanConsulting LLC Fixes Business Challenges Through Innovative Ideas and Strategies&nbsp;</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">Often when you are too close to something you don&rsquo;t see everything. As outsiders, KanConsulting will see your business and category from a different perspective. It&rsquo;s this perspective that enables us to develop new ideas and solutions to get you results.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In today\'s fast-paced and ever-changing business landscape, having a solid marketing strategy is crucial for success. Without one, marketing efforts can be scattered, ineffective, and ultimately, a waste of resources. A well-planned marketing strategy, on the other hand, can drive acquisition, retention, engagement, competitive advantage, and brand awareness. KanConsulting believes that its outsider perspective is the key to unlocking your business\'s full potential.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Amy Kan, the founder and CEO of KanConsulting, has over 20 years of combined experience in business growth, advertising, and marketing. With a proven track record of developing effective marketing campaigns for both large and small businesses, Amy knows what it takes to drive results. She starts by understanding what sets your business apart and what makes it unique. What pain points can she solve for your customers? What are their needs and wants? KanConsulting develops a customized marketing strategy that aligns with your business goals and objectives.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As the old adage goes, \"Say something interesting and say it in an interesting way.\" Amy believes that this is especially true in today\'s advertising landscape where attention spans are shorter than ever. To break through the noise, you need a marketing strategy that is not only creative but also effective. At KanConsulting, Amy has the expertise and experience to develop campaigns that drive results.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Before developing a marketing strategy, Amy needs to understand your business inside and out. This means gaining insight into your business model, competitive landscape, and goals. Amy believes that marketing must align with these goals and be integrated into every aspect of your business. Whether you\'re launching a new product or service or looking to revamp your existing brand, KanConsulting has the expertise to help you achieve your objectives.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">KanConsulting offers a range of services designed to help you achieve success. From building the basics &ndash; such as setting up social channels, creating a website, and developing a logo &ndash; to creating a go-to-market strategy that minimizes risk and optimizes success, Amy can help. Her team of experts has the expertise to develop effective marketing campaigns for both large and small businesses.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Amy\'s approach is centered around creating content that is both unique and engaging. She believes that this is critical for any brand, big or small. Whether you\'re looking to create social media content or develop a comprehensive content marketing strategy, KanConsulting can help. Her team has the expertise to develop content that resonates with your target audience and drives results.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Once you have a solid brand identity in place, it\'s time to take your marketing efforts to the next level with advertising. At KanConsulting, Amy has the expertise to handle all aspects of advertising &ndash; from TV commercials to radio ads, print ads to out-of-home advertising. Her team will work with you to develop an advertising strategy that aligns with your business goals and objectives.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In conclusion, KanConsulting believes that its outsider perspective is the key to unlocking your business\'s full potential. With over 20 years of combined experience in business growth, advertising, and marketing, Amy has the expertise to develop customized marketing strategies that drive results. Whether you\'re looking to launch a new product or service or revamp your existing brand, KanConsulting can help.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As an entrepreneur herself, Amy understands the challenges of starting a new business and is passionate about helping others succeed. Her extensive experience in developing effective marketing campaigns for both large and small businesses make her uniquely qualified to help entrepreneurs navigate the complex world of marketing.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">When she\'s not working with clients or running her own company, Amy can be found cheering on her favorite MMA fighters at Eagle FC events or enjoying quality time with her family.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;With a robust network of video editors, copywriters, graphic artists, etc, we can quickly scale to meet the budget and time constraints of any project.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'kanconsulting-llc-fixes-business-challenges-through-innovative-ideas-and-strategies', '2022-05-14', 'us/visionaries-network-kanconsulting-ceo-founder.webp', 17, 'profile', 'Innovative Business Solutions | KanConsulting LLC', 'business consulting, strategy, innovation, KanConsulting, problem solving, growth solutions, business strategy, visionaries network, management consulting, business growth, strategic planning, process improvement, consulting services', 'KanConsulting LLC solves business challenges with innovative strategies, helping companies grow, adapt, and thrive in competitive markets.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://kanconsultingllc.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kanconsulting-llc', 'KanConsulting LLC', ' 2020', ' Stamford, CT'),
(95, 7, '<p><strong>Navigator Business Solutions: Provides End-to-End SAP ERP Software Solutions</strong></p>', '<p><img class=\"img-responsive magazine-profile-image\" alt=\"\">The modern business world is a very fast and aggressive market, and at times, growth-oriented organizations are restricted by current business processes and systems. At Navigator Business Solutions, the team realizes the necessity of a strong, scaled, and agile ERP system as the vehicle for business growth. Its team is proud to guide firms out of the constraints of clear, noncurrent systems and deploy next-generation solutions that will be tailored to meet unique needs.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Being an SAP Gold Partner and among the largest implementation partners for SAP globally, Navigator has a long history of delivering to the small and mid-market segments. It helps its clients with the best-optimized solution deployment approach using harmonized best practices with an innovative workshop-based implementation methodology that accelerates digital transformation for the ERP platform of companies.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Navigator wishes to be recognized as a leader in transforming the way companies and people work with business systems through innovation in technology and business processes. Its mission is to empower customers by helping them optimize their business through the development and delivery of industry-specific technology solutions that are innovative, intuitive, flexible, and scalable. Navigator calls this mission home by continuously investing in its people to let them focus on trying to solve problems faced by its customers and create an innovation-oriented environment built on a foundation of focus and passion.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Navigator specializes in developing out-of-the-box solutions to meet the needs of its industry customers. It has developed its solution set through industry experience spanning over 15 years, delivering integrated SAP ERP offerings tailored to small and mid-size organizations and molded to its client\'s needs and desires now and into the future.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Navigator is expert in helping growth-focused companies deploy cost-effective, cloud-based ERP solutions based on market-leading SAP Business One, SAP Business ByDesign, and the SAP S/4HANA Cloud Public Edition platform. It provides project planning, implementation, consulting, and training, along with US-based development and client support activities, for award-winning ERP professional services and support.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With more than 500 clients under its portfolio, Navigator has never missed its deadline or budget. That is why they have been the number one SAP partner for the last 15 years, and why small and medium-sized businesses have to search no more for better operations and growth in their revenues.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Navigator&rsquo;s cloud-based ERP solutions deliver rapid time-to-value and rapid time-to-benefit, enabling a company\'s resources to be better applied toward the analysis and transformation of its business in addressing today\'s demanding market challenges. For sure, cloud-based solutions can cut down operational costs of a company and prevent problems that might arise from associated server and storage hardware maintenance.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The SAP S/4HANA Cloud Public Edition is a full ERP with embedded intelligent technologies such as AI, machine learning, and advanced data analytics. Being a cloud-enabled ERP suite, this helps companies with new business model adoption, dealing with rapid and continual business change, orchestrating both internal and external resources, and using the predictive power of AI in empowerment.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At Navigator Business Solutions, the team believes a single system can run a business from anywhere. Its cloud-based ERP solutions provide predictable pricing&mdash;seen as an operating expense, not a capital expense&mdash;letting the companies focus on their business, not on IT.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Navigator&rsquo;s skill set gracefully transcends the usual core functions of accounting and inventory management to offer a full suite that empowers total business management in the areas of Human Resources, Financials, and Analytics, touching Supply Chain, Project Management, and CRM. The company helps its clients unlock their full potential in the integral business process by offering comprehensive solutions covering each end-to-end business process with pre-configured best practice processes and industry-scenario-based solutions.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Chris M. Nielsen, President &amp; Chief Executive Officer</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Chris Nielsen has over 20 years of hands-on experience as head of finance, operations, and technology for various divisions of global corporations. Chris&nbsp;has&nbsp;led the implementation of ERP, and other key IT, systems in several countries and understands the critical impact of these projects and decisions. Chris received his Bachelor of Science degree from the University of Utah and holds an MBA from Westminster College with the final year, and course work, completed at the University of Chicago.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&ldquo;We have built our extensive expertise working on more than 500 ERP implementations and ERP system optimization projects.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'navigator-business-solutions-provides-end-to-end-sap-erp-software-solutions', '2022-05-14', 'us/visionaries-network-chris-m-nielson-navigator-ceo-president.webp', 18, 'profile', 'End-to-End SAP ERP Solutions | Navigator', 'SAP ERP, ERP software, business solutions, Navigator, cloud ERP, enterprise software, digital transformation, visonaries network, SAP partner, supply chain, finance, manufacturing, automation, ERP consulting, data integration', 'Navigator Business Solutions delivers complete SAP ERP software solutions, helping businesses streamline operations and drive digital transformation.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.nbs-us.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/navigator-business-solutions', 'Stamford, CT', '2005', ' Lehi, Utah');
