(100, 8, '<p><strong>6 Group is a global search and talent intelligence firm focused on the identification, engagement, and development of the world&rsquo;s standout talent</strong></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In a world where satisfying mere requirements can be common practice, 6 Group rejects mediocrity in a bid to be recognized as the genuine alternative. As a facilitator of successful transformation, 6 Group works with its clients to ensure their goals become their own. With operations across EMEAI, Asia Pacific, and the Americas, 6 Group has established itself as a leader in the executive search and leadership development industry.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">6 Group was established 17 years ago by Managing Director James Beazley, a seasoned professional with a wealth of experience in the recruitment and talent acquisition sector. Prior to founding 6 Group, James held a prominent position at Shell, where he served as the Head of Experienced Resourcing for the EMEAR (Europe, Middle East, Africa, and Russia) region.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">During his tenure at Shell, he had the opportunity to collaborate with numerous top-tier search and assessment firms, gaining valuable insights into the industry. However, he soon realized that many of these firms lacked a truly collaborative approach, which often hindered the potential for achieving outstanding results in talent acquisition. This realization became a pivotal moment for James, as he recognized a significant gap in the market for a recruitment service that prioritized genuine collaboration and partnership.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Motivated by his experiences and the desire to create a more effective and client-focused alternative, he took the bold step of founding 6 Group. The company was built on two foundational principles: \"Go Beyond\" and \"Partnering.\" The principle of \"Go Beyond\" reflects 6 Group\'s commitment to exceeding client expectations and delivering exceptional results. This means not only meeting the immediate needs of clients but also anticipating future challenges and opportunities in the talent landscape. By adopting a forward-thinking approach, 6 Group aims to provide solutions that are not just effective but transformative, helping organizations to thrive in an ever-evolving market.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The second principle, \"Partnering,\" emphasizes the importance of building strong, collaborative relationships with clients. At 6 Group, the focus is on understanding the unique needs and goals of each organization, fostering a partnership that goes beyond traditional client-vendor dynamics. This collaborative spirit enables 6 Group to tailor its services to align with the specific objectives of its clients, ensuring that the recruitment process is not only efficient but also strategically aligned with the broader vision of the organization.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Through these guiding principles, 6 Group has established itself as a trusted partner in the recruitment industry, dedicated to delivering innovative solutions and exceptional service to its clients. Over the years, the company has grown and evolved, but its core mission remains the same: to provide a real alternative in talent acquisition that prioritizes collaboration, foresight, and partnership.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Today, 6 Group\'s expertise stretches across three core areas: Global Executive Search, Talent Mapping &amp; Pipelining, and Assessment &amp; Development. Its global executive search is about exploring the world\'s standout talent, matching the skills, character, and aspirations of top talent with the specific requirements of its clients\' senior and specialized roles. 6 Group has developed a tried and trusted evidence-based methodology that has led to one of the highest search success rates in the industry (92% search completion vs. the industry average of 64%) and a client re-utilization rate of 100% since 2006.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">6 Group\'s approach is based on an insatiable appetite for discovery, gathering insights into the world\'s top talent through its client solutions. It knows who is in demand, who would be willing to have a conversation, and the remuneration they would expect. Everything it does is underpinned by fact, from exploring a world of senior talent with fresh research and intelligence at hand to presenting its clients with people who have prevailed in an evidence-based assessment process.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Talent mapping and pipelining are about awareness, rendering complete clarity to its clients\' talent market, and utilizing that holistic insight to their advantage. 6 Group builds relationships on behalf of its clients, nurturing strong bonds between them and their talent market so that when they want to engage them, they\'ll be ready to join. It also shapes perceptions by conveying its clients\' employer brand and employee value proposition to the external market, building and communicating a justified narrative of why they are a genuine employer of choice.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">6 Group\'s approach is diverse by design, presenting its clients with the truest representation of their talent market possible. Decision-making becomes empowered when diverse companies outperform those that aren\'t - it\'s simply good business practice.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">At 6 Group, it has designed a refined concept within its talent mapping &amp; pipelining services that brings its clients\' talent acquisition strategy and execution to a new level. It calls this concept its Capability Engine&trade;. This proprietary attraction strategies &amp; engagement platform promotes access to diverse talent to ensure its clients get the greatest choice of the best talent for them, not just the most available or the people with the right keywords on their CV or LinkedIn profile.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong>&ldquo;Today, we are one of the world&rsquo;s most innovative firms operating across EMEAI, Asia Pacific, and the Americas.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', '6-group-global-search-talent-intelligence-firm-identification-engagement-development-of-the-worlds', '2025-03-11', 'us/visionaries-network-6group-james-beazley-md-cover.webp', 1, 'cover', '6 Group is a global search and talent intelligence firm helping businesses identify and develop exceptional leaders worldwide.', 'talent intelligence, executive search, global recruitment, leadership hiring, talent mapping, succession planning, strategic hiring, headhunting, workforce analytics, talent development, recruitment firm, hiring strategy, visionaries network, executive recruitment, top talent', 'Meta title within 60 character, meta keyword 15 words, meta description within 160 character', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.6-group.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/6group/', '6 Group', '2006', 'Altrincham, Cheshire'),
(101, 8, '<p><strong>BDS Connected Solutions, LLC.: </strong>Award-winning sales and marketing solutions provider connecting your brand with consumers everywhere</p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">What can strikingly make one business triumph over others, especially in fast-moving and changing business environments, is adaptability. Considering that, in retail, consumer preferences and behavior are changing really fast, for any brand nowadays, it\'s more important than ever to keep one step ahead. Enter BDS: a people-powered, digital-first, customer-obsessed business that has been creating fully integrated solutions since 1992.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">BDS is a people-powered, digital-first, customer-obsessed company that has been creating fully integrated solutions for over three decades. Founded in 1984 by three partners&mdash;Baker, Dean, and Sherwood&mdash;the company envisioned providing an exceptional working environment to its people while believing that this would eventually translate into exceptional care for its clients. The rest, as they say, is history.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">For generations, BDS has been organically growing through strategic acquisitions that have allowed the business to develop a sturdy suite of integrated solutions to meet the evolving needs of its clients. Strategic partnerships enabled it to grow its offerings and shape today\'s customer journey across multiple touchpoints. At its core, BDS values authenticity, agility, and achievement.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">One of its core values is to be true to one\'s self and others, sharing the whole picture, clearly setting expectations. It also supports being fast and flexible, embracing change, and acting bravely. Getting things done right, being goal-oriented, and relentless in pursuing a success outlook are equally subscribed to by BDS.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In the past years, BDS has grown and evolved but maintained the same culture. It remains people-powered and digitally first in customer obsession. With a bunch of award-winning industry experts and hard-working colleagues, BDS has never stopped delivering outstanding results for clients.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">BDS offers a full range of retail merchandising solutions designed to ensure that its brands maximize their shelf presence. The company delivers project and continuity-based retail merchandising solutions tailored toward each client\'s specific retail environment and sales cycles. One such innovation at BDS is IoTrace&trade;&mdash;a remote display management system that empowers brands to manage their interactive displays in real-time across the globe.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With IoTrace&trade;, brands can manage their displays from anywhere and at any time, with an added layer of security, by optimizing everything using data captured at the endpoint and driving sales and conversion while reducing downtime with remote monitoring. There are many advantages associated with IoTrace&trade;, which has changed the way brands interact with their customers and manage their retail presence.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\"><strong>Del Tanner, CEO</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">A seasoned industry expert with a proven track record of delivering cutting-edge sales and marketing solutions, Del Tanner has spent his career pushing the boundaries of innovation and excellence. As the founder of Channel Partners, a pioneering training and merchandising company acquired by BDS in 2006, Del\'s entrepreneurial spirit and vision have driven his success.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">As CEO, Del\'s mission is to empower clients with the most effective and impactful solutions, drawing on his extensive experience and expertise. With a passion for mentoring and coaching others, he shares his life lessons and insights to help others achieve their goals.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Outside of the office, Del\'s enthusiasm for life is evident in his diverse pursuits. A self-proclaimed jack-of-all-trades, he has dabbled in pizza making, scuba diving, and even speaking Japanese. When not working, you can find Del indulging in his favorite hobbies, including off-roading, snowmobiling, woodworking in his shop, or capturing stunning photography shots.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Born and raised in Arizona, Del is a proud Sun Devil alumna of Arizona State University, where he earned a degree in Finance. Among his greatest accomplishments are marrying his wonderful wife, being a devoted father to his three daughters, and becoming a proud grandfather.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">With his unique blend of business acumen, creativity, and passion for life, Del Tanner is an inspiring leader who embodies the spirit of innovation and entrepreneurship.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong>&ldquo;Our industry-leading experts never stop working to discover, design, and deploy custom buying solutions that empower brands to achieve and exceed their unique sales goals.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'bds-connected-solutions-llc-award-winning-sales-and-marketing-solutions-provider', '2025-03-11', 'us/visionaries-network-del-turnner-bdsconnected-solutions.webp', 2, 'profile', 'BDS Connected Solutions delivers award-winning sales and marketing strategies that connect your brand with consumers across every channel.', 'sales solutions, marketing agency, brand engagement, retail marketing, consumer connection, experiential marketing, digital strategy, field marketing, visionaries network, retail execution, merchandising, training services, marketing experts, sales support, shopper engagement', 'BDS Connected Solutions | Sales &amp; Marketing Experts', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.bdssolutions.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/bdsconnectedsolutions', 'BDS Connected Solutions, LLC ', '1984', 'Lake Forest, California'),
(102, 8, '<p><strong>DigitBridge </strong>gives you the tools you need for B2B, B2C, and B2B2C digital commerce operations</p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In today\'s digital age, the importance of effective operations management cannot be overstated. As the pace of technological innovation continues to accelerate, businesses of all sizes must adapt to stay ahead of the competition. For small and medium-sized businesses (SMBs), navigating the complexities of digital commerce can be a daunting task. However, with the right tools and strategies in place, SMBs can not only keep pace with the giants but also thrive in this rapidly changing landscape.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">At DigitBridge, the team understands the unique challenges faced by SMBs in today\'s digital marketplace. That\'s why they have developed powerful digital operations management systems designed specifically for small and medium-sized businesses. The company&rsquo;s solutions are designed to help SMBs streamline their operations, reduce errors, and increase efficiency, allowing them to focus on what they do best - delivering exceptional products and services to their customers.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">DigitBridge&rsquo;s partnership approach is about more than just software - it\'s about supporting growth, fostering innovation, and helping SMBs focus on what they do best. This is the heart of the company&rsquo;s mission - a commitment to ensure that every small and medium business it partners with has the tools to navigate and excel in the digital economy. The organization believes in working hard and being nice to people - as evidenced by the sign hanging in its office lobby. This work ethic and passion provide results for DigitBridge&rsquo;s customers, both in terms of the service they receive and their overall company success.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">DigitBridge is committed to making digital transformation a smooth and accessible journey for every business that partners with them. Their focus is on seamless integration, enabling their clients to work with technology that feels like a natural extension of their daily operations. DigitBridge holds itself accountable for not just providing the necessary tools, but also getting into the thick of it with its customers and sharing its expertise as demanded. Empowering every team member and customer is not just a goal - it\'s the way DigitBridge does business every day.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The trillion-dollar American Wholesale industry is rapidly evolving from its reliance on manual systems to embracing the digital world. Dominated by small and medium-sized businesses, the sector has struggled with the complexity and errors of using multiple systems and tools for everyday tasks.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Now, with e-commerce\'s rapid growth, it\'s clear that a modern approach is essential. That\'s why DigitBridge offers a streamlined Enterprise Resource Planning (ERP) solution to meet the modern demands of wholesale &amp; retail. DigitBridge&rsquo;s solution simplifies your varied systems into one platform, making it easier to manage sales, customers, inventory, supply chain, and more - all in real time with automation process tools.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">DigitBridge&rsquo;s ERP solution includes features such as Complete Omnichannel Operations, Inventory &amp; Catalog Management, Sales Order Management &amp; A/R Reconciliation, Automated Sales Forecasting &amp; Replenishment, Customer Relationship Management (CRM), Point of Sale (POS), Returns &amp; Refunds, Purchase Order &amp; Supply Chain Management, Manufacturing BOM &amp; WIP, Dropshipping Capabilities, Robust Data Analytics &amp; Real-Time Insights, and EDI Communications. With features designed for the nuances of dropshipping and B2B2C transactions, DigitBridge enables seamless data flow between wholesalers and retailers.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In addition to DigitBridge&rsquo;s ERP solution, it also offers a state-of-the-art Product Information Management (PIM+) system. The modern wholesaler does more than just manage a warehouse and fulfill orders - a huge amount of time is spent on omnichannel catalog management. Each sales channel presents its unique set of content demands, tech specifications, and media nuances. Staying on top of it is difficult, let alone keeping it all organized. DigitBridge&rsquo;s PIM+ system lets you accomplish everything at lightning speed using AI-powered features such as AI Assisted Content Creation, Digital Shelf Optimization, Channel Feed Management, Style/Product Master Feature, Visual Media Organization, Digital Sales Promotion Management, and Digital Channel Insights.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">By leveraging DigitBridge&rsquo;s ERP and PIM solutions, SMBs can streamline operations, reduce errors, and increase efficiency. DigitBridge&rsquo;s solutions are designed to help businesses thrive in the digital marketplace, providing them with the tools they need to compete on an equal footing with larger players. At DigitBridge, the team is committed to making digital transformation a smooth and accessible journey for every business that partners with us.<br><br><strong>Petersen Zhu, Founder</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Petersen Zhu, a seasoned entrepreneur with over 30 years of experience in the apparel industry, founded DigitBridge in response to the challenges faced by small to medium-sized businesses (SMBs) and wholesalers in navigating the digital commerce landscape. He recognized the need for a solution that would enable these businesses to operate efficiently and effectively across various sales channels.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Frustrated by the high cost and complexity of existing software solutions, Petersen teamed up with his partner and CTO, Bolan You, to develop a tailored solution specifically for SMBs in the consumer goods industry. In 2020, they started building DigitBridge, an affordable and holistic platform designed to help these businesses work from anywhere, do business everywhere, and connect with everyone.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">As DigitBridge continues to onboard new customers, Petersen is committed to helping these businesses unlock their full potential in the world of digital commerce.<br><br><strong>&ldquo;We eliminate the headache of complicated integrations and technical know-how. Our cloud-based platform dramatically minimizes the stresses of running a business, allowing you to focus on product development, customer care, and your bottom line.&rdquo;</strong></p>\r\n<div style=\"mso-element: para-border-div; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'digitbridge-gives-tools-for-b2b-b2c-b2b2c-digital-commerce-operations', '2025-03-11', 'us/visionaries-network-petersen-zhu-digitbridge-founder.webp', 3, 'profile', 'DigitBridge empowers businesses with digital tools to manage B2B, B2C, and B2B2C commerce operations seamlessly across channels.', 'digital commerce, B2B tools, B2C solutions, B2B2C platform, eCommerce, unified commerce, online sales, digital tools, visionaries network, business growth, digital platform, omni channel, commerce software, retail solutions, enterprise commerce', 'DigitBridge | Unified B2B, B2C &amp; B2B2C Commerce Tools', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://digitbridge.com/', 'linkedin.com/company/digitbridge', 'DigitBridge', '2020', 'Monrovia, California'),
(103, 8, '<p><strong>Exemplary Marketing </strong>is a Chicago-based social media marketing agency, delivering an worldwide outstanding marketing solution</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Innovation in augmented reality, virtual reality, and mixed reality can take the lead in changing the world of computers. The virtual and mixed realities tend to bring a tectonic shift on how we interlink, learn, and experience the surrounding environment.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Exemplary Marketing is a contemporary social media marketing agency that has its inception in Chicago and has since spanned the globe, representing a committed front in the provision of unsurpassed marketing solutions to businesses of all dimensions. Among the bouquet of extensive marketing services that this agency offers is Application Designs &amp; Development. By providing clients with guarantee-secured applications on every solution, its team of technical experts ensures it is secure, reliable, and efficient.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Exemplary Marketing values quality above all and strives for improvement in order to come up with solutions of world-class standards that help answer clients\' unique needs. Its team of experts works tirelessly to transform groundbreaking ideas into reality, ensuring that the business of its clients grows and thrives.<br><br><strong>&ldquo;We offer comprehensive solutions to various sizes of businesses around the globe.&rdquo;</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>AR/VR Software Development: A Specialization</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Exemplary Marketing is the top-rated AR/VR development company whose professionalism, experience, and expertise in developing visually breathtaking experiences using AR and VR software have no match. Its solutions are designed to help businesses drive ROI rampantly through better, immersive customer experiences.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The company has a highly experienced team that makes VR software development pioneers and offers services that are unmatched in the field. They develop tailored solutions for customers and work with many technologies, including HTC Vive, Oculus, Samsung Gear VR Hardware, and Google Daydream VR.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Exemplary Marketing AR/VR development services include:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">1. Custom VR Software Development: Exemplary Marketing works on applications designed to increase the efficiency of operations and interaction of systems with the user.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">2. Design and Development of VR Games: The company designs and develops high-definition VR games that immerse the player into realistic worlds.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">3. 3D Tourism: Exemplary develops photo-realistic geo-visualizations across environments while taking the user to places they would otherwise have to travel to see.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">4. Corporate Training: The organization provides specially designed employee training software that maximizes the effectiveness of the employee and ensures the realization of the business objectives.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Mixed Reality (MR) Software Development: A New Horizon</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Exemplary Marketing is also gradually becoming a forerunner in the field of MR software development companies. It focuses on using innovative web-based applications that ensure the creation of content, 3D models, and many more. Its MR software development facilitates :</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">1. Mixed Reality Software Development: Exemplary Marketing develops full-bodied MR solutions enabling content, 3D model creation, and more.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">2. Internet of Things Integration: Exemplary Marketing is retrofitting current AR, VR, and MR devices so they can interact with IoT-connected devices like cameras and sensors.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">3. 3D Data Visualization Platforms: The company created a platform that will allow the fast-tracking of data flow, enabling businesses to smoothly and seamlessly operate with the interpretation of big data.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">4. Computer Vision Software: The organization integrates computer vision software along with image analysis technologies to make sure of getting maximum performance while enhancing the workflow.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>E-commerce and Retail</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Exemplary Marketing AR/VR solutions in the e-commerce and retail space add a customer-friendly feature where every consumer gets the benefit of trying out any product virtually to get the shopping feel and quickly get converted into a paying customer. Its 3D enabling delivers a product view after every angle by the customers, where return decreases, and by turning up the returns, the customer rule level goes up.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Marketing and Advertising</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This is further used in marketing and advertising by making different campaigns more interesting and interactive for the viewers. Using augmented reality, Exemplary Marketing creates the displays that come into action, the product demonstration, and even the entire brand experience.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Industrial and Medical</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Exemplary Marketing AR/VR solutions showcase its features in the industrial and medical segments with enriched training programs and product demos and allow versatility in their operations. Images can be analyzed through its knowledge in the development of computer vision applications so as to refine the performance, thus making the workflow more accurate with reduced errors.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\"><strong>Malik Kurdi CEO &amp; Founder</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Malik Kurdi, as the esteemed CEO of Exemplary Marketing, has demonstrated exceptional skill in leading the company\'s App Development/Design department. He excels at developing and managing innovative lead-generating technologies that captivate new prospects and existing clients with engaging, educational, and problem-solving content. Additionally, he fosters brand awareness, drives inbound traffic, encourages product adoption, and collaborates with the internal marketing and public relations teams to achieve these goals.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">With both strong written and analytical abilities, Malik creates compelling mobile applications that effectively structure and optimize Exemplary Marketing\'s digital presence. He utilizes these skills to aggressively drive leads and engagement with the company\'s content.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Under his guidance, Malik maintains an exceptional standard for all app development/design projects, ensuring that they align with the company\'s brand, vision, values, and positioning attributes. He establishes effective benchmarks for measuring the impact of mobile application development and analyzes the effectiveness of technologies to maximize results.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">As a seasoned leader, Malik effectively manages and enhances Exemplary Marketing\'s digital presence, driving the tactical execution of the company\'s digital plans. With a solid understanding of mobile application development, a keen eye for detail, a creative mind, and flawless execution and organizational skills, Malik has earned a reputation for delivering high-quality results.</p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'exemplary-marketing-chicago-based-social-media-marketing-agency', '2025-03-11', 'us/visionaries-network-malik-kurdi-exemplary-marketing-founder.webp', 4, 'profile', 'Exemplary Marketing is a Chicago-based social media agency delivering outstanding global marketing solutions to elevate your brand online.', 'social media marketing, digital marketing, Chicago agency, visionaries networking, content creation, influencer marketing, online strategy, paid ads, SEO services, marketing experts, global marketing, media solutions, creative agency, social engagement, marketing campaigns', 'Exemplary Marketing | Social Media Agency in Chicago', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://exemplarymarketing.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/exemplary-marketing', 'Exemplary Marketing', '2014', 'Tinley park, Illlinois'),
(104, 8, '<p><strong>ISmile Technologies </strong>delivers automation-enabled Intelligent Solutions and Managed IT services</p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">ISmile Technologies is a trusted technology advisor and key implementation partner that delivers automation-enabled intelligent solutions and managed IT services to businesses worldwide. With a deep-rooted expertise in AI, robotics, data, and analytics, ISmile helps companies compete by adopting cutting-edge technologies. Its vision is to become the trusted technology advisor and key implementation partner for companies looking to adopt disruptive technologies, recognized by its clients for delivering excellence.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">ISmile Technologies\' mission is driven by its MILE model, which stands for Maximum Impact, Less Effort. It strives to maximize cloud excellence by identifying high-yield areas to apply high-yield methods and techniques, thereby accelerating business outcomes. Additionally, the company provides tried-and-tested packaged solutions to deliver faster, more effective, and cost-efficient results.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">ISmile Technologies&rsquo; primary mission is to ensure the satisfaction and happiness of its customers. It takes immense pride in the fact that nearly all of its clients are not only satisfied with its services but are also eager to recommend us to others. This level of trust and endorsement is a testament to its unwavering commitment to delivering exceptional value and service.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Integrity is at the core of ISmile Technologies&rsquo; operations. It believes that fostering an environment of trust, openness, and honesty is essential for building strong relationships, both internally among its team members and externally with its clients. By prioritizing these values, ISmile Technologies creates a workplace where everyone feels respected and valued, which in turn enhances collaboration and innovation.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">ISmile Technologies\' dedication to achieving results is reflected in the culture it has cultivated at ISmile Technologies. It emphasizes performance and accountability, encouraging its team to set ambitious goals and strive for excellence in every project. This results-driven approach not only benefits its clients but also drives its employees to reach their full potential. Moreover, the company recognizes the importance of continuous improvement and learning.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">ISmile Technologies actively supports its employees in their professional development by providing opportunities for growth and encouraging them to learn from both successes and challenges. This commitment to lifelong learning fosters a dynamic and adaptable workforce, ready to embrace new challenges and innovations in the ever-evolving tech landscape.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The company&rsquo;s end-to-end Solutions accelerate innovation and drive speed to market. ISmile Technologies\' team of experts has years of hands-on experience and implementation expertise, providing out-of-the-box solutions that are 100% customizable to meet business needs. Its Cloud Foundation/Enablement Solution provides a solid foundation for public or private cloud success. As a proud partner to top public cloud providers AWS, Microsoft Azure, and Google Cloud, the company offers a cloud governance model and core framework to ensure scalable and secure operations.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">ISmile Technologies believes in building trust, respect, and support among its clients, teammates, and partners. It takes on responsibility for its environment through environmentally compatible and resource-saving work. The company empowers organizations to be a force for good by defining core ESG metrics, tracking progress towards these goals, and fostering trust with key stakeholders through enhanced transparency.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">ISmile Technologies Cloud Services help businesses reduce costs, increase scalability, improve collaboration, and ensure flexibility and agility. Its clients have experienced increased productivity and new opportunities for innovation through its cloud services. The company&rsquo;s Cloud Management &amp; Optimization services ensure operational efficiency while minimizing costs and risks. It offers intelligent management of multi-cloud environments, higher uptime through automation, deployment into the cloud with near-zero downtime, and prioritizing workload management.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">ISmile Technologies is a trusted name in cloud management and optimization due to its ability to ensure operational efficiency while minimizing costs and risks. The company intelligently manages multi-cloud environments, attains higher uptime through automation, deploys into the cloud with near-zero downtime, and prioritizes workload management. By partnering with ISmile Technologies, organizations can leverage its expertise in automation-enabled intelligent solutions and managed IT services to drive business agility, enhance security, and achieve their goals.<br><br><strong>Deena Hasan, Chief Executive Officer</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Deena is a trusted advisor with experience across technology, strategy, and innovation. She has guided consumer-focused companies to new areas of growth, led many organizations through digital transformations, executed corporate strategy innovation projects, and advised C-level executives on people/process/technology changes.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong>&ldquo;Operating globally, our deep-rooted expertise helps businesses compete by extending the adoption of disruptive technologies such as AI, Robotics, Data, and Analytics.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'ismile-technologies-delivers-automation-enabled-intelligent-solutions-managed-it-services', '2025-03-11', 'us/visionaries-network-deena-hasan-ismile-technologies-logo.webp', 5, 'profile', 'ISmile Technologies delivers automation-enabled intelligent solutions and managed IT services to drive innovation and business growth.', 'managed IT services, automation, intelligent solutions, cloud services, cybersecurity, visionaries network, DevOps, digital transformation, IT consulting, infrastructure management, cloud automation, data analytics, IT outsourcing, enterprise IT, tech solutions', 'ISmile Technologies | Intelligent IT &amp; Automation Solutions', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://ismiletechnologies.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ismiletechnologies/', 'ISmile Technologies', '2011', 'Bolingbrook, Illinois'),
(105, 8, '<p><strong>itSynergy </strong>specializes in Tailored IT Services and solutions for&nbsp;Phoenix&nbsp;businesses</p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In today\'s fast-paced business environment, having a reliable and efficient IT infrastructure is crucial for success. At itSynergy, the team understands the importance of technology in achieving business goals and objectives. As a fully outsourced, supplemental, and project-based IT contract provider, itSynergy offers a range of services designed to meet the unique needs of small and mid-sized businesses.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">For over 20 years, itSynergy has been providing managed IT services and outsourced technology management to businesses in Phoenix and beyond. The company&rsquo;s team of experts has developed a proven approach to helping clients increase productivity, eliminate risks, and achieve their goals. They are committed to providing exceptional quality service, transparent pricing, and 24/7/365 support.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Why Choose itSynergy?</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Quality of Service Matters: itSynergy&rsquo;s team is composed of passionate and dedicated individuals who are committed to delivering exceptional quality service. It believes that its clients should experience tangible results, not just talk about them.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Fair and Transparent Pricing: </strong>itSynergy appreciates fair and transparent pricing as much as its clients do. It doesn&rsquo;t have hidden fees, and its clients never get a bill they didn\'t agree to.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>24/7/365 Support: </strong>itSynergy&rsquo;s IT infrastructure doesn\'t take breaks or vacations, and neither does its support. It keeps a close eye on monitoring its clients\' IT around the clock and stays available whenever they\'re needed.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Proactive Approach:</strong> The organization proactively eliminates risks before they arise by performing 24/7/365 Remote Monitoring and Maintenance (RMM). This helps prevent problems from happening in the first place.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>The itSynergy Mindset</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">At itSynergy, the team believes that when technology works as it should, it supports and enhances an organization\'s ability to accomplish its goals and objectives. It partners with its clients to deliver highly-available, secure, and flexible IT systems that meet their unique needs.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">itSynergy&rsquo;s managed IT plans are designed to maximize productivity and eliminate bottlenecks in daily operations. They understand that each business has its unique DNA, and its IT support is tailored to meet those specific needs.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The company is committed to helping its clients use technology to grow their business. When you succeed, itSynergy succeeds.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>itSynergy IT Values</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Success = Productivity:</strong> itSynergy&rsquo;s priority is to optimize your technology infrastructure and eliminate bottlenecks in your daily operations to keep your productivity uninterrupted.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Your Vision is Unique:</strong> The company starts by understanding your organization on a granular level before making any plans.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>When You Grow, itSynergy Grows:</strong> If itSynergy is not helping your business use technology to grow, they not doing their jobs.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>A Proactive IT Solution is the Only IT Solution:</strong> The organization constantly watches your IT like a hawk to anticipate new requirements, risk factors, and opportunities to avoid costly downtime.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Expert IT Consulting Services</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In the ever-evolving world of technology, strategic IT guidance is crucial for business success. itSynergy offers expert IT consulting services designed to empower your business with the right technological tools and strategies. Its approach focuses on understanding your business goals and aligning them with innovative IT solutions to drive growth, efficiency, and competitive advantage.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">itSynergy&rsquo;s customized IT roadmaps ensure that your technology investments deliver maximum value. Its consultants help you optimize your current IT infrastructure and identify opportunities for innovation, ensuring you stay ahead of technological advancements.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Why Partner with itSynergy?</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Deep Industry Knowledge:</strong> itSynergy&rsquo;s team brings extensive experience and deep industry knowledge, allowing them to provide insights and solutions that are both practical and forward-thinking.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Proactive Approach:</strong> The company proactively addresses IT challenges, helping you avoid potential pitfalls and capitalize on opportunities.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Focus on Business Impact:</strong> The organization&rsquo;s consulting services are not just about technology; they\'re about the impact on your business. They focus on solutions that drive efficiency, productivity, and growth.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Transform Your Business with itSynergy\'s Consulting Expertise</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Enhance Business Processes:</strong> Leverage itSynergy&rsquo;s expertise to enhance your business processes through technology.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Strategic IT Investments:</strong> Make informed IT investments that support your long-term business goals.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Continuous Improvement and Adaptation:</strong> Benefit from itSynergy&rsquo;s commitment to continuous improvement and adaptation in the face of rapidly changing technology landscapes.<br><br><strong>Michael W. Cocanower, Founder and President</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Michael W. Cocanower is the founder and president of itSynergy. Since its inception in 1997, Phoenix-based itSynergy has been the leading IT Consulting organization empowering small and mid-market businesses with strategic information technology (IT) guidance, and comprehensive IT services solutions that provide distinct competitive advantages.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong>&ldquo;Our team is composed of some of the most passionate and dedicated individuals in the industry.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'itsynergy-specializes-tailored-it-services-and-solutions-forphoenixbusinesses', '2025-03-11', 'us/visionaries-network-michael-cocanower-itsynergy-founder.webp', 6, 'profile', 'itSynergy specializes in tailored IT services and solutions for Phoenix businesses, delivering secure and scalable technology support.', 'IT services, Phoenix IT, managed IT, cybersecurity, cloud solutions, IT support, tech services, IT consulting, network support, business IT, data security, visionaries network, IT outsourcing, IT management, custom IT solutions', 'itSynergy | Tailored IT Services for Phoenix Businesses', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://itsynergy.com/', 'linkedin.com/company/itsynergy', 'itSynergy', '1997', 'Phoenix, AZ');
