(106, 8, '<p><strong>MOST Programming, Inc.</strong> harnesses the power of data and automation to improve workplace efficiency, increase business agility</p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Data in this fast and constantly digitally changing era has risen as the most important asset for enterprises, and there is great potential for those who understand and realize the importance of this asset. Enterprises understand that the difference this data-driven decision-making strategy can bring gives them a competitive edge and fuels them in pursuing this resource toward refining operations and steering strategic choices. MOST Programming, Inc., a certified Women\'s Business Enterprise National Council and Veterans Affairs, VET-certified, is proud to be in the leadership of this revolution of software development.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">MOST Programming aims to establish long-term partnerships rather than create relationships where one is a vendor and the other is a purchaser who is there only for the short term. MOST Programming works with a vision to aid businesses in tackling challenges they might face in an ever-changing technical world. MOST Programming assures that organizations are furthered in making their data significantly more beneficial for them to achieve their goals and strategic purposes with a trusted partnership.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">MOST Programming is founded on the basic belief that is central to their philosophy: \"If it can be measured, it can be managed.\" This is at the core of their software development and data analytics approach. They have a professional team that can build investment decision analytic platforms and develop complex interactive web-based tools. ALL these tools aim to automate and improve targeted areas in the business to help clients track performance and improve it along multiple dimensions.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Advanced data analytics offered further by MOST Programming allows for complete measurement capabilities from customer acquisition to return on investment, payroll, and operational efficiency. MOST Programming lets the customers make sense of complex data through intuitive and visually interesting dashboards.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">MOST Programming also assures that through simplified complicated analytics and automatic reporting, it can guarantee that businesses make speedy decisions. Their data visualization tools, which may embed Power BI or custom-coded solutions, yield intelligent charts and graphs, thus enabling informed decision-making. These interactive and full-of-insight visualizations play a critical role in formulating business strategies and making operational enhancements.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Automation and optimization process development is a very important area of expertise in MOST Programming. The way that this company is brilliant in how it streamlines business operations by automating repetitive activities and integrating workflows fluidly is what saves time and cost while boosting productivity and enhancing customer experience. MOST Programming optimizes those processes to make businesses productive and effective in handling core business expansion and innovation.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">MOST Programming is a company that offers data analytics and automation services. It is amongst the prime organizations with a custom-based software need. MOST Programming handles the creation of custom solutions to suit the unique requirements of organizations. The developers at MOST Programming are well experienced in implementing advanced solutions to interface and interact with the digital infrastructure put in place effectively. MOST Programming can provide this support for clients either to upgrade their existing systems or in full package their respective custom-based support. By guaranteeing that every delivered solution matches the operational requirements and strategic objectives of the business, they ensure high-quality and customized software.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Core values drive each and every aspect of the company\'s approach to business at MOST Programming. The dedicated team goes the extra mile to serve human capital and wide-ranging clientele, keeps on learning and improving constantly with new technologies, and gives back to society through volunteering and investment. MOST Programming believes in making informed business decisions because as they say, knowledge is power. MOST Programming has a mission to create positive change in the business world by fostering a culture of learning and community engagement.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The \"turning data into gold\" slogan of MOST Programming conveys their relenting effort and commitment that, by using data analytics, visualization, and automation, one can deliver valuable insights that spell out the success in any business. Their commitment to innovation with transparency makes them a trusted and lean partner for all their clients. MOST Programming enables businesses to turn their data into usable intelligence to realize their goals and sustain competitive advantage in the digital age.<br><br><strong>Wayne Schell, Co-founder</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Wayne Schell is driven by a passion for harnessing technology to drive operational excellence and customer-centric solutions, ultimately creating a competitive edge in target market niches.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; tab-stops: 130.5pt;\" align=\"center\"><strong>&ldquo;We develop business-driven solutions through interactive web applications and custom-built software, empowering its customers to achieve their goals with greater ease and precision.&rdquo;</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"tab-stops: 130.5pt;\">&nbsp;</p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'most-programming-inc--harnesses-the-power-of-data-and-automation', '2025-03-11', 'us/vsionaries-network-most-programming-wayne-schell-cofounder.webp', 7, 'profile', 'MOST Programming, Inc. leverages data and automation to boost workplace efficiency, enhance agility, and drive smarter business operations.', 'data automation, business agility, workplace efficiency, process automation, data solutions, IT services, digital transformation, custom software, visionaries network, tech consulting, workflow optimization, enterprise solutions, data management, agile business, software development', 'MOST Programming, Inc. leverages data and automation to boost workplace efficiency, enhance agility, and drive smarter business operations.', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://most-us.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/most_us/', 'MOST Programming, Inc.', '2016', 'Denver, Colorado'),
(107, 8, '<p><strong>OmniAccess:</strong> Premium digital solutions for the maritime industry including Cybersecurity, IoT/ OT, Connectivity, Cloud &amp; IT, Network</p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The foundation of OmniAccess is built upon three core values: Innovate, Simplify, and Commit. These principles have been instrumental in shaping the company&rsquo;s mission to transform the landscape of maritime connectivity and communication. By embracing innovation, they have consistently sought out new ways to enhance their offerings, ensuring that they remain at the cutting edge of technology.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The commitment to simplification has allowed them to streamline processes and make complex solutions more accessible to their clients. Meanwhile, their unwavering dedication to their commitments has fostered trust and reliability, essential components in building long-lasting relationships with customers.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>As the years have progressed, OmniAccess has solidified its position as a formidable leader in the maritime industry. Their reputation is built on a foundation of innovative thinking and a series of remarkable achievements that have set them apart from competitors.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The company&rsquo;s proactive approach has enabled it to not only adopt emerging technologies but also to anticipate industry trends, allowing it to seize opportunities that enhance its service offerings. This forward-thinking mindset has empowered them to consistently exceed client expectations, establishing a benchmark for excellence in maritime digital solutions.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Looking ahead, OmniAccess is driven by a clear vision: to advance the future of maritime digital solutions. Their primary objective is to create possibilities everywhere, fostering an environment of innovation that enhances the way customers connect and communicate. By placing customers at the heart of their operations, they are committed to delivering exceptional solutions that prioritize not only performance but also security and privacy. This customer-centric approach ensures that every solution is tailored to meet the unique needs of their clients, reinforcing their dedication to providing top-notch services that empower users in the maritime sector.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">They at OmniAccess manage a very diverse fleet, from over 600 superyachts and more than 100 boutique cruise ships to special expedition vessels like research vessels and USVs. Their international team works in line with the single goal of supporting every step in their clients\' maritime journey, which is delivered through the supply of cutting-edge communications and technology solutions at the very edge of technology.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Their passion and commitment have kept them on the path to innovation and the creation of state-of-the-art products and services that make multiple technologies integrate in perfect harmony to provide seamless connectivity and communication. There is a fully certified 24/7 Security Operations Center monitoring the security for their clients at all times, along with expert-driven consultancy and training programs.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Their connectivity plans under the nextGen Fusion umbrella give every vessel tailored solutions, bridging the best in advanced technology that carriers like Starlink, OneWeb, O3b mPower, GEO connectivity, and 4G/5G mobile data have to offer. Completely managed and supported by their 24/7 Technical Support Center, their plans entail guaranteed uptime, seamless carrier integration, and remote access from wherever they cruise.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">NextGen Fusion is their package for integrating different WANs against different applications. Be it critical conference calls, streaming of high-definition content, or high-frequency trading, the best available connection for any client is always guaranteed. Seamlessly switch between GSO/VSAT, LEO/Non-GEO, and 4G/5G to leverage available networks and enhance the on board experience.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The OmniAccess UNITY platform represents a significant advancement in the realm of maritime digital solutions, specifically engineered to ensure that users can maintain the most current and effective connectivity options available. In an industry where reliable communication and data transfer are paramount, UNITY provides a comprehensive solution that streamlines access to multiple Wide Area Networks (WANs) through a singular, cohesive stream.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This innovative approach allows users to manage all their connectivity needs from a single, intuitive interface, simplifying the complexities often associated with maritime communications. By consolidating various WANs into one platform, UNITY empowers users to fully leverage the advantages of their diverse connections. This means that whether they are utilizing satellite, cellular, or other forms of connectivity, they can tailor their network usage to meet specific operational requirements.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">For instance, a vessel may need high-speed internet for video conferencing while simultaneously requiring a more stable connection for critical navigation systems. UNITY facilitates this by intelligently managing the different technologies at play, ensuring that each application receives the optimal network performance it demands. One of the standout features of the UNITY platform is its ability to automatically select the most suitable network for each application in real-time.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This dynamic selection process is crucial in maritime environments, where conditions can change rapidly and the availability of certain networks may fluctuate. By continuously monitoring network performance and application requirements, UNITY can redirect traffic as needed, ensuring that users experience minimal disruption and maximum efficiency. This capability not only enhances operational effectiveness but also contributes to improved safety and decision-making on board.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\"><strong>Carlos Carbajal, CEO at OmniAccess</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">From our roots as a small IT support team in Palma de Mallorca, we\'ve become the leading provider of premium digital solutions in the maritime industry.</p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'omniaccess-premium-digital-solutions-for-maritime-industry-cybersecurity-iot-ot', '2025-03-11', 'us/visionaries-network-carlos-carbojal-ceo-omniaccess.webp', 8, 'profile', 'OmniAccess delivers premium digital solutions for the maritime industry, including cybersecurity, IoT/OT, connectivity, cloud, and IT network services.', 'maritime IT, cybersecurity, maritime connectivity, IoT, OT solutions, cloud services, vessel IT, satellite internet, network security, maritime technology, digital transformation, visionaries network, marine cloud, maritime automation, IT support', 'OmniAccess | Digital Solutions for the Maritime Industry', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.omniaccess.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/omniaccess/', 'OmniAccess', '2007', 'Palma, Illes balears'),
(108, 8, '<p><strong>Sales Geek is on a mission to change the way the world perceives sales</strong></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Sales Geek was founded to change the world, it offers part-time interim Sales Directors and trainers to small businesses that might ordinarily be priced out of the market for top-level talent. The company has been successful sales leaders, Directors, and Business Owners so they understand the commercial pressures of running a team or business. With over 800 years of sales leadership experience, Sales Geek has developed thousands of sales people across the UK and beyond.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Part of changing the way the world perceives sales is changing the way sales training is &ldquo;done&rdquo;. Sales Geek has a unique hybrid model where they can work with your Sales teams, face to face, online, and via their free-to-use app. They are also the only sales training and consultancy company to have a dedicated app with hundreds of sales training videos and podcasts that can be accessed by your team anytime anywhere.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Outsourced Sales Director</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Driving revenue growth for your business without breaking the P&amp;L Hiring a sales director is a big deal for any company. If you are a small or medium-sized business, it is critical that you get it right. A Sales Director should become the driving force in your business for years to come. However, there are some formidable challenges in the hiring process. A Sales Director&rsquo;s salary can be prohibitive, particularly if you want the very best sales leaders with significant experience and a great track record in sales growth.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In sales, the cream almost always rises to the top and in return, the very best in the sales profession get heavily rewarded. Usually, the most talented sales professionals end up in large corporate organizations, typically being paid a salary beyond the reach of most businesses. It seems the best sales talent is almost always out of reach. But not any longer! Your Sales Director from Sales Geek provides your business with top-level sales leadership on an interim basis that won&rsquo;t break your P&amp;L.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The work they do will transform your sales operations and the people within and behind it. Through their flexible &ndash; &lsquo;consume what you need&rsquo; &ndash; model, you will have access to a leading sales director/business leader from within their field and access to all the Geeks in the background who are all available to support you and your business in various disciplines, from people training to e-Commerce, Marketing, Strategy, Process and Development and beyond.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">For most businesses that usually means 1-3 days per month. For others, Sales Geek could be working with you once a week or more. A typical contract length is 6-12 months but they will be in your corner for as long as it takes for you to hire that full-time sales leader that you can afford and is the perfect fit for your business in the long term.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Want to get more from your sales training? Use sales training from Sales Geek</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Sales Geek are well known in the industry for the quality of their sales training and they have won many awards over the years. All their sales training is endorsed by the Institute of Sales Professionals. The company wants to EMPOWER your sales team to grow your business. They give them sales training that delivers the skill sets they need to create and nurture long-lasting relationships with your customers.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">When it comes to Sales Training most people have 2 crucial questions:</p>\r\n<ol style=\"margin-top: 0cm;\" start=\"1\" type=\"1\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\">Will the sales training distract us from our core function of actually selling our product/service?</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\">How do I know if the sales training is going to be any good?</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Don&rsquo;t worry. They have a cunning Geeky plan. The way they work with all their training and the reason that their learning points gain real traction in people&rsquo;s minds is that they work with real-life situations, real time issues, and real time deals. Experience is the greatest teacher, so why fight it? All their sales training is also bespoke to your needs and happens around the work your team is currently involved in.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">How do I know if the sales training is going to be any good? It&rsquo;s a reasonable question. You need a return on your investment. Maybe your fingers have been burned before? Hopefully, they can reassure you.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">All their training is endorsed by the Institute of Sales Professionals (ISP) a Government-backed professional body dedicated to elevating the sales profession globally. That means they have to meet rigorous standards with the sales training they provide and the materials they use. It also means they can issue CPD points for all the sales training you and your teams undertake.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Sales Consultants in the UK that Deliver Results</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Sales Consultancy for your business delivering sales strategy, transformation, and operations. The importance of ensuring your &lsquo;Sales Enablement&rsquo; strategy is robust, operationally fit for purpose, and aligned with your business and go-to-market strategies is critical to the success of your company.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Sales Geek can provide you with a proven Sales Consultant who will be the driving force in sales for your business for as long as you need them. Your business can tap into the years of experience their Sales Consultants have from across a vast array of industries. Their Sales Consultants will help you ensure that your systems, structures, people, and sales processes are the best they can be for your business model.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Having access to a team of experienced, highly trained, and distinguished leaders at your fingertips gives your business a competitive edge and their Sales Consultants offer a flexible &ndash; &lsquo;consume what you need&rsquo; &ndash; model where you will have access to a leading Sales Operations Director/ Business Leader and access to all the Geeks in the background who are all available to support you and your business in various disciplines: from people training to e-Commerce; Marketing, Strategy, Process and Development and beyond.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">For most businesses that usually means 1-3 days of Sales Consultant support per month. For others, their Sales Consultants could be working with you once a week or more. A typical contract length is 6-12 months and their Sales Consultant fees start at &pound;495+VAT per month.<br><br><strong>Richard Few, Founder</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Richard founded Sales Geek with a bold vision to revolutionize the way sales is perceived and make top-notch sales leadership accessible to all, regardless of company size. As the driving force behind the Geeky team, he has overseen the company\'s growth and success, earning numerous accolades for their innovative work. When not leading the charge, Richard can be found spending quality time with his loved ones, Reggie the loyal bulldog, and enjoying the thrill of a rugby match (which may occasionally involve a bit of conversion practice on the pitch!).</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; tab-stops: 156.75pt;\" align=\"center\"><strong>&ldquo;We are inspired by supporting our ambitious clients to grow and smash their goals.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'sales-geek-is-on-a-mission-to-change-the-way-the-world-perceives-sales', '2025-03-11', 'us/visionaries-network-richard-few-founder-sales-geek.webp', 9, 'profile', 'Sales Geek is on a mission to revolutionize how the world views sales through innovative training, strategy, and expert support.', 'sales training, sales consultancy, sales strategy, visionaries network, sales coaching, sales leadership, sales support, sales experts, sales growth, sales transformation, sales performance, sales innovation, remote sales, sales development, sales mindset', 'Sales Geek | Redefining Sales for the Modern World', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://www.salesgeek.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/sales-geek/', 'Sales Geek', '2017', 'Blackburn, Lancashire'),
(109, 8, '<p><strong>Zilliant puts pricing at the heart of your business, transforming how you use data to price and sell</strong></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In today\'s fast-paced business landscape, companies are constantly seeking ways to optimize their pricing strategies and maximize revenue. One company that has emerged as a leader in this space is Zilliant, which offers a suite of pricing solutions designed to help businesses manage the entire pricing lifecycle. With its innovative cloud-native software and passion for customer success, Zilliant has established itself as a trusted partner for businesses seeking to drive growth and profitability.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Succeeding with Zilliant</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">At Zilliant, customer success is paramount. The company takes the time to understand its customers\' unique needs and invests in their success, delivering financial and operational benefits that drive business growth. This customer-centric approach has enabled Zilliant to build a loyal following of satisfied clients who have achieved significant returns on investment.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Evolving Pricing Strategies</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Zilliant\'s pricing solutions are designed to help businesses put pricing at the heart of their operations. By leveraging data science-driven insights and advanced analytics, companies can identify the most significant sources of margin and revenue leakage, and develop more effective pricing and sales strategies. This approach enables businesses to maximize revenue and profitability, while also improving customer satisfaction and loyalty.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Streamlining Price Management</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">One of the key challenges faced by businesses is managing complex pricing processes, which often involve cumbersome spreadsheets and manual data processing. Zilliant\'s price management software offers a modern alternative, providing a flexible, scalable platform for managing all types of prices, including list, matrix, negotiated, and agreements. With its intuitive interface and advanced data processing capabilities, Zilliant\'s software makes it easy to manage prices, reduce errors, and increase efficiency.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Revenue Intelligence</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Zilliant\'s revenue intelligence solutions are designed to help businesses generate customer-specific actions from their data. By analyzing customer behavior and preferences, companies can identify opportunities to increase revenue and profitability. This includes identifying at-risk customers, recommending products to drive growth, and prioritizing sales efforts to maximize return on investment.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Best-in-Class Data Science</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">At the heart of Zilliant\'s pricing solutions is its advanced data science capabilities. The company\'s data scientists have developed a range of algorithms and models that can be tailored to specific business needs. These capabilities enable businesses to capitalize on the power of artificial intelligence and machine learning, driving revenue growth and profitability.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>eCommerce Solutions</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In today\'s digital age, eCommerce is a critical component of many businesses\' sales strategies. Zilliant\'s eCommerce solutions are designed to help companies optimize their online pricing strategies, deliver personalized product recommendations, and drive revenue growth. By leveraging advanced data science and machine learning algorithms, Zilliant\'s eCommerce solutions can help businesses increase average order value, reduce cart abandonment rates, and improve customer satisfaction.<br><br><strong>Pascal Yammine, Chief Executive Officer</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\">Pascal joined Zilliant as CEO in 2022. He brings more than 20 years of experience in executive roles within enterprise software and business consulting, with proven leadership in developing strategic visions, developing new products and programs that can be scaled globally, and leading organizations through digital transformations.<br><br>Most recently, Pascal was the Senior Vice President &amp; General Manager of Salesforce Revenue Cloud, where he led product direction, marketing, go-to-market, and operations. In that role, Pascal scaled the Salesforce CPQ business into the next $1B cloud.&nbsp;He previously held various leadership roles in the Salesforce Customer Success Group, numerous senior consulting roles, and executive roles in media and communications industries, ran his own successful consulting firm and served as chief information officer of a communication service provider.<br><br>Pascal earned a Bachelor of Arts and master&rsquo;s degree in Organizational Communication from the University of Illinois Urbana-Champaign.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong>&ldquo;Our data science, cloud-native software, and passion for customer success deliver the highest ROI, fastest time to value, and highest customer satisfaction.&rdquo;</strong></p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'zilliant-puts-pricing-at-heart-of-your-business-transforming-use-data-to-price-and-sell', '2025-03-11', 'us/visionaries-network-pascal-yammine-ceo-zilliant.webp', 10, 'profile', 'Zilliant transforms pricing with data-driven solutions that optimize how businesses price and sell for smarter revenue growth.', 'pricing software, sales optimization, data-driven pricing, visionaries network, price management, AI pricing, B2B pricing, pricing analytics, price optimization, dynamic pricing, sales strategy, pricing intelligence, pricing automation, business insights, pricing solutions', 'Zilliant | Data-Driven Pricing &amp; Sales Optimization', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://zilliant.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/zilliant/', 'Zilliant', '2023', 'Austin, TX'),
(110, 12, '<p><strong>Helping You Grow Your Money for Life: Plum&rsquo;s Smart Way to Save and Invest</strong></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Managing money doesn&rsquo;t have to be overwhelming. Whether you&rsquo;re saving for a rainy day, planning a dream holiday, or investing in your future, progress begins with small, consistent steps. And Plum is here to make every one of those steps count.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Plum is a smart money app built to help people take control of their finances through automation, intelligent saving tools, and secure investment options. It&rsquo;s not just a budgeting app&mdash;it&rsquo;s a financial companion designed to help you build wealth over time, with less effort and more confidence.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In a world where personal finance can feel complex or intimidating, Plum brings clarity, simplicity, and even a little humour to the table.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>The Power of Starting Small</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Many people believe that serious financial progress requires large sums or complicated strategies. But the truth is, meaningful change often starts small&mdash;a few pounds saved here, a minor habit changed there.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">That&rsquo;s the idea behind Plum. A single pound invested today can grow into something far bigger tomorrow. And with Plum&rsquo;s automation tools, this happens quietly in the background, without you needing to lift a finger.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">From rounding up your purchases to automatically setting aside small amounts based on your spending patterns, Plum helps you form better money habits&mdash;effortlessly.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>From Friendly Bet to Fintech Innovation: The Plum Story</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Back in 2014, two friends from Cyprus&mdash;Victor and Alex&mdash;made a friendly bet: who could save more money? While Victor followed the standard advice (budgeting, transferring money manually to savings), Alex took a different approach. He built an algorithm to do it for him. Unsurprisingly, the algorithm won.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This sparked a bigger idea. Why is managing money still so reliant on willpower and spreadsheets? Why not automate the entire process and make it smarter?</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">In 2016, Plum was officially launched to bring this vision to life. Today, Plum serves over 2 million users, with offices in London, Athens, and Nicosia. Voted the Best Personal Finance App in 2023, Plum is continuing its mission to make money management easy, secure, and empowering.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>How Plum Works: Four Simple Steps</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Getting started with Plum is quick and straightforward. In just a few minutes, you can begin your journey toward smarter money habits:</p>\r\n<ol style=\"margin-top: 0cm;\" start=\"1\" type=\"1\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><strong>Download the App</strong><br>The Plum app is available for free and easy to set up on iOS or Android.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><strong>Connect Your Bank</strong><br>Securely link your bank account so Plum can analyse your income and spending patterns.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><strong>Pick Your Money Moves</strong><br>Choose how you want to save or invest&mdash;automate deposits, invest in funds, or stash cash in high-interest &ldquo;Pockets.&rdquo;</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><strong>Watch It Grow</strong><br>Track your progress, adjust your goals, and celebrate your milestones along the way.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Whether you&rsquo;re a complete beginner or already confident with your finances, Plum offers a simple and effective way to take control.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Smart Features That Make a Big Difference</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Plum offers a suite of tools that make it more than just a digital piggy bank. These include:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0cm;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l4 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><strong>Auto Savers</strong>: Automatically set aside money based on what you can afford.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l4 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><strong>Round-Ups</strong>: Save your spare change from everyday purchases.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l4 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><strong>Rainy Day Rule</strong>: Trigger savings when the weather turns gloomy.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l4 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><strong>52-Week Challenge</strong>: A proven method to save over &pound;1,000 in a year.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l4 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><strong>Investment Portfolios</strong>: Choose from a curated selection of funds for long-term growth.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l4 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><strong>Cash ISA</strong>: Earn up to 4.85% AER (variable) tax-free, and keep your savings growing.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">These tools are designed to help you form better money habits without thinking about it. Over time, small savings build up, and automated investments put your money to work for the future.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Cash ISAs: Your Tax-Free Savings Powerhouse</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">One of Plum&rsquo;s standout products is the <strong>Cash ISA</strong>, which currently offers up to <strong>4.85% AER (variable)</strong> for new customers meeting certain conditions. This includes a 1.56% bonus rate for savings left untouched for 12 months.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">You can:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0cm;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l2 level1 lfo3; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\">Open a new Cash ISA with just &pound;1.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l2 level1 lfo3; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\">Transfer an existing ISA to Plum.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l2 level1 lfo3; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\">Save up to &pound;20,000 each tax year, tax-free.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The FSCS protects eligible deposits up to &pound;85,000 per person, per bank, providing peace of mind that your savings are secure.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Investing with Plum: Grow Your Wealth Confidently</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">If you&rsquo;re ready to move beyond saving, Plum makes investing accessible with its Stocks &amp; Shares ISA. You can invest up to &pound;20,000 annually into diversified portfolios that suit your risk appetite.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">All investments carry risk, and Plum is clear about this. Market ups and downs mean you could get back less than you invested. But over the long term, investing can offer greater growth potential than keeping cash in a savings account.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Plum&rsquo;s approach to investing is transparent and educational, with useful insights to help users make informed decisions without needing to be financial experts.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Your Money, Protected and Regulated</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Plum may not be a bank, but it follows strict regulations to protect your funds. Depending on the product, your money is held with trusted partners like Citibank, Lloyds Bank, Investec, and BlackRock.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Here&rsquo;s how protection varies:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0cm;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l1 level1 lfo4; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><strong>Cash ISAs and Easy Access Pockets</strong>: FSCS protected up to &pound;85,000.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l1 level1 lfo4; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><strong>Primary Pockets (E-Money)</strong>: Safeguarded under FCA rules, but not FSCS-protected.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l1 level1 lfo4; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><strong>Investments</strong>: Held via Alpaca (SIPC protected up to $500,000 in the U.S.).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Security measures include bank-grade encryption and advanced fraud detection systems. You can rest easy knowing your money is in safe hands.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Brits and Their Funny Relationship With Money</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Let&rsquo;s face it, money can be an awkward topic&mdash;especially in the UK. Research shows that UK households have around &pound;300 billion sitting in non-interest-bearing accounts. That could mean &pound;15 billion lost in interest in just one year!</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Plum believes it&rsquo;s time to take money seriously&mdash;but not too seriously. That&rsquo;s why they teamed up with comedian Mark Simmons to create a joke book that makes personal finance more approachable.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">From punchlines to Plum Points, this light-hearted approach helps users open up about money and start making better choices.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Why Plum Stands Out</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Unlike traditional banks or other money apps, Plum combines smart automation, humour, and transparent financial tools to create a user-friendly experience. It&rsquo;s not just about saving or investing&mdash;it&rsquo;s about forming sustainable habits that last a lifetime.</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0cm;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo5; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><strong>Free to start</strong> with premium features available.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo5; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><strong>Customisable goals</strong> to match your lifestyle.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo5; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><strong>Clear risk disclosures</strong> to help you make informed choices.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo5; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><strong>Award-winning design</strong> and user experience.</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo5; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><strong>Over 2 million users</strong> and growing fast.<br><br></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\"><strong>Victor Trokoudes, Co-founder &amp; CEO</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\"><em>&ldquo;Whether you&rsquo;re at the start of your money journey or consider yourself a pro, Plum&rsquo;s here to help &ndash; from the pennies right up to the pounds.&rdquo;</em><br><br>&ldquo;We&rsquo;re just like any other savings provider, except we&rsquo;re not. We help make saving a habit, not a chore.&rdquo;</p>', 'VisionariesNetwork Team', 'helping-you-grow-your-money-for-life-plums-smart-way-to-save-and-invest', '2025-06-17', 'us/visionaries-network-victor-trokoudes-co-founder-ceo-plum-cover.webp', 1, 'cover', 'Discover Plumâ€™s intelligent approach to saving and investing. From automated budgeting to smart investments, Plum helps you grow your money for life with ease and confidence.', 'Plum app, smart saving, automated investing, money management, visionaries network, personal finance tools, investment app, save and invest, financial planning, Plum finance', 'Grow Your Money for Life with Plum | Smart Saving &amp; Investing', NULL, 1, 'no', 'https://withplum.com/about', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/plum-fintech/', 'Plum', '2016 ', 'London, England ');
